UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done $N, I will be sure to give these to the Arch Druid himself when he has need of them. Meanwhile, please accept this as a token of the Cenarion Circle\'s appreciation.$B$BOur need for morrowgrain, for now, is constant; if you wish to continue aiding us, then please return when you have cultivated more of it.' WHERE `entry`=3785;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done $N, I will be sure to give these to the Arch Druid himself when he has need of them. Meanwhile, please accept this as a token of the Cenarion Circle\'s appreciation.$B$BOur need for morrowgrain, for now, is constant; if you wish to continue aiding us, then please return when you have cultivated more of it.' WHERE `entry`=3786;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you for coming, weary traveler!  Allow me to introduce myself - I am Quintis Jonespyre, druid and humble servant of Malfurion and the Cenarion Circle. My colleagues (General Shandris Feathermoon and the Protectorate - mayhap you\'ve heard of us) and I wanted to talk with you about the work you are doing for Fandral Staghelm in Darnassus.$B$BBefore we get much further, I\'d like to ask that our discussion stay between just us. If you have no problem with this, then we may proceed.' WHERE `entry`=3787;
