UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Use Rexxar\'s Battle Horn at the Altar of Goc, then kill Goc. Return to Rexxar at Thunderlord Village in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains when this is done.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='The battle was hard and you fought well, $N. I am honored to have stood by your side in the battle against Goc. I am thankful beyond words.$B$BThe Mok\'Nathal should know of these great defeats, but I am not ready to face them yet. I know my father\'s mind, and I know my heart. There is still much I can learn and do to become stronger, to show to him that I am his true son.' WHERE `entry`=10742;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Kurdran listens to your report.>$B$BThat is good news, indeed! Mere days ago, I wouldn\'t have dreamt that we could break the Legion\'s siege on the stronghold.$B$BNot only have you halted their offensive, but you\'ve broken the back of their war machine as well! You have the gratitude of the Wildhammer clan for your valor, $N.' WHERE `entry`=10744;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The overlord listens to your report.>$B$BExcellent news! Holding the line against the Legion\'s infernals was taking too many resources. Not that I expected my men to break, but they were greatly strained.$B$BYou have proven your worth to the Horde this day. The Kor\'kron guard would be honored to fight by your side anytime.' WHERE `entry`=10745;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Samia Inkling has asked you to use the Blackwhelp Net to capture 10 Wyrmcult Blackwhelps. Return them to her at Evergrove in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh my goodness, these are more than I\'d hoped for! You are certainly to be lauded for your heroics!$B$BThis looks like a fine brood of blackwhelps to make a start with. Examining them, that is.$B$BPlease, accept this as payment. I insist!' WHERE `entry`=10747;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='On behalf of the Cenarion Expedition druids of Evergrove, and the indigenous life of the Ruuan Weald, Tree Warden Chawn has asked you to slay Maxnar the Ashmaw. Return to him at Evergrove in the Blade\'s Edge Mountains after you have done so.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now we can breathe more easily knowing that the leader of our enemy has been dealt with. Not only that, but you\'ve saved the entire mountain range from their depredations.$B$BWhatever their ultimate goals, you\'ve foiled them!$B$BYou have our gratitude, $N. Please accept this token of our esteem, as well as our unending hospitality.' WHERE `entry`=10748;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is unsavory business, this use of poisons. But it will do what we want.' WHERE `entry`=10749;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Travel to the Path of Conquest in Shadowmoon Valley. Once you have done a preliminary assessment of the area, use the Kor\'kron Flare Gun to signal a Kor\'kron Wind Rider.$B$BSpeak with Overlord Or\'barokh should you lose your Kor\'kron Flare Gun and require a replacement.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Indeed, these troublesome whelps are up to something insidious. We must investigate further...' WHERE `entry`=10750;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='What have you to report, soldier?' WHERE `entry`=10750;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Slay 20 Eclipsion Soldiers, 10 Eclipsion Cavaliers, and 10 Eclipsion Spellbinders and then use the Kor\'kron Flare Gun to signal another Kor\'kron Wind Rider to report your task complete.$B$BSpeak with Overlord Or\'barokh at Shadowmoon Village in Shadowmoon Valley should you lose your Kor\'kron Flare Gun and require a replacement.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You won\'t believe this, grunt.' WHERE `entry`=10751;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So Thundris Windweaver still thinks I need looking after? I\'ll need to remind him who saved whom; he seems to forget it was I that pulled him from harm\'s way.$B$BWell now that you\'re here, $R, perhaps I can find something for you to do.' WHERE `entry`=10752;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Kill 4 Felsworn Scalewing, 4 Felsworn Daggermaw, and 2 Fel Corrupters.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I do not pride myself knowing we destroyed what Elune has created, but the corruption needed to be stopped. You have done well $C.' WHERE `entry`=10753;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Could this be?  Let me take a closer look at that mold.' WHERE `entry`=10754;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A key mold? Could this be what grants us access to the Shattered Halls?' WHERE `entry`=10755;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Bring the Primed Key Mold to Rohok in Thrallmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nazgrel wants me to work on a key? Does he forget we\'re in a battlefield? There are blades and spears to forge!' WHERE `entry`=10756;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. Let\'s give it a shot.' WHERE `entry`=10757;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve succeeded! Only thing left for you to do is try it out.' WHERE `entry`=10758;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The arakkoa cackles.>$B$BYes, I am the deserter mentioned in the commander\'s journal. I have been waiting for the day when others might recognize the threat posed by those I once called brothers.' WHERE `entry`=10759;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I don\'t see much of use here, but there are a couple of entries that could prove useful. It looks as though these arakkoa were preparing some kind of elaborate magical ritual up until the time of their deaths, but why? There\'s also a curious note here about a \'deserter.\'' WHERE `entry`=10760;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The arakkoa cackles.>$B$BYes, I am the deserter mentioned in the commander\'s journal. I have been waiting for the day when others might recognize the threat posed by those I once called brothers.' WHERE `entry`=10761;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A key? Danath should have us working on siege engines!' WHERE `entry`=10762;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let\'s try it then. Let\'s see what fel orc crafting is all about.' WHERE `entry`=10763;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done it, laddie!  Only thing left to do is for you to take it to Hellfire Citadel and kill yourself some orcs!' WHERE `entry`=10764;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Slay Chancellor Bloodleaf and Corok the Mighty and recover Illidan\'s Command. Use the Kor\'kron Flare Gun to signal another Kor\'kron Wind Rider once you have accomplished this task.$B$BSpeak with Overlord Or\'barokh at Shadowmoon Village in Shadowmoon Valley should you lose your Kor\'kron Flare Gun and require a replacement.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='So they are attempting to gain the favor of the giants. eh? I have a plan that promises to sever this unholy union.' WHERE `entry`=10765;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Pleased to meet you, $N. Name\'s Plexi.$B$BI won\'t bore you with formalities. We both know why we\'re here. Now, let\'s get to work.' WHERE `entry`=10766;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You must be the $R Blood Guard Gulmok told me to expect. I have a plan in mind, but I\'ll need your help to complete the preparations.' WHERE `entry`=10767;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Collect 10 Illidari Tabards and then use the Kor\'kron Flare Gun to signal another Kor\'kron Wind Rider.$B$BSpeak with Overlord Or\'barokh at Shadowmoon Village in Shadowmoon Valley should you lose your Kor\'kron Flare Gun and require a replacement.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah-ha! These will do quite nicely.' WHERE `entry`=10768;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, well, well... If it isn\'t the grunt I sent out into the field. You\'re back and in one piece.$B$B<Or\'barokh nods.>$B$BI knew you wouldn\'t let me down, soldier. You\'ve stopped a major Illidari advance and, in doing so, earned yourself a little reward.' WHERE `entry`=10769;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There are so many that we can never kill them all, but you have given me hope. Perhaps I shall try a little harder for another few centuries to revive my beloved wood.' WHERE `entry`=10770;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You destroyed many of those foul little creatures. I can rest easier knowing that so many were destroyed.' WHERE `entry`=10771;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Travel to the Path of Conquest in Shadowmoon Valley. Once you have done a preliminary assessment of the area, use the Wildhammer Flare Gun to signal a Wildhammer Gryphon Rider.$B$BSpeak with Thane Yoregar at Wildhammer Stronghold in Shadowmoon Valley should you lose your Wildhammer Flare Gun and require a replacement.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Indeed, these troublesome whelps are up to something insidious. We must investigate further...' WHERE `entry`=10772;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='What have you to report, soldier?' WHERE `entry`=10772;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Slay 20 Eclipsion Soldiers, 10 Eclipsion Cavaliers, and 5 Sons of Corok and then use the Wildhammer Flare Gun to signal another Wildhammer Gryphon Rider to report your task complete.$B$BSpeak with Thane Yoregar at Wildhammer Stronghold in Shadowmoon Valley should you lose your Wildhammer Flare Gun and require a replacement.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You won\'t believe this, soldier!' WHERE `entry`=10773;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Slay Chancellor Bloodleaf and Corok the Mighty and recover Illidan\'s Command. Use the Wildhammer Flare Gun to signal another Wildhammer Gryphon Rider once you have accomplished this task.$B$BSpeak with Thane Yoregar at Wildhammer Stronghold in Shadowmoon Valley should you lose your Wildhammer Flare Gun and require a replacement.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='So they are attempting to gain the favor of the giants, eh? I have a plan that could serve to sever this unholy union.' WHERE `entry`=10774;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Collect 10 Illidari Tabards and then use the Wildhammer Flare Gun to signal another Wildhammer Gryphon Rider.$B$BSpeak with Thane Yoregar at Wildhammer Stronghold in Shadowmoon Valley should you lose your Wildhammer Flare Gun and require a replacement.',`objectives_loc6`='Collect 10 Illidari Tabards and then use the Wildhammer Flare Gun to signal another Wildhammer Gryphon Rider.$B$BSpeak with Thane Yoregar at Wildhammer Stronghold in Shadowmoon Valley should you lose your Wildhammer Flare Gun and require a replacement.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah-ha! These will do quite nicely.' WHERE `entry`=10775;
