UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, my friend. Now I will be able to fashion more of the special alloy that is going into the creation of our forces\' weapons and armor.$B$BAnd, I have some leftover extract from the process, which you\'ll likely find handy for use on your weapons. Please, take your pick of whichever will serve your purposes.$B$BReturn to me again on the morrow. No doubt I will need more armaments.' WHERE `entry`=11544;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are a virtuous soul, $N. It is easy to forget the fallen amidst the turmoil of war and the euphoria of victory. The friends and families of the dead thank you.' WHERE `entry`=11545;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent, $N.$B$BI hope this will aid you in your efforts here.' WHERE `entry`=11546;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, yes. Let\'s have a look now, shall we?$B$BThings seem to be in order. Very well. Here is your translocator.$B$BIf any of your readings are faulty, there\'s no telling where you\'ll end up, and mind you, you\'ll only have yourself to blame.' WHERE `entry`=11547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are a virtuous soul, $N. It is easy to forget the fallen amidst the turmoil of war and the euphoria of victory. The friends and families of the dead thank you.' WHERE `entry`=11548;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You truly are a generous person and a worthy ally. From now on you shall be known as $N of the Shattered Sun and all who fought here will know of your deeds!' WHERE `entry`=11549;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Kil\'jaeden bears down upon this world with the full force of the Burning Legion. Should the summoning complete, our world will once more be flung into the throes of chaos. Your assistance on the Isle of Quel\'Danas is critical to our success against the Burning Legion.$B$BOur mages are working on bringing down the barriers blocking access to the Sunwell. Do your part in battling the forces of the Legion by helping the Shattered Sun Offensive.' WHERE `entry`=11550;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your aid in the offensive has not gone unnoticed, $N. The combined forces of the Aldor and Scryers offer you their thanks.' WHERE `entry`=11554;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You continue to prove yourself in this most important battle, $N. Please accept this as a token of our continued gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=11555;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We couldn\'t have gotten where we are without you, $N. The combined might of the Aldor and Scryers is not enough to crush the Legion and Kael. We are thankful to have allies of your caliber among us.' WHERE `entry`=11556;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are one of our very best, $N. Your name will be known throughout our ranks for a long time to come. Please accept this small gift on behalf of our forces.' WHERE `entry`=11557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are for me? Is this some sort of $R trick? No?$B$BWell then, thank you! Come back any time that you have more clams, and we\'ll do business!' WHERE `entry`=11559;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now no matter what happens, the Winterfin murlocs have a secure future.$B$BYou are to be commended, and rewarded, for your selflessness, $N!' WHERE `entry`=11560;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am pleased. I can smell the coppery tang of their blood on your hands.$B$BThis is a good start for you, $R.' WHERE `entry`=11561;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Aw, so you must be the so-called King Mrgl-Mrgl\'s lackey. I suppose that $R has sent you to appease me?$B$BGood, I have just the thing that needs doing for someone as powerful as you!' WHERE `entry`=11562;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not bad. This will make a nice feast!$B$BWith the king of the orcas dead the attacks upon us should diminish while the whales fight amongst themselves for dominance.' WHERE `entry`=11563;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Aw yes, these will do nicely.$B$BJust plop them down anywhere. You can have some of my leftover stew from last night. And since you\'ve been helping us with our other problems, you can have my recipe, too.' WHERE `entry`=11564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Upon seeing the spare murloc suit, the king rubs his costumed appendages together.>$B$BNicely done. Now, back to the pressing matter at hand. I\'ve got something of great importance for you to do.' WHERE `entry`=11565;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Regrettable, but necessary. I\'ll take the claw, $N.$B$BThank you for all of the help you\'ve given us. With Claximus defeated, maybe we\'ll be able to reunite the remaining murlocs and seal off those caverns.$B$BPlease, my friend, take this... it\'s the least I can do for all of the help you have rendered us!' WHERE `entry`=11566;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We must return all of the artifacts, $N. When all four are gathered, you will put them back in their graves.' WHERE `entry`=11567;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Grim tidings, $N. My people are in danger and must be warned. These sea faring aberrations will take no mercy upon the Kalu\'ak.' WHERE `entry`=11568;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Frozen Heart of Isuldof Returned',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Ancient Armor of the Kvaldir Returned' WHERE `entry`=11568;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Quickly, hand it here!' WHERE `entry`=11569;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is wonderful news! And you say that Lurgglbr discovered that the emanations from the caverns are what caused this insanity?$B$BIt must be that the magic from Coldarra is growing stronger. The Nexus War... the battle between the blue dragonflight and all of the other dragons, is spilling over.$B$BSoon, we will all be embroiled in it!' WHERE `entry`=11570;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='Yes, $N, what can I do for you?' WHERE `entry`=11570;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now I will be able to use Scalder\'s essence to impart my understanding of the Winterfin murloc tongue to you.' WHERE `entry`=11571;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Kalu\'ak thank you for all that you have done, $N. We must now prepare for battle and warn our brothers and sisters across the sea of what is to come.$B$BI hope it is not too late...' WHERE `entry`=11572;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lunk-tusk lives? At least there is some good news to be had on this day...' WHERE `entry`=11573;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You can tell your friend that her rescue was our pleasure, as well as our duty.$B$BHer encounter was but a small piece in what I believe to be a large puzzle.$B$BDalaran is sparing no effort in solving this mystery and to be honest, we could use a bit of assistance....' WHERE `entry`=11574;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You can tell your friend that her rescue was our pleasure, as well as our duty.$B$BHer encounter was but a small piece in what I believe to be a large puzzle.$B$BDalaran is sparing no effort in solving this mystery and to be honest, we could use a bit of assistance....' WHERE `entry`=11575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fascinating! This is the largest disruption yet.$B$BThough the worst is yet to come, I fear.' WHERE `entry`=11576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Desecrate the Alliance\'s Westfall bonfire!' WHERE `entry`=11581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It was how big?$B$BThat\'s impossible! I need to report to Dalaran at once!' WHERE `entry`=11582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Honor the Silverpine Forest flame.' WHERE `entry`=11584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A hero of the Horde, eh?$B$B<Garrosh sniffs at the air around you.>$B$BFear...$B$B<Garrosh spits.>$B$BYou won\'t last long.' WHERE `entry`=11585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Do not think that I have forgotten what you did for my people in Nagrand, $N. Hellscream never forgets.$B$BFor that I am indebted to you and it is why I give you this chance now: run. Leave this place and never look back.$B$BReturn to your home and say a prayer for the dying.' WHERE `entry`=11586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $N.$B$BThe Kirin Tor graciously accept the assistance you have rendered. Know that any service you provide us will not go unrewarded.$B$BPlease, accept this humble offering as a token of Dalaran\'s appreciation.' WHERE `entry`=11587;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N.$B$BWe\'ll have him prepared for his interrogation at once.' WHERE `entry`=11590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='Have you captured a Beryl sorcerer yet, $N?' WHERE `entry`=11590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This isn\'t good, $C.$B$BLongrunner Proudhoof says that these are the burial grounds of his honored ancestors.' WHERE `entry`=11591;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Blood and thunder! You\'ve salvaged our newborn relations with the taunka.$B$BThank you for putting the situation to rights. Aka\'Magosh, $N!' WHERE `entry`=11592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $C. We are the Horde, we do not leave our dead behind!$B$BIt should never have been necessary in the first place. Steeljaw was a fool!' WHERE `entry`=11593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $C! You must have a great deal of experience fighting the undead. And, if you didn\'t before, you have some now.$B$BYou\'ll need it if you\'re going to survive in Northrend.' WHERE `entry`=11594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Overlord Razgor salutes.>$B$BYour reputation precedes you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=11595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just in time... The Nerubians have seemingly doubled in number in just a week\'s time. We could use all the help we can get out here.' WHERE `entry`=11596;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve slowed them down, but more are sure to join the fight. Were you able to locate any of their egg sacs while in the quarry?' WHERE `entry`=11598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The corpse matches the description that Leryssa gave you of William Allerton. Oddly enough, there are no bite or claw marks on him.' WHERE `entry`=11599;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Do you think William\'s death was a random killing by the Scourge?  Things sure seem fishy.$B$BSomething\'s up. We must find Thassarian.' WHERE `entry`=11600;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Can\'t say I can help you friend. But I might know someone who can.' WHERE `entry`=11601;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They just keep on coming, despite our best efforts. Something\'s gotta give, $N.' WHERE `entry`=11602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Nerub\'ar Egg Sac Destroyed' WHERE `entry`=11602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Mmmmm... not too bitter... not too dry... it\'s just like the old days, with the lads at the barracks.' WHERE `entry`=11603;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Whad\'ya want?  I have enough problems as it is!' WHERE `entry`=11604;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Elder Atkanok\'s voice greets you as you approach his statue.>$B$BWell done, $N. With the names of the wandering elders, we can continue the ceremonies disrupted during the attack. However, before the elders\' spirits can be led to their stones, we must calm the spirits of the murdered craftsmen and shaman. Otherwise, the ancestor spirits may never hear the ceremony\'s call.' WHERE `entry`=11605;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='If my calculations are correct - and they\'re often not - you\'re gonna need about 10-20 seaforium depth charges.$B$BOh yea, you\'ll be planting these mothers into their sinkholes.' WHERE `entry`=11606;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can sense the upheaval in the spirit world beginning to calm. You have done well, $N. The spirits of the ancestors are fortunate to have your help in this time of need.' WHERE `entry`=11607;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'ll stop \'em - at least I think it\'ll stop \'em. Either way, you\'ve done your part. That\'s all an $R can ask for, no?' WHERE `entry`=11608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='West Nerub\'ar Sinkhole Destroyed',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='North Nerub\'ar Sinkhole Destroyed' WHERE `entry`=11608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<You hold the objects before the statue of Elder Atkanok.>$B$BThose will suffice, although they are in a sad state. Some of them have survived centuries of use, only to be battered and stolen by barbarians.' WHERE `entry`=11609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The ancestors have found their statues, and they have you to thank, $N. The craftsmen of Kaskala will return to the quarry and ensure that the line of ancestors continues unbroken. For our part, the ancestors will continue to observe you with interest, as it seems your path is just beginning.' WHERE `entry`=11610;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Most of them made it back. The ones smart enough to know that we\'re inside the gigantic metal and stone building, anyway...$B$BRegardless, a job well done. I hear you sprung more than a couple peons loose.$B$BOh yes, you\'re the talk of the... um... fortress.' WHERE `entry`=11611;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now that these strange mages know that the people of Kaskala and their allies will not give up the quarry so easily, we must maintain our efforts and defeat them completely.$B$BMy brothers in Kaskala have also come under attack and will not be able to support us, but with your help, $N, we can overcome these pillagers.' WHERE `entry`=11612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done my people a great favor, $N. I must ask one more thing of you, however.' WHERE `entry`=11613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It doesn\'t get much deader than this... Strangely, the Nerubians did not devour the corpse.$B$BAfter careful examination you see that Luther\'s death was self inflicted - deadly poison. Smart. Nerubians won\'t come near this toxic corpse.$B$BYou notice that Luther is holding a journal.' WHERE `entry`=11614;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Barthus flips to the last page of the journal and begins reading.>$B$BThis is very bad news. Hellscream must be notified at once.' WHERE `entry`=11615;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Hellscream reads the journal entry.>$B$BIs that all?' WHERE `entry`=11616;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The mage hunters won\'t find it as easy to plunder our quarry and steal our artifacts as they\'d imagined. With your help, we\'ll win back the quarry and set things right again.' WHERE `entry`=11617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is it? Hellscream sent a single $R $Gboy:girl;?$B$BIf I still had a jaw it would be on the floor right now.' WHERE `entry`=11618;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did it, $N!  The spirits of the slain tuskarr can now rest in peace - their deaths have been avenged!' WHERE `entry`=11619;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hsssssssssssss!  Have you come to mock me, $R?' WHERE `entry`=11620;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The curator and his men must\'ve thought the quarry an easy target for their looting, but you\'ve shown them otherwise, $N. I am deeply grateful for your help and I\'m certain the ancestors will continue to watch over you.' WHERE `entry`=11623;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are foolish to come here, little $R.$B$BWhat is it that you seek?' WHERE `entry`=11624;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yesssssss!  We will slay the Kvaldir\'s beast!  I will show these brutes to never cross a priestess of the scale!' WHERE `entry`=11625;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My people\'s spirits can rest in peace. You\'ve helped me honor my father... perhaps I will one day be as strong as you are.' WHERE `entry`=11626;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am pleased, though no doubt they will still continue to quarrel a bit longer.$B$BHowever, there is something else that you will need to accomplish before you can return to your spirit talker.' WHERE `entry`=11627;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='As much as I dislike bringing such disease-ridden things into the village, they may give us an advantage over our foes.$B$B<The chieftain gestures to Sage Aeire and waves dismissively at the pelts.>$B$BWhile she is preparing the pelts, there is one other element we need to create the cloak.' WHERE `entry`=11628;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Imperean gave you a primal essence of herself? I can hear its howling winds!$B$BI know a ritual we can make use of it in. We must hurry before her primal rips itself apart!' WHERE `entry`=11629;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Chieftain Wintergale gingerly accepts the clods of soil you gathered.>$B$BWe should get these into Sage Aeire\'s hands as soon as possible.$B$B<The chieftain grunts, pretending not to be disturbed by the tainted dirt.>$B$BWe can never know when the Scourge commander will launch the final assault on the village.' WHERE `entry`=11630;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They\'ve shackled his spirit. $N, we have to put an end to his torture!$B$BYou must descend into the bowels of Magmoth and find a way to free him!' WHERE `entry`=11631;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Saurfang grins.>$B$BIt looks familiar... The Might of Kalimdor trampled a thousand bugs like this one in the desert of Silithus.$B$BThis is a different place - a different environment - but the result will be the same.$B$B<Saurfang looks you over.>$B$BYou will bring pride and honor to the Horde in Northrend, $N.$B$B<Saurfang nods.>' WHERE `entry`=11632;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Chieftain Wintergale listens as your describe your observations.>$B$BThe information you\'ve gathered will help us to plan our assault on the Temple City. We\'ll need to find a way to defeat the officers you identified and get into that necropolis.' WHERE `entry`=11633;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ay, mon. I been exceptin\' you.$B$B<To\'bor points west.>$B$BTake a peek. Across dat tundra be death, mon... death.' WHERE `entry`=11634;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for the reprieve, $C. If only my true freedom were so easy to attain.' WHERE `entry`=11635;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='NO MERCY FOR THE DEAD!$B$BNone of \'em had the guts to stay behind to defend our glorious tanks after Hellscream deemed the coast \'condemned.\' It\'s mostly quiet here, seein\' as how the Scourge are formin\' up ranks to assault Warsong Hold. Sometimes I get a stray zombie or ghoul, but they don\'t last very long.$B$B<Gorge strokes his axe.>$B$B\'Course, there\'s the mist...$B$B<Gorge shudders.>' WHERE `entry`=11636;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am freed. Thank you, $N.$B$BAnd now, I have one final request of you.' WHERE `entry`=11637;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for freeing his spirit from Kaganishu and returning with his remains. We have little to reward you with, but you may take whatever catches your eye.$B$BAnd now, I will return him to the living where he belongs.' WHERE `entry`=11638;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The dead are honored by your actions, $N.$B$B<The wounded orc nods and exhales slowly.>$B$BPerhaps now I can find my way back to being the warrior I once was.' WHERE `entry`=11639;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Chieftain Wintergale reads the words written on the scrolls.>$B$B\'Shabtir bakh sokhen.\'$B$BWords of the ancient, harsh language used by the Nerubians, and apt ones at that.$B$B\'The servant bows to the master\'s authority.\' These are the words that will gain you entry into the necropolis.' WHERE `entry`=11640;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have proven your fearlessness and demonstrated your prowess in combat. I believe you would make a fine taunka warrior. I only wish the chieftain had the same understanding.$B$BWe are fortunate to count you as an ally in our struggle to evacuate the village before it is overrun by the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=11641;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re the new tank driver, $Gbuddy:lassy;? Fine by me! We just need to get these things up and running again. Yea, you try to go out into the Plains of Nasam without a tank and you\'re as good as dead.' WHERE `entry`=11642;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great work, $Gbuddy:lassy;! Now where\'d I put those spare parts...' WHERE `entry`=11643;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great work, $Gbuddy:lassy;! Now where\'d I put that pneumatic tank transjigamarig.' WHERE `entry`=11644;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, $N, you\'re just the best!$B$BHere\'s your coin as promised.' WHERE `entry`=11645;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It was wise of Donathan to send you, $C.$B$BAs it turns out, I am in need of someone outside the Kirin Tor.' WHERE `entry`=11646;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Sage Aeire accepts the totem from you.>$B$BDid the totem work? Its preparation required ancient magics the sages haven\'t used in generations. Of all the knowledge passed down, only a fraction of it remains in use today.' WHERE `entry`=11647;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! It was crucial that we collect that intelligence.$B$BWell done, friend.' WHERE `entry`=11648;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I regret the loss of those tempests, but my word is my bond... even to a mortal such as yourself.$B$BNow, let us see if we can fashion something of use to you.' WHERE `entry`=11649;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Alright, that\'s more like it! Now all we gots to do is put all this together.$B$BYeah, as if you\'re going to help me with that.$B$BHold your horses, this\'ll just take a second now that I\'ve got my tools back!' WHERE `entry`=11650;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With the current state of our transports and shipping lanes, we haven\'t been able to get a damned siege engine to Warsong. These tanks are all that we have left from the original expedition. Now that they\'re operational, you\'re gonna use \'em to stomp the Scourge offensive at the Plains of Nasam.' WHERE `entry`=11651;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Kel\'Thuzad? So it\'s true - Naxxramas returns...$B$BPerhaps I underestimated you, $N. You\'ve done the Horde a great service. The Warchief would be proud!$B$B<Garrosh pauses to think.>$B$BIf Kel\'Thuzad is controlling these Scourge, there\'s no telling what else the Lich King has in store for us... I\'ll need time to think through this new information, $N. You are dismissed.' WHERE `entry`=11652;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='Well? What happened?',`ObjectiveText1_loc6`='Scourge Unit obliterated',`ObjectiveText2_loc6`='Injured Warsong Soldier rescued' WHERE `entry`=11652;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Whadya mean it didn\'t work?!$B$BBut... but...$B$B<Crafty begins to sob.>$B$BOkay, we can deal with this. I\'m a big girl. Time to think outside the box!' WHERE `entry`=11653;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The taunka snow tracker appears weak and barely responds to you.>$B$BI haven\'t... long. Maybe... maybe you can stop them... before...' WHERE `entry`=11654;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Sadness overcomes Waltor.>$B$BRuin... That is all they leave in their wake. They must be taught a lesson.' WHERE `entry`=11655;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A show of resistance to the Kvaldir savages might be what is needed to save my people at the other encampments. Perhaps the Kvaldir will rethink their actions should they believe that retribution will come.' WHERE `entry`=11656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Bor\'s Hammer destroyed',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Bor\'s Anvil destroyed' WHERE `entry`=11656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Torch catching is a lot of fun, don\'t you think?  But have care!  You don\'t want to get singed!' WHERE `entry`=11657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice, but those clothes reek!$B$BPersonally, you\'d never catch me dead in such rags. But we\'re going to have to sort through them and find some that fit your, um... figure.' WHERE `entry`=11658;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I feared they might\'ve captured Grumm, but I never thought they\'d do such horrific things to him. I\'ve never seen a warrior survive a losing battle with the Scourge.$B$BThank you for bringing word of his fate, $N. He was a mighty warrior and we will remember him as such.' WHERE `entry`=11659;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You must call for Orabus using the Horn of the Ancient Mariner.' WHERE `entry`=11660;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It seems that the loss of their lieutenant has only stirred the nest. They are more angry and aggressive than before!$B$B<Waltor sighs.>$B$BYou\'ve done what you can here, friend. At the very least you deserve some form of compensation for thinning their numbers.' WHERE `entry`=11661;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Waltor was wise in sending you to me, $R. The gods smile down upon those that mete justice. You will be he that doles out punishment to the wicked!' WHERE `entry`=11662;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Forgive me, $N. I know that was unpleasant work.$B$BWere it not for the desperation of our circumstance I\'d never have asked you to assist us in such a manner.$B$BSo... what have you discovered?' WHERE `entry`=11663;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is whispered in the winds, friend. Your name is known to the elements. You have done a great service to Mootoo on this day and you shall be rewarded.' WHERE `entry`=11664;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What a mean little creature!  I\'m sure the Rokk will make something tasty with him.$B$BI\'m just kidding, of course.$B$B<Old Man Barlo winks slyly.>' WHERE `entry`=11665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well look at that... you caught a big one!  This old man is eating in style tonight.' WHERE `entry`=11666;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There he is!  I\'d know that scar anywhere.$B$BTo be completely honest, I thought he\'d be... bigger. Well, I suppose I\'ll let him go and try again another day.' WHERE `entry`=11667;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are skilled with both the hook and knife. Hand those sweet tidbits over, and I\'ll let you have a taste.' WHERE `entry`=11668;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That is the biggest, ugliest fish I\'ve seen. I can\'t even imagine what you used for bait.$B$BJust set the beast on the ground, and I\'ll deal with it once I\'m sure it\'s dead.' WHERE `entry`=11669;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Holey moley, you did it!$B$BAlright, now those pesky magnataur and their snobold flunkies should turn their attentions on the Horde.$B$BHow can I ever repay you, $N?' WHERE `entry`=11670;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Broken? $B$BLet me have a look....' WHERE `entry`=11671;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'ve been expecting your arrival, $N. Welcome to Northrend.' WHERE `entry`=11672;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Huh? What?$B$BBonker who?$B$BI\'ve no idea who you\'re talking about, but I\'ll take your word for it. If you rescued him or her from the pit of Magmoth then I suppose you deserve a reward.$B$BLet me see what I\'ve got lying around in here....' WHERE `entry`=11673;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The greatmother sent you. She must be disappointed in me.$B$BBut when I saw the great object fall from the sky, I could not wait for a full group of longrunners and snow trackers to accompany me. Knowledge waits for no one.' WHERE `entry`=11674;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What else can we do but ease their suffering? In any case, they came here to die, so do not mourn them. At least you have given them some dignity.$B$BNow we must put an end to that which is causing the plague.' WHERE `entry`=11675;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Each prisoner saved is one less undead aberration that we have to deal with, $N. You\'ve done a great service for the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=11676;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The sage hangs her head and sighs in relief.>$B$BThis is a good start. If only that were our only problem.' WHERE `entry`=11677;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am... not... long for this... world, little $R.' WHERE `entry`=11678;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The frivolous games you play here are of no consequence....$B$BYou and your Dalaran allies pick at loose threads while the fabric of this world\'s future is being shredded.$B$BStill, this may provide my drakes some needed amusement.$B$BShow me this key....' WHERE `entry`=11679;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is it, the key is ours!' WHERE `entry`=11680;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your heroic efforts shall not be forgotten, $C.$B$BPlease, accept this with my sincere gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=11681;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, $R, we speak again.$B$BWhen you\'ve heard my words you may wish we had not.' WHERE `entry`=11682;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N.$B$BThe Lich King and his Scourge are a blight upon Northrend. We must not stop until they are all truly dead, and his existence is put to an end!' WHERE `entry`=11683;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Greatfather Mahan accepts the map, but makes no move to examine it..>$B$BWe\'ll be able to use your information later, once we\'re prepared to carry out the plan.' WHERE `entry`=11684;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These should be enough to form the core of a mighty elemental, but stone alone will not give my elemental life.' WHERE `entry`=11685;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is far worse than what was noted in Luther\'s journal. They\'ve got this place covered in Scourge and are infecting everything they touch.$B$B<Ickoris nods.>$B$BIt gets worse - if you can imagine such a thing...' WHERE `entry`=11686;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Bristlehorn is dead?!$B$BI should never have let him go there by himself.' WHERE `entry`=11687;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I think I\'ve got it, $R!' WHERE `entry`=11688;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What word do you bring from Highmesa?$B$B<You explain what you know and give the greatmother the bad news concerning Longrunner Bristlehorn.>$B$BMy... my grandson!$B$B<The greatmother fights to keep control of her emotions.>$B$BHe died an honorable death like a true taunka!$B$BYou were the last to be with him, $N, so he shall always be a part of you. I give you my thanks for completing his last wishes.' WHERE `entry`=11689;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re a true hero, $N. My kodos would have died out there without you. You have my thanks and the thanks of all the soldiers and journeymen that will use these kodos to strengthen our presence in Northrend!' WHERE `entry`=11690;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The magma totem bursts into three separate flames as it is brought near the ice stone. The stone shimmers, then is gone...' WHERE `entry`=11691;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice work, but I\'d grab a shower the next chance you get.$B$BNow, let\'s really deal with the problem out here.' WHERE `entry`=11693;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew you had it in you. Now there\'s something else that I need to ask you to take care of.' WHERE `entry`=11694;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Barah accepts the pieces of the horn from you and begins trying to fit them together.>$B$BStormhoof would be proud of you, $N. Perhaps when we\'ve dealt with the Scourge, I will take the horn with me on a pilgrimage to Stormhoof\'s tomb.' WHERE `entry`=11695;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The cold of Ahune spreads through these caverns, $N; a seed of the frigid death that awaits us if he gains his full strength. I thank the Earthmother for sending you.' WHERE `entry`=11696;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey there! Who are you?$B$BBixie sent you? Excellent, let\'s get me out of here!' WHERE `entry`=11697;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks, $N.$B$BThe Lich King and his Scourge are really scary, but we can\'t stop until they are all lying still in new graves!' WHERE `entry`=11698;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Outstanding! Now just a little modification here, and a tweak there....' WHERE `entry`=11699;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Tinky\'s got an evil twin?!$B$BWell, if she says she\'s okay, and that she\'ll be able to get herself back to the airstrip soon, that\'s good enough for me.' WHERE `entry`=11700;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s quite a tale, $N. With all of the problems out here, it\'s a wonder that the airstrip hasn\'t been wiped out already.$B$BBut, thanks to you, there\'s one less adversary to worry about.$B$BI put aside some special things for just such an occasion as this. Why don\'t you take your pick?' WHERE `entry`=11701;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Finally, help! And by the looks of you, Horde.$B$BThat\'s alright... your people are very skilled in the art of combat. We\'re going to need a lot of that.' WHERE `entry`=11702;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Getry looks you over.>%B%BThis is all Ickoris could send?' WHERE `entry`=11703;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Finally, help! And by the looks of you, Alliance.$B$BThat\'s good... your people are very skilled in the art of combat. We\'re going to need a lot of that.' WHERE `entry`=11704;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='And you returned victorious, just as I thought! I told Saurfang you\'d be fine.$B$B<Hellscream grunts knowingly.>$B$BPerhaps this will show that old dog that he doesn\'t have all the answers, eh?' WHERE `entry`=11705;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='<Hellscream raises an eyebrow at you.>$B$BWhat\'s this I hear about a Scourge necrolord?' WHERE `entry`=11705;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your efforts against the Nerubians have given us a reprieve from the overwhelming Scourge assault. Thanks to your accomplishments, we can strike at the the Scourge fortress to the northeast without fear of attack from the west.$B$BAs for the horn, I will safeguard it until next we need its power. Stormhoof gave his life to secure the horn and we cannot suffer its loss again.' WHERE `entry`=11706;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see that Skyhopper finally got around to sending help. And none too soon I might add!$B$BWelcome, $Gbrother:sister;, we need your help badly!' WHERE `entry`=11707;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The old man sent you to me, huh? He tell you everything that\'s going on out here?$B$BGood... let\'s take care of business then!' WHERE `entry`=11708;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='Hello there.' WHERE `entry`=11708;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Nork scoffs.>$B$BPrisoners? These aren\'t prisoners. They\'re cowardly dogs! Just look at \'em. Did you know that without exception, every single one of these yellow-bellied "soldiers" came to our gates and surrendered their arms and armor?$B$BFrom what we\'ve been able to gather, these men and women are discharged and sent back to their homes if captured by us.$B$B<Nork spits.>$B$BPathetic...' WHERE `entry`=11709;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s great, $C! These parts look like they\'re in serviceable condition.$B$BNow if I could only figure out how to fix this blasted thing....' WHERE `entry`=11710;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good job, $N. That\'s one less filthy, useless, Alliance scum-bag that we\'ll have to provide for...$B$BIf you\'re lookin\' for more work, the tauren and blood elf nearby need some help.$B$B\'Course we\'ve got our own set of problems to deal with out here as well...' WHERE `entry`=11711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='<Tungok grunts.>$B$BDid you take care of the deserter?' WHERE `entry`=11711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did it... it worked!$B$BI can\'t believe you were able to save so many. We\'re fortunate to have you around here!' WHERE `entry`=11712;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Abner accepts the map from you, then examines it closely.>$B$BGreat! This is all the information we need to begin the operation.' WHERE `entry`=11713;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A job well done, $N! Thank you!' WHERE `entry`=11714;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Abner sets about draining the fuel tank of the collector.>$B$BDistilling this by hand is going to be messy, but I\'ll have it taken care of soon. In the meantime, we\'ll need one more material to complete the machine.' WHERE `entry`=11715;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lovely! Just lovely!$B$B<Laurith applies a sprinkling of pollen to one of the bloodspore carpels and then utters an incantation.>$B$BHrmph... I don\'t understand. Unless... Why of course!' WHERE `entry`=11716;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A-ha!$B$B<Laurith sprinkles the moth pollen onto the bloodspore carpels.>$B$BLook at that!' WHERE `entry`=11717;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Abner inspects the hides, coughing at all the dust rising from them.>$B$BDon\'t these animals even try to keep clean? Some of these are absolutely filthy. Well, I guess I\'d better get started cleaning them. It\'s not like anyone\'s got spare time around here.' WHERE `entry`=11718;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Primal Mighthorn will be delighted! This is better than even I expected!$B$BPerhaps it\'s time that I told you the truth.' WHERE `entry`=11719;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The bloodspore that you collected might just be enough to give us an edge against the magnataurs of Gammoth - with your help, of course.' WHERE `entry`=11720;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A job well done, $N! Would you honor Laurith and I by taking the head of the beast and presenting it to Hellscream? He will be extremely pleased.' WHERE `entry`=11721;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Hellscream picks up the head of Gammothra with one arm and spits in its face.>$B$BThey will learn, $N... They will all learn. The Horde is not to be trifled with...' WHERE `entry`=11722;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Abner listens eagerly as you report your success and the success of the Shake-n-Quake 5000.>$B$BFizzcrank will be delighted to hear the news! And who knows, perhaps we\'ll make a mechanic of you yet!' WHERE `entry`=11723;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Alkor is no more, eh? A pity... As for the egg, we have no real use for it anymore. We\'ve got much bigger problems to deal with now.' WHERE `entry`=11724;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank goodness. It was terrible.$B$BThere was a bright flash on the ground, and then, the next thing I know, the squadron\'s going down! I\'m hurt pretty badly, so I haven\'t had a chance to comb the site for other survivors, but something tells me I don\'t think there will be many.$B$B<Iggy grimaces in pain.>$B$BWill you help me complete my mission?' WHERE `entry`=11725;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Iggy holds his nose as he empties the spice pouches and addresses you in a nasal voice.>$B$BNow that we have what we need, I\'ll combine it with my emergency rations to create a bait for the wolves.' WHERE `entry`=11726;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='By Magni\'s beard!  Looks like the heavy artillery\'s arriving.' WHERE `entry`=11727;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Iggy holds his nose as he accepts the microfilm from you.>$B$BYuck, well, we\'ve complied with section 8.2, paragraph B of the emergency protocol here and recovered the film. Nothing in the protocol says I\'m responsible for cleaning it, though.' WHERE `entry`=11728;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My screwdriver... you found my screwdriver! I\'d been wondering where that thing got lost.$B$BHmm, you found it inside one of their robots, you say? That gives me an idea....' WHERE `entry`=11729;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Woo hoo! And you brought back the screwdriver intact, too!$B$BReprogramming those robots is going to turn out to be a huge advantage in our favor in the fight against Gearmaster Mechazod. I think you\'ve earned a little something for that.' WHERE `entry`=11730;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Quick! There\'s no time to waste!' WHERE `entry`=11731;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc6`='Braziers Hit' WHERE `entry`=11731;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Desecrate the Alliance\'s Arathi Highlands bonfire!' WHERE `entry`=11732;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome to Coldarra, $C.$B$BUnder the Transitus Shield we lie hidden just a stone\'s throw from the Nexus, fortress of the great aspect Malygos and his blue dragonflight.$B$BDo make yourself comfortable.' WHERE `entry`=11733;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Desecrate the Alliance\'s Elwynn Forest bonfire!' WHERE `entry`=11745;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Desecrate the Alliance\'s Feralas bonfire!' WHERE `entry`=11746;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Desecrate the Alliance\'s Loch Modan bonfire!' WHERE `entry`=11749;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Desecrate the Alliance\'s Hinterlands bonfire!' WHERE `entry`=11755;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Desecrate the Alliance\'s Silithus bonfire!' WHERE `entry`=11760;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Desecrate the Alliance\'s Stranglethorn Vale bonfire!' WHERE `entry`=11761;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Desecrate the Alliance\'s Tanaris bonfire!' WHERE `entry`=11762;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Desecrate the Alliance\'s Winterspring bonfire!' WHERE `entry`=11763;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Desecrate the Horde\'s Badlands bonfire!' WHERE `entry`=11766;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Desecrate the Horde\'s Tirisfal Glades bonfire!' WHERE `entry`=11786;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wow, you survived!$B$BI guess all that\'s left to do now is to deal with Gearmaster Mechazod.' WHERE `entry`=11788;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, $N. This man\'s recovery will be slow, but we won\'t lose him.$B$BWhat do you say?  You found cultists inside the Stormbreaker?  You\'d best notify someone... and bring some evidence.' WHERE `entry`=11789;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Cultists? Below deck? I ought to have my whole crew flogged!$B$BListen... why don\'t we have Admiral Cantlebree take care of this... situation?' WHERE `entry`=11790;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for your concern, $N. We were made aware of the situation not too long ago.$B$BCounselor Talbot assures me that this was an isolated incident and not a cause for military concern.$B$BOur civilian authorities will make sure everyone involved is properly prosecuted.' WHERE `entry`=11791;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Be discreet, $N. We cannot look at this evidence in front of prying eyes.' WHERE `entry`=11792;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Speak quickly, $C. What information do you have on the cult?' WHERE `entry`=11793;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well, $N. However, I can\'t shake the feeling that this is not the last we\'ve seen of these death cultists.$B$BDarkness has a way of hiding even in plain sight.' WHERE `entry`=11794;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you once again, $N. With your help, I may yet be able to complete this mission, disastrous as it\'s been, and return to Fizzcrank to make my report and properly honor the dead.' WHERE `entry`=11795;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Once again, you have my thanks, $N. Without you, I would not have been able to recover anything useful from this disaster.' WHERE `entry`=11796;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice job, $N. Show the lads how it\'s done. The only good creeper\'s a dead creeper!' WHERE `entry`=11797;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The old gnome breathes a heavy sigh of relief.>$B$BIt is done then... you have saved us! If you hadn\'t stopped him here, then who knows how far his madness would have spread?$B$BWith the threats from the blue dragons and the Nexus War, not to mention the Lich King, the last thing we need is a mad creation of the Titans running loose!$B$BThank you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=11798;
