UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Honor the Hinterlands flame.' WHERE `entry`=11860;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Honor the Thousand Needles flame.' WHERE `entry`=11861;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Honor the Zangarmarsh flame.' WHERE `entry`=11863;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The demon has many names and each name has held special meaning at one time or another. While the details were sometimes insignificant, the end result was always the same: death.$B$BBut it is now, nearly fifty years after it all began, that the details will find the devil and lead to his downfall.$B$BThis time, we have him... There will be no escape for Nesingwary.$B$BNorthrend will be the battleground for our war. The hunter will become the hunted!' WHERE `entry`=11864;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You do the Earth Mother\'s work, $N, but do not revel in this victory for too long. We have discovered the hiding place of the trapper leader.' WHERE `entry`=11865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These will hang around my neck. Let them hear our message and let these ears be the vessels that carry our truths!' WHERE `entry`=11866;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These will hang around my neck. Let them hear our message and let these ears be the vessels that carry our truths!' WHERE `entry`=11867;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perhaps her death will serve as an example to others that dare slay animals for sport and riches.' WHERE `entry`=11868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now let us see how their nerve holds up when they see what became of their companions!' WHERE `entry`=11869;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Cenius sent you? Well you\'re not a moment too soon!' WHERE `entry`=11870;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A job well done, $N. Now we strike at the pirate leader!' WHERE `entry`=11871;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. We are closing in on Nesingwary!' WHERE `entry`=11872;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Fizzcrank listens to your report, looking somewhat relieved.>$B$BI should\'ve gone with them. We might\'ve been able to complete the mission without losing any pilots.$B$BTailspin is right, though, we have you to thank for what you\'ve been able to salvage. Your efforts may just make the difference in the fight against the Nerubians.' WHERE `entry`=11873;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The troops of the Shattered Sun Offensive will need every advantage they can get to beat back the allies of Kil\'Jaeden. My colleagues in Stormwind have created oils which will strengthen the blades and armor of our troops.$B$BThe key ingredient, nether residue, pervades Outland  -- if you know where to look. Any master herbalist, skinner, or miner who knows the signs can gather it while plying $G his:her; trade. Those herbs, ores, and beasts unique to Outland may all bear the residue.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for your help, $N. No contribution to the war effort is too small. Our men are going to need every advantage they can get in this battle.' WHERE `entry`=11875;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Arch Druid Lathorius wipes away his tears.>$B$BThey never stood a chance. Now orphaned, they will surely die on their own.' WHERE `entry`=11876;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Lord Torvos accepts the plans and looks over them.>$B$BYou\'ve done the offensive a great service, $N, but we should not rest. I wouldn\'t put it beyond our foes to plan more mischief in the future.' WHERE `entry`=11877;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<You hear a voice in your head. It is Khu\'nok.>$B$BYour name has been heard in the whistling winds, $N. You have done a great thing for my kin. For this we will consider you an ally. Alas, our torment cannot end without bloodshed and violence.$B$BThe price of peace for the mammoths will be the death of Kaw...' WHERE `entry`=11878;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Lathorius takes the halberd from you.>$B$BIs this what I think it is?$B$B<Lathorius grins.>$B$BSmashing! Outstanding! Another of Nesingwary\'s lackeys brought to justice!' WHERE `entry`=11879;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks for your help. You don\'t know what it\'s like to have to deal with "Doctor" Wafflefry over there. In between his "checkups" on my progress, he\'s busy hawking some gadget or another derived from his military inventions.' WHERE `entry`=11880;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Fezzix looks over the salvage.>$B$BJenny\'s a little roughed up, but she\'ll be fine. As for the salvage, it\'s a bit more... piecemeal than I had hoped, but I should be able to find a use for it. You\'re not off the hook yet, though. We\'re going to rebuild this baby.' WHERE `entry`=11881;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well met. You\'ve come to learn some new ways to handle fire?' WHERE `entry`=11882;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='At least for now the rhinos will know peace. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=11884;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! Take this. I\'ve prepared this bundle with items symbolizing the foes you\'ve defeated. They will allow you to summon Terokk.$B$BBeware, $N. He is the most powerful arakkoa to ever exist. Do not underestimate him!' WHERE `entry`=11885;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is worrisome, friend. It hints at a much larger plot beyond simple agitation of the local fire and water elements, and something here bears investigation...' WHERE `entry`=11886;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Gnomish tools? For me? These should make rebuilding that flying machine even easier than I expected.' WHERE `entry`=11887;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It does not surprise me that the $R chieftain does not have time to hear of our troubles. The ambassador\'s efforts will likely be like so much mist blowing in the wind.$B$BBut you are here now. We shall see if he chose well in sending you.' WHERE `entry`=11888;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'ll beat them if they come by land and we\'ll beat them if they come by air. If these motherless undead come by sea we\'re going to give them the beating of their lives.' WHERE `entry`=11889;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Troubling news indeed.$B$BMy people are leaving this place soon. We are going to break through the Scourge lines to get to our capital, Icemist, in the Dragonblight.$B$BBut, before we do that, we must deal with what the gnomes in their insanity have wrought.' WHERE `entry`=11890;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='What did you find out, $R?' WHERE `entry`=11890;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They seek to summon a frost lord into our world? No! They cannot tip the balance!' WHERE `entry`=11891;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='Have you learned their secrets?' WHERE `entry`=11891;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Alas, Nesingwary is gone. Perhaps he was never here to begin with...$B$B<Lathorius sighs.>$B$BThe demon is a slippery one, but his days are numbered. We will find him and when we do...' WHERE `entry`=11892;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Dorain nods.>$B$BGood. This should be sufficient to show Fezzix exactly what I\'ve been trying to tell him.' WHERE `entry`=11893;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fantastic! A few more tweaks and I\'ll be an airborne goblin!' WHERE `entry`=11894;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I feel the power of the storm coursing through you!$B$BYou are ready, $N. Let us begin.' WHERE `entry`=11895;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With their robotic minions dealt with, it is time for us to move on to bigger prey. Unfortunately, even now I feel the power of the storm waning from within you.$B$BNevertheless, it served its purpose, and I think that you\'re more than capable of taking the next step without it.' WHERE `entry`=11896;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Without you, Valiance Keep might\'ve not held against the attackers. Thanks to your help we\'ll live to fight another day.' WHERE `entry`=11897;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With the prince defeated, the Scourge presence in Borean Tundra is broken. I have no illusions that they will stay away for long, which is why I must focus on preparing Durm to lead the villagers on their way to Icemist.$B$B<The chieftain shakes his head slowly.>$B$BFor all the disagreements I\'ve had with Durm, I trust his judgment and his abilities. I cannot bring myself to abandon Taunka\'le, so I will defend it until I am slain.' WHERE `entry`=11898;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now we must free the souls that you have captured.' WHERE `entry`=11899;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is worse than I expected.$B$BMalygos is channeling too much power to this place. If he\'s not stopped, Azeroth will be the next Outlands!$B$BFortunately, I believe that I\'ve engineered a temporary solution....' WHERE `entry`=11900;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Northern Coldarra Reading',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Western Coldarra Reading' WHERE `entry`=11900;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your stomach feels uneasy as you approach the grain. The smell is nearly unbearable.' WHERE `entry`=11901;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Those poor lads... they never had a chance!$B$BThis sure sounds like an inside job. Probably a Cult of the Damned infiltrator. Curse those madmen!' WHERE `entry`=11902;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve communicated with the Scourge in the only language they understand: violence and death. Unfortunately they just keep coming!' WHERE `entry`=11903;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, $N. This ore will be of vital importance to the Alliance in the times to come. I\'d like to think we\'ve made a difference today.' WHERE `entry`=11904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. The tremors have already begun to subside.$B$BWith any luck, your efforts have granted us sufficient time to find a way to thwart Malygos\' efforts.' WHERE `entry`=11905;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is the taunka way to leave the land pristine before we move on.$B$BWe will be traveling to our capital, Icemist, very soon. You have helped by allowing us to depart that much more quickly.$B$BThank you.' WHERE `entry`=11906;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N.$B$BWith these odd creatures destroyed, dealing with the rest of the pools should now be a simple matter.$B$BWe owe you a debt of gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=11907;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent!  The information I need should be in here.' WHERE `entry`=11908;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The greatmother breathes a heavy sigh of relief.>$B$BIt is done then... you have saved us! If you hadn\'t stopped him here, then who knows how far this mistake of the gnomes would have spread?$B$BWith the threats from the blue dragons and the Nexus War, not to mention the Lich King, the last thing we need is a mad creation of the Titans running loose!$B$BThank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=11909;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, yes. These shall do nicely.$B$BThank you, $R.' WHERE `entry`=11910;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fascinating!$B$BAnd they\'re aggressive too, you say. That would suggest that some intelligence is behind this manipulation. It may not be natural at all....$B$BPlease, $N, accept this as a token of our gratitude for your efforts. Dalaran will hear of your service.' WHERE `entry`=11911;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, it\'s not much, but it should keep us alive for another day.$B$BI believe you\'ll find this to be a fair price for your efforts.' WHERE `entry`=11912;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, $N. I would hate to see survivors of the attack on Farshire stumble upon plagued grain.' WHERE `entry`=11913;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your service to Dalaran will not go unnoticed, $R.$B$BI hope you find this payment sufficient.' WHERE `entry`=11914;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Greetings. You\'ve come learn some new ways to handle fire?' WHERE `entry`=11915;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I fear that you may be too late, champion. Many of my brothers and sisters have already abandoned Taunka\'le, seeking shelter in the Dragonblight, far to the east.$B$BThere is much work left to be done here and few willing to lend us their strength...' WHERE `entry`=11916;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well. It may seem a small act, but even this can aid the fight as a whole. Take this with my blessing, and return later, as I may have more for you to do.' WHERE `entry`=11917;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Alright, $C, now that you\'ve become familiar with the enemy it\'s time for you to get to work.' WHERE `entry`=11918;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The fate of these young drakes need not burden your conscience, $R. Malygos alone is accountable for this.$B$BI am working ceaselessly to discover the secrets of these runes. We shall take no more lives than we must.' WHERE `entry`=11919;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Cultists? Below deck? I ought to have my whole crew flogged!$B$BListen... why don\'t we have Admiral Cantlebree take care of this... situation?' WHERE `entry`=11920;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done!  You\'ll be a fire juggler faster than the fuse on a ground flower!  Now gird yourself!  The next test is when things really heat up...' WHERE `entry`=11921;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='Quick! There\'s no time to waste!',`ObjectiveText1_loc6`='Braziers Hit' WHERE `entry`=11921;
