UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let me look at those.$B$B<The chronicler examines the artifacts that you have recovered.>$B$BHmph, I\'d say that we\'re lucky you liberated these when you did, $C.$B$BHow very interesting. This artifact here depicts the events of the Sundering. There was a time when Northrend was the far northern portion of Kalimdor.$B$BBut after the Sundering, the land broke off, eventually becoming Northrend.$B$BThis, of course, is why we see Drakkari in the southern continents as well as here.' WHERE `entry`=12650;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, Hemet sent you? We were just about to let him know that we\'ve gotten things up and running here. Please forgive Marvin if he seems to be ignoring you, but he gets very absorbed in his work.' WHERE `entry`=12651;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Num num!' WHERE `entry`=12652;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The cat goddess howls in pain.>$B$BMy spirit cries out in grief at the loss of another friend. But fear not, he will return and his spirit will live on forever.' WHERE `entry`=12653;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You got it! Now all I have to do is make a trophy out of it. That\'ll be the hard part -- finding a way to preserve it so that Hemet doesn\'t have a good laugh at my expense.' WHERE `entry`=12654;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Zim\'Rhuk acknowledges the offerings you intend to place before him, though he knows that you took them from the corpses of others.>$B$B<If you give the offerings to him, he reluctantly agrees to grant you his blessing.>' WHERE `entry`=12655;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Zim\'Rhuk forces an image into your mind of one of his guardians squishing you beneath its foot. Perhaps you should attempt to appease Zim\'Rhuk with more offerings.>' WHERE `entry`=12656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The horns of war will soon echo across this land, waking the dead and calling forth the Scourge war machine. Woe unto those that would stand in our way!$B$BYou and your brethren will lead the charge, $N. When next I look upon the Scarlet lands, my sights will be obscured by the legions of Acherus. The march upon New Avalon begins now.' WHERE `entry`=12657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, these are very nice! I\'ve gotten so tired of robotic squirrels and chickens for company. It\'ll be wonderful to have a pet whose joints won\'t require oiling!' WHERE `entry`=12658;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Aw, me thinkin\' that too funny.$B$B$N is my kind of $R!$B$BYou still got my knife?' WHERE `entry`=12659;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, $R. You\'re proving to be a worthy ally.' WHERE `entry`=12660;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, now... I must admit I\'m more than a little surprised to see you, $N.$B$BTell me what you\'ve learned.' WHERE `entry`=12661;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did it!$B$B<Dagoda gives you a big kiss on the cheek.>$B$BYou have no idea how much of a relief that is to me! Defending against trolls on all sides is really putting a strain on us. Not to mention his incessant yelling.$B$BPlease, $N, take your pick of what we have to offer.' WHERE `entry`=12662;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, now ya be seein\' what we be up against, mon.$B$BGo down, take some time ta learn da land, prepare some strategy. $B$BI\'ll be havin\' some tasks for ya soon.' WHERE `entry`=12663;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, now ya be seein\' what we be up against, mon.$B$BI want ya ta go down, learn da land, mingle with yer bretheren. Prepare yourself...$B$BSoon, dere be much for ya to do. Don\'t ya be disappointin\' me!' WHERE `entry`=12664;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for bringing my kitten back safely.$B$BDeep down I knew it. I wanted to deny it, but your eyes have revealed the truth.$B$BNevertheless, I sense something else. All is not as it seems.' WHERE `entry`=12665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='What seems to be the delay, $N?' WHERE `entry`=12665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The leopard goddess looks saddened at the collection of holy symbols that you have brought before her.>$B$BThere was a time when these meant something. Let\'s see if we can put them to better use.' WHERE `entry`=12666;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$R worm. Tell me why I should not annihilate you where you stand?' WHERE `entry`=12667;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Exquisite. Perhaps you will be of some use after all.' WHERE `entry`=12668;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice work, $N!$B$BDiluting those cauldrons will not only save lives, it will slow the growth of the Scourge in this region.$B$BNow come, tell me what you\'ve learned of Drakuru\'s strategy in Zul\'Drak.' WHERE `entry`=12669;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Do you smell it?$B$B<Valanar sniffs at the air.>$B$BFresh meat... The scent of Scarlet Crusader wafts through the air.$B$B<Valanar salivates.>$B$BApologies, death knight, I\'m sure you\'re not interested in my choice of fine cuisine. You are here to work! To lead the charge! Yes... I know. The Lich King has told me all that I need to know about you, $N.$B$BThe time for bloodshed is now.' WHERE `entry`=12670;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You saved my life up there, $Gbuddy:lassy;. Nice flying!' WHERE `entry`=12671;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They\'ll do. Likely I won\'t even need them.$B$BBut it was fun watching you run around at my command.' WHERE `entry`=12672;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Da crystals be pilin\' up like never before!$B$BYou keep up da good work, $N. I got more tasks for ya real soon.' WHERE `entry`=12673;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The terrible spirit before you lets loose a blood-chilling cackle.>$B$BThey had it coming. And I\'ll give them more of the same again and again and again....' WHERE `entry`=12674;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A portion of my spirit?$B$B<The snow leopard goddess pauses a moment to consider.>$B$BThat\'s quite an expensive gift considering that this is for revenge and I\'m already greatly weakened by the actions of my subduers.$B$BStill, I may know a way.' WHERE `entry`=12675;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent!$B$BYour undercover work has truly paid off, $N.$B$BNow let\'s have a look at that scepter....' WHERE `entry`=12676;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fascinating!$B$BWe\'ll look into the properties of these crystals right away.$B$BNow tell me, $N, what is the latest with this Drakuru fellow?' WHERE `entry`=12677;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Do you feel it, $N? That sensation is raw power coursing through your body. Such a thing cannot exist for mortals.$B$BThe front lines are now dismantled. The geist will finish the job and prepare the grounds for Razuvious. We turn our attention now to more tactical targets.' WHERE `entry`=12678;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, death knight! You feed the Scourge war machine with your deeds!$B$BAh yes, your reward - as promised.' WHERE `entry`=12679;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now for the true test. Can you show mastery over an unbound charger and brutally overtake the thing that you desire most?' WHERE `entry`=12680;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Colvin looks admiringly at the talons you\'ve brought back.>$B$BThese will more than suffice. The gorlocs have a saying that the more gnarled the talon, the more power it holds. I\'m sure the archmage will get his money\'s worth from this expedition.' WHERE `entry`=12681;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful! Here\'s your payment, as agreed. And, uh, a bit of advice: you might want to enjoy long, hot baths the next few days if that \'burning sensation\' persists.' WHERE `entry`=12683;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very well. Let us see if this works....' WHERE `entry`=12684;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The witch doctor shakes his head in disbelief.>$B$BIt sounds like you barely escaped Quetz\'lun\'s underworld alive.$B$BI\'m glad that it\'s you out there. I don\'t know if I would have had the courage to deal with that situation!' WHERE `entry`=12685;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ya done good, $N. You be learnin\' faster than I had hoped.$B$BGo now, get ya some rest. Soon I be givin\' ya an even greater test!' WHERE `entry`=12686;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have succeeded where most initiates fail, $N. For that you will be rewarded handsomely.$B$B<Salanar bows.>' WHERE `entry`=12687;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='You must take the deathcharger by force, $C!' WHERE `entry`=12687;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for freeing Helice and seeing to her safe return. We all started to get worried when she didn\'t return from her crystal hunting trip.' WHERE `entry`=12688;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hi! Really glad see you again!$B$BI knew we friends. I knew it! You good friend. Not just for us, but for all Oracles.$B$BI saw you bonk that puppy-man good! Undead thing said he your friend before? I not know that. You done with puppy-men though, yeah? Just Oracle friend now?$B$BI know you choose right! Thank you for saving us! Thank you, thank you!' WHERE `entry`=12689;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We done it, mon!$B$BI got da chieftains all caged up and you led my abominations to victory over their armies.$B$BIt be time ta celebrate, mon!' WHERE `entry`=12690;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The huge stone key turns with a deep grunt as the coffer lid opens up to reveal hidden treasure inside.' WHERE `entry`=12691;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It good to see you again. I knew you not a traitor, I glad Zepik prove me right.$B$BI hear you Lich Hunter now - that pretty good! You make Harkek proud.' WHERE `entry`=12692;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good to see you again! We worried when you not come back right away.$B$BJaloot beat you back - lot of energy in Jaloot, he pretty fast. He told me how you save him from lich thing. Moodle told me how you save mosswalkers too. You really nice.$B$BI hope you stay with us for while. Always something need doing.' WHERE `entry`=12695;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The professor sent you my way? All right.' WHERE `entry`=12696;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have fought hard to invade the realm of the harvester... Wait.$B$B<Gothik looks at his notes.>$B$BMy apologies, $R. Old habits die hard.$B$BValanar sent you, then? I trust you are somewhat competent.$B$BI do have a gift for the Scarlet dogs. One that is sure to speed up their work in the mines.' WHERE `entry`=12697;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They now know that the mines are no longer safe. They will double their efforts in retreating, leaving their backs open to us!' WHERE `entry`=12698;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have served us well, death knight. Few of your brethren have survived our initial attack upon the Scarlet interlopers. You remain as one of the strongest.$B$B<Prince Valanar nods.>$B$BEast of us, past the Havenshire Mine, is the coast - called Light\'s Point by the Scarlet Crusade. A thousand soldiers stand between us and their ships. Insurmountable? Hardly the point...' WHERE `entry`=12700;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The entire Scarlet fleet wiped out in a matter of minutes! I will receive a commendation from the Lich King for this! All that remains of the Scarlet Crusade now are the denizens of New Avalon.$B$BI\'ll set the fire starters and necromancers upon Havenshire immediately. You will carry my report to the Highlord!' WHERE `entry`=12701;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You good at this.$B$BMaybe someday we just dump Goregek in river so you not have to do this no more.' WHERE `entry`=12702;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ritual went so easy for you!$B$BYou come back later for more killing someday, okay?' WHERE `entry`=12703;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So many good shinies! You good at this.$B$BCome back for more again later, yes?' WHERE `entry`=12704;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Soo-holu strong, huh? I very glad he accept you to share his body for fight.$B$BHe more trusting of people he met before, so maybe come back another time to help more, yes?' WHERE `entry`=12705;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Highlord Mograine reads over the report.>$B$BThe ENTIRE Scarlet fleet?$B$B<Highlord Mograine nods.>$B$BSuch power, $N... I have not seen such a display of domination in years... Since my father wielded...$B$B<Highlord Mograine shakes his head.>$B$BIt\'s not important...$B$BYes, your commendation, lest I forget.' WHERE `entry`=12706;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Score one for the victims, mon!' WHERE `entry`=12707;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That should make them think twice about making more of those things. I shudder to think what it would be like to have to fight an army of those things.$B$B<The element-tamer is thoughtful for a moment.>$B$BI guess it would be just like fighting the endless waves of the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=12708;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just look at all of that!$B$BSee here, $N. This piece you recovered vividly illustrates that the Drakkari became aware of the weakening of the land that the Scourge caused by their presence.$B$BThe warlord felt compelled to take the opportunity this presented. He pushed the prophets to kill their gods in an effort to control the power and fight back against the Lich King\'s forces.$B$BEither way they were doomed. They inadvertently chose to be the instrument of their own destruction!' WHERE `entry`=12709;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, there ya have it, mon.$B$BWe be makin\' da ultimate scourge army ta serve da Lich King. He gunna be most pleased!$B$BYou keep da scepter, $N. You gunna be needin\' it ta command my army in battle....$B$BSoon!' WHERE `entry`=12710;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Atop the mailbox are several illegible letters and scrolls. Useless...$B$BPerhaps you should check inside?' WHERE `entry`=12711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It might have been better if I hadn\'t asked you to bring it back here instead of heading directly to Gundrak.$B$BHowever, I think that it\'s best that you hear what else I have to say first.' WHERE `entry`=12712;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, it is done.$B$BWe still have much to do, but our work here will be much more manageable thanks to your efforts.$B$BPlease accept this as a token of our gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=12713;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Havenshire is ours! A thousand corpses litter the ground, patiently awaiting rebirth. We strike now at our enemy with the awakened strength of the Scourge!$B$BThe ghouls have already begun their assault upon New Avalon. Our forces have moved in behind them and taken the Crypt of Remembrance.' WHERE `entry`=12714;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hail, death knight. I am the blood lord, Keleseth, ruler of the southeastern reaches of Northrend. The Lich King has sought to utilize my talents in ending this mortal affront to the Scourge. As with all things the Lich King asks of me, I am happy to oblige. Of course, a sea of endless souls to sate my thirst certainly sweetened the deal, don\'t you think?' WHERE `entry`=12715;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect! Now give me a moment to get things set up.' WHERE `entry`=12716;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The plague cauldron jumps to life when the skulls are placed inside.$B$BAfter a few seconds some vials of dark liquid float to the top.' WHERE `entry`=12717;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The plague cauldron jumps to life when the skulls are placed inside.$B$BAfter a few seconds, the plague cauldron grants you the dark and frothy splendor of Noth\'s Special Brew.' WHERE `entry`=12718;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The registry will tell us many things about the Scarlet insects.$B$B<Keleseth flips through the pages of the registry.>$B$BDeath rates, births, but most importantly, movement.$B$BLook here, $N, they have already sent three vessels abroad. Let me see here... Where are they headed?$B$B<Keleseth mutters something about latitude and longitude under his breath as he calculates the route.>$B$BWHAT? This is impossible. They sail to Northrend!$B$BBeside the coordinates are the words: "Crimson Dawn."' WHERE `entry`=12719;
