UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What is this? What a boon! They have captured such Light into this artifact, it shines nigh bright as the moon! Our priests will channel this power against our foes, and the Lich King\'s invasion will surely fail. Thank you, $N. Our world tree will be safe.$B$BWhat\'s more, we have sensed that perhaps another world tree grows far to the north, nestled hidden near the Lich King\'s own domain. Perhaps someday... we will shepherd both trees and herald a new era of peace.' WHERE `entry`=12773;
