UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Where both the Alliance and the Horde failed, the Argent Crusade succeeded. The success, however, was short lived. Our breach into Icecrown was quickly - and with force - rebuffed.$B$BThe Lich King\'s retaliatory strike was immediate and brutal. Now we are on the defensive.' WHERE `entry`=13036;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Even the chieftain is beginning to lose his memories? The past is being rewritten before our eyes and if we do not find out who is behind this, the entire legacy of Stormhoof could be lost forever.' WHERE `entry`=13037;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The chieftain\'s spirit told you to bring this to me?$B$B<Xarantaur examines the totem.>$B$BAh, I see what he intended. By telling you to use this totem to close the rifts in the deep, he has given us a clue as to what\'s happening to the timeline. A wise chieftain, this Swiftspear, watching over his people even in death.' WHERE `entry`=13038;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='How many of them could there possibly be? we\'ve killed enough to fill ten graveyards and still they come. The situation looks grim, friend.' WHERE `entry`=13039;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. I will begin the tests on these samples immediately. It is my hope that a cure will be found soon.' WHERE `entry`=13040;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Here is your Dalaran Jewelcrafter\'s Token as promised. I have new shipments going out all the time, check by from time to time to see what I need.' WHERE `entry`=13041;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very interesting. It sounds to me that you handled that perfectly. I\'m surprised that the doctor was using a vargul as an assistant given what he was working on.' WHERE `entry`=13042;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You discovered and put an end to the doctor\'s machinations.$B$B<The banshee-controlled witch smiles and places a large hand gently upon your shoulder.>$B$BThat\'s a fine poke in the eye for the Lich King, but I think we can do better.' WHERE `entry`=13043;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Penumbrius nods.>$B$BMy kin will help. Together we will battle the Lich King and his undead legions.' WHERE `entry`=13044;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Arthas... He strikes recklessly - without care or caution. We have caught him off guard.$B$B<Highlord Tirion Fordring pauses, lost in thought for a moment.>$B$BWe will bolster our defenses and weather the storm.$B$BHow good are you with a cannon, $N?' WHERE `entry`=13045;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='As you anchor the tooth in Arngrim\'s jaw, you get the impression that your efforts may have taken the edge off of the old king\'s hunger pangs... for now.' WHERE `entry`=13046;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='No... it cannot be...$B$BNo one can defeat Thorim in single combat. Not a giant, nor a beast... no one! Especially not that coward of a brother of his.$B$BOn my forefather\'s names, this I swear...$B$BLoken will pay for this!' WHERE `entry`=13047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='Ach, $N! It\'s good to see you, little one.' WHERE `entry`=13047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Xarantaur accepts the Lorehammer from you.>$B$BAt last, we\'ve pinpointed the time of Stormhoof in history. With this knowledge, we can restore the timeline.' WHERE `entry`=13048;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We are fortunate that you have recovered these intact, $N. With them, I can use the Lorehammer to send you back in time, to where the North Wind started to corrupt the true timeline. It\'s the only way we can restore the true history of this place.' WHERE `entry`=13049;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes... these will do. Let us hope my plan works, $N.$B$BVeranus is a great drake. I\'d hate to have to settle for a lesser one.' WHERE `entry`=13050;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to have my old friend back. It appears that my luck is finally starting to change... and it\'s all thanks to you, little friend.' WHERE `entry`=13051;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This hurts bad, mon. Don\'t know if I\'m gonna make it.' WHERE `entry`=13054;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, mon. I might live another day now.' WHERE `entry`=13055;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m already feeling much better, mon. Not sure if it\'s the antidote or the news of that filthy worg getting what he deserved.' WHERE `entry`=13056;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'re here, $N. My brother\'s forces will learn the meaning of defeat today.' WHERE `entry`=13057;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What you have done today will ensure that Stormhoof and his story will never be forgotten. As well, you have written yourself into the pages of Azeroth\'s history. I will remember and record your accomplishments for all eternity.' WHERE `entry`=13058;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $C... thank you!$B$BYou\'ve given me the satisfaction of knowing that the coward who made me into this will rot for all eternity as surely as I will.$B$BNow leave before I lose control of myself and cut you down.' WHERE `entry`=13059;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Olut winces.>$B$BThat looked painful. It was a pretty grand entrance though.$B$BAre you here to help us find a path into Icecrown? As you can see, our first foray in that direction didn\'t end too admirably. I\'m thinking we might be better off breaching the place from another side.' WHERE `entry`=13060;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve really made it this far. Never would I have thought you\'d progress so quickly among the hyldnir.' WHERE `entry`=13061;
