UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Back! Careful! The plague has gripped me and I\'ll not see it spread to you nor anyone else.' WHERE `entry`=13068;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are a true champion for the cause, $N!$B$BWon\'t you please come speak to me again tomorrow? I\'m certain that there will be more of those nasty proto-drakes to shoot down.' WHERE `entry`=13069;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We must be quick or face being overtaken by the Scourge! There\'s really no time for instructions, $R. You\'re just going to have to jump in and hope for the best.' WHERE `entry`=13070;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yay, yay! $N is best proto-drake stealer.$B$BYou come back tomorrow and we make more fire!!!' WHERE `entry`=13071;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Bridenbrad has contracted the plague? I cannot imagine a worse fate for one who has devoted his life to the ways of light, nor can I fathom leaving him to die without lifting a finger to help.$B$BNo, undeath shall not be his fate. We shall find a way to aid this hero.' WHERE `entry`=13072;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello child.$B$BI understand Tirion\'s request and trust in his judgment, we will see what we can do for this Crusader Bridenbrad. What you ask is no simple task - the scourge are not of this world, and many have failed in attempting to strip their corruption over the years.$B$BIn a being of nobility and light, all is not without hope.' WHERE `entry`=13073;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, young one.' WHERE `entry`=13074;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Tirion sent you to Remulos? I\'m... I\'m flattered. One does not call favors in with beings of such power idly, no matter how noble or altruistic they might be. You too are kind to have gone to such lengths on my behalf. You have my thanks.$B$BPlant the seed - I am ready.' WHERE `entry`=13075;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It saddens me to hear that it did not work. No reason to fret though, I have met other beings of good that may still be of aid to us.' WHERE `entry`=13076;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Greetings to you, $R.$B$BThe concern is clear on your face. Please tell me what troubles you.' WHERE `entry`=13077;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With Dahlia\'s Tears and ancient magic, I fashion you some small amount of hope for your great crusader.' WHERE `entry`=13078;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The breath of Alexstrasza... you have gone to the dragon-queen herself? I\'m extremely grateful.$B$BI understand the risks of such cleansing and I am prepared. Proceed, $C.' WHERE `entry`=13079;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Scourge plague is no simple foe to defeat. Alexstrasza\'s words suggest that perhaps we can yet save our Bridenbrad from the unimaginable fate of the unliving should he fall, but I will not give him up so easily.$B$BThere is yet one more path of light I would like to pursue. One more being who might avert this horrible fate.' WHERE `entry`=13080;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<A gentle ringing fills your head as you approach the naaru.>$B$BI know why you have come.' WHERE `entry`=13081;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<As you approach Crusader Bridenbrad, you cannot help but notice that his skin has taken on a pale hue and his breaths are shallow. It is clear that he has little time left.>$B$BYou have returned to me, $C. I must admit... it is good to see you again... your face renews my hope that this land will be free of Arthas\'s grasp one day soon. I\'m proud to have met you...' WHERE `entry`=13082;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am glad you were able to save him from undeath. With A\'dal\'s blessing, he will know no evil in his afterlife.$B$BWe shall take heart in his shining example and in your selflessness. Thank you for all that you have done.' WHERE `entry`=13083;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The duke looks at you a moment and nods.>$B$BYou\'re inflicting horrible mental trauma on the Jotunheim vrykul. This is where they were first reawakened. It is a place of significant importance to them, second only to Ymirheim.$B$BYou must keep up the pressure there while I hold the vault from the assault of the Lich King.' WHERE `entry`=13084;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I think I can guess why you\'re here, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13085;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You handled the cannon like a goblin gunner, friend. You\'ve saved the Vanguard and the Argent Crusade - all the while backing the Highlord himself up on the field of battle! Amazing!' WHERE `entry`=13086;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ya gots me meat!  Here is your recipe, I gots cookin to do!' WHERE `entry`=13087;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That will keep our recruits fed!  Here\'s how you cook it.' WHERE `entry`=13088;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We can quickly turn this flesh into stew.' WHERE `entry`=13089;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I give my thanks to you.' WHERE `entry`=13090;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I have never seen such terror in the eyes of a vrykul. They think themselves masters of their world.$B$BYou and I are going to prove them wrong. Very wrong.' WHERE `entry`=13091;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='And now we shall see what the future holds for you.$B$B<The Bone Witch casts the bones upon the rug in front of her.>$B$BChoose your fate, $C.' WHERE `entry`=13092;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Choose your fate, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13093;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You found it!? Yes, yes, it\'s all here.$B$BPlease, take this with my gratitude. And if it\'s not too much to ask, it would be better for me if Berinand never learned of this.' WHERE `entry`=13094;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You found it!? Yes, yes, it\'s all here.$B$BPlease, take this with my gratitude. And if it\'s not too much to ask, it would be better for me if Berinand never learned of this.' WHERE `entry`=13095;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ya done it?! Gal\'darah be no more?$B$BHere ya go, mon. Take dis gift for bringin\' justice to that wretch.' WHERE `entry`=13096;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lissen up, mon. Dere be dangerous work ta be done!' WHERE `entry`=13097;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Bah\'Kini scans the engraved tablets for a moment, then turns her attention back to you.>$B$BDese be authentic, $R. I\'ll be placin\' dem in their proper place in my collection.$B$BPerhaps we can finally be puttin\' an end to dis behavior.' WHERE `entry`=13098;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Long-time student? Hah!$B$BIf by long-time ya mean my whole life, den I suppose dat be accurate.$B$BTo\'kini be my cowardly father - too fearful to take up a position so near Gundrak... so he sent me!' WHERE `entry`=13099;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This looks great!  Thanks!' WHERE `entry`=13100;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is plenty of food for everyone!  I am sure the customers will be pleased.' WHERE `entry`=13101;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This will be consumed in no time!   Thanks!' WHERE `entry`=13102;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Aha, this appears to be a fine vintage!' WHERE `entry`=13103;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My knowledge of Scourge tactics is without equal.$B$B<The Ebon Watcher peers at you.>$B$BBefore the battle for Light\'s Hope Chapel, my knights and I served under the Lich King - his icy grasp controlling our every action. The light of dawn changed everything...' WHERE `entry`=13104;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your power has grown, my faithful knight.$B$B<Highlord Darion Mograine peers at you.>$B$BVengeance is at hand, $Gbrother:sister;. Koltira aids the Horde upon the gunship, Orgrim\'s Hammer, while Thassarian assists the Alliance aboard the Skybreaker. The Ebon Blade will soon wash over Icecrown and leave the armies of the Lich King in ruin.' WHERE `entry`=13105;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good. We\'ll need all the help we can get. Olakin here is the Argent Crusade\'s contribution to our effort. Let\'s cut the chatter and get down to the business of denying the Scourge their armies of the flesh.' WHERE `entry`=13106;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect!  I Just hope the Dalaran Destroyers finally win one!' WHERE `entry`=13107;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That vile worm is dead?$B$BYou have turned out to be a great boon to my people, little $R.$B$BPlease accept this gift in return for your loyal friendship.' WHERE `entry`=13108;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Volkhan shall haunt the dreams of my people no more.$B$BContinue your efforts, little $R. In time, I am certain my people will grow to forgive Thorim.' WHERE `entry`=13109;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The path of the righteous crusader is one beset by inequity and evil. To cut through the middle is the only salvation. You have done that on this day and much more.' WHERE `entry`=13110;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahh, yeah mon! Dat be what I\'m lookin\' for.$B$BHere ya go - take somethin\' nice for your troubles.' WHERE `entry`=13111;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Is this food from Awilo? Can you promise me there isn\'t any gnome in it?' WHERE `entry`=13112;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My guests should find this acceptable. Just don\'t tell them it came from Awilo.' WHERE `entry`=13113;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Stew looks good. Thanks for your help.' WHERE `entry`=13114;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This wine is quite amazing! I must know where it\'s from.' WHERE `entry`=13115;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect!  I Just hope the Dalaran Destroyers finally win one!' WHERE `entry`=13116;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<You tell the darkrider about your discoveries at the summoning altar.>$B$BI suspected such. We can\'t let this continue. Our first priority is to destroy those summoning altars and then deal with the mess the Scourge has already created here.' WHERE `entry`=13117;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $N. Keeping their numbers down will give the Argent Crusade the time that they need to set a foundation.' WHERE `entry`=13118;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Darkrider Arly nods in approval.>$B$BGood. Now, we can focus our efforts on shutting down the rest of the Fleshwerks.' WHERE `entry`=13119;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Third Summoning Altar destroyed',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Fourth Summoning Altar destroyed' WHERE `entry`=13119;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Darkrider Arly closes her eyes and seems to focus on something far away.>$B$BWith the eyes of death itself, I watch our enemy. With this knowledge, we will utterly destroy them.' WHERE `entry`=13120;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect! It\'s true that Iskalder is rumored to have been the finest vrykul warrior ever to live. And Vardmadra herself is going to come here to judge him!$B$BWe must move quickly if we are to get to this ancient hero before they do!' WHERE `entry`=13121;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now let me see if there\'s something that I can do with these stones to give us a little bit of insight.' WHERE `entry`=13122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Listen well, $R.$B$BYour work here has just begun!' WHERE `entry`=13124;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A hard fought victory, $N! The lieutenants will be replaced, but at least for today the air about Scourgeholme stands still.' WHERE `entry`=13125;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is as I had hoped, $R. We work well together.$B$BMay our continued cooperation be enough to overcome the challenges that yet await!' WHERE `entry`=13126;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Victory is in reach, friend.$B$BFocus, for now comes the true test.' WHERE `entry`=13127;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Raelorasz listens intently to your report.>$B$B$N, this is most welcome news.$B$BNot since the onset of this conflict have we dealt a blow of this magnitude to the Lord of Magic.$B$BPlease, friend, accept the gratitude of our unified dragonflights.' WHERE `entry`=13128;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Mack looks at you and laughs uncontrollably.>$B$BAww noo... Why\'d she hafta run off an\' git \'ershelf killed?$B$BYa know, I should write a lil shong about \'er. That should cheer me up!$B$B<hic>' WHERE `entry`=13129;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Heartwood by nature is resistant to disease, rot and plague. This heartwood, however, goes so far as to repel such things! The masonry, affected by the fallout of the Unbound Thicket, will work in much the same way.$B$BSoon we will break ground.' WHERE `entry`=13130;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Brilliant! Ye\'ve gone and done it, matey.$B$BNow I can show me face to the Cap\'n without fearin\' fer me life, thanks be ta you and yer mates.$B$BHere\'s a little booty fer you in return.' WHERE `entry`=13131;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Splendid! Mebbe now me mateys be able ta rest in peace.$B$BHere ya go, $G lad:lass;. Don\'t let it be said that ol\' Brigg weren\'t generous ta those who showed \'im a kindness.$B$BGood doin\' business wit yeh.' WHERE `entry`=13132;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='He\'s a fine specimen and will serve us well.$B$BNow, we have to make sure to use him properly to trap Vardmadra!' WHERE `entry`=13133;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<A dark, hollow laugh greets you as you report to the darkrider.>$B$BYou reek of victory, $N, and that is good news, indeed.' WHERE `entry`=13134;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, this is perfect. The bomber should be up and running in no time.' WHERE `entry`=13135;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Olakin handles the shards of metal gingerly.>$B$BYou saw these on all of the ghouls down there? I\'ve never seen anything like this in all my battles against the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=13136;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve put Vardmadra aside for the moment. She\'s someplace safe until we can enact our final revenge!' WHERE `entry`=13137;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There is no doubt, this is raw saronite. we\'ve seen weapons made from it in the hands of the Lich King\'s chosen before, but this is the first time it\'s been used to arm anything else. The scale of that mining operation must be huge.' WHERE `entry`=13138;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your assistance has been integral in securing the front. The first true victory of this war is close at hand - which is why our next step is the most crucial.$B$BRest assured, $N, the Scourge will not give up without a fight. Your most difficult challenge awaits.' WHERE `entry`=13139;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These plates match the shards almost exactly. They must be using cuttings from them to "enhance" the ghouls produced here. The Scourge is desperate enough to make a weapon of anything, it seems. All the more reason to hasten our destruction of this abominable place!' WHERE `entry`=13140;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Blessed Light! We have taken the pinnacle! Finally, construction of Justice Keep can begin. Highlord Fordring and the knights are already en route to our new base. You must meet them there, $N!' WHERE `entry`=13141;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Words cannot describe what I\'m feeling at the moment, $N. My revenge is complete and there is naught else for me to do.$B$BIf only I could be there when the Lich King is finally taken down.$B$BDon\'t fool yourself though, Jotunheim is far from \'dealt\' with. I will remain in possession of this witch until such time as the vrykul are no longer a threat.$B$BLook around, there are many items of value in this cave. Take your pick.' WHERE `entry`=13142;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve chained the wretch to the post over there and I\'ll look into getting my hands on more of them.$B$BNow lets make some use of that eye.' WHERE `entry`=13143;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, good. There\'s nothing like the smell of roasted putrid flesh in the morning. That\'s the smell of victory over the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=13144;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work. It seems more death knights remained loyal to Arthas than I initially thought.$B$BHe certainly is sparing nothing in his attempt to replace Acherus. A pure Saronite citadel would be hard to destroy indeed. There\'s no need to destroy it though... we can halt production and put down these death knight leaders here and now, before they become a real threat.$B$BMost importantly, we need to disrupt them enough to get those death knights away from from the leaders so that we can make our strike.' WHERE `entry`=13145;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Icy Lookout explored',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Runeworks explored' WHERE `entry`=13145;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They didn\'t even think to lay a hand on you, did they? At least they\'re predictable.' WHERE `entry`=13146;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='No need to sacrifice our own men when they are this easily manipulated, eh?' WHERE `entry`=13147;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='How did you find this!  Many of these necklaces were looted from one of my shipments a few weeks ago!  Let me repay you with this Jewelcrafter\'s Token.' WHERE `entry`=13148;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, friend. The plagued grain was exposed to Arthas\' troops.$B$BListen carefully, now. There remains more to be done.' WHERE `entry`=13149;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $N.$B$BThe Infinites have been foiled and this thread of history remains intact.$B$BI thank you for your invaluable assistance, as does the entire Bronze Dragonflight.' WHERE `entry`=13151;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Dakrider Arly throws her head back and laughs darkly.>$B$BA fitting end for the \'good\' doctor, wouldn\'t you say?' WHERE `entry`=13152;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Augh. It\'s still dripping. Couldn\'t you have at least dried it off first?' WHERE `entry`=13153;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! This will help fuel the flames of war for days to come.' WHERE `entry`=13154;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Vile Hold... a testament to how much Arthas hates losing. Let\'s drive the blade deep.' WHERE `entry`=13155;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! This will help protect our troops against the cold.' WHERE `entry`=13156;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A long and arduous journey awaits us as we make our way to the gates of Icecrown Citadel. I, and the soldiers of the Argent Crusade, wish to thank you for all that you have done. We rest easier knowing that you will fight alongside us in this cursed place.$B$B<Highlord Tirion Fordring salutes.>' WHERE `entry`=13157;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not a moment too soon.$B$BAre you prepared to defend Dalaran, $C?' WHERE `entry`=13158;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The crisis is averted, then?$B$BThat is good news indeed. I will forward the news on to Rhonin.$B$BPlease, accept this with the gratitude of Dalaran.' WHERE `entry`=13159;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not so much of a threat when they\'re sleeping.' WHERE `entry`=13160;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The world will be a much better place without Rokir in it - trust me.' WHERE `entry`=13161;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can\'t deny, I\'ll miss her laugh... and that smile that would creep onto her face just before she killed someone. A little less need to watch my back though, so I suppose I can\'t complain.' WHERE `entry`=13162;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So he finally lost? Good to hear.' WHERE `entry`=13163;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Morgraine himself arrived to see the deed done then? I imagine there was some ill blood between those two - no surprise that he wanted a piece of the wretch.$B$BYou\'ve done exceedingly well, $R, and you shall be awarded appropriately. The Ebon Blade thanks you.' WHERE `entry`=13164;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Lich King has returned to Northrend, wounded by the Ashbringer, but the second floor still holds the last of his armies.' WHERE `entry`=13165;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, death knight. The remaining Scourge will be dealt with in short order and the rebuilding process will begin anew.$B$BI have but one last task for you.' WHERE `entry`=13166;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<A fierce glow emanantes from all of Kilix\'s eyes as he stares at the husk.>$B$BIt is DONE!$B$B$R! Your name shall be recorded in the history of our people.$B$BI am in your debt....' WHERE `entry`=13167;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nothing to it, eh? Any intelligent being should have little trouble controlling lesser undead. I suspect only the likes of a true necromancer could use these to sieze control of any of the more powerful undead. That won\'t be a problem though - I can already think of quite a variety of destruction we can wreak with even the most paltry minions.$B$BShall we have at it then?' WHERE `entry`=13168;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='The options of subterfuge made available to us with the eyes are obvious. These will be very useful tools.' WHERE `entry`=13168;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Put them right to sleep, didn\'t it?' WHERE `entry`=13169;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Without even getting your hands dirty.' WHERE `entry`=13170;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work. We should have little threat in the air then.' WHERE `entry`=13171;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Practically defenseless. It doesn\'t get much easier than that.' WHERE `entry`=13172;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let\'s see here... what do we have...$B$B<Keritose buries his head in the papers for a bit, seemingly gleaning little that he did not already know. Suddenly he finds what he is looking for...>$B$BMalykriss! The Vile Hold. It seems Arthas did not take the loss of his death knights so well... I\'m not exactly sure what he\'s doing with all of that Saronite, but I have a feeling he might be overcompensating for something.$B$BThat boy is not used to losing.' WHERE `entry`=13174;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Glorious! Truly, you are among the champions of the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=13177;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lok\'tar! Victory for the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=13178;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Glorious! Truly, you are among the champions of the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=13179;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lok\'tar! Victory for the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=13180;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just what I wanted to hear! A victory in Lake Wintergrasp - even a temporary one - is crucial to our overall strategy against the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=13181;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='Do you bring word of victory?' WHERE `entry`=13181;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It saddens me to see that things have come to this. If only we could return our great empire to what it once was...' WHERE `entry`=13182;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is a truly great thing you have accomplished this day. Be recognized for your sacrifice!' WHERE `entry`=13183;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='What news do you bring?' WHERE `entry`=13183;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good job. Murp wish he was there to help.' WHERE `entry`=13185;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. That should slow down their assault.' WHERE `entry`=13186;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $C.$B$BMay your deeds renew hope for our people, that someday we may reclaim the city of our ancestors.' WHERE `entry`=13187;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Varian stares off into the distance.>$B$BIndeed old friend... Blood and honor.$B$B<Varian affixes his gaze upon you.>$B$BWere it not for this letter from Tirion, you would be a stain upon my floor. Only an endorsement from one of the greatest paladins to ever live could have ensured your survival.$B$BWe... We will work together against the Scourge. Against the Lich King!$B$BGLORY TO THE ALLIANCE!' WHERE `entry`=13188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Eitrigg is alive because of this paladin. He would have been executed had Lord Fordring not broken him out of Stratholme.$B$BTirion Fordring, to have sacrificed everything to save the life of an orc... I have ever only known one other human to make such a sacrifice.$B$B<Thrall blinks back a tear.>$B$BYou will be in my heart always, Taretha.$B$BYes. For Tirion Fordring and for Eitrigg! We will accept you as a member of the Horde and your order as allies.$B$BBlood and honor! For the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=13189;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahah!$B$BMay the mocking scent of failure eat at their empty souls!$B$BThank you, $C. Today, you have struck a blow against the unliving.' WHERE `entry`=13190;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! This will help us defeat the Alliance in the battles to come!' WHERE `entry`=13191;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ooh, ya dats da stuff, mon!' WHERE `entry`=13192;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, I guess its another night of sharpening bones for me. Why didn\'t I stay in Silvemoon City like my brother?' WHERE `entry`=13193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, this will go far to treat our soldier\'s wounds.' WHERE `entry`=13194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! This will help protect our troops against the cold.' WHERE `entry`=13195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! This will help fuel the flames of war for days to come.' WHERE `entry`=13196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! This will help fuel the flames of war for days to come.' WHERE `entry`=13197;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Augh. It\'s still dripping. Couldn\'t you have at least dried it off first?' WHERE `entry`=13198;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, I guess its another night of sharpening bones for me. Why didn\'t I stay in Silvemoon City like my brother?' WHERE `entry`=13199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! That should put a dent in their war machines!' WHERE `entry`=13200;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, this will go far to treat our soldier\'s wounds.' WHERE `entry`=13201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ooh, ya dats da stuff, mon!' WHERE `entry`=13202;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Do you have any idea what you\'ve been carrying around, $C?$B$BThe cave beasts you\'ve been harvesting have no traditional method of excreting their waste. You might want to wash your hands...$B$BThank you for the thought, but if you come across any more of these please keep them for yourself.' WHERE `entry`=13204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Mordun whistles.>$B$BWill ya just look at \'em? Incredible.$B$BI half expected these neanderthals to be swingin\' around clubs and throwin\' rock.$B$BNo such luck...' WHERE `entry`=13205;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Marrah has informed us of the superiority of the Vrykul\'s weaponry. We\'ll have a look at these and see if there\'s anything to learn.$B$BTake this for your trouble, $C.' WHERE `entry`=13206;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Always more questions than answers, eh, $G lad:lass;?' WHERE `entry`=13207;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Crusader Olakin Sainrith listens solemnly to your report.>$B$BIt is not the burial they deserved, but it is better than nothing, and better for those who yet live. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13211;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, I suppose it\'s good that we\'ve "recovered" the crusader, though I doubt his comrades had this in mind. Let\'s see what we can do to get him back on his feet so we can get this charade over with and complete our mission here.' WHERE `entry`=13212;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have bested our finest warriors. Your name is renowned, $N.$B$BPerhaps you think that this concerns me: it does not. If they can fall to you then they are not worthy and should be nothing but lowly vargul!$B$BBut perhaps I can give you and your friends different sport. Valhalas is also a place for combat of all types with many different kinds of foes.$B$BSpeak to me again when you and your friends are ready to proceed. We shall see if you are truly worthy.' WHERE `entry`=13213;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='New blood.$B$B<The vrykul death knight spits on the ground at your feet.>$B$BYou all think that you have what it takes to fight here.$B$BYou are nothing before the might of the vrykul and the Scourge!$B$BStill, you did manage to defeat six incompetent corpses, so you must have some skill in you. Not likely enough for the next challenge though.' WHERE `entry`=13214;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You want me to be impressed by the fact that you and your friends were able to bring down a lone Nerubian priest?$B$BGet out of my sight before I summon my ghouls upon you!' WHERE `entry`=13215;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The defeat of one of the hyldnir is mildly impressive, $R, but you did have the help of your friends.$B$BYou\'re lucky that her drake didn\'t get involved.' WHERE `entry`=13216;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m starting to respect your prowess in the ring, $N. Now I really don\'t like you.$B$BI would much rather have preferred to see you and your friends stuck to the bottom of that flesh giant\'s foot!' WHERE `entry`=13217;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I don\'t know what trickery it was that you used to bring down the thane -- I couldn\'t see it from this angle -- but I can assure you that you will not survive your next match.$B$BYes, I know who it is. Run, little $R. Flee to the far corners of the world.$B$BOr stay and die. It matters little to me.' WHERE `entry`=13218;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your defeat of Prince Sandoval sickens me. An unwashed peasant such as yourself should have willingly given over $G his : her; life simply for the chance to meet him and kneel at his feet.$B$BYou\'ve earned your damned reward. Be quick about your choosing.' WHERE `entry`=13219;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Olakin should consider himself fortunate. No one is rescued from the Scourge, no one. No amount of thread and heroism will save him a second time. I\'ll make certain he remembers it.' WHERE `entry`=13220;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank the Light. I\'d thought Father Kamaros dead, or worse. Through your bravery and compassion, you have restored a great ally to the Argent Crusade. You have my thanks and those of the crusade.' WHERE `entry`=13221;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That should show them the power of Gnomish invention!' WHERE `entry`=13222;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good job. Murp wish he was there to help.' WHERE `entry`=13223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Korm salutes.>$B$BDamn the Scourge and damn the Alliance! Hork was one of our best. We will have our revenge. For Hellscream and for the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=13224;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Captain Bartlett salutes.>$B$BHe was a damn fine soldier. Damn the Horde and damn the Scourge!' WHERE `entry`=13225;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My faithful knights have served me well. It seems that their recruitment efforts have yielded a hero!' WHERE `entry`=13226;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My faithful knights have served me well. It seems that their recruitment efforts have yielded a hero!' WHERE `entry`=13227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They saw the Alliance assaulting the gate and they attacked them from behind...$B$B<After a brief pause, Korm bursts into laughter.>$B$BTHAT is what it means to be HORDE!$B$BWere it not for them, the Alliance maggots would likely be holding that gate!$B$BTheir boldness has bought us precious time.' WHERE `entry`=13228;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well. We thought Father Kamaros lost, for certain. Your bravery will serve as an example to all those who oppose the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=13229;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The time of tolerance for the Alliance has passed, $N.$B$BThey have earned our hatred! They shall live in fear of the Horde until they no longer pollute our world!' WHERE `entry`=13230;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc6`='Dying Alliance Soldiers Slain' WHERE `entry`=13230;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So... It was a rout - a total loss. This shall not be forgotten.$B$BMark my words, $C. The Horde shall pay for this... there will be no mercy!' WHERE `entry`=13231;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That was a difficult thing you did, $C. But it was the right thing.$B$BDon\'t allow the memory of your actions to haunt you. Harness that sorrow and pain you feel! Direct it at those who caused it.$B$BThe Horde must pay!' WHERE `entry`=13232;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc6`='Dying Soldiers Slain' WHERE `entry`=13232;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N!$B$BHunt them down and make them pay!' WHERE `entry`=13233;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $C.$B$BSoon, the Alliance shall run from you in fear and the Horde shall honor your name!' WHERE `entry`=13234;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With the Lich King\'s flesh giant champion defeated, he must know that the rest of his forces are vulnerable as well. With you by our side, we will teach the Lich King the meaning of fear once more.' WHERE `entry`=13235;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The prince\'s true power wasn\'t his ability to make armies out of corpses... that was easy$B$BBut killing his own men, with whom he\'d shared many battles... the prince\'s true power was his ability to do what had to be done.' WHERE `entry`=13236;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Really, $C?$B$BNothing notable to report?$B$BI beg to differ...' WHERE `entry`=13237;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Too busy? Phooey! This baby flies herself!$B$BNevermind that. You\'ll do...' WHERE `entry`=13238;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wahooo! I saw them light up all the way from here! I\'ll just chalk that up as another success and begin bottling this stuff up for the invasion - of course it might need a little more testing as we go if you\'re at all interested....' WHERE `entry`=13239;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The archmage nods even before you say a word.>$B$BI know. You destroyed the constructs as I foresaw and were then able to go on to fight Varos Cloudstrider.$B$BExcellently done, $N!' WHERE `entry`=13240;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Outstanding work, $N.$B$BWithout having done so, the surviving berserkers would surely have swarmed you during your fight with the king.' WHERE `entry`=13241;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Saurfang looks to the heavens.>$B$BLike Brox, my son died a hero. Do not mourn him, $N. For an orc, there could be no better end! No greater honor! At this moment, my heart swells with pride.$B$BI thank you for returning our battle armor. It will be placed upon his pyre at the Ancestral Grounds of Nagrand.$B$BWe must turn our full attention to more pressing matters.' WHERE `entry`=13242;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We are saved for now. Thank you.$B$BUnfortunately due to the nature of their interference, the Infinite\'s will have almost unlimited opportunity to do so again.$B$BWhat I can discern is that in the future, you are at the heart of the struggle to stop them, $N!' WHERE `entry`=13243;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We are all in your debt, $N.$B$BIf I am certain of anything, it is that you have not failed us, nor will you in the future!' WHERE `entry`=13244;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very well. Just put the axe down over by the wall.$B$BI\'m sure that Valgarde and Vengeance Landing will rest easier tonight knowing that you have dealt with that savage.' WHERE `entry`=13245;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Regrettable, but extremely necessary.$B$BThe Kirin Tor could ill afford a prominent red dragon falling into the hands of our greatest enemy. Malygos\'s use of her against us in the Nexus War would have been devastating.$B$BI simply regret that we couldn\'t have saved her instead.' WHERE `entry`=13246;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. The examination of that tuner should provide us with further insights into how Malygos is manipulating the ley lines.$B$BIf we can find a weakness in his approach, we might be able to exploit it and turn the tide.' WHERE `entry`=13247;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The archmage somberly nods as you hand him the rather large piece of jewelry.>$B$BWhat\'s done is done. Such a noble race these vrykul. It is unfortunate that the Lich King has sunk his deathly hooks into them.' WHERE `entry`=13248;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With any luck, now that it\'s leaderless, Drak\'Tharon Keep will now prove less of a thorn in the side of those fighting against the Scourge in the region.$B$B<The archmage looks down at the tiki in your hand.>$B$BIt\'s just as well that the tiki has lost its mojo. I wouldn\'t have the first idea about how to use it, or even if it would be proper to do such a thing.' WHERE `entry`=13249;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. I will see to it that the very essence of the god is kept safe until it can be handed over to the Zandalar tribe.$B$BPerhaps they\'ll be able to find a way to reincorporate Akali from it?' WHERE `entry`=13250;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Amazing! I\'ve never quite seen anything like it. I will see to it that it gets into the proper hands within the Violet Citadel.$B$BIf only you\'d been allowed to change the course of history. Perhaps if Arthas had been kept from... no, down that path leads madness.$B$BSurely the Keepers of Time know best in these matters.' WHERE `entry`=13251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Is not Titan technology amazing? The information is contained within the disc itself!$B$BI only hope that we can figure out a way to get it out of the disc.' WHERE `entry`=13252;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Archmage Lan\'dalock breathes a sigh of relief.>$B$BTo be honest, I feared the worst had befallen you. It\'s difficult to stand idly by while others, such as yourself, deal with the matters of life and death which confront our world seemingly on a daily basis.$B$BNow what are we going to do with that gigantic ring?' WHERE `entry`=13253;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What horrors you must have faced while traversing the Upper City.$B$B<Lan\'dalock glances down at the tarnished crown clutched in your fist.>$B$BPerhaps we should put that aside for their new king whenever the nerubians decide to coronate one?' WHERE `entry`=13254;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The archmage eyes the brain warily.>$B$BNow that I think of it, I\'m not quite sure that it\'s safe to be so near to that thing. You say that it\'s still alive?$B$B<He shakes his head.>$B$BWe have a place for such things in the citadel. I\'ll see to it that one of my apprentices takes it there straight away.' WHERE `entry`=13255;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The danger is over and the rest of the prisoners that had broken free are being imprisoned once more.$B$BDalaran owes you a debt of gratitude, $N!$B$BNow I need to go speak with someone about why it was so easy to bypass the city\'s anti-teleportation protections within the prison?!' WHERE `entry`=13256;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The demon lord, Varimathras, and the Forsaken\'s chief apothecary, Putress, are responsible for this betrayal.$B$B<Thrall nods.>$B$BYes, the same Putress responsible for discovering the cure for the recent Scourge plague outbreak.$B$BThose that would not side with their regime have been executed or banished. Sylvanas was nearly killed in the coup.$B$BThe Horde has lost the Undercity. Orgrimmar will take on the Forsaken refugees until there is a resolution to this crisis. For now we are under martial law.' WHERE `entry`=13257;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just in time, $N. Koltira spoke highly of you. Perhaps you\'ll be able to push the scales in our favor.' WHERE `entry`=13258;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You made quick work of the Scourge, $N. Let\'s finish what we came to do here.' WHERE `entry`=13259;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Koltira looks you up and down.>$B$BI hope for your sake that you\'re up to this, $C.' WHERE `entry`=13260;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='No good!$B$BKorm kept telling me he was too busy and when I finally got him to come topside and have a look, you had already used the last of the oil. Now he\'s ticked at me and won\'t even allow me in his presence again until tomorrow...$B$BCome back then and we\'ll try again!' WHERE `entry`=13261;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These bombs look pretty potent. They should at least put a dent in the surrounding structure.' WHERE `entry`=13262;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This pulsing object is covered in a thick layer of ice. It shimmers strangely beneath the water.' WHERE `entry`=13263;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You see, $C?$B$BIngenuity can sometimes even the odds against a seemingly overwhelming enemy.' WHERE `entry`=13264;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='May you slay many humanoids and take their cloth.' WHERE `entry`=13265;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let me get you up to speed, $N.$B$BUndercity is a war-zone. Putress\' apothecaries and Varimathras\' demons have seized control. They\'ve taken a defensive position inside and are using that damned blight against our troops.' WHERE `entry`=13266;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Tomorrow brings with it uncertainty. Gone are the days of Alliance and Horde battling alongside each other in pursuit of a common enemy. A new battle dawns, $N - a battle in which there can be no victor.$B$BBut we must continue our march towards Icecrown. We have no choice in that matter. Our salvation lies with heroes like you, $N. The future of the Horde - of the world - depends on you.$B$BLet us return to Orgrimmar. You must return to Northrend at once.' WHERE `entry`=13267;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Come back when you have the skill and I can provide all of your tailoring training.' WHERE `entry`=13268;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='May you slay many humanoids and take their cloth.' WHERE `entry`=13269;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='May you slay many humanoids and take their cloth.' WHERE `entry`=13270;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I saw him get rid of it, you know? He threw it all the way down here.$B$BSaid he wouldn\'t need it anymore. Said it made him weak.' WHERE `entry`=13271;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='May you slay many humanoids and take their cloth.' WHERE `entry`=13272;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ruined? What d\'you mean, the camp\'s been ruined?$B$B<Brann clenches his fists in anger,>$B$BThose iron dwarves will pay for this! There\'s little we can do now, and we have to focus on finishing the key. But once I get into the halls of Ulduar, the irons and their masters will answer for what they\'ve done!' WHERE `entry`=13273;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is really it! The key is almost within our grasp. All we need now is a way to combine the shell and the core into a single key. Let\'s see what Prospector Soren had to say about this...' WHERE `entry`=13274;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What are you waiting for? You have to rub it on you!$B$BQuick! Or he\'ll see you!' WHERE `entry`=13275;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see your skills with the abominations are developing nicely.$B$BBe diligent, friend, and soon the gate will belong to the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=13276;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. These look to be usable samples.$B$BTime again to use the enemy\'s strength against them....' WHERE `entry`=13277;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $C.$B$BPerhaps with some investigation, we can discover how they are bringing such a creature into existence.' WHERE `entry`=13278;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $C.$B$BWhen our armies arrive to march on the Citadel, we will have a solid plan in place for taking the death gate.' WHERE `entry`=13279;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='YOU DID IT! YOU DID IT!$B$B<Frazzle jumps and gives you a big hug.>$B$BOh, you\'re just my favorite hero ever!$B$BYou think you could come back again tomorrow?' WHERE `entry`=13280;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='One less plague cauldron to account for when the battle commences.$B$BYour commander will be pleased.' WHERE `entry`=13281;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N! We thought you were dead!$B$BWe lost a few men in that explosion... but we sure put a hurt on the Scourge. They\'re scrambling their forces back to the citadel and leaving big gaps in their defenses. It\'s time to push forward.' WHERE `entry`=13282;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew you were the right $R for the job!$B$BI gotta admit that right now you\'re my favorite $C of all time!$B$BWhat do you say to a repeat performance again tomorrow? I can make it worth your while!' WHERE `entry`=13283;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have my thanks.$B$BThis has been a brutal operation, but we haven\'t had any great options otherwise - they\'re being equally as unforgiving to our aerial assault. We need to route these vrykul if we\'re going to stand any chance of pressing on in Icecrown.$B$BWe\'re likely to need more help later. Please lend yourself to the battle again should the chance present itself.' WHERE `entry`=13284;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Boktar nods in approval as you tell him how you helped Brann recover the pieces of the keystone and combine them.>$B$BBrann may prove to be just the ally we need to discover what is truly happening in Ulduar. You\'ve done well in aiding him. We need all the help we can get against this Loken and his iron dwarf minions.' WHERE `entry`=13285;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It was wise of Captain Bartlett to send you.$B$BWhile he frets over your conflict with the Horde, someone must remain exclusively focused on the real mission here - the march on Icecrown Citadel.$B$BWho better to direct your efforts than a former servant of the Lich King?' WHERE `entry`=13286;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Really, $C?$B$BNothing notable to report?$B$BI beg to differ...' WHERE `entry`=13287;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You see, $C?$B$BIngenuity can sometimes even the odds against a seemingly overwhelming enemy.' WHERE `entry`=13288;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see your skills with the abominations are developing nicely.$B$BBe diligent, friend, and soon the death gate will belong to the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=13289;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Cappy sent you in his place, did he?$B$BVery well, $C. Roll up those sleeves... time to get to work!' WHERE `entry`=13290;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good news!$B$BI\'ve managed to reproduce the solution - hardly an accomplishment, of course.$B$BDoubt I\'ll live to see the day those neanderthal goblins cook up somethin\' a gnome can\'t recreate in his sleep!' WHERE `entry`=13291;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good show! Good show indeed. You\'re turning into a regular wyrmslayer!$B$BCome back when you\'re ready to thin their numbers even further.' WHERE `entry`=13292;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh man, am I glad to see you! Did the chief send you down from the Hammer?' WHERE `entry`=13293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Thassarian on the Skybreaker wants you to bring him 5 Pustulant Spines from the Pustulant Horrors on Mord\'rethar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. These look to be usable samples.$B$BTime again to use the enemy\'s strength against them....' WHERE `entry`=13294;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $C.$B$BWhen our armies arrive to march on the Citadel, we will have a solid plan in place for taking the death gate.' WHERE `entry`=13295;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Did the chief send you down from the Skybreaker? Isn\'t that thing sweet?!' WHERE `entry`=13296;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='One less plague cauldron to account for when the battle commences.$B$BYour captain will be highly pleased.' WHERE `entry`=13297;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $C.$B$BPerhaps with some investigation, we can discover how they are bringing such a creature into existence.' WHERE `entry`=13298;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Their being driven insane? Voices in their heads?$B$BVoices in your head?!$B$BI want you to clear your mind of the taint that has crept into that place, boy.$B$BWe\'ll try to get the remainder of them out of there again tomorrow when you\'ve had a chance to rest.' WHERE `entry`=13300;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have my thanks.$B$BThis has been a brutal operation, but we haven\'t had any great options otherwise - they\'re being equally as unforgiving to our aerial assault. We need to route these vrykul if we\'re going to stand any chance of pressing on in Icecrown.$B$BWe\'re likely to need more help later. Please lend yourself to the battle again should the chance present itself.' WHERE `entry`=13301;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Their being driven insane? Voices in their heads?$B$BVoices in your head?!$B$BI want you to clear your mind of the taint that has crept into that place, boy.$B$BWe\'ll try to get the remainder of them out of there again tomorrow when you\'ve had a chance to rest.' WHERE `entry`=13302;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Demolisher has seen better days, but the structure hasn\'t suffered any permanent damage. The parts you obtained should be enough to get it running again, at least temporarily.' WHERE `entry`=13304;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You see? You killed your fair share, but for every one you destroyed, another rose from the dirt to take its place$B$BYou don\'t know what you\'re up against, $N. Let me show you.' WHERE `entry`=13305;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Koltira nods curtly.>$B$BGood. It\'s not much protection, but it\'s better than nothing. That gate is still the perfect choke point if the Scourge commanders know what they\'re doing. We must gain control of as much of the surrounding area as possible.' WHERE `entry`=13306;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have removed the Scourge banner-bearers and their minions? Good. Our preparations must continue.' WHERE `entry`=13307;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Another wave of euphoria, mixed with some pain, crashes through your mind as you approach the creature.>$B$BGood... good! So that you know I am being fair, I will first give you your reward as promised.$B$BAnd then you will willingly hand me the key.' WHERE `entry`=13308;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Ground Commander Koup at the edge of the glacier east of Ymirheim has ordered you to use the Skybreaker Suppression Turret to keep the Skybreaker Troop Transport alive long enough to make all of its drops.',`objectives_loc6`='Ground Commander Koup at the edge of the glacier east of Ymirheim has ordered you to use the Skybreaker Suppression Turret to keep the Skybreaker Troop Transport alive long enough to make all of its drops.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, soldier. We could use more able bodies like you around here - stop by another day if the operation hasn\'t wrapped up.' WHERE `entry`=13309;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Only partly useless then. Good work.' WHERE `entry`=13310;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are quickly becoming a master of the quill. The tarot cards are of great interest to the Darkmoon Faire, so do not hesitate to call upon us if you manage to create more. We are not without our own skilled tradesmen, so please allow us to offer something in trade for the cards.' WHERE `entry`=13311;
