UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect! Thank you so much. I would hate to lose more records of our culture to war - far too much has been sacrificed already.' WHERE `entry`=13505;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='"Another?" They have more than one. I will not leave any of my people to be tortured, we must act quickly.' WHERE `entry`=13506;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work. One more threat we can worry a bit less about. We\'ll continue the offensive while they are still off-guard.' WHERE `entry`=13507;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You\'re here... to save me? A bit later... than I hoped.' WHERE `entry`=13508;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The trolls are building their forces and supplies at the war camp to the north. When they feel they are ready, they will almost certainly launch their attack on Lor\'danel from that location. It shouldn\'t take us long to route this rabble, but I\'m not one for taking unnecessary risks.$B$BI want you to fight your way into the war camp and set fire to any stockpiles of supplies that you see. The setback should buy us quite a bit of time before they can muster a counterattack.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work. That should slow them down a bit.' WHERE `entry`=13509;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Some sort of shield you say? We might have a way around that. Balthule had an idea for breaking whatever protective enchantments their shaman had, so it might work on this too. Thank you for saving Aynasha and bringing me this information - it may well make the difference in our battle.' WHERE `entry`=13510;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Alanndarian is dead then. That saddens me greatly, but it is not entirely unexpected. I expect no mercy from these savages, and will show them none.' WHERE `entry`=13511;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve shown a great deal of talent for one so young. Good work. It seems the final battle is before us.' WHERE `entry`=13512;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Retrieve 6 Shatterspear Amulets.',`objectives_loc6`='Retrieve 6 Shatterspear Amulets.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='These will do perfectly. I will prepare them for Sandrya - you are sure to be dispatched to meet with her shortly.' WHERE `entry`=13513;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You performed excellently up there! We are fortunate to have you with us. I haven\'t yet received word regarding their leader. If you haven\'t spoken with Sandrya at the cave in the back of the vale, be sure to do so before you depart.' WHERE `entry`=13514;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Speak to Sandrya Moonfall to start the attack, and aid her in killing Jor\'kil the Soulripper',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='We owe a great debt to you for all that you\'ve done to see this battle through. Not often can we claim victories so decisively, but it seems there\'s far more to this plot than just the Shatterspear. If you haven\'t already checked his body for information, make sure to do so before you leave.' WHERE `entry`=13515;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $C. Some of them surely would not have made it without you.$B$BWe\'ll be taking the wounded to the main building once we have them all safely back in town. Perhaps you can meet us there later?' WHERE `entry`=13518;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Shaldyn rescued',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Volcor rescued' WHERE `entry`=13518;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well, $N. The Twilight\'s Hammer is a dangerous cult. It would be foolish to underestimate the danger they represent.' WHERE `entry`=13519;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This will do perfectly. Thank you so much! I suspect they will want to thank you personally should they recover, so perhaps you can stop by later on.' WHERE `entry`=13520;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Lovely! I hope you didn\'t kill too many of them. We\'re not trying to wipe out the population, we just need to get to the source of this corruption quickly! I\'m proceeding with the analysis now.' WHERE `entry`=13521;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your efforts are very much appreciated. Since the Cataclysm, the elementals have been out of control. We have little hope of taking back Auberdine without extinguishing their presence first.' WHERE `entry`=13522;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve succeeded... it hasn\'t all been in vain... My time approaches. Go now, $N, and may Elune protect you.' WHERE `entry`=13523;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Why have you come here, outsider? The elf is right. The forces of Felwood have seeped into Darkshore and sickened my people.' WHERE `entry`=13525;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are poor, weak stalks, but they are all we have. The corruption spreads quickly, even among the plants of the forest.' WHERE `entry`=13526;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This definitely looks like the stuff they were eating. Let me take a closer peek...' WHERE `entry`=13527;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' The results are coming in now. We should have some information on how the bears contracted this in just a moment.' WHERE `entry`=13528;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is done then. Thank you. I only hope that the wildlife here will see more peace with his passing.' WHERE `entry`=13529;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It looks like fishing\'s your thing. My belly appreciates the gift. I\'m thinking you would get more use out of this pole than I would. Have at it.' WHERE `entry`=13537;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I heard the explosion from here! Excellent job - we\'ve already begun rerouting the power into the Titan relic to super-charge our own forces.' WHERE `entry`=13538;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now in order to kill the enemy, our men must be roused to anger; that there may be advantage from defeating the enemy, they must have their rewards. I hope that these are sufficient for your service to the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=13539;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I cannot thank you enough, $N. Now we\'ll have a fighting chance to retake the ruins as soon as we are in better health.' WHERE `entry`=13542;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Without those three coaxing them, perhaps the flow of elementals into the Ruins of Auberdine will be stemmed.$B$BThank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13543;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This is exactly what we needed. The bear\'s spirit favors us and there may be hope for my brothers after all.' WHERE `entry`=13544;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well. My people have begun to emerge from their madness, but they will fall back into it if we do not deal with the source of the corruption.' WHERE `entry`=13545;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. You are a hero to my people. Without you, we would be doomed to madness and death. May the bear spirit always watch over you.' WHERE `entry`=13546;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So much death and pain. Can there be any doubt that there is more yet to come?$B$BAll I wish to do is move onward into the Goddess\'s embrace as do these others.$B$BBut first, let us see if we can keep even more misery and destruction from being spread.' WHERE `entry`=13547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Taldan\'s spirit coaxed',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Caylais Moonfeather\'s spirit coaxed' WHERE `entry`=13547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Candy buckets like this are located in inns throughout the realms. Go ahead... take some!' WHERE `entry`=13548;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very fine specimens indeed, $N! These are sure to provide many hours of curious speculation amongst my colleagues back home.' WHERE `entry`=13549;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This should be plenty! Thanks so much! I\'ll get working on a cure for this nastiness immediately.' WHERE `entry`=13554;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='One, two, three,... hehe, that be a good number o\' them, mon! Now we be safe for quite some time!' WHERE `entry`=13556;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am pleased to hear that you were able to free some of the remaining wildlife. With a bit of good fortune, we will find the cure for the corruption that the others have faced before any more of them die.' WHERE `entry`=13557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc6`='Uncorrupted animals freed' WHERE `entry`=13557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yalda? The spirits of others from the Ruins of Auberdine?$B$B<The druid ponders what you\'ve conveyed about your adventure in the ruins.>$B$BI remember them all. They will be dearly missed, but they have moved on into the Goddess\'s embrace and that is for the best.$B$BAnde\'thoras-ethil, may your troubles be diminished, $N!' WHERE `entry`=13558;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Sons of Hodir accept your tribute, small one. You continue to prove your worth as an ally in more ways than one.' WHERE `entry`=13559;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The decoys worked then? Great to hear it! Don\'t you worry yourself one bit about the treasures. Me and Gary will take care of the rest this time around. Truth be told, if something went wrong again and I lost any more of you adventurer types, I\'m pretty sure they\'d kick me out of town.' WHERE `entry`=13560;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have my thanks. Though they may not be able to show it, you have the thanks of the Highborne spirits as well. Fare safely, traveler.' WHERE `entry`=13561;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have our thanks. It is time that we leave the past behind us, and start looking to our future.' WHERE `entry`=13562;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I would like to extend my gratitude for saving us. I would call myself fortunate, but my beloved, Anaya, lays long dead. I am alone and deeply troubled, and sadly, I require your aid yet again.$B$BWandering the woods of Darkshore after my rescue, I found myself in the ruins of Bashal\'Aran... where I saw the haunted spirit of my beloved.$B$BShe must be freed, but I lack the heart to do it. Her spirit must be destroyed.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. Perhaps it would have been better... if I had done it myself. But even after these thousands of years, I could not bear to raise my hand against my beloved.$B$BPlease, I would be alone with my grief...' WHERE `entry`=13563;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Greetings, traveler. You seem to have an interest in my friend here. You\'re here on behalf of his friend Volcor then I imagine? If Volcor didn\'t come himself, he must be injured as well. I hope he recovers quickly. Gimclaw is too injured to be moved far and he\'s going to need some immediate treatment. I\'m afraid I can\'t let you take him back just yet, but perhaps you can help me while I tend to him.' WHERE `entry`=13564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, ally. We shall keep a more vigilant eye should they return.' WHERE `entry`=13565;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These will do perfectly. These are the final ingredients for an incense I\'ve been working on. I will explain in just a moment, let me mix these in first.' WHERE `entry`=13566;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am the caretaker for my kind, leading not through force, but through wisdom and swift action. Wisdom is what carries us into the deeper forest when danger beckons and swiftness is what leaves our enemies basking in our absence. In this wisdom, I see through to your true intentions, and I know that you are deserving of my blessing, the blessing of my swiftness. It can be yours, but know that the other spirits will not welcome you once you proceed - consider this carefully before accepting my boon.' WHERE `entry`=13567;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I share these forests willingly, accepting night elf kind into my home, and on occasion calling them friend. Though they have been tainted greatly in recent memory, I can see in you the same strength, honor, and spirit that first endeared them to me. If you place value in the ferocity necessary to overcome all odds, then I am willing to call you my champion. Know now that if you side with my kind, the other spirits will not accept you, so consider your choice carefully.' WHERE `entry`=13568;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So it is done. You have received the blessing of a great animal spirit, and I shall now complete the ritual for you. Please stand still.' WHERE `entry`=13569;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Above the stale, unwashed stench, you catch a whiff of a familiar smell!  It appears as if this once-mighty adventurer has a real love for kungaloosh.$B$BPeeking through the bars, you can barely make out the recipe written on his arm....' WHERE `entry`=13571;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. With your efforts, we might be able to save the Blackwood who remain.' WHERE `entry`=13572;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There is no time to waste, $C. It is taking every ounce of my power to keep Darkshore\'s entire landmass from being shattered and swept into the ocean... you must listen to me very carefully.' WHERE `entry`=13573;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Peering Into the Vortex (DEPRECATED)' WHERE `entry`=13574;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I have much respect for the great Malfurion Stormrage. I cannot, however, leave my people in their time of need. Maybe there is a way we can both help each other.' WHERE `entry`=13575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The element of fire is unique in that attacking it indiscriminately can often lead it to spreading further... succeeding only in agitating its flames.$B$BWe are wiser than that, $N. We are going to dispose of it properly.' WHERE `entry`=13576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A terrible sadness surrounds the creature. Its eyes stare beyond you as you approach it.' WHERE `entry`=13577;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, $R. Soon my kin will rest.' WHERE `entry`=13578;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='If the great Malfurion requires my presence, it is my duty to heed his call. It is also my duty to protect these ruins, however.$B$BPerhaps you\'ll help me fulfill both my obligations, $N?' WHERE `entry`=13579;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We are in your debt, $N. Perhaps now, with Malfurion\'s help, we can save the rest of Darkshore.' WHERE `entry`=13580;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is fortunate news, $N. The furbolg may seem little more than a savage race, but their ties to the land are ancient and their shamans are second to none.' WHERE `entry`=13581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Finally kin may rest.' WHERE `entry`=13582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The wildkin were once the guardians of the land. It is good to hear they haven\'t all forgotten their old ways.' WHERE `entry`=13583;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s become clear, $N. The elements won\'t be calm until Malfurion succeeds in returning balance to the land. Aiding him is, in a way, also fulfilling my task.' WHERE `entry`=13584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent job, $N!  Selenn\'s help in holding back the vortex will be invaluable.' WHERE `entry`=13585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Malfurion calls?  Yes... I can hear his voice through the dream...' WHERE `entry`=13586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, $N. You\'ve given me my freedom. Let\'s see what we can do for your world now.' WHERE `entry`=13587;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We are turning the tides, $N. We should be able to contain further damage.$B$BMuch work still remains to be done.' WHERE `entry`=13588;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Glynda sent you to lend a hand, did she? I\'m glad she did - I could certainly use the help. I\'m working on our initial plans to start whittling away at their ranks. Please feel free to help Tysha and Balthule in the meantime.' WHERE `entry`=13589;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is good to meet you. Word has been sent to me of the efforts you have made to aid us against the trolls, and I must admit I am a bit impressed. The final fight is upon us now, I hope you are prepared.' WHERE `entry`=13590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, this news is disturbing indeed. I will start dispatching messengers to Ashenvale immediately and see if we can\'t get some reinforcements prepared for them. I cannot thank you enough for all the help you\'ve lent us in these trying times. Such heroic deeds deserve reward. I think I might have something that will serve you perfectly.' WHERE `entry`=13591;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome back from your exercises, $N. Even while we practice for the competition, it\'s good to remind ourselves that the Scourge is still out there.' WHERE `entry`=13592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We are proud that you have agreed to train with us and compete on our behalf.' WHERE `entry`=13593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' A job well done, $C. If you\'re any indication of the quality of the $R adventurers we\'re going to be seeing more of, we should have this war against the orcs and their Horde taken care of faster than expected.' WHERE `entry`=13594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have helped me to return to the ground, $N. Now my hair will cease to sprout for these creatures. Better yet, I will be regrown all the sooner.' WHERE `entry`=13595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. Now give me a moment to examine the plans you\'ve brought me.' WHERE `entry`=13596;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='For countless ages I have walked these forests and lived in these mountains. Through snow and fire, I have watched civilizations crumble and nature press on. Now, the very earth turns against us, and it becomes very apparent that we must fight if our legacy is to continue. Your heart is true, and I would choose you as our champion. If you value the thick hide and resilience of my kind, then accept my boon. Know that the other spirits will not accept you once this choice is made, so choose wisely.' WHERE `entry`=13597;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have my thanks, young one. We should be able to speed Grimclaw\'s recovery dramatically with this salve.' WHERE `entry`=13598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve returned! It is good to see you again. I suppose we have you to thank for Grimclaw\'s return? I\'m afraid... I have some bad news. I\'ve been unable to purge the toxin... their conditions worsen. Gershalla died shortly after you left, and Volcor... Volcor passed just before you came back. He lived long enough to see Grimclaw come back safely, so he died with a smile on his face. I\'m just sorry that I couldn\'t do more. For now, I\'m doing everything I can to save Shaldyn, so please excuse me.' WHERE `entry`=13599;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The marshal accepts the Blade of Drak\'Mar from you.>$B$BA fine weapon, and perfectly balanced. It will serve me well in the next match.' WHERE `entry`=13600;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you for coming to our assistance. As you can see, the refugees\' situation is dire.' WHERE `entry`=13601;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very well done, $N. Your actions in the Zoram Strand against the naga are commendable. I know your feat was not easily accomplished, for the strength and guile of the naga is well known to the night elves. We know this, for we share a history with them. The naga are cursed Highborne night elves. Ten thousand years ago, Queen Azshara made a pact of desperation with the Old Gods to save her surviving people from a watery grave. The naga are the result of that pact.' WHERE `entry`=13602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So the tales were true? This is a fine blade and I have no doubt that it will serve me well in the tournament. You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13603;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The platinum disc fits perfectly inside the console. It begins to spin as its contents are scanned by white beams of light.' WHERE `entry`=13604;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Escort Archaeologist Hollee to safety',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Aye, you\'re the fine $G lad : lass; who saved my Hollee!$B$BWell, I\'ve got a fitting reward for you here, I\'m sure. We really can\'t thank you enough for bringing her to safety, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13605;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. We\'re one step closer to saving Azeroth!' WHERE `entry`=13606;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s locked? Figures!$B$BLet\'s see what information this junk heap can give us...' WHERE `entry`=13607;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ye did it! I don\'t know how, but ye did!' WHERE `entry`=13609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ye never cease to impress, $N.$B$BYe and me are having a pint together after all this is done, ye hear me?' WHERE `entry`=13610;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve got to hand it to you, $N. Our odds might not be the best, but I feel a lot better with you lending a hand.' WHERE `entry`=13611;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, $C! Your efforts will help keep the enemy on their heels while our forces sweep across the land!' WHERE `entry`=13612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $R. I shall include your service to the Horde in my report. I should have these troops fit to fight again in no time!' WHERE `entry`=13613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Stand by for verification.$B$BAccess to the Celestial Planetarium granted. Please retrieve your key.' WHERE `entry`=13614;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $C. This should help get us by until our shipment arrives.' WHERE `entry`=13615;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The blade is as fine as the stories say. It would seem there\'s little reason to complete the repairs on my customary blade. Winter\'s Edge is far superior and I will continue to carry it. You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13616;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello, $C. What\'s that? You say that Shyela sent you? Very well, let\'s get started.' WHERE `entry`=13617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Listen carefully, $R....' WHERE `entry`=13618;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' It is as I feared, then. May his rest be peaceful - only not yet!' WHERE `entry`=13619;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let\'s have a look, $C.' WHERE `entry`=13620;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $R. The elf captain is dead and the soul of one of our beloved brethren can sleep in peace. I shall pass on word of your deeds to my superiors in Orgrimmar.' WHERE `entry`=13621;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Analyzing fragments... please stand by.' WHERE `entry`=13622;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, Evenar was succesful. Actually, more to the point, YOU were successful. I cannot thank you enough, $C, but there is more that must be done to the leaves before they will serve as a curative for what ails the child, Relara.' WHERE `entry`=13623;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'d received a report about you from some of my scouts out in the forest but I had no idea how capable you are! Thank you, $N. With what you\'ve accomplished the tide is turned. I\'ve no doubt now that we\'ll route them by the end of the day!' WHERE `entry`=13624;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. Mounted combat is often hard to pick up for those accustomed to fighting on foot. I have no doubt that you\'ll continue to improve with practice, which is more than I can say for some warriors.' WHERE `entry`=13625;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I do not look forward to writing the letter to the Argent Dawn embassy in Darnassus. At least we\'ll be able to send their most prized possessions back for their loved ones. I cannot thank you enough for your courage, $N. Please accept this on behalf of the post.' WHERE `entry`=13626;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='All excellent planks, and the price is right, too! Even better, those Argent Crusade sticks-in-the-mud will never know. They\'ll get their precious coliseum and I\'ll get my early completion bonus. Now that\'s a win-win if I ever saw one.' WHERE `entry`=13627;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome, $C. It is good to see that the road to Mor\'shan Ramparts remains clear.' WHERE `entry`=13628;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Object integrity confirmed. Please hold while solidified residue is removed.' WHERE `entry`=13629;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. With the moonstones of Ordil\'Aran deactivated, we should not need to worry about any further incursions of furbolg here. However, my scouts have returned with disturbing news from the furbolg village. There is an imminent danger massing there. I wonder, might I entice you to carry a warning to Astranaar for me?' WHERE `entry`=13630;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re here. Let us hope this works. For all our sakes.' WHERE `entry`=13631;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We are in your debt, $C. If I know anything about the furbolg, they do not like their noses bloodied. It won\'t be long now before they tuck tail and return to their village.' WHERE `entry`=13632;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you\'re saying this knight\'s story is a sham? Most suspicious. Dishonorable at the least, and murderous at the worst. Still, we can\'t confront him until we know for certain whether he was involved in these murders.$B$BDo nothing to arouse his suspicions, $N. Discretion will serve us well as we continue to investigate.' WHERE `entry`=13633;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you\'re saying this knight\'s story is a sham? Most suspicious. Dishonorable at the least, and murderous at the worst. Still, we can\'t confront him until we know for certain whether he was involved in these murders.$B$BDo nothing to arouse his suspicions, $N. Discretion will serve us well as we continue to investigate.' WHERE `entry`=13634;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The South Gate status report? Excellent. I\'ve been awaiting news from them for a while. With the increasing number of troggs in the hills on all sides, I fear the outposts will be the first to feel any aggressive action.' WHERE `entry`=13635;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Orders! Let\'s see what we have here... hah! He wants me to deal with the infestation of rat men. We\'re already in the middle of that, so no real deviation there. Care to lend a hand?' WHERE `entry`=13636;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmph, it\'ll take more than a Dark Iron ambush to stop the deliveries!$B$BBut Saean... I would never have suspected him to be one of their sympathizers. We\'ve been working with him for almost a year now... maybe I missed the signs.$B$BWell, I\'ll consider that later.' WHERE `entry`=13639;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It seems you\'ve solved one problem only to face another, $C.' WHERE `entry`=13640;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This one will do nicely. All that remains is to imbue it with the power of the Light, giving it the ability to find truth amid deception.' WHERE `entry`=13641;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With the concoction blessed by the Light of Elune, it should be ready for delivery to Astranaar. There is no time to waste, $N!' WHERE `entry`=13642;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you say Lorien Sunblaze was done in by poison and Sir Wendell was burnt alive? Dreadful ways to die, both of them. Only Conall was killed by cold steel, and from your description, it was a coward\'s strike, not honorable combat that laid him in his grave.$B$BAll three sparred with and were scheduled to fight the Black Knight. This cannot be a coincidence. Now, we must find a way to prove it was the Black Knight\'s work.' WHERE `entry`=13643;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With the death of the harbinger, I can begin to cleanse the lake. You have my deepest thanks, $N. I mourn the loss of your friend, but know that his remains will fuel the reclamation of the forest hereabouts.' WHERE `entry`=13644;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Teronis is dead? We must see to it that his sacrifice was not in vain. Are you willing to see this through, $C? Very well, allow me some time to think about how we should proceed. I will know shortly.' WHERE `entry`=13645;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Avana is alive?! I feared that she might be dead when we heard about the attack on Maestra\'s Post! As you can see, we have our hands full with the Horde here as well. You have given me the greatest gift by letting me know she is well. Any time that you wish to ride one of my nightsabers back to Maestra\'s Post, it is yours.' WHERE `entry`=13646;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello there, $G laddy:lass;! The mountaineers sent you over, eh? I do suspect we might have just the sort of work you\'re looking for. Welcome to the Farstrider Lodge!' WHERE `entry`=13647;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You brought that damned spy to justice! This is good news. We can all rest a little bit easier, not worrying about that one.' WHERE `entry`=13648;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Woo! I\'m relieved... I was worried they\'d all be destroyed by now. Thank you for checking in on them.' WHERE `entry`=13650;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for the oil, $C. Now prepare yourself! My runner has returned with some desperate news.... Splintertree is surrounded!' WHERE `entry`=13651;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Gorka... We must always be prepared for losses. Her honorable service to the Horde will not be forgotten. And her sacrifice shall not be in vain!' WHERE `entry`=13653;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Crusader Rhydalla examines the bag\'s contents with a look of disgust on her face.>$B$BIt\'s all here, $N: the poison that killed Lorien, a collection of knives, torches, and oil. No man has cause to possess these things here and no squire would do so without orders from his knightly master. We\'ve found our murderer, $N, but who is he working for?' WHERE `entry`=13654;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well look at that. You found one of our stolen documents!$B$BWe\'re much obliged for its return. Hopefully a bit of gold will suit your fancy for the finder\'s fee?' WHERE `entry`=13655;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello, $G sonny:lass;! You seem to have found one of our stolen documents, eh?$B$BThank you kindly for bringing it back to us. We\'ll gladly lend some coin as thanks for its return.' WHERE `entry`=13656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Our historical records! The thought of dark iron vermin delving into our past just made me sick to my stomach. We appreciate you bringing this back to us. We\'d like to offer you some coin as a reward.' WHERE `entry`=13657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ug, I can\'t believe they got their hands on our transport routes - that was just asking for trouble!! Thank you for getting this back to us before they were able to do much with it! You probably saved us a lot of heartache. Please accept some coin as a reward for your efforts.' WHERE `entry`=13658;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hah! Think they got a kick out of seeing how low they were on our list of threat assessments! This document was admittedly a bit out of date, but none the less amusing. Of course, we\'ll offer you some money as a reward for returning this anyway - your efforts are appreciated!' WHERE `entry`=13659;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Our artifact records! I was pretty well worried what the dark irons might try to steal with this information at their disposal. Thank you for bringing this back to us. We\'ll gladly part with some coin to express our gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=13660;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Keep the residue pouring in!' WHERE `entry`=13662;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Crusader Rhydalla\'s face pales as she reads the orders.>$B$BThis can only mean one thing, $N. The Black Knight is a member of the Cult of the Damned and has been sent by Arthas to disrupt the tournament!$B$BThe Black Knight has proven himself a fearsome combatant, and you will need to be every bit as good if you wish to face him. When you are a champion, return to me and we\'ll find a way to ensure his defeat.' WHERE `entry`=13663;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With the death of the Black Knight, the tournament may once again serve its purpose. The champions of the Horde and Alliance may demonstrate their skill at arms and train for the day when Arthas and his minions will no longer threaten us.$B$BYou have the thanks of the Argent Crusade, $N, and that of all who have answered our call.' WHERE `entry`=13664;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done. Training against the other valiants is one of the best ways to prepare yourself for tournament competition. I know you\'ll make Stormwind proud, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So there is some truth to those old tales? It seems they did not lie about the quality of the blade. Well done, $N. The champion who wields it will be a lucky man, indeed.' WHERE `entry`=13666;
