UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $C. They\'re in complete disarray. Just look at them!' WHERE `entry`=13865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Protector Arminon slain',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Ashenvale Scouts defeated' WHERE `entry`=13865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are just in time, $C. Old Kulg has been slinking around those woods too long. He grows too cautious, jumping at shadows. We will fear this forest no longer - the time has come to subdue Ashenvale once and for all!' WHERE `entry`=13866;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N.$B$BWe are under constant threat from the furbolg. Hopefully this will keep them at bay for a bit longer.' WHERE `entry`=13867;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A troll charm? What are the furbolg doing with such a thing? You\'re right, it does have a feeling of corruption about it... even I can sense that. There\'s someone here who might be able to help.' WHERE `entry`=13868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='While what the satyrs have done to the trees is horrible, nothing compares to the mass slaughter that the orcs have been engaging in!$B$B<The ancient shakes with visible rage, his leaves falling all around you.>$B$B$R, I would have you head across the road here at the lumber camp and recover the remains of those trees, treants, and ancients that the Horde have hewn down in their prime.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I have lived a very long time in peace with the forest, but what these orc-things are doing makes me want to feed them back to the ground! I will put this wood to rest now. Thank you for this kindness, $N. I will never forget.' WHERE `entry`=13869;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' If only you\'d arrived an hour ago.... The diplomat suffered mortal wounds at the hands of an elf assassin. How the enemy was able to infiltrate the camp undetected remains a mystery.' WHERE `entry`=13870;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Security!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $C. One last request - it would probably be best if none of my laborers knew this assassin ever existed.' WHERE `entry`=13871;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Guardian Menerin wants you to deliver the Sealed Missive to Guardian Gurtar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I\'ll deliver this to Hellscream personally, $R. In the meantime, there\'s something I need you to do for me....' WHERE `entry`=13873;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You\'ve likely saved the Thistlefur from themselves, at least in the short run. If they can keep from stealing objects of power that don\'t belong to them, that is. I understand that the night elves are having problems with the other furbolg tribe to the south. That\'s something that Raene is going to want to speak to you about. However, there are more immediate concerns that I would ask for your help with.' WHERE `entry`=13874;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Oh, $N. Thank you for this gift! It means more than you could know. He hasn\'t forgotten...' WHERE `entry`=13875;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What was done had to be done. As our leader, Dal\'s sickness from the troll charms was destroying us. It was better for the health and dignity of the tribe that it was you, outsider. This way there will be no civil war amongst us and we will easily find new leadership... hopefully one that does not have a tendency to so easily trust outsiders. Perhaps I am guilty of this as well? Here, allow me to repay the debt we owe you before we part ways forever.' WHERE `entry`=13876;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My brother must have sent you. He wouldn\'t have done so unless you are capable of doing what must be done. For all of our sakes I hope that he\'s right. The elementals here are now my allies. You must do as they ask if we are to prevent the destruction of the rest of Ashenvale.' WHERE `entry`=13877;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You save the wolves! So brave! Someday, maybe you get a wolf just like that to ride. What should I do now?' WHERE `entry`=13878;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' The spirits whispered that help would soon arrive. Pardon my surprise, but I was hoping the spirits would guide someone a little more... heroic. These elementals are trusted allies. Listen to them and do their bidding. If we fail, there will remain nothing in Ashenvale worth fighting for.' WHERE `entry`=13879;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $R. Lord Magmathar\'s fire is now trapped, restrained within the earth once more.' WHERE `entry`=13880;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Consumed',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' $N, this is terrible. What is that thing, and how did it get there? Something is devouring these animals, physically and spiritually. I had suspected the satyrs or some sort of disease was the culprit, but this is shaping up to be something ... unnatural.' WHERE `entry`=13881;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect, this is everything. Did you have fun collecting the wisp? I used to chase the wisps around Ashenvale when I was just a girl. I\'m afraid I\'ve found out what we\'re dealing with.' WHERE `entry`=13882;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, $R. I\'ll show them how an armored ship should be built!' WHERE `entry`=13883;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You acquitted yourself well in battle on the field. However, I\'m afraid that Lord Magmathar has taken notice of you and the destruction that you\'ve wreaked upon his minions. You will have to deal with him or he is sure to burn you alive, $N.' WHERE `entry`=13884;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So the animals are safe, then. Thank you, thank you! But now it\'s time to turn our attention to the source.' WHERE `entry`=13885;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is done. The power of fire is subdued and the four elements are returned to harmony. You have saved the rest of Ashenvale through your brave and selfless actions, $N. You have our eternal thanks.' WHERE `entry`=13886;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work. Honestly, I\'m amazed you were able to find this many. With each clutch, they seem fewer in number.$B$BI\'ll let you raise one of the freshly-hatched venomhides. It shouldn\'t be shy about letting you know what it needs.' WHERE `entry`=13887;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done it! The spirits were right after all! The power of fire is subdued and the four elements are returned to harmony. The rest of Ashenvale is spared this fiery fate. You have the eternal thanks of the Earthen Ring.' WHERE `entry`=13888;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The venomhide hatchling seems satisfied with the giant meal you\'ve provided, but there\'s no way of telling when it will be hungry again.' WHERE `entry`=13889;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice work, $R! No more ships will run aground, thanks to you.' WHERE `entry`=13890;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Love of Elune, look at you. That must\'ve been some fight! You\'re covered in what looks like... chowder. If a mere minion could cause so much agony here in Darkshore, I can\'t even imagine the suffering that a true Old One could bring about. Well, at least the animals are safe for now. I will plant the sapling you created to help rebuild this shattered land. Thank you, $N! I\'d give you a hug but, you know. Chowder.' WHERE `entry`=13891;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is dire news, $N. If you are correct, then we\'d best act swiftly and decisively. We cannot allow this "Soggoth" to be brought back to life.' WHERE `entry`=13892;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The dwarf\'s story is unsettling... yet informative. It seems we have few options left.' WHERE `entry`=13893;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Aros\'s body appears to be lifeless yet still warm. Perhaps his killers are nearby.' WHERE `entry`=13895;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, we know a thing or two about this Soggoth. The question is... do you really want to know?' WHERE `entry`=13896;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We can finally rest here now, $N. It appears Darkshore has been saved -- and we have you to thank for it.' WHERE `entry`=13897;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. The naga seek the destruction and subjugation of all surface-dwellers -- do not hesitate to drive them out of our lands and back into the shadowy ocean depths where they belong.' WHERE `entry`=13898;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The walord doesn\'t seem to have the horn on him. Perhaps he was telling the truth.' WHERE `entry`=13899;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well, $N. Unfortunately the battle is far from over.' WHERE `entry`=13900;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='There is more to this Naga problem than meets the eye, $C. It appears that the issue will not be resolved by merely thinning their numbers. To humble them, a more severe impression must be made.$B$BTravel to the northern end of Zoram Strand and enter Blackfathom Deep. Once there, demonstrate to the naga that their presence in this region will no longer be tolerated!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! Let the naga retreat back into the seas where they belong!' WHERE `entry`=13901;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='If Malfurion placed his trust in you, then so shall I. You\'ll find that our enemies greatly outnumber us this far south.$B$BWhere brute force and numbers fail us, strategy and guile will prove our biggest advantages.' WHERE `entry`=13902;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your venomhide hatchling flashes you a toothy smile and then settles in for a nap.' WHERE `entry`=13903;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your hatchling licks its lips after devouring the meal of silithid eggs. For a moment, you think it seems disappointed that feeding time has come to an end.' WHERE `entry`=13904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The venomhide hatchling accepts the feathers and begins looking them over, holding several up to its armbands.' WHERE `entry`=13905;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It looks like both of you have managed to do some growing without killing one another.$B$BThere, everything\'s finished. I\'ve trained your venomhide ravasaur to respond when you blow this whistle.$B$BFew have the dedication to hand-feed and raise a venomhide, but they\'re well worth the effort.' WHERE `entry`=13906;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Bravo, $N! Now let\'s take a look-see at our new situation. What? MORE murlocs? I swear on my stones, the more murlocs you kill, the more murlocs appear. Is it just me? We\'re going to need a new approach.' WHERE `entry`=13907;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Well, not much here that don\'t look stepped on, sat on, or soaked in a toilet. But toss some thatch on top and it\'ll do. Tell me, $N, do you consider yourself an architect?' WHERE `entry`=13909;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Har har, that sounds like quite a heap you built there. Did they take to it? Good, good! Let\'s see if my plan comes to fruition. What have I done?' WHERE `entry`=13910;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you\'ve helped the Prospector find his missing journal! To think it was here all along. Someday you\'ll have to show me this other set of ruins he\'s always going on about.' WHERE `entry`=13911;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Spectacular! Good work, $N. I\'m sure Remtravel would thank you himself if he could remember your name. Look at the surface of the disc - these microscopic etchings - this is amazing. I\'m certain this strange wheel holds information, if only we could read it...' WHERE `entry`=13912;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Rescue Boog the "Gear Whisperer" and Minx from Painmaster Thundrak\'s Wagon of Unending Agony.',`objectives_loc6`='Rescue Boog the "Gear Whisperer" and Minx from Painmaster Thundrak\'s Wagon of Unending Agony.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. Grim news you bring of the rest of the gnome team, but at least you managed to save a few. For that I am grateful.' WHERE `entry`=13913;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The venomhide hatchling accepts the feathers and begins looking them over, holding several up to its armbands.' WHERE `entry`=13914;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The venomhide hatchling seems satisfied with the giant meal you\'ve provided, but there\'s no way of telling when it will be hungry again.' WHERE `entry`=13915;
