UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful!  Another batch of powder! Just between us jewelcrafters, I\'ve been making hand over fist selling "pure titanium" jewelry to the local Dalaran mages. Even with their superior intellect, they aren\'t particularly savvy with their gold. If you get more, I\'ll be here.' WHERE `entry`=14103;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ornolf\'s crew will want to avenge their leader, but without him, they will be easier to defeat. We must live to carry out our mission, to see Icecrown rid of the Scourge and other evils.' WHERE `entry`=14104;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are truly an example to all who have gathered beneath our banner, $N. Together, we will show the Scourge that we will not be defeated.' WHERE `entry`=14105;
