UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, well, well, if it isn\'t my wayward protege, Mr. $N. I\'m hurt and disappointed. You didn\'t send me an invitation to your little party out there. Sorry about the crashers... you know how pirates can be. So, shall we get down to business?' WHERE `entry`=14116;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. As their scouts fail to report in, Talrendis will feel the terror they\'ve tried in vain to inflict on us.' WHERE `entry`=14117;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Meat - and lots of it! Well done. This will keep bellies full as we build our arsenal.' WHERE `entry`=14118;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A bazillion macaroons?!?! Where are we going to get that kind of moolah? Um... did the Trade Prince say anything about letting me escape with you on his yacht?' WHERE `entry`=14120;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='We\'re all going to die!!!$B$B<You slap Megs to calm her down.>$B$BSorry about that, $G Mr. : Ms.; $N. Okay, we need to find a way to get a lot of moolah quickly.$B$BThere are reports of the Trade Prince sending hired looters into the streets.$B$BYou could take the hot rod out there and run them down, snatching the loot that they\'ve illegally stolen. There wouldn\'t be anything wrong with that, right?',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wow, you really did it?! Well, they had it coming, I guess. That\'s an awful lot of loot. Do you think it\'s enough to get you a spot on the Trade Prince\'s yacht? Are you going to be able to bring anyone with you? I don\'t make too much working in marketing.' WHERE `entry`=14121;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey, you have been saving! I\'m so proud of you! Um, boss... this isn\'t nearly enough.' WHERE `entry`=14122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, wow! These are worth a fortune. I just hope that the Trade Prince doesn\'t notice them when you hand them over with the rest of your wealth....' WHERE `entry`=14123;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='$G Sir : Ma\'am;, we need tons of moolah to pay the Trade Prince and get off Kezan! Well, tons of it is just waiting for the taking down there in the Kaja\'mine!$B$BThese are the last known deposits of kaja\'mite anywhere. This is the raw stuff that made us the genius tinkerers and alchemists we are today. If that\'s not worth a bazillion macaroons, I don\'t know what is!$B$BTake some of my kablooey bombs and blowup the deposits. Then, pick up the chunks.$B$BJust watch out for the rebellious trolls!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nicely done, sir, nicely done! That\'s a fortune you have there in your bags. With all of that, I bet the Trade Prince will let all of us come along on his yacht!' WHERE `entry`=14124;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='447',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is nothing. You should see Bilgewater Port... the whole thing is going up in flames! Fine, fine, I don\'t have time to inspect this place. Here\'s the moolah from the Bilgewater Cartel\'s insurance policy. I\'ve got to find a way off the island! Good luck, $N!' WHERE `entry`=14125;
