UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Is that you, $N? Still alive? You aren\'t trashing my explosive stockpiles are you? Hmmm... you say you found a clear crystal pendant. That makes sense. A perfect prism would refract the gaze of the basilisk. Maybe we can use this to our advantage. Time to drop some science!' WHERE `entry`=14190;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is clear to you now that these ruins are those that Furien recorded in his journal. After examining the engravings upon the ruins themselves, you feel that you are able to decipher more of Furien\'s writings.' WHERE `entry`=14191;
