UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='After filling it with liquid from the melons, you proceed to wash your eyes from the ancient font. Upon opening your eyes, you are able to see the spirits of ancient elves, still faithfully carrying out rituals to their goddess.' WHERE `entry`=14193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Refleshification',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, good. Now we can get these slackers back to work. You\'ve earned a cut of the profits though - minus the usual company fees. Take your pick!' WHERE `entry`=14194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is clear to you now why you were guided here. You recognize this ancient runestone from Furien\'s final journal entry: "The ancients revered the gems created by this mystical object, claiming that they were gifts from the goddess herself. It was believed that they were weapons capable of delivering them from any enemy."' WHERE `entry`=14195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is done! Furien\'s exhaustive research was not in vain. The raging Vortex is ready to be unleashed upon your enemies at last!' WHERE `entry`=14196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done! When it comes to iron, always pick quantity over quality.' WHERE `entry`=14197;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very impressive, $C. You completed Furien\'s work and rained vengeance down upon his killers. You have brought peace to my brother\'s soul, and to my mind. Please accept this gift for your diligence.' WHERE `entry`=14198;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is good to see that you have emerged victorious from the trial. Truly, you are a champion, not only of the Argent Crusade, but indeed of the Kirin Tor as well.$B$BOne can only hope that you have dealt the final blow to that dark villain and that\'s the last that we will see of him.' WHERE `entry`=14199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' So the spirits of the dead still haunt those old stones, hm? Well $N, as it happens, I\'m counting on their help. Let\'s see what the dead have to say...' WHERE `entry`=14201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Beautiful work! Now that we know the area better, we can tear this lake a new one.' WHERE `entry`=14202;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is quite a find, <name>. I can\'t have you selling this to anyone else, so I\'m willing to offer generously.' WHERE `entry`=14203;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. I\'ll start rounding up some help to get these cannons positioned.' WHERE `entry`=14204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Busted ball bearings! Look at this stuff - ugh, SMELL this stuff - my poor, poor dozer! $N, I consider myself a goop expert and this here goop ain\'t natural. It\'s supernatural. This is ghost goop. We\'re going to need more than a mechanic...' WHERE `entry`=14209;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Sacrifices',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Brace yourself, $N. Here they come.' WHERE `entry`=14212;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The divine brazier indiscriminately endows you with a blessing.' WHERE `entry`=14213;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew Crowley would come through. His weapons will be more than useful to us.' WHERE `entry`=14214;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You reel as the spirit\'s vision fades, relieved to once again feel the earth beneath your feet and the comforting rhythm of your own quickened heart.' WHERE `entry`=14215;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A Sarcen stone? That\'s the stuff of legend - let me see that! $N, Sarcen stones are used to redirect the ley lines of magical energy. You realize what this means? The mages of Mennar weren\'t staying behind out of misguided loyalty. They sacrificed their lives in order to create this artifact in an attempt to draw energy away from the portal through which the demons were flooding Azeroth. They were buying time for the rest of the world to fight back! History never recorded their deeds. What a discovery!' WHERE `entry`=14216;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The divine brazier indiscriminately endows you with a blessing.' WHERE `entry`=14217;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well, $N. You\'ve done more than could be asked of any Gilnean. We\'re running low on ammunition. It\'s time to regroup inside now.' WHERE `entry`=14218;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With the ritual completed, you are awarded a divine gift. You can\'t help but wonder what Elune would think of someone such as you receiving one of her boons.' WHERE `entry`=14219;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'ve given them everything we have... yet still they come. Do not worry, $N. We\'ll slay many more before today is over.' WHERE `entry`=14221;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They... they\'ve stopped coming. No, $N. That\'s not a good thing.' WHERE `entry`=14222;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is done. Sorrem should be able to sleep in peace now that Kohor\'s threats have been silenced.' WHERE `entry`=14223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is most fortunate that you took the time to search for this. No one would have expected the Burning Blade to be in possession of something so powerful!' WHERE `entry`=14225;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Do not fret, and better yet, do not forget, to do not let the bug juice set or you will regret... well, you\'ll regret the smell of your boots really! It won\'t smell good today and it won\'t smell good even more tomorrow!' WHERE `entry`=14226;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You diverted what would have been a serious crisis, $C. If that summoning was delayed just a bit longer, the demon would have become far too powerful for our small forces here to contend with. Please accept this gift as our thanks for your service.' WHERE `entry`=14227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Peachy. Back to work then. Thanks, snookums.' WHERE `entry`=14230;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ears of the Burning Blade? Well done, $C. This is just a shadow of what will soon become of that vile cult!' WHERE `entry`=14232;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Orcs?! They were sunk and stranded too?  And now the Alliance are on the island? Do you think they\'re going to kill us? I think it\'s time for a little sitdown with these orcs.' WHERE `entry`=14233;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I apologize. It has been a very rough couple of days for all of us. I am Aggra. All of us here are what remains of the crew of the Draka\'s Fury. Perhaps we can work together. We have a common enemy in the Alliance. Their SI:7 assassins are all over this island and they\'re not going to stop until we\'re all dead.' WHERE `entry`=14234;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$R, can you fight? For your sake, I hope so. Otherwise, there may be no breaking through this hell of killer plants.' WHERE `entry`=14235;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I saw it with my own eyes, and still I do not believe it! You have our thanks and the debt of our lives, little $R. I hope that soon we can repay you the honor. May I ask a small favor of you while my scouts and I move on?' WHERE `entry`=14236;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Throm-Ka, $N. We have a problem.' WHERE `entry`=14237;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N, well done. We\'ll make an orc of you yet! Time to move on. We\'d better hurry.' WHERE `entry`=14238;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello, little $R. Bastia is fast, no? We have something very important that needs doing. Can you help us?' WHERE `entry`=14240;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm, where the heck is the ignition? It\'ll be a wonder if it flies without doing something weird, like turning into a chicken or shrinking down to the size of an ant. Hey look, someone left their loose change in the ashtray! What else is in there?' WHERE `entry`=14241;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='If not for you, I would surely be on my way back to Stormwind to be paraded as a trophy and a slave. The Alliance dogs found me unconscious on the shore and put me in this magical cage. It was keeping me from connecting with the elements. No longer!' WHERE `entry`=14242;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done what few others could have, $N. Our world owes you a debt larger than you can possibly understand.' WHERE `entry`=14243;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='While you were rescuing the Warchief and saving us all from the Alliance, Foreman Dampwick built this rocket sling to shoot us over the shark-infested strait to the bigger island.$B$BLuckily for us, the foreman managed to salvage a Town-In-A-Box from the shipwreck. Once you get it set up, we\'ll have a town of our own. I can\'t wait to sleep in a bed again!$B$BDampwick\'s down there at the Landing Site, waiting for you. Why don\'t you take the next rocket over?',`objectives_loc6`='Survive the Rocket Sling shot across the Dire Strait.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N, I sure am glad you survived the trip... not everyone did!' WHERE `entry`=14244;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Hey! Where\'s the dock?! Someone stole the dock and the oil refinery from our town-in-a-box! Who would do such a thing? Where\'s the Trade Prince?' WHERE `entry`=14245;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $C. This land is in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=14246;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You look around, scanning the horizon for what might be responsible for placing this stone here....' WHERE `entry`=14247;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Boss! Er, well, I guess you\'re not the boss anymore, but still, good to see you! Can you believe it? We\'ve got a cave full of intelligent killer monkeys mining Kaja\'mite!' WHERE `entry`=14248;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ha ha! Perfect! Let me toss this together really fast. The Archmage is sure to be taken in by my style!' WHERE `entry`=14249;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work. This should keep us for another few hours before we have to go back for more. He doesn\'t seem to be the brightest of giants. I expect we\'ll be able to keep doing this for a while before he catches on.' WHERE `entry`=14250;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='There\'s never been danger of centaur attack this far north before. Someone put \'em up to it, I just know it!$B$BRegardless, I\'m wiped out. I had everything invested in this haul.$B$BFortunately, there\'s one thing no centaur can take from me and that\'s goblin ingenuity! I\'ll start from scratch and build an empire!$B$B<Bizby spots a scorpion in the distance.>$B$BThere\'s always a market for poison. Whatdya say, friend?',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is how I got my start, you know. Slingin\' poison to the rogues in Orgrimmar. Ahh, those were the days....' WHERE `entry`=14251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'ll do, $C. A few more friends like you and I\'ll be back on my feet in no time!' WHERE `entry`=14252;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well now, that\'s quite a load of feathers, $C. They\'ll make for a good pillow \'til I get \'em to market!' WHERE `entry`=14253;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Heavy Metal',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='What\'s this? Wahoo! I know someone who will be most interested in acquiring these samples. Most generous in payment for them as well, I\'ll wager. Here, $C. Take this as your finder\'s fee.' WHERE `entry`=14254;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is good that you have come. There is grave danger looming here.' WHERE `entry`=14255;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So now you see. These are not a simple band of displaced naga, but a well organized army, capable of great devastation. Do you agree to assist me in my investigation?' WHERE `entry`=14256;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $C. But I\'m afraid that your work here is just beginning.' WHERE `entry`=14257;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Sweet! Beautiful! Brilliant! Who loves you? With my mortars re-supplied, I can help you as you assault the Naga east of here. Use these markers to call in an artillery strike anywhere on the cliffs, and I\'ll splatter the whole area with fiery hurt. Oh delicious, merciless, random destruction! I hope you\'re well-armored...' WHERE `entry`=14258;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Don\'t just stand around, when there is so much to be done! Must I instruct everyone on each detail?' WHERE `entry`=14260;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What? So you didn\'t bring any of the drake pieces back? Disappointing. I knew I should have made you sign a contract before I sent you out...' WHERE `entry`=14261;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' And still they come! They are like a plague, $N. But with strength like yours, we will crush them. Someday.' WHERE `entry`=14262;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect. It\'s quite interesting how useful the most random things end up being to incantations of this sort. So much more to learn!' WHERE `entry`=14263;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The enemy\'s ranks are thinning, little minnow. Perhaps you are worthy of assisting in our search....' WHERE `entry`=14264;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N!  Where have you been? Anyway... it\'s great to see you in one piece.' WHERE `entry`=14265;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='You\'re alive, $N!  That must mean I did something right.$B$BIt\'s a shame our lessons were cut off a little short. But perhaps there\'s a thing or two I can teach you that might be handy in a time like this.$B$BTry out your new technique against the bloodfang worgen to our west.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Sergeant Cleese and learn Charge. Practice using Charge against a Bloodfang Worgen.' WHERE `entry`=14266;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The stone in the center of this shrine emits a faint glow and roars with the power of the angry sea.' WHERE `entry`=14267;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes! You\'ve found it! Neptulon\'s engravings... there can be no mistake!' WHERE `entry`=14268;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, hey!  There you are!' WHERE `entry`=14269;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The keystone shard slides into place and previously invisible runes suddenly erupt onto the surface of the stone, shimmering in blue and violet hues. Your knees buckle as powerful arcane currents suddenly race into your body...' WHERE `entry`=14270;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='An energy barrier, you say? This explains a great deal! I\'ve seen firsthand how Naga leaders have been able to turn aside the blades of some of my best warriors. Now we know the source of their power, $N. Let\'s finish this!' WHERE `entry`=14271;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Good to see you alive!$B$BNo, of course I don\'t have that gold I owe you. Now\'s not really the time to bring that up is it?$B$BListen, maybe I can teach you a trick or two that might save your skin with all the carnage going on. I\'d call it more than even then. What do you say?$B$BAfter your lesson is over, try using your new technique against the Bloodfang Worgen to our west.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Loren the Fence and learn Eviscerate. Practice using Eviscerate against a Bloodfang Worgen.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Don\'t get ahead of yourself now. Just remember who taught you everything you know. And now let\'s see if we can get out of this city with our skins attached.' WHERE `entry`=14272;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A darkness has descended over our lands. And not our kind of darkness, if you know what I mean.' WHERE `entry`=14273;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='It is true then!  You live!$B$BI never got a chance to share my greatest discovery with you. From the depths of the nigh-indecipherable books of Balcephoth of the felshadows... I\'ve learned the forbidden secrets of...$B$BImmolate!$B$BOf course I will share this knowledge with you... who else around here would appreciate such powerful understanding?$B$BGo now, and practice your new spell against the Bloodfang Worgen to our west.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Vitus Darkwalker and learn Immolate. Practice casting Immolate on a Bloodfang Worgen.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes!  You can feel the power, can\'t you?' WHERE `entry`=14274;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N!  I knew you had to be around here.' WHERE `entry`=14275;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='So I\'ve got good news and bad news.$B$BThe bad news is that there are more worgen in the woods than in here... so we really have no safe place to go to.$B$BThe good news is that I still have a thing or two to teach you. Who knows the sort of skill that might save your life in a time like this.$B$BTry your hand at it against the bloodfang worgen to our west.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Huntsman Blake and learn Steady Shot. Practice using Steady Shot 2 times against a Bloodfang Worg.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. These $R will regret ever setting foot in our lands.' WHERE `entry`=14276;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A disciple of the arcane always finds a way forward. I\'m glad to see you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=14277;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Light is with you, $N. It\'s still quite a relief to see you.' WHERE `entry`=14278;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='You have much to learn, $N. And I\'ve much to teach you.$B$BThese are perilous times, however, and I fear that we might have to accelerate certain lessons.$B$BHave no fear, $G brother:sister;. The Light will guide us through this.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Sister Almyra and learn Flash Heal. Use Flash Heal 2 times on a Wounded Guard.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are blessed, $N. The Light shines upon you, even in these dark times.' WHERE `entry`=14279;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We have been blessed today!  You are alive and well!' WHERE `entry`=14280;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The path ahead is difficult, $N. We must devote the entirety of our mental power to the task at hand.$B$BYet sometimes, that is not enough. Sometimes the situation calls for raw firepower.$B$BI know just the spell for such a situation and I\'ll be more than glad to share it with you. Once you\'ve learned it, practice using it against the Bloodfang Worgen to our west. You\'ll only get the chance to use your new spell after casting a different spell.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Myriam Spellwaker and learn Arcane Missiles. Use Arcane Missiles against a Bloodfang Worgen.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve learned with such speed and ease. Soon you\'ll be the one doing the teaching.' WHERE `entry`=14281;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The vision was true! You have singlehandedly succeeded where others have failed. The Circle will be have no choice but to pay attention to these findings.' WHERE `entry`=14282;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='We were driven to the edge of extinction once before, $N. But we druids, keepers of the old ways, saved our people from famine.$B$BWhen we cut ourselves off from the outside world and our crops failed, it was our order who called upon the earth\'s blessings and restored the harvest.$B$BJust as we did then, it is best to put our fate in the hands of a higher power. Join me now and learn what the wild has to teach us.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Celestine of the Harvest and learn Rejuvenation. Practice using Rejuvenation on a Wounded Guard.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not bad at all. Perhaps there is still hope for the old ways.' WHERE `entry`=14283;
