UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Horde is in your debt, $N. You\'ve made your people proud with your courage in defending our lands.' WHERE `entry`=24225;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve brought great honor to the Horde, $N. Your victory today will ensure a thousand victories tomorrow!' WHERE `entry`=24226;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There is no greater honor than driving invaders from Horde territories. We salute your great courage in aiding our forces today!' WHERE `entry`=24426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='You\'re back!  Do you bring news of victory?' WHERE `entry`=24426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Win an Alterac Valley battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`objectives_loc6`='Win an Alterac Valley battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just what I wanted to hear!  A victory in Alterac Valley - even a temporary one - is crucial to our overall strategy against the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=24427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `RequestItemsText_loc6`='Tell me, $N. What news do you bring from the front?' WHERE `entry`=24427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What? How did you get this? Isn\'t she... Never mind the details, I suppose. You\'ll be wanting one of these baubles as recompense, no doubt.' WHERE `entry`=24428;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve brought me the head of someone who is... No, best not to think about it too hard. You\'ll be wanting recompense for your heroic deeds, no doubt.' WHERE `entry`=24429;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh yeah! I love the smell of freshly-cratered dirt! Word around camp is that the elven front line is collapsing back toward the river. Talk to Chawg and see if there\'s anything you can do to help seal the deal.' WHERE `entry`=24430;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is quite a find, $N. I can\'t have you selling this to anyone else, so I\'m willing to offer generously.' WHERE `entry`=24431;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Here you are, $C. With this you should find maneuvering in the sea to be nearly effortless. $B$BNow we must get to work. There is much to be done in little time.' WHERE `entry`=24432;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lok\'tar ogar, $N! As they discover the bodies of their comrades they will learn that no place is safe from the fury of the horde, and their will to fight will crumble.' WHERE `entry`=24433;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Images of a great and distant tree flood your mind. Your stomach lurches as you reorient the stone, briefly filling your senses with visions of a fiery portal, a towering mountain, a frigid wasteland, and a terrible scar across the earth. After a moment, the magical energies of the stone calm, and you feel you are but a step away from Valormok. Andorel\'s invasion can begin...' WHERE `entry`=24434;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='There are a lot of Naga left on this beach. Looks like you have some wet work ahead of you, $G son:girl;.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good clean fun.' WHERE `entry`=24435;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fine job there, bud. We\'ll have this beach cleaned up in no time.' WHERE `entry`=24436;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hah hah! Brilliant. Right fine job there, boy.' WHERE `entry`=24437;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Exodus',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks for stopping, $N. Our carriage got hit pretty bad. The one in front of us got it worse.' WHERE `entry`=24438;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='...Then it is done! There are still pockets of resistance around our camp, but this rearguard action appears to be masking a full-fledged retreat to Ashenvale. Azshara is ours! The Warchief will hear of this victory and your part in it. But we will surely need the help of a $C like you elsewhere. Be sure to speak with Kroum here in camp before you leave.' WHERE `entry`=24439;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Grimtotem... I\'d hoped to see the end of my days before $R attacked other $R senselessly on the very plains of Mulgore. But be proud, $N. You have done a great thing for the land, and for our people.' WHERE `entry`=24440;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. The purity with which these beasts hunt is vital in the creation of the next cleansing totem. The Thunderhorn Well is a symbol of my own tribe, and to know it is being desecrated by our own kind raises a fury in me I haven\'t felt for years.' WHERE `entry`=24441;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Mariel accepts the orders and the captured seeing crystal and examines both.>$B$BGood work, $N, and quick thinking. I\'m sure the theft of this trinket won\'t slow them down for long, but I think you\'ve bought us time to warn the leaders of the Horde and Alliance about the impending attacks.' WHERE `entry`=24442;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The quilboar have not only razed our buildings, but have taken tauren captives. I saw them take Miira Thunderhoof, a young shaman trainer of ours, away in one of their foul cages. Please, find a key on one of the quilboar\'s bodies and go save her!' WHERE `entry`=24444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N! You made it in one piece, good. We\'ve got a lot of work for you to handle for us inside the ruins, but we\'re sending you in with the best to take care of it. You\'re working with GAMA Force now, Goblin Army: Mergers and Acquisitions. Molotov says you can handle it - that\'s all I need to hear.' WHERE `entry`=24448;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='And you come with the artifact! The operation was a success then. Mergers and Acquisitions can definitely handle themselves. This thing will fetch quite a pretty penny. And you - I heard you did some impressive work down there. You may well have cut-down expenses by 10% single-handedly. That\'s the kind of smarty businessman I want in my army! Here are your wages, as promised. And a little something extra too - I hope you like it.' WHERE `entry`=24449;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work. Now that this is in our hands, we must get it to Myralion Sunblaze as soon as possible. We can\'t risk the Silver Covenant taking the book from us again.$B$BI\'ll get that tabard back to Shandy and see that he\'s well compensated for his assistance. Once the book is in Myralion\'s hands, the Silver Covenant won\'t be a threat anymore.' WHERE `entry`=24451;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hahah! Sweet deal. I\'ll get the ball rolling on this. All I need now is to find a buyer and get the go-ahead from Uncle Bedlam. Here are your wages for your work here. Excellent work, soldier.' WHERE `entry`=24452;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What?! I got left out of the action completely? Are you serious? Alright, alright... no shooting the messenger. Thanks for the news, bud. Maybe I\'ll see you back at town.' WHERE `entry`=24453;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Caladis accepts the heavy book and begins leafing through it.>$B$BI knew the symbols on the blade were familiar. The weapon was most certainly forged by the dragons and gifted to one of the mortal races, but which blade is this, and how did it come to rest in Icecrown?' WHERE `entry`=24454;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice to meet you soldier. Commander Molotov speaks highly of you.' WHERE `entry`=24455;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done great honor for both me and my ancestors today. Please, take this with my gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=24456;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I sensed you would be coming to me, $C. I can always recognize one who is trying to pass the Rites of the Earthmother.' WHERE `entry`=24457;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh! This is it! It\'s the big one! We\'re in business boys!' WHERE `entry`=24458;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well met. If Ahmo has already explained the minor quibbles of what kind of goblin we\'ll be driving from our lands, let\'s get to work.' WHERE `entry`=24459;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have remade the blade of Quel\'Delar, although Blood-Queen Lana\'thel proclaimed we could not! The blade must still be tempered, but she and her master will not stand in our way!' WHERE `entry`=24461;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You say Talrendis Point has fallen? That\'s good news! It also explains the exodus of elves I\'ve seen along this road.' WHERE `entry`=24463;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You truly amaze me, mortal. It\'s rare to meet someone so dedicated and resourceful. Azuregos and I are likely to depart Azshara and remain discrete for a while. I do hope that we meet again someday though. Perhaps to put an end to Deathwing himself. Farewell, $N. Stay safe.' WHERE `entry`=24467;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done it again, $N. You have my thanks.' WHERE `entry`=24468;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Impressive work, laddie. We can hold the perimeter from here on out. Here, take this for yer troubles. It might come in handy, as I\'ve got something more important to ask of ye...' WHERE `entry`=24469;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm... they blame us for destroying their home, ye say?  Well, that wasn\'t us, that was the horrible earthquake we had earlier today. Are they that dense that they can\'t see we nearly lost our camp too? Can\'t blame a trogg for fightin\' for his home, though.' WHERE `entry`=24470;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Many of those that y\'saved have already made it back to camp. The wounds\'re well-dressed!  Ye might have a future in first aid, if ye\'re into that sorta thing.' WHERE `entry`=24471;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You definitely got the ettin angry, $N. I heard him myself. Let\'s hope this works.' WHERE `entry`=24472;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Achh.. and what do YOU want?  Can\'t ye see I\'m busy in here!  Go an\' bother someone else, I haven\'t the time. Wait, what\'s that ye say?  Joren sent you to help?  Well why didn\'t ye say so?' WHERE `entry`=24473;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Ahh... that hits the spot. Now we can get some work done around here.' WHERE `entry`=24474;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This\'ll have to do for now. We\'ve a lot of people to feed here, but we\'ve got to make do with what we\'ve got. With any luck, King Bronzebeard in Ironforge will send us some help shortly.' WHERE `entry`=24475;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I... I don\'t understand. Tempering the sword should\'ve restored the blade to its original condition. What has happened here?' WHERE `entry`=24476;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful!  Look at this one... it must be over 200 years old! Now, onto other matters...' WHERE `entry`=24477;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Brilliant. You certainly don\'t let cold feet stop you. Or cold any part for that matter! No? ...too soon?' WHERE `entry`=24478;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I like the way you move, apprentice. Don\'t you worry about where I got all the souls from. They were obtained in a perfectly humane manner, I assure you.' WHERE `entry`=24479;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I had not thought it possible for evil to take hold in such a sword, but I suppose it was naive of me. If the greatest of dragonkind\'s creations could be corrupted and turned against them, why not a mere sword?$B$BUther\'s advice is wise, $N, and I would urge you to heed it quickly.' WHERE `entry`=24480;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Stormglen',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to see you made it, $N. It looks like most everybody did. We\'re not doing too bad so far for an emergency evacuation.' WHERE `entry`=24483;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well, $N. The spiders are everywhere, however, and I\'m afraid we\'ve barely put a dent in their numbers.' WHERE `entry`=24484;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well would you look at this!  An axe blade, a couple of arrowheads, and what appears to be some sort of rudimentary spoon. This is indeed fascinating. Thanks again for your help, $N. I\'ve much studying to keep myself occupied while Joren\'s got us under lockdown.' WHERE `entry`=24486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome, $C. Are you ready to get to work?' WHERE `entry`=24487;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s my boy! Now to get one of these useless hunks of metal in working order and you into the game!' WHERE `entry`=24488;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm... interesting. From what you\'re saying, it sounds like a fire elemental might have snuck in from Searing Gorge. Or, the earthquake opened up a crack to the elemental plane... Either way, this is bad news. You should probably report this information to Grelin.' WHERE `entry`=24489;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='To Ironforge?  Well first, you\'ll need to go through Kharanos, and before that, you\'ll have to go through this tunnel.' WHERE `entry`=24490;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Milo Geartwinge, reporting for duty. You sent up a distress signal?' WHERE `entry`=24491;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Took you long enough. Hold on tight, and take a good hard look!  Chances are you won\'t be coming back here for quite some time.' WHERE `entry`=24492;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Coldridge Valley?  I\'ve got my own problems here!  What, they can\'t deal with a couple of troggs?  And trolls?  And incursions from the elemental plane? Actually, on second thought, that\'s kind of a lot. I\'m surprised they\'re doing as well as they are. I\'ll see what I can do.' WHERE `entry`=24493;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are dark days, friend. Look around you... even here in remote Coldridge, the sprits are rebelling. The land is crying out for help. Yet still, even in times such as these, the spirits will always turn an ear to those who ask for their assistance.' WHERE `entry`=24494;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. It will take some time, but I\'ll try to make sense of what we have.' WHERE `entry`=24495;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The power of the arcane is everywhere, $N. Only some of us have the ability to see it, and fewer still possess the ability to master it. You are one of those few.' WHERE `entry`=24496;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s past time that these night elf scum be purged from Azshara. Glad to have an able body like you to sink the point home. Ready to get to work?' WHERE `entry`=24497;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well this day. With many of the slaves freed and now with access to the forges, it will not be long before I have a strong force to aid in delivering us from Scourgelord Tyrannus and this foul pit.' WHERE `entry`=24498;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just in time! Thank you, $N.$B$BThe Pit of Saron lies ahead, and if our scouts are correct, past that will be the Halls of Reflection. It is there that Arthas lets his guard down, and it is there that we hope to find a clue to his weakness... or maybe, just maybe, his redemption.' WHERE `entry`=24499;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Jaina is still catching her breath.>$B$BI can barely believe we\'re still alive. It was foolish of me to follow him. I\'ve made that mistake too many times. And you... it was reckless of you to come after me instead of escaping with the information! But... well... thank you. You truly are a hero.$B$BWith Uther\'s guidance, we may stand a chance at defeating Arthas. All the lives lost today were not in vain.' WHERE `entry`=24500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great job, $N. We\'ve heard rumors of survivors further in the mountains. Now we\'ll be able to send scouts there.' WHERE `entry`=24501;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Uh... you did it, kid. You REALLY did it! We won the game and.... DID YOU SEE THAT DRAGON?!!!' WHERE `entry`=24503;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Patrolling the high road is grave business, but it must be done. These narrow mountain trails are, for the time being, one of our only lifelines into Stonetalon. They must be preserved.$B$BThank you.' WHERE `entry`=24504;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So the Alliance is probing the twists and turns of the high road?$B$BEven if they were to map it out, they couldn\'t attack these hills in numbers. This is our land, $N. And they will pay dearly for presuming otherwise.' WHERE `entry`=24505;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good. $N, I know of you. You\'ll be perfect for these tasks.$B$BWe\'ve been afforded a rare chance to delve into Icecrown Citadel, but we must move quickly if we\'re to avoid Arthas\' notice.' WHERE `entry`=24506;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well this day. With many of the slaves freed and now with access to the forges, it will not be long before I have a strong force to aid in delivering us from Scourgelord Tyrannus and this foul pit.' WHERE `entry`=24507;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N! I\'m so glad you\'ve come.$B$BWe\'ve been afforded a rare chance to delve into Icecrown Citadel, but we must move quickly if we\'re to avoid Arthas\' notice.' WHERE `entry`=24510;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well timed, $C!$B$BThe Pit of Saron lies ahead, and if our scouts are correct, past that will be the Halls of Reflection. It is there that Arthas lets his guard down, and it is there that we hope to find a clue to his weakness... and a route to vengeance long overdue.' WHERE `entry`=24511;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='From up here I got the perfect view of the havoc you just caused, $N. Our lost brothers reclaimed some of their dignity, and the Alliance dogs were sent scrambling. Sharp work, my friend!$B$BIf the Alliance sleeps comfortably at night, we are not doing our job.$B$BWe will never let up.$B$BWe will never give in.' WHERE `entry`=24512;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have them? I\'ll take your word for it. Hearing Peake scream like one of his victims is reward enough for me.$B$BNow leave me be, $N. I do not wish to be a burden to my clan.' WHERE `entry`=24513;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Onatay looks over the fresh hides, nodding her head slowly.>$B$BYes $N, I can work with these. You work fast!$B$BThese hides will help us hold out for reinforcements longer. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=24514;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So my sister recognized the old signals? Her hunter\'s eyes are as sharp as ever.$B$B$N, when we first set up this camp we were at the edge of this jungle. Now look at it!$B$BSomething is amiss.' WHERE `entry`=24515;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent, $N. It will be some time before we can assault the hold proper, but until then, we must teach them to fear the Barrens.' WHERE `entry`=24517;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Kilrok pages through the plans you discovered.>$B$BThis explains much, $N. No wonder our foes are so hellbent on taking the southern Barrens. It\'s at the center of their plans for the continent!$B$BBut they didn\'t account for us, did they $C?' WHERE `entry`=24518;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, good. We\'ve got to keep Honor\'s Stand isolated.$B$BAlone ... afraid ... $N, if we keep up the pressure, maybe someday they\'ll simply surrender the pass.' WHERE `entry`=24519;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re kidding, right?! DEATHWING?!!! Okay, this\'ll work out just fine. We\'ll throw your party and by the time it\'s over, I\'m sure that the dragon will be long gone and the ground will stop shaking. If not, we can always charter a ship off of the island.' WHERE `entry`=24520;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Admit you to the Sunwell? That\'s impossible! The Sunwell is the most sacred and important site of our people. We have only recently reclaimed it with the help of the Shattered Sun Offensive. It is not a place for tourists or travelers.' WHERE `entry`=24522;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very good, $N. I can feel the sacrifice of the land in this offering, and my spirit swells with sadness, and pride.' WHERE `entry`=24523;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done it. You have cleaned the wells, and healed our land. Bloodhoof village is grateful, $N.$B$BMay the wind whisper your deeds for a hundred seasons, and may the waters of Mulgore remain clean forever.' WHERE `entry`=24524;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So it is done.$B$BNormally these scavengers are part of the Earthmother\'s cycle of life. But on the heels of the devastation wracked by both the Alliance and the cataclysm, their numbers grow overwhelming. It is good to thin them out.' WHERE `entry`=24525;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Excellent!  Let\'s get started.$B$BFirst, you\'re going to have to learn the spell Arcane Missiles. This spell is a little bit different from others you\'ve learned in the past. Each time you cast another spell, you have a chance to create an opening to use Arcane Missiles. Why not get a feel for the spell using those training dummies the militia trainees put up outside the entrance to Anvilmar?',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Arcane Missiles from Teegli Merrowith. Successfully cast Arcane Missiles 2 times on the Training Dummies outside the entrance to Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='There we go!  One spell down, many many more to go. Come back to me after you\'ve had some experience casting this spell, and I\'ll show you some more tricks.' WHERE `entry`=24526;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Excellent!  Let us begin.$B$BThe first skill you will learn is that of the Primal Strike. The primal spirits, when called upon, will strengthen your arm to deliver a mighty blow.$B$BHelpful, isn\'t it?',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Primal Strike from Teo Hammerstorm, then use Primal Strike 2 times on a Training Dummy near the entrance of Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='This has been but one of many footfalls on the long path of the $C. Come back to me after you\'ve had some experience in the field, and I will help guide you on your next step.' WHERE `entry`=24527;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Are ya ready to start?  Wonderful!  We\'re glad to have ya.$B$BBefore ya go back outside, I\'m gonna need ya to learn the Seal of Righteousness. It will grant Holy damage to your swings, helping ya dispatch yer enemies quicker.$B$BThe other thing yer gonna want to know is that any time ya have a seal active, ya can use the light to judge yer enemies. Yer judgement will deal damage each time ye invoke it.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Seal of Righteousness and Judgment from Bromos Grummner. After casting Seal of Righteousness on yourself, use Judgment on one of the Training Dummies at the entrance to Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='There, ya did it. The Light favors quick learners like you. Come back to me after you\'ve spent some time using what I\'ve taught ya, and I\'ll show ya something new.' WHERE `entry`=24528;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s bad enough to have one\'s village sacked... but to spend the following night in a quilboar cage? I\'m glad you were there to help, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24529;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Lesson one. Aside from your sword and shield, what\'s the most important tool you have in your arsenal?$B$B<Thran awaits your response.>$B$BOh never mind, I\'ll answer it for you. It\'s your mobility. One of the strengths of the warrior is the ability to get around the battlefield quickly. Here, $N, I\'ll train you to use your legs to your advantage.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Charge from Thran Khorman, then use Charge on one of the Training Dummies outside the entrance to Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now we\'re getting somewhere. You\'ve got quite a manly bellow, sir! Come back to me in a bit, and I\'ll teach you something else.' WHERE `entry`=24531;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='One of the things that makes a rogue dangerous is our ability to use combinations of combat maneuvers and wait for the chance to use a devastating technique.$B$BNow that you\'ve had a chance to master Sinister Strike, it\'s time to show you a new skill you can use as a follow up.$B$BPlease, allow me to train you.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Evisecerate from Solm Hargrin, then use Eviscerate 3 times on the Training Dummies near the entrance to Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve got the hang of it. Go get some practice out there... maybe take out a few of those troggs or trolls. Or rabbits, I don\'t care. Return after you\'ve gotten some practice, and I\'ll show you another trick of the trade.' WHERE `entry`=24532;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Now, if ya DO want to become somethin\' special, ye\'ll need to talk to me. A priest is nothin\' without his spells. And I know a couple of spells that I might be able to teach ya.$B$BThe first is a quick heal that can fix ya up when you\'ve taken damage. Tell me, $G boy; lass:, do ya ever take damage?',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Flash Heal from Branstock Khalder, then cast Flash Heal 5 times on Wounded Militia members in Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. You\'ll make a fine $C in due time. Return to me after you\'ve proven yourself a bit more, and I\'ll reward you by teaching you another spell or two.' WHERE `entry`=24533;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What? He attacked you with a dozen boars? I guess quilboar have their own ideas of what "single combat" means.$B$BStill, the Bristleback will be left reeling after the blow you delivered. It will not be long before a new champion rises amongst them to stir up trouble... but at least this buys us some time to get these refugees relocated safely.$B$BThank you, $N. The survivors owe you a great debt.' WHERE `entry`=24534;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I confess that I did not expect Thalorien\'s spirit to recognize you as the heir to Quel\'Delar, but I defer to his judgment. You may enter the Sunwell, but I remind you that you are a guest in the most our most sacred of precincts, and you should act accordingly.' WHERE `entry`=24535;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey, thanks, kid. Give it over, let\'s take a look. Oh, that ain\'t good.' WHERE `entry`=24536;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. But now on to the larger question:$B$BWhere is this overgrowth coming from? And why is it raging out of control?' WHERE `entry`=24539;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome back, $N. What was done was not for revenge, or pride. It was simply to protect Thunder Bluff, and all our people, from torment and fear. Today, Mulgore is safe once more. The Earth Mother thanks you for all your brave deeds, $N, as do I. You have earned your reward, hero. May you be welcome in Thunder Bluff always.' WHERE `entry`=24540;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You got it, huh? Good job, kid. Top notch. Let\'s see what we got here.' WHERE `entry`=24541;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, samples from different parts of the overgrowth? These will be immensely helpful, yes. Thank you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=24542;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Kirge listens intently and then falls to one knee.>$B$BAlive! My boy still lives! Praise to the earthmother, I still have a son.$B$B<Kirge composes himself.>$B$B$C, my boy\'s mother didn\'t make it out of Taurajo alive. I will avenge her death, even if it means my son grows up without either of his parents.' WHERE `entry`=24543;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A deep sense of dread washes over you as the flame devours the items.' WHERE `entry`=24545;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you held your ground! With tenacity like yours we may yet drive the Alliance from our lands.' WHERE `entry`=24546;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You seem to have endured this leg of your trial admirably, $R. Pray that fate continues to smile upon you in your endeavor...' WHERE `entry`=24547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These should suffice, $C. Speak to me when Shadow\'s Edge has been thoroughly empowered and I will attempt its completion.' WHERE `entry`=24548;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Congratulations, $C. Against insurmountable odds, you have weathered the storm. I trust that you shall find your reward proportionate to your conviction...' WHERE `entry`=24549;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome to Thunder Bluff, $N. You\'ve done great things for our people. Tell me of your journey.' WHERE `entry`=24550;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Bloodhilt looks at the badges, then allows them to spill from his hands onto the sands below. His lips curl open into a toothy grin.>$B$BNow THIS is what I like to see, $C! What is your name again?$B$BYou will go far here.' WHERE `entry`=24551;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah yes... I see a cunning in your eyes that was not present before. Well done, $C.' WHERE `entry`=24552;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is unbelievable, $N. You\'ve really done it! All of the quel\'dorei have heard of Thalorien Dawnseeker and Quel\'Delar, but no one ever thought the sword would be restored.' WHERE `entry`=24553;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Myralion takes the hilt from you and scrutinizes the artifact.>$B$BThis came from the citadel? What was it doing there? This blade is certainly not of Scourge manufacture.$B$BWeapons of this quality can only be crafted by a few of Azeroth\'s creatures. We will have to consult them and see if they can help us identify it.' WHERE `entry`=24554;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We must recover that book from the Silver Covenant. Without that book from Krasus, we stand little chance of solving the mystery of the sword in Icecrown or unlocking its power.' WHERE `entry`=24555;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew Shandy would find a way to make it work. Let me get this enchanted and ready for you to use. With any luck, the tabard\'s owner won\'t even know it\'s missing and Shandy will cover the rest of our tracks.' WHERE `entry`=24556;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Magister Hathorel reads the captured orders.>$B$BThe agent you intercepted was supposed to deliver the Wyrmrest tome to Icecrown, after meeting with one Arcanist Tybalin inside the Silver Enclave. We have to reclaim that book, $N, and we only have one chance before it leaves the city. We have to work quickly.' WHERE `entry`=24557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Myralion accepts the heavy book and begins leafing through it.>$B$BThose symbols on the blade seemed familiar and now there\'s little wonder why. This is certainly a dragon blade, gifted to one of the mortal races, but which blade is this, and how did it come to rest in Icecrown?' WHERE `entry`=24558;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have remade the blade of Quel\'Delar in defiance of that Blood-Queen Lana\'thel\'s pronouncement! Now, the blade must be tempered before we can show her the folly of her words.' WHERE `entry`=24559;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Tempering the sword should\'ve restored the blade. Why hasn\'t it worked?' WHERE `entry`=24560;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='How can evil take root in such a sword? I would not have thought it possible if the evidence wasn\'t here before my eyes. If the greatest of dragonkind\'s creations could be corrupted and turned against them, why not a mere sword?$B$BI believe Uther is right. You must heed his advice quickly, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24561;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hope you understand that I can\'t just admit you to the Sunwell, $N. This is the most sacred place known to the sin\'dorei and we have only recently regained control over it.$B$BYou would raise the hopes of our people with tales of Quel\'Delar? Without proof of the truth of your claims, I see no reason to take you at your word.' WHERE `entry`=24562;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You truly do carry Quel\'Delar. This is a great day for all of Quel\'Thalas and the sin\'dorei. You have my leave to enter the Sunwell and finish the sword\'s restoration. Keep your head high, $N. The children of Silvermoon have dreamt of this day for years.' WHERE `entry`=24563;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE `entry`=24564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. I\'m pleased to see you return intact; the viciousness I\'ve been seeing among these creatures is startling.' WHERE `entry`=24565;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh dear. It seems the forces at work here are a bit difficult to control...$B$BPlease, don\'t bother Naralex with this. It will only upset him.' WHERE `entry`=24566;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There you are, my boy! Quick, there\'s no time to waste! We need to get one of these shredders back in working order. I\'m bringing you off the bench... you\'re going to win the game and the title for us!' WHERE `entry`=24567;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Siegebreaker',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very good. Now, should they storm the gates, they will have to do so with infantry.$B$BDo you think they have the stomach for that?' WHERE `entry`=24569;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These will do perfectly. Bright colors like these don\'t occur naturally in the barrens, but they haven\'t developed any other mutations so far.' WHERE `entry`=24570;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m concerned by how...active these are. Nevertheless, it simply means we must continue to act quickly before the corruption here becomes worse.' WHERE `entry`=24571;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. I\'ll have their bodies strung up along the gold road as a message to the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=24572;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Winnoa bows her head.>$B$BThank you.' WHERE `entry`=24573;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Yonada Eulogized',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Omusa Eulogized' WHERE `entry`=24573;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Naralex slowly takes the squirming heart from you, visibly disturbed.>$B$BI\'ve been a fool. The one truth I did not want to accept has been staring me in the face this entire time...this foul thing is proof of that.$B$BYou and I have much work to do.' WHERE `entry`=24574;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done it again, $N. The freed villagers are eager to help us against the Forsaken in any way they can.' WHERE `entry`=24575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You got his ledger? Really? That\'s great, $N. There\'s probably loads of good information in here.' WHERE `entry`=24576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Gar\'dul breaks into a sweat.>$B$BLook - ah - let\'s not discuss this here, in front of the men...' WHERE `entry`=24577;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve been expecting you, $N. Do not be alarmed. My name is Belrysa. I am a priestess of the moon... a night elf. You might not know my people, but the destinies of our two races have been linked since the Curse befell you.' WHERE `entry`=24578;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With Sartharion slain, surely Deathwing and Sinestra\'s plans are now stalled.' WHERE `entry`=24579;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Word of your success precedes you, $C. Anub\'Rekhan is no more. You did him a great service, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24580;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s one less thorn in our side. With Noth destroyed, Scourge research into refining the means of creating the undead will grind to a halt.' WHERE `entry`=24581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $C. The Scourge military command out of Naxxramas has been thrown into disarray by Razuvious\'s demise.' WHERE `entry`=24582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Children everywhere will sleep easier knowing that Patchwerk is no more.' WHERE `entry`=24583;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With Malygos defeated, the Nexus War should come to a swift conclusion. You have the gratitude of the Kirin Tor, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I never cease to be amazed by the horrors that can be created through the use of technology.' WHERE `entry`=24585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now Veranus can finally rest in peace.' WHERE `entry`=24586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I trust that you did not have to face too many of his iron construct assistants?' WHERE `entry`=24587;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The greatest weakness of Ulduar is its masters\' blind faith in their inventions to protect it.' WHERE `entry`=24588;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='All of Azeroth is fortunate that Timear foresaw the Eredar lord\'s arrival and that you were there in time to slay him.' WHERE `entry`=24589;
