UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You... You\'re not Snivel. Did he send you? He\'s so late, I had started to give up hope...$B$B<Tears start welling up in the woman\'s eyes once she realizes that you aren\'t there to deliver a message from Snivel.>$B$BThat\'s not like my Snivel, but what other choice is there?' WHERE `entry`=24848;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='All he talked about was leaving town with all his money? Then he really has abandoned me, hasn\'t he?$B$BOh, $N, I was such a fool to fall for him, but how could I help myself? He was so irresistible!' WHERE `entry`=24849;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc6`='Stormwind Counting House searched',`ObjectiveText2_loc6`='Stormwind Auction House searched' WHERE `entry`=24849;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re not Snivel. He was supposed to be here an hour ago! What have you done with him? This isn\'t like my sweet Snivel. Do you think something\'s happened to him?' WHERE `entry`=24850;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='All he talked about was leaving town with all his money? Then he really has abandoned me, hasn\'t he? I can\'t believe I fell for such a horrible goblin! But he was so irresistible when we first met.' WHERE `entry`=24851;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc6`='Orgrimmar Bank searched',`ObjectiveText2_loc6`='Orgrimmar Auction House searched' WHERE `entry`=24851;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks to you, our people are free to fight for our home.' WHERE `entry`=24852;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Zen\'Aliri was wise to send you here. I\'ve hit a dead end in my studies.' WHERE `entry`=24854;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The scent of bloodpetal pollen hangs about your head, $C. This is good. You\'ve earned your reward.' WHERE `entry`=24855;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Boss, we gotta problem.' WHERE `entry`=24856;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is quite alarming indeed! But with this information we can call on our brethren from Bloodhoof Village to help thwart the attack. You have saved the lives of many $R, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24857;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I wish I could have seen the looks on their scaly faces when you blew up their banners and replaced them with our own. On second thought, I don\'t want to be close enough to see their snarls.' WHERE `entry`=24858;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'re going to be filthy rich, I tell you! Well, if we can get off of this island, that is.' WHERE `entry`=24859;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There is balance in all things. As Greatmother Hawkwind\'s spirit takes its final journey, you will begin your first.' WHERE `entry`=24861;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They\'re ambushing the roads to Stonetalon, too? We just can\'t get a break here. Where are they coming from, anyways?' WHERE `entry`=24862;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What ... our supplies? These were meant for Stonetalon. No matter, at the rate we\'re going, we need them more here. Honor\'s Stand has been cut off from the coast, $N. Commander Singleton is at his wit\'s end.' WHERE `entry`=24863;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, they\'re so cute! I wish that we could turn them into little plush toys and sell them for a gazillion macaroons!' WHERE `entry`=24864;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh... wow... it\'s some really old food. Hey Hol\'anyee, take a look at this!  This $R brought us those old rations that we abandoned! No, not from Marshal\'s Refuge... from the old base camp! I\'m not sure I want to peek inside. I\'ll just give it to Nolen, I guess... he\'ll know what to do with it.' WHERE `entry`=24865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well I\'ll be... that\'s Shizzle\'s old portable dinomometer!  Where did you find this? I\'m surprised it\'s still functional, even after all these years. I\'ll have it delivered to Shizzle promptly.' WHERE `entry`=24866;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A faceless of the deep? What\'s that? That does NOT sound like a naga! Well, you killed it, whatever it was. It doesn\'t matter now. We have other fish to fry....' WHERE `entry`=24868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N!$B$BI owe you a debt of gratitude for rescuing a friend whom I had thought forever lost to the clutches of the Cult. And the Argent Crusade owes you a debt for the invaluable intelligence Darnavan brings with him from his time walking the halls of this Citadel as one of the Cult.$B$BPlease, take this as a token of this appreciation, and may the Light bolster you as you carve a path through this terrible place.' WHERE `entry`=24869;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Whew, I thought I was a goner! I heard talk of a resurrection ritual going on in these Halls and went in for a closer look, but one of those blasted vampires sniffed me out. They strung me up here, draining my life energy and hoping I\'d break and divulge our plans of attack. As if I even know what Tirion has planned!$B$BPlease, take these spoils of war as a small token of gratitude for saving my life.' WHERE `entry`=24879;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N? We\'re saved! Who am I kidding? We\'re all going to die!!!' WHERE `entry`=24897;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Okay, I think that\'s good enough for now, but they took a bunch of the townsfolk captive. We\'re going to have to take the fight to them!' WHERE `entry`=24901;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Plague?  Something so heinous that not even the orcs condone its use?  I\'d say this warrants notifying King Greymane.' WHERE `entry`=24902;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You present me with the most difficult choice of my life, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24903;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'ve driven the Forsaken back. We hold three out of the four districts. But at what cost...' WHERE `entry`=24904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc6`='Battle for Gilneas City Complete' WHERE `entry`=24904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='You know, while you were out doin\' your thing, Megs stopped by here. I hadn\'t seen her in months, but she barely gave me the time of day, just wanted me to tell you she had more business lined up.$B$BShe said she was headed over to the Dunemaul Compound to set up shop, something about ogres. Since you\'re done here, might as well head over...I woundn\'t keep a goblin like her waiting.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve got a great one for you this time, $N. We\'re gonna initiate these ogres into the Horde...working directly under us.' WHERE `entry`=24905;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm, mostly usable. This is good stuff. I\'ve already got buyers lined up, of course. Here\'s your advance for the rest of the work you\'re gonna do for me and the Bilgewater Cartel...partner.' WHERE `entry`=24906;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Property values have already gone up since you left. People like seafront views that don\'t include briny, gnarled giants stomping around. Here\'s your cut, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24907;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='[NOT USED] Build the Fort Placeholder',`details_loc6`='Nice work! For our next placeholder, talk to that dude. Uh, Foreman Franklin. Special stuff will happen.' WHERE `entry`=24908;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Isn\'t it nice when you can do a good deed, and see enormous future financial gains from it? It warms my little goblin heart. And my big goblin wallet. You did great, kid. Gadgetzan\'s gonna be ours soon. Here\'s a little token of my appreciation.' WHERE `entry`=24910;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey Hol\'anyee, look at the getup on this one! Ahem. Our recruiter sent you?  Good. Let\'s start out with a bit of honesty: Un\'Goro isn\'t the perfect nirvana that you may have been promised. You\'ve probably figured that out on the way over here, though. Shall we get to work?' WHERE `entry`=24911;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Stand Clear, $C, and steady yourself.' WHERE `entry`=24912;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am moved, $N. Prophet Velen has been in closely guarded seclusion. He has dared not waste his energy on anything save preparing for the final confrontation he has foretold. And yet, he came here, in person, to comfort a single dying soul. I must thank you as well, for helping me make my last effort to comfort my friend. My research will continue... and I hope that Magtoor will continue to watch over me.' WHERE `entry`=24913;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Impossible... Father, is it you?! You have done me a great service, hero. I offer you the reins of my faithful steed. Do with it as you please, but do not forget those that assisted you in this monumental feat.' WHERE `entry`=24915;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What... how did you manage to come by this!? You have done me a great service, hero. My heart could not bear to keep this locket, but I will place an enchantment upon it that you may find useful. Do with it as you please, but do not forget those that assisted you in this monumental feat.' WHERE `entry`=24916;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Aye. I know this blade... and I will treasure it always - a moment of time that will be lost forever. You have done me a great service, hero. I offer you a gift from the Frostborn dwarves. Do with it as you please, but do not forget those that assisted you in this monumental feat.' WHERE `entry`=24917;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Sylvanas silently reflects for a moment before returning her gaze to you.>$B$BYou have done me a great service, hero. I offer you the boon of the Banshee Queen. Do with it as you please, but do not forget those that assisted you in this monumental feat.' WHERE `entry`=24918;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Uther stares at the medal, speechless for a moment.>$B$BArthas\' medal.$B$BI remember well the day I presented it to him...$B$BYou have done me a great service, hero. My soul may now rest in peace. I offer you a memory lost in time. Do with it as you please, but do not forget those that assisted you in this monumental feat.' WHERE `entry`=24919;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well, $N. Almost everybody managed to make it through.' WHERE `entry`=24920;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hm? What unit are you with, $C? No matter, we need all hands. My fleet is in tatters and they\'ve broken into the hold. You armed? That\'s good enough for me.' WHERE `entry`=24921;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N? What are you doing wearing that pygmy helm? Looks like it\'s about to fall apart. I\'m glad that they sent you up here. I thought for sure they were going to send that jerk, Grapplehammer and his ego-enabling assistant.' WHERE `entry`=24924;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great job, but that\'s not even half of the hostages that they took from town. Darn it all! They must have taken the rest of the captives to their other villages up in the volcano!' WHERE `entry`=24925;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='She decided to stay?  Fascinating... I\'ll have to look over this data and find out why. Thank you again, $N. I really appreciate it.' WHERE `entry`=24926;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m pleased to report that our brand recognition in this area has skyrocketed now that you\'ve killed most of the people who didn\'t want us here.' WHERE `entry`=24927;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful job. Have you ever thought about becoming a full-time arsonist? I know a few people, it\'s a nice gig. Well, we\'ll chit-chat about that one later. More to do here!' WHERE `entry`=24928;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice work, bud! Hope he wasn\'t too tough.' WHERE `entry`=24929;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='If I hadn\'t seen you kill a few of the mangy things with my own eyes, I\'d think you did not complete the task I asked of you. It looks like we\'re hardly putting a dent in their numbers.' WHERE `entry`=24930;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahh, perfect! Just what I need...full of potent focusing energies... ...ahem! I mean, perfect for my collection! Narain Soothfancy is in no need of artificial enhancement of any kind! Now take your pay and be off!' WHERE `entry`=24931;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This isn\'t goin\' fast enough. There\'s gotta be a faster way...' WHERE `entry`=24932;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Man, this stuff looks delicious. I\'m half tempted to just fry some up myself. No! We\'ve gotta focus on gettin\' out of here. Maybe just one piece...' WHERE `entry`=24933;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You make a hell of a marine, $N. We\'ll mop up the others. But it looks like the Horde fleet is disengaging - maybe to land more troops ashore? Admiral Aubrey will know what to do. Talk to me when you\'re ready to fly back!' WHERE `entry`=24934;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They turned some of our people into zombies? Tell me something I don\'t know....' WHERE `entry`=24937;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Aubrey sent you? Good! I take it you know your way around a cannon?' WHERE `entry`=24938;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ho ho! The beach is ours! We just might keep a foothold on this miserable dustball of a continent after all.' WHERE `entry`=24939;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My star player has arrived!' WHERE `entry`=24940;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Horde is massing at the base of the hill. Breathlessly, you stuff the debris you collected into the muzzle of the cannon, step back, cover one ear, and tug on the igniter cord...' WHERE `entry`=24941;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did it! No more zombies to worry about. Let\'s pause a moment in silence for the stinky departed. Okay, done.' WHERE `entry`=24942;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great work! We\'ve knocked them on their heels, maybe long enough to shore up our defenses. Provided we find a way to take out their artillery...' WHERE `entry`=24943;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A steady stream of the walking wounded have come up the hill to see me, $N. I trust that was your work? Well done!' WHERE `entry`=24944;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I gotta tell you, that\'s a load off of my mind. That is, I won\'t have to worry about no new zombies coming after my brains!' WHERE `entry`=24945;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This will do. In fact, it\'s more than we need. I devised an ingenious idea for a weapon that the boots will be turned into once you get them to Hobart. Hand the powder over and I\'ll load it into the the Super Booster Rocket Boots.' WHERE `entry`=24946;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Momentum',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good thing you\'re here! I\'m gonna need a lot of help if we want to beat these gnomes to the punch.' WHERE `entry`=24947;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good! Without heavy equipment, the Horde will have to pull back to regroup. We\'ve bought ourselves some time to re-secure the fortress. Well done!' WHERE `entry`=24948;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Beautiful! And to think these idiots were just sitting on it. Here\'s a bit up front, we\'ll talk about profit-sharing bonuses later.' WHERE `entry`=24949;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Sea giants? You think he was training them towards Gadgetzan on purpose? Whatever, he\'s splitsville now. And Gadgetzan owes us big time! I can\'t wait to see the look on Marin\'s face. Here\'s your cut, babe. You\'re moving up in the world.' WHERE `entry`=24950;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Look at the size of it! It\'s glorious. This ugly sucker\'s gonna help us bring down the whole hive.' WHERE `entry`=24951;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There\'s no time to waste, boy! What\'s wrong with the actuator on the left boot?!' WHERE `entry`=24952;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh man, that was awesome! You should\'ve seen the flames coming out of the hive! Here\'s your reward, for entertaining me as much as for clearing the hive!' WHERE `entry`=24953;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Careful with those glands, $N, careful! And now to load them into the refashioned shredder boot. I\'m certain that you\'ll be surprised and amazed by my genius invention.' WHERE `entry`=24954;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Un-Chartered',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wow, nice work! I\'m amazed you even got them to hold a pen without eating it. You can uh, just throw the suit over there. Away from me. In the fire.' WHERE `entry`=24955;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Rageroar\'s battleships intercepted our vessel as we fled from Gilneas. We were to be carried here as trophies to the Warchief. As we neared the shore, some of us fought back. Rageroar - he began killing indiscriminately - howling with laughter. Our ship capsized and he ordered his men to fire at us as we drowned. Few of us made it to land. Afterwards, I learned that he wore my brother\'s scalp as... as a trophy.' WHERE `entry`=24956;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ugh! This entire camp is like a sampler course of awful smells. Let\'s not handle these things any longer than we have to.' WHERE `entry`=24957;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Volcanoth!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I managed to get everyone else safely back to town. Jump in, we gotta get out of here before the volcano blows for good!!!' WHERE `entry`=24958;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello there. You must be... $N?' WHERE `entry`=24959;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well, $C. As you can see, not all of us have resigned to our fates. I\'m glad to see that you\'re at least willing to work. Valdred will be a valuable asset to the Forsaken. As for the other two... there is not much we can do. We cannot force them to join us.' WHERE `entry`=24960;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You say she ran away?  What a shame. Very well. As long as she\'s maintained her free will, there\'s still hope.' WHERE `entry`=24961;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I will be here to train you as you grow in experience... find me as often as you like. I charge a minimal fee, but you\'ll find everything I can teach you to be worthwhile. Go now and test your skill. Many more things will become known to you as you gain experience, some of which I am unable to discuss with you here. Just know that Sylvanas will need hunters with your type of cunning in the future. You will be the backbone of our salvation. Do not forget it.' WHERE `entry`=24962;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good job, you\'ve taught half the ogres here to fear and respect anything vaguely $R-shaped. It\'s amazing what a little reward will do to keep people under your thumb, isn\'t it? Here\'s your payment, by the way. ...what\'s with that look?' WHERE `entry`=24963;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I\'ve been told that I\'m supposed to train you how to be a hunter. That\'s all well and good, but in my opinion, you\'ll get more training out in the field than you will talking about theories with me.$B$BI suppose I can show you a couple of my tricks. Here, come take a look at this...',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Steady Shot from Xavier the Huntsman in Deathknell, then practice using Steady Shot 5 times on a Training Dummy.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You seem to be somewhat of a natural, $N. This is good. I can\'t teach you everything myself. Go, practice what we\'ve discussed today. Return when you\'re stronger, and we\'ll cover some more tricks and abilities.' WHERE `entry`=24964;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Let\'s get some work done, shall we?  I\'ve got a new spell for you. You interested?$B$BThis spell won\'t work like anything you\'ve previously learned. Each time you cast another spell, there\'s a chance you\'ll have an opening to cast Arcane Missiles.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Arcane Missiles from Isabella in Deathknell, then practice using Arcane Missiles 2 times against a Training Dummy.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve got to admit, the spell I just taught you probably won\'t increase your intellect severalfold. That was a lie to get you to buy my services. But it will still be a helpful spell for you and your allies. No hard feelings!' WHERE `entry`=24965;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='A Forsaken priest is a curious beast,$B$G his: her; path an unusual course.$B$G His: Her; shadowy rites cannot come from the Light, so $G he: she; seeks a more sinister source.$B$BNot only has the world forsaken us, $N... it seems the Light has left us as well. As the poem hints, however... we are not without power.$B$BFirst, I shall teach you a fast heal to repair damage. Speak with me again, and I will share with you the word\'s proper incantation.',`objectives_loc6`='Train Flash Heal from Dark Cleric Duesten in Deathknell. Then, practice casting Flash Heal 5 times on Wounded Deathguards.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re a good student, $N. You\'ll go far. If you ever need any further training, return to me and I\'ll happily oblige.' WHERE `entry`=24966;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='As you continue your career as a warlock, you\'ll find it helpful to keep your spellbook filled with the latest incantations. Lucky for you, I know these spells, and I\'m willing to train you... for a price.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Immolate from Maximillion in Deathknell, then practice casting Immolate 5 times on a Training Dummy.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Congratulations... you\'re one step closer to being a master of the dark arts. Go practice a bit, and return when you\'re stronger. I\'ll have more to teach you then.' WHERE `entry`=24968;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='If you want to become a stronger warrior, you\'ll need to work on your weapons. You\'ll find stronger swords and larger shields out on your adventures, that I have no doubt about. However, as a warrior you also shouldn\'t forget your legs. $B$BTrain with me, $N, and I\'ll show you how to move quickly around the battlefield. You care to learn?',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Charge from Dannal Stern in Deathknell, then practice using Charge on a Training Dummy.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have the makings of a great $C, $N. Go, practice what we\'ve discussed, and return when you are stronger. Then I may have more to teach you.' WHERE `entry`=24969;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N. You made it. You see those tents up there?  That\'s where we\'re headed. The battle\'s probably already started.' WHERE `entry`=24970;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Being born again under the power of a val\'kyr is a strenuous process. Many don\'t survive the shock, turning into zombies or ghouls. Others retain just enough humanity to seem normal on the outside... but they\'re sick inside. We should have slain those rotbrains the day they were raised. As for you... you\'re a strong $C, $N. I knew you\'d do well. You\'ll be headed out of Deathknell soon.' WHERE `entry`=24971;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, this is very good. You\'ve done well in obtaining this information, $N. Hmm... names of the Scarlet Crusade officers in the Tirisfal Glades... Imagine the blow we could deal to the morale of those bloody zealots if we were to kill their leaders in one swift strike. I will pass this information forward.' WHERE `entry`=24972;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, it\'s a start. It\'ll take a few weeks or months to fully clean out the infestation. After that, we\'ll have to get down there with some torches to burn away the webbing. You\'ve done your duty well, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24973;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, look at him!  Isn\'t he the most adorable thing you\'ve ever seen?  Thank you, $N. I feel more energetic already.' WHERE `entry`=24974;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have performed your bidding well, young $C. You are proving yourself to be quite an asset to The Dark Lady\'s army.' WHERE `entry`=24975;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Now comes the fun part.' WHERE `entry`=24976;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='By the Light!  Finally some food!  Sweet, sweet pumpkin. . . .' WHERE `entry`=24977;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve the makings of a mighty $C, $R. I heard the cries of those humans from all the way over here. Perhaps soon we will be rid of this human blight.' WHERE `entry`=24978;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Scarlet Crusade takes no prisoners. That they would do so with this young woman... curious. The powers that you describe are even curiouser. She passed through the bars of her prison and killed her captor?  Why hadn\'t she done that in the first place?' WHERE `entry`=24979;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc6`='Find the Scarlet Prisoner' WHERE `entry`=24979;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Most excellent, $C. Your skill in the art of combat is undeniable.' WHERE `entry`=24980;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It sounds like we\'ll have to keep our eyes out for this Voss character. I don\'t expect any Forsaken to receive a reward if we capture her... I\'m just worried she\'ll eventually turn against us.' WHERE `entry`=24981;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, I\'m Brill\'s local magistrate, reporting directly to the Dark Lady. Impress me, and you may end up meeting the Banshee Queen herself. Now, onto your first task...' WHERE `entry`=24982;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Magistrate Sevren wants a report? Very well: the defenders at The Bulwark are holding the majority of the Scourge at bay, but some do slip through on occasion.$B$BWe have seen sporadic Scourge activity east of this station, with a concentration around the Balnir Farmstead.' WHERE `entry`=24983;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I appreciate your efforts, $N. May Sylvanas recognize your bravery one day. . . .' WHERE `entry`=24988;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is troubling to hear of the Scourge slipping past the Bulwark. Even now, they are ceaseless in their assaults. But we will not give in. The Lich King is dead; we will not be taken again!' WHERE `entry`=24989;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $N and I thank you for your efforts.' WHERE `entry`=24990;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Holland?  He\'s an amateur. You don\'t need a fancy two-story apothecarium to make plague... you need love. And maybe some good assistants. Let me show you how plague is REALLY made.' WHERE `entry`=24991;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm... yes, that makes sense. Since the worgen have come streaming out of Gilneas, I knew it would only be a matter of time before they arrived here in Tirisfal.' WHERE `entry`=24992;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='To think, they\'ve been right under our noses!  I\'ll put my deathguards on alert... this will NOT happen again.' WHERE `entry`=24993;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Collect 10 Doom Weed.',`objectives_loc6`='Collect 10 Doom Weed.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, my doom weed. Excellent! These will come in quite handy. You\'ve done me, uh, the Lady, a fine service today, $N. As promised, here is the reward that you deserve.' WHERE `entry`=24994;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The scales are perfect, $N. Exactly what I needed for this concoction.' WHERE `entry`=24995;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, a drink at last. What matter of ale is this?  I\'m sure it\'s no Rhapsody Malt but I\'ll take anything to wet the old whistle at this point.' WHERE `entry`=24996;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Expertly done, $N. The Scourge are mistaken if they think they can use those corpses against us, and the fluid you gathered from the Rot Hide slaves will be studied by my master. It may have secrets we can use against them.' WHERE `entry`=24997;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work!  Now if only I can convince Jerrod to let us move our operation into that shack...' WHERE `entry`=24998;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Did they run from you, $N?  Good. This is better than killing them... if they live to tell the tale, then future generations of murlocs will learn to fear us.' WHERE `entry`=24999;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey, you\'re tougher than you look. These terrortooth hides reflect arrows and turn axe-blades - they don\'t go down easy, but their hides are worth their weight in silver in these light-forsaken Barrens. Nice work.' WHERE `entry`=25000;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Sandscraper',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='And that\'s a wrap! Nothing left here for us but sand. Good job, babe. Well, maybe I shouldn\'t be so hasty. Did you find anything in that ogre den?' WHERE `entry`=25001;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Scavenged',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='My supplies! Well, that showed some real initiative, $C. Those rap-saws or whatever they\'re called have torn lesser men to ribbons. Thank you!' WHERE `entry`=25002;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your actions struck a telling blow against the Scourge. And your victory will not go unnoticed - not by the Forsaken, nor by our enemies. Continue the struggle as we all do, $N, and one day the Forsaken will have the dominion over Azeroth that they are owed!' WHERE `entry`=25003;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your efforts are appreciated, $N. I will not thank you for doing what is necessary, but I will remember your name.' WHERE `entry`=25004;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Devlin Agamand?  Is that him you carry in your sack there?  Ha! Yes, I know what Coleman wants to try, and I want to try it too. I hope you\'re prepared, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25005;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, how unfortunate. Perhaps the Scourge\'s dominion over Devlin\'s mind remained too strong. Or perhaps our methods are simply not strong enough. It\'s also possible that Devlin was too simple-minded to comprehend what we were asking him.' WHERE `entry`=25006;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Not much of a $C, are you?  Well, you will be when I\'m done with you.' WHERE `entry`=25007;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ooooo-oooh aye! The best Hecklefangs are the dead ones.' WHERE `entry`=25008;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your actions will slow down the Scarlet Crusade\'s advancement in Tirisfal quite a bit... hopefully for good. But other threats loom.' WHERE `entry`=25009;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='As you look over the ruins of the camp, you hear a whisper behind you. <"I could kill you right now if I wanted to. You\'d better watch your step, $R.">' WHERE `entry`=25010;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Sure, I\'ll give you a ride. If High Executor Derrington asks for it, then technically I have to.' WHERE `entry`=25011;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome back, $N. I\'ve heard stories from the east. Who would have thought that a young $R $C like you would have been the one to wipe out the last whimpering remnants of the Scarlet Crusade?' WHERE `entry`=25012;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, this venom will do perfectly, $N. Everything else has been added to my concoction and boiled down. Thank you, $C!' WHERE `entry`=25013;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You found that in the ogre den? That\'s... ...nothing to get excited about, I\'m sure! I\'m sure it\'s just...a perfectly benign trinket...that I\'m going to give you precisely detailed instructions on exactly how to handle. Keep your voice down and don\'t wave that thing around.' WHERE `entry`=25014;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' So, this is what the quilboar are using against us? Do you think they used these to create this jungle?' WHERE `entry`=25015;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $C. We would be hard pressed to face such enemies without your assistance.' WHERE `entry`=25017;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Of all the...you found this in an ogre den? Unthinkable. I\'m amazed they didn\'t try to smash it to pieces. With any luck, $C, we\'ll be able to obtain even more fascinating antiquities here...if you\'re willing to help.' WHERE `entry`=25018;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. The less interference from the Alliance, the better.' WHERE `entry`=25019;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. With that dealt with, we can focus our attentions fully on exploring the gateway.' WHERE `entry`=25020;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Dey drink de blood, dey get de power. I drink dere blood...' WHERE `entry`=25021;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work. Gaines passed through here not long ago on his way to Northwatch and a warm bath. The mission wasn\'t a total loss, though. We\'ve learned a good deal about these quilboar and their leadership structure. Now we can handle things ... MY way.' WHERE `entry`=25022;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I told you we would meet again, $N. Unfortunate that it\'s under such dire circumstances.' WHERE `entry`=25023;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve not seen a finer display of $C prowess.' WHERE `entry`=25024;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Didn\'t like ya much, eh? More in this world craves blood than just trolls, mon. Let\'s find the other blade...' WHERE `entry`=25025;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Jang\'thraze eludes me, mon...de blood is not enough. We gonna need somethin\' stronger to find it.$B$BWhen you need every troll you got to help out to scrape by, one o\' them dyin\' on ya is a big problem, mon, an\' dat\'s why de Sandfury learned to raise our dead wit\' da voodoo. You fall over, you just get back up again and keep workin...forever!$B$BDe zombies we make be imbued wit\' darkest mojo. You go on to de west an\' find a whole mess o\' dem, an\' get me dat mojo, yah?',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Powerful stuff, mon...ah, if ya could see what I see now...mebbe you go try it yaself sometime. The spirits call...' WHERE `entry`=25026;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='...Torn limb from limb!? Well, I\'d almost feel bad but the burning hatred gets in the way. She got what she deserved. Problem solved.' WHERE `entry`=25027;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, samples from different parts of the overgrowth? These will be immensely helpful, yes. Thank you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=25028;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Revenge has a sweet taste, don\'t you think? When you destroyed the Agamands, did you catch any hint of free will within them? I hope so. I hope they knew fear before they were smashed into oblivion.$B$BIt is a foolish hope, I know. But it is a hope I foster nonetheless.' WHERE `entry`=25029;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Is this Dargol?  He was vicious even in life, with a temper that bit deep and a blade that bit deeper. Undeath has not done him any favors, though it suits his personality. Yes, this was certainly Dargol. I can sense his malice, even from the remains you\'ve fetched. You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25030;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Argh!  Get back!  Oh, you\'re not Scourge, are you? Thank the Banshee Queen that you\'re here. I\'ve greatly underestimated how bad it\'s gotten up here.' WHERE `entry`=25031;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Mazoga? He\'s taken the sword? That filthy... At least you escaped with your life. The Lasher\'s bite is a vicious one.' WHERE `entry`=25032;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, $N! I\'ve been talking you up to the General here. Thank you again for saving my life.' WHERE `entry`=25034;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good to have ya, brotha. Vol\'jin makes us all proud in dese moments. It feels good ta be tacklin\' threats head on.' WHERE `entry`=25035;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, Paxton says there\'s no jungle in the Barrens? What do you call THIS!? I\'ve got a pile of supplies to move to the interior and my camp has been overrun by a forest that - I swear - grows by the hour!' WHERE `entry`=25036;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oi! Tasty, mon. Thank ya for your great kindness, young one. Da spirits shall surely be regardin\' ya with great favor.' WHERE `entry`=25037;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Master want weeds. Us gots big hands and not good at picking. You help us and we not hurt you. Us need gloom weed. Many weeds around here and near road.$B$BWhen you have gloom weed you take to Master Holland in Brill.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='What\'s this? Gloom weed?! I\'ve no need for gloom weed! That mindless mass of flesh is out there picking daisies and convincing the Lady knows how many dupes like you into doing the same. No offense. We\'ll deal with the gloom weed later. For now, we\'ve got other matters to discuss.' WHERE `entry`=25038;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='$R!  Listen up, I got somethin\'... odd to discuss.$B$BI was out fishin\' by Brightwater Lake when I saw the darnedest thing... some sorta wolf-man, running around Tirisfal. Ya don\'t suppose that could be a... worgen, do ya?$B$BAnyway, I keep tellin\' myself I should tell Executor Zygand about it, but I just get so scared when I talk to that guy. Maybe you could talk with him?' WHERE `entry`=25039;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice work! How was it? Did you enjoy the hunt? Did you run through tall grasses, the scent of your prey urging you forward, until you leapt at its throat, adrenaline surging as your slavering fangs... Well, something like that.' WHERE `entry`=25041;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Oh yeah... oh ... YES! I\'ll have mine raw. I suppose I can grill some up for the others... How would you like yours?' WHERE `entry`=25042;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very good. We may never drive the Horde completely from these lands, but with a strong presence we can undermine their will to fight.' WHERE `entry`=25043;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I have not forgotten my brush with death at the hands of the quilboar in that filthy jungle. The General here has ordered some tactical strikes, but he stops short of genocide. I have no such qualms.$B$BTake this horn that I \'borrowed\' during my negotiations. Blow the horn within the Bristleback challenge ring west of our position - you can\'t miss it. I want you to challenge the champion of the Bristleback, Sabersnout, to single combat. His death in front of his followers will leave them in utter chaos.',`objectives_loc6`='Take the Horn of Challenge to the Bristleback Challenge Ring in Southern Barrens. Blow the horn to challenge Sabersnout and kill him.' WHERE `entry`=25044;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your report, $C? Incredible, $N! You\'re a real asset to the Alliance. I\'ll see to it that my men follow your example!' WHERE `entry`=25045;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='From birth to grave to undeath, we all have our own path to follow. Some are easier than others. It sounds like this Voss girl has had a rough path so far. Hopefully she ultimately chooses to join us and follow the Dark Lady. With power like hers, we could do incredible things. By the way, $N... excellent work out there. If you\'re ever ready and willing, I may have some more work for you in the Plaguelands.' WHERE `entry`=25046;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='This badly broken figurine was discarded by its last owner. However, with the right materials and your skill in jewelcrafting, it could be completely restored.' WHERE `entry`=25047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Most of this looks just fine! How lucky! The Steamwheedle goblins will be so happy to see their cargo back safe and sound. And here\'s a reward for your good deeds, of course! We\'ve got lots of other stuff to do though! Busy busy!' WHERE `entry`=25048;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, it\'s going to be so much nicer around here now that they\'re gone! At least until more show up. But thank you!' WHERE `entry`=25049;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That was great! It looks like most of the goblins we helped made it back here and didn\'t blow up. We really showed that goblin girl! Here\'s a special reward for you, mister.' WHERE `entry`=25050;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is a great relief, $C. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25051;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good job! We\'re really cleaning up around here!' WHERE `entry`=25052;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Isn\'t that just so pretty to watch?' WHERE `entry`=25053;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='It\'s just really so wasteful that all these pirates have golden treasures laying around. Some of this stuff could be used for practical things! Like melting into wire, or intrinsic shielding matrices, or selling to other stupid races that buy gold just to keep it around.$B$BAnd speaking of other stupid races, I bet those greedy goblins are going to be taking all of it. We can\'t let that happen! Go collect that treasure for Gnomeregan!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fantastic! Gosh, this will make enough wire for an entire army. Lucky us!' WHERE `entry`=25054;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The elements are restless, $C. The earthquakes that plague the land and threaten to collapse Ironforge are not normal. The Earthen Ring are convinced that we must put the elements to rest before they tear Azeroth apart. We need your help, $N.$B$BI will give you a bag of Earthen Ring supplies. In it you will find two items, elemental sapta and a cleansing totem. Use the sapta to see into the elemental world. Then use the cleansing totem to subdue the agitated earth spirits.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done $N. But for every element that is subdued another one takes it\'s place. The solution we have here is merely a stopgap. Hopefully my brethren in the Earthen Ring are making more headway.' WHERE `entry`=25055;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dithers, you\'ve done it again!  These are perfect.' WHERE `entry`=25056;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. Several of the looters have already crawled back, requesting clemency. I\'ll let them stew for a bit in the Northwatch brig. Thank you for helping maintain discipline in the ranks. It is important for our army to be perceived as soldiers, not common bandits.' WHERE `entry`=25057;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Score one for the goblins! Stupid dwarves and gnomes.' WHERE `entry`=25058;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What have you dug up for me? Hmm. Interesting. This notice from Orgrimmar indicates a change in Horde leadership is underway - I guess heads are going to roll after what we did to Taurajo. What\'s this? A death warrant for the General here! This is good to know... Very good to know...' WHERE `entry`=25059;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='We received reports that a goblin shipwreck occured on this beach some time ago, with the survivors left to fend for themselves. We expected there to be a modicum of survivors, perhaps some even suitable for interrogation.$B$BWhat we found was a crew of Bilgewater goblins who have all become insane, delusional, and maniacally violent...to further degrees than is normally observed, rather.$B$BIn short, they are useless and dangerous. Gnomeregan will be best served by cutting down as many as we can.',`objectives_loc6`='Kill 10 Crazed Survivors.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your reports of their behavior are truly disturbing...but also slightly amusing. If only that Dreadshredder wench had escaped on these vessels instead...' WHERE `entry`=25060;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m amazed that Soothfancy was capable of following a simple set of instructions. And ones that required him to keep his foolish mouth silenced as well. In addition, it is honestly good to see you again, $N. Now that I\'ve dropped the charade, you\'ll get to see how gnomes get things done around here.' WHERE `entry`=25061;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Gnomeregan previously learned that the Bilgewater goblins of the Horde survived a crash on an uncharted island near Kalmidor before arriving in Durotar. We initially came here to investigate what techniques and technology could possibly allow a hopeless pack of green-skinned imbeciles to survive such harsh conditions.$B$BWhile the goblins are at a loss, we still need to find out exactly what happened here. Search the beach for wreckage and belongings and bring anything that appears significant back to me.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I\'m trying not to laugh. This is classic. They have no idea they\'re even on Kalimdor! These later pages though...something more significant may be occuring here.' WHERE `entry`=25062;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Terrapination',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, gosh, this day just keeps getting better and better! I may actually smile. When you\'re not looking. You\'ve seen enough of that already.' WHERE `entry`=25063;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Moraya',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey there, hon. Vol\'jin sent you? So sweet of him to be thinkin\' of me. I surely could use da help, but ya have a bit more walkin\' ahead of ya.' WHERE `entry`=25064;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. The contents of this chest are sure to advance Gnomeregan\'s knowledge base significantly. I believe you\'ve earned a reward.' WHERE `entry`=25065;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='An impressive start. Be prepared for more.' WHERE `entry`=25067;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Marvelous. To think the shapers of our world crafted these...' WHERE `entry`=25068;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This chest lies undisturbed, sealed for thousands of years.' WHERE `entry`=25069;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The chest now grinds open again, the rest of the antechamber fallen silent.' WHERE `entry`=25070;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks for the help, this was really killin\' things here. Once you start losing men, you start losing manpower. And morale. And weapons. And the magazines you loaned to that one guy. You know how it is.' WHERE `entry`=25072;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome, young $R. Ya come highly recommended, mon. It\'s nice ta finally be meetin\' ya in person.' WHERE `entry`=25073;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Have you heard? The General never made it! Killed in the field, like some kind of dog!' WHERE `entry`=25074;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Pick-a-Part',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oohh look! A mostly complete exhaust manifold, a reciprocating junction box, a working counterweight slip differential ... you sure know your junk, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25075;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great! Set the keg down right here. I\'ll measure out some charges once I\'ve donned my full-body protective gear.' WHERE `entry`=25079;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Oh, OH! That\'s nasty! I love it!' WHERE `entry`=25080;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Incredible work, $N! My men report a breakthrough. Their stronghold won\'t survive much longer...' WHERE `entry`=25081;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That oughta take care of our bug problem for a while - they\'ll be hard-pressed to tunnel their way outta that!' WHERE `entry`=25082;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve my thanks, if not that of the entire Earthen Ring. Maybe someday we\'ll find a way to talk it out with these pigs, but we can\'t heal the land if we\'re dead in our sleep.' WHERE `entry`=25084;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s a relief. Maybe the rest of \'em will keep to their own devices now. The less fighting around here, the better.' WHERE `entry`=25085;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What? Little Logan thinks I might need protection? It\'s me doing the protectin\'! The quilboar here are poised to rampage. They\'ve choked off the entire south, and we\'re the only thing standing in their way.' WHERE `entry`=25086;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Quite a name you\'re earning for yourself here in the Barrens, $N. But Roberts isn\'t going far enough. What we need is a decisive victory...' WHERE `entry`=25087;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Those val\'kyr have been really busy resurrecting you newbies lately. I\'ve already seen a couple dozen new bodies run down that hill since this morning. You, however, are the most promising $C I\'ve seen today.' WHERE `entry`=25089;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done. I enjoyed watching you smash those $R into rotting pulp!' WHERE `entry`=25090;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Marin sent you? I\'m appreciative of his help. I\'m here to seek out Sul\'thraze. If you wish to help, speak with Mazoga...he\'s been cooperative so far.' WHERE `entry`=25091;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done $N. But for every element that is subdued another one takes it\'s place. The solution we have here is merely a stopgap. Hopefully my brethren in the Earthen Ring are making more headway.' WHERE `entry`=25092;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. The spirits of the fallen can now be put to rest.' WHERE `entry`=25093;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not bad. You\'ve got a ways to go, however.' WHERE `entry`=25094;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Rather impressive. Few can bear to see a silithid reaver face to face, let alone defeat it.' WHERE `entry`=25095;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Once again you have helped us to overcome our mutual enemy, the Alliance. Now it is time for us to help you.' WHERE `entry`=25098;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Of course you can borrow Bastia. That is, if she\'ll take you.' WHERE `entry`=25099;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N?! Nice kitty. Look we don\'t have much time here. You might have noticed that the volcano is blowing?!' WHERE `entry`=25100;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thought you might be responsible for them clouds of dust I saw to the east. Nice work! Them bulls ain\'t sissies.' WHERE `entry`=25102;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re with Megs, huh? Word is she\'s been pretty hell-bent on making nice with Noggenfogger. Not like I care. Are you ready to kill some bugs?' WHERE `entry`=25103;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Father sent you? He worries too much. There\'s nothing here I can\'t handle... But I\'d still appreciate the help.' WHERE `entry`=25104;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Lila\'s pet Nibbler got into my workshop again!$B$BI was making a bracelet, to be delivered today. The work was almost done, except for the gems. I spent all night cutting them, but when I stepped out for a bit of breakfast, the little beast came into my workshop and swallowed every gem in sight!  The thing can digest ANYTHING, and trust me, you\'d break your back trying to pick up its leavings.$B$BI need to get replacement gems fast; the courier is coming in tonight. Help!',`objectives_loc6`='Cut three Solid Zephyrites and give them to Isabel Jones in Stormwind City.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve really saved my skin, $N. Thanks!' WHERE `entry`=25105;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My father would be proud of you, $N. Now, to get this flying machine up and about again...' WHERE `entry`=25106;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is truly incredible. The hieroglyphs are undoubtedly titan, but the markings below it... Some of these characters resemble ancient Kaldorei writings. And you say the antechamber was covered in hieroglyphs? You\'ve made a find more monumental than any riches, $N. Please, take whatever reward you prefer.' WHERE `entry`=25107;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Aye, it\'s for the best I suppose.' WHERE `entry`=25108;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Huh... what? Who?' WHERE `entry`=25109;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Alchemists pay through the nose for these things. Sure, maybe I tell some of them they\'re dragon parts, but that ain\'t my problem, right?' WHERE `entry`=25111;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Butcherbot',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice going, kid. Didn\'t lose any fingers? Good, we can get some more work for you then.' WHERE `entry`=25112;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Beautiful! We\'ll have these puppies shined up and ready to sell in no time.' WHERE `entry`=25115;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ll rest easier knowing one of those lumbering things won\'t be wandering into my bedroom at night... again. Thanks much.' WHERE `entry`=25118;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Momentum',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hi there! The fun\'s already started!' WHERE `entry`=25121;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hate the Trade Prince, but you can\'t argue with the results of his methods. Kaja\'Cola Zero-One is a huge improvement over regular old Kaja\'Cola at half the calories and twice the ideas!' WHERE `entry`=25122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Gobber\'s mind freed',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Other goblin\'s minds freed' WHERE `entry`=25122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your soulstone has expired, Blastshadow!' WHERE `entry`=25123;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Looks a little rickety....' WHERE `entry`=25125;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmmm, not bad, $N. But don\'t let it get to your head...you\'ll fight tougher than boars in your career.$B$BNonetheless, you\'ve proven yourself well, and your next trial will be against a considerably more dangerous opponent, so you\'ll need some extra protection.' WHERE `entry`=25126;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There is an important lesson that you must take away from fighting scorpids. The smallest or largest of opponents can still send you to your doom. In fierce combat, any number of things can prove your downfall.$B$BI have no more to teach you, $N. You have done well, and I will watch your progress with interest.' WHERE `entry`=25127;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My blow was not enough to kill him, but looking at the damage I inflicted gives me some small measure of pride. That small measure will be all I have to sustain myself if I die, and in that light, the short list of my life\'s accomplishments fills me with anger.' WHERE `entry`=25129;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='From your description of the beast, I believe you must be speaking of Sarkoth! It is no wonder that Hana\'zua was overtaken by it. Aid will be dispatched to him immediately, trouble yourself no more with Hana\'zua\'s plight.$B$BHowever, I must say, I am most impressed to hear that you brought Sarkoth to death. It is a feat to be proud of, $N. And that you would fight for a stranger\'s honor, while other tasks occupied your time, your own honor is heightened.' WHERE `entry`=25130;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $N.$B$BAlthough the Vile Familiars were merely pets of the darker powers within the Burning Blade, your success against them foretells greater deeds ahead.' WHERE `entry`=25131;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Slay 7 Felstalkers and obtain the Burning Blade Medallion.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You retrieved it! Well done!$B$BYour efforts within the Burning Blade Coven are key in rooting out this cult in the Valley of Trials. But I fear they have further aims in our land.$B$BWe have not seen the end of them.' WHERE `entry`=25132;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hm... your report comes at a bad time. The Burning Blade is no longer seen here in Sen\'jin, but we will be vigilant in our efforts to prevent their return to the area. The orcs are friends of the Darkspear Trolls. Honorable friends. We want to help the orcs, but... we need help too.' WHERE `entry`=25133;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, good. Maybe they\'ll think twice before slacking next time!  Thanks for the help!' WHERE `entry`=25134;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great, you got it! Thanks a lot, $N. This is my favorite pick! Now if my peons ever finish chopping down these trees, maybe we can find a nice cave to mine!' WHERE `entry`=25135;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful, $N! As promised, here is your cactus apple surprise plus a little something extra.' WHERE `entry`=25136;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Valley of Trials: PRK - H - Warlock Pet Imp' WHERE `entry`=25137;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahh, where to start... introductions!  I\'m Acrypha - the one who sent you that parchment - I\'ve spent the last several years in an Undercity library, my head in a book. I learned everything I could about the arcane, and now I\'ve returned home to share it with grunts like yourself. Shall we begin?' WHERE `entry`=25138;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='You already know how to fire an arcane shot. Good. But doing so depletes your focus. To gain your focus back you will need to switch to a second type of ranged attack. I can teach it to you.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Steady Shot from Karranisha in the Valley of Trials. Locate a Training Dummy and practice using Steady Shot 5 times.' WHERE `entry`=25139;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Let\'s start with the basics, shall we?  I\'m the only rogue trainer in town, so you\'re going to have to learn it from me.$B$BHere\'s how it\'s going to go: you give me your money, and I\'ll teach you how to finish off a foe. Do we have a deal?',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Eviscerate from Rwag in the Valley of Trials. Locate a Training Dummy and practice using Eviscerate 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You won\'t be sorry. The ability to capitalize on the opportunities created by previous attacks is one of our greatest strengths.' WHERE `entry`=25141;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I will teach you the art of the primal strike. By following these steps, you can deal additional damage to your foes with your weapon. Speak with me again and I will show you the way.$B$BAfter your lessons are complete, practice using the training dummies outside the Den.',`objectives_loc6`='Train Primal Strike from Shikrik in the Valley of Trials. Look for a training dummy near Shikrik and practice using Primal Strike 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very well. Now that you know how to speak with the elements, we will test your bond with them.' WHERE `entry`=25143;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='It is my duty to train you, and I intend to do just that. Speak with me again and I will show you how to wreathe your opponents in a demonic fire.$B$BOnce your lesson is complete, practice your new spell against one of the training dummies around here.',`objectives_loc6`='Train Immolate from Nartok in the Valley of Trials. Locate a Training Dummy and practice casting Immolate 5 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You appear to be a quick learner.' WHERE `entry`=25145;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I\'ve been instructed to prepare you for battle. Though, from the look of you, it looks like you\'ve already spent a little time out in the field. Good.$B$BIt\'s been said that a warriors fight not only with their arms but their legs. You must learn to move quickly around the battlefield .$B$BSpeak to me again, and I will teach you how to charge.',`objectives_loc6`='Train Charge from Frang in the Valley of Trials. Locate a Training Dummy and practice using Charge.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You understand now?  Good, let\'s try it out.' WHERE `entry`=25147;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Alright, here\'s the easy part. All you have to do is listen to me. And pay me a little bit of copper.$B$BSpeak with me again and we\'ll teach you the rite of Arcane Missiles. This isn\'t just an ordinary spell, $N. Each time you attack with a spell, you\'ll have a chance to activate Arcane Missiles, so be attentive.$B$B Once your lesson is finished, practice your new spell against a training dummy.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Arcane Missiles from Acrypha in the Valley of Trials. Locate a Training Dummy and practice using Arcane Missiles 2 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good. Now we practice.' WHERE `entry`=25149;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Ah... that\'s the stuff. Ol\' Barkerstout... Thank you, friend. That\'ll make this... a little easier.' WHERE `entry`=25151;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Finally, you are of age, $N... of age to battle in the name of the Horde. To conquer for the glory of the Warchief.$B$BYes...$B$B<Kaltunk looks you over.>$B$BYou will do nicely.$B$BNo doubt you wish to find a great dragon or demon and strangle it with your bare hands, but perhaps it would be wise to start on something less... dangerous.$B$B<Kaltunk laughs.>$B$BReport to Gornek, he should be able to assign a task better suited to a young $C. You will find him seated at the fire behind me.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Another one of Kaltunk\'s recruits, hm?$B$BA sorry state of affairs we find ourselves in if this is the best the Horde can produce. No matter. By the time we think you\'re ready to leave the Valley, you\'ll be a proud warrior of the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=25152;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re a legend, $N. The other survivors and I will be telling the story of your deeds for years to come.' WHERE `entry`=25153;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks!  I\'m sure to beat out that Marith Lazuria in Orgrimmar with these!  I can\'t wait to see the look in her beautiful eye when I give this to her.' WHERE `entry`=25154;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your work is as good as it is rumored to be!' WHERE `entry`=25155;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks. Erm. Just set them over there. I need to figure out how to get my hand off of this jar' WHERE `entry`=25156;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It did what!?  We\'re ruined!  Hmm. Well, actually... Maybe the professor can find some other applications for it?' WHERE `entry`=25157;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Lila\'s pet Nibbler got into my workshop again!$B$BI was making a bracelet, to be delivered today. The work was almost done, except for the gems. I spent all night cutting them, but when I stepped out for a bit of breakfast, the little beast came into my workshop and swallowed every gem in sight!  The thing can digest ANYTHING, and trust me, you\'d break your back trying to pick up its leavings.$B$BI need to get replacement gems fast; the courier is coming in tonight. Help!',`objectives_loc6`='Cut three Solid Zephyrites and give them to Marith Lazuria in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve really saved my skin, $N. Thanks!' WHERE `entry`=25158;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It did what!?  We\'re ruined!  Hmm. Well, actually... Maybe the doctor can find some other applications for it?' WHERE `entry`=25159;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks!  I\'m sure to beat out that Isabela Jones in Stormwind with these!  I can\'t wait to see the look in her beautiful eye when I give this to her.' WHERE `entry`=25160;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your work is as good as it is rumored to be!' WHERE `entry`=25161;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks. Erm. Just set them over there. I need to figure out how to get my hand off of this jar' WHERE `entry`=25162;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m glad you were here, mon. Toshe be lookin\' like he wants to chase dem down. You should go help\'em.' WHERE `entry`=25164;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is it!  The scorpid juju Bom\'bay been waitin\' for!  Now we gonna fix you right up, $C. You come back to Bom\'bay when you be needin\' a pickup. Bom\'bay got the spells to fix ya!' WHERE `entry`=25165;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='He was controlling a sea giant? Fascinating. If we\'d managed to investigate further... Oh, I mean, wow, that\'s totally crazy! But thank goodness he\'s gone, hooray! Mister Noggenfogger will be so pleased. Here\'s a nice big reward, you!' WHERE `entry`=25166;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, we\'ve stymied their efforts for now, but they\'re still here. We\'ll have to press on, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25167;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, hero. You done good for Sen\'jin today. No... you done good for all of Durotar.' WHERE `entry`=25169;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ya mon, that\'s tha stuff. Now we get the other jujus.' WHERE `entry`=25170;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That $R wants us to send help?  Bah, he can forget it. I\'ve got my own human problems to worry about, and even those are the least of my worries right now. Sen\'jin Village is right next to Echo Isles and the Valley of Trials. Old Gadrin should find plenty of youngbloods to help him with his human infestation.' WHERE `entry`=25171;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Executed with quickness and discretion. A job well done.' WHERE `entry`=25172;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Word of your bravery travels fast, $C. Tales of your victory at Tiragarde Keep will be heralded in Orgrimmar.' WHERE `entry`=25173;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What... WHAT!? Bael\'dun in ruins? Corpses everywhere - no. No! The Bilgewater goblins, was it? They want a fight do they? We\'ll show \'em what it means to be a part of the Horde, we will. I\'ll fill the Battlescar with their corpses. I\'ll redden the dirt with their blood. Goblins. Are going. To die!' WHERE `entry`=25174;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' That was my boy, $N. My only boy. They\'ve made it personal, $C. Personal.' WHERE `entry`=25175;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='$G Hey there, handsome!  I\'ve had my eye on those big, beefy biceps ever since you stepped into town.: What\'re you looking at, ugly?  I\'ve seen you walking around Razor Hill, trying to steal MY men from me!;$B$BListen, I\'ve got something for you to do. I hear Gar\'Thok\'s got you headed over to Tiragarde. While you\'re there, think you could find some abandoned Kul Tiras knicknacks?$B$B$GThanks sweetie!: Don\'t ask why, just get to it!;',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You brought me my treasure!  What a sweetheart!' WHERE `entry`=25176;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The scent of the sea hangs about you, $N. Your efforts may have purchased another day for Razor Hill. I will pass word of your deeds up my chain of command. You have our gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=25177;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='$G Hey handsome, welcome back!  You wouldn\'t mind running another errand, would you?  I\'d be EVER so grateful...: You!  Stop right there, you tramp!  I\'m not finished with you yet.;$B$BI hear you\'re headed off to the shore east of here. The beach is filled with crashed ships, and those ships have gnomish tools in them... tools that I can use.$B$B$G See you soon, beefcake!: Get cracking, missy!;',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You really know how to treat a girl, you know that?  If you ever need anything...' WHERE `entry`=25178;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve already spoken with several orcs that have returned from the beach. All of them told me that you were the one who saved them. You\'ve done a noble task today, $N. Lok\'tar ogar!  For the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=25179;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Why would Twilight\'s Hammer take an interest in these tablets? Brann himself wrote that he hardly knows their significance, although he did mention something about becoming one with the earth. I will need to confer with my fellow Explorer\'s League scholars to decipher these as soon as possible.$B$BThank you, $N. Without your aid, these tablets would\'ve fallen into enemy hands.' WHERE `entry`=25180;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Why would Twilight\'s Hammer take an interest in these tablets? Their contents are a mystery to our most learned scholars and deciphering them will take some time. If Twilight\'s Hammer knows about these relics and desires them, what more are they plotting?$B$BWe are most fortunate that you protected them from capture, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25181;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I want to see some dead goblins, $N! Just west of here you\'ll find a whole warren of those little insects burrowing into the mountain.$B$BLet\'s see to it that they\'re digging their grave.$B$BDestroy them. Lay waste to their whole grubby operation. They\'ve sown their own demise in Bael\'dun, $C, and it is time to meet the reaper.',`objectives_loc6`='Kill 10 Frazzlecraz Miners at the Frazzlecraz Motherlode in Southern Barrens.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dead? Good. Let word of this deed spread, and with it, terror. The Horde will feel the consequences of their attack on Bael\'dun, and they\'ll rue the day they ever crossed us, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25182;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='As we would say in the Tinker\'s Union, out of the heat-applied metallic cooking container and into the oxydizing, energetic mixture of reacting gases and solids!' WHERE `entry`=25184;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Very nice work, $N. I suppose there\'s some strategic value in depriving the Horde of those minerals, but I\'d have done it anyway just to crush those little green monstrosities.' WHERE `entry`=25185;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So our supplies aren\'t getting through? Hmmm. Honor\'s Stand just gets more and more isolated. Still, the defeat of Thunderwalk should send a signal to our foes that we mean to stay. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25186;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see... so the trick is that you need to put the LITTLE end of the spyglass up to your eye. I\'ll remember that piece of information.' WHERE `entry`=25187;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Find Misha',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Find Zen\'Taji' WHERE `entry`=25187;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I used that trick you taught me with the spyglass, and I watched you running around down there. Quite impressive! How\'d you make the old woman fly, by the way?' WHERE `entry`=25188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Help Misha Tor\'kren',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Help Zen\'Taji' WHERE `entry`=25188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My grandmother was a powerful shaman in her day. I thought she had lost most of her powers in her old age, but I suppose some things stay with you forever.' WHERE `entry`=25189;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Good, good. One step closer to eliminating those beady-eyed, basket-wearing, hog-nosed, two-toed... ...hunchbacked, squealing, prickly... no-good... gnome-loving... GREEEAAAAGH!  Quilboar!' WHERE `entry`=25190;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What, what!? Can\'t you see we\'re under attack here! Yes sure of course I\'ll give Nibb\'s findings careful study. Later. From the safety of the Eastern Kingdoms, if I have any say about it!' WHERE `entry`=25191;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You\'ve done well, stranger. I\'m sorry you had to see me like that. Thank you for killing the quilboar, but maybe you should leave before I fly into another one of my rages.' WHERE `entry`=25192;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $R. I will get to work on the necklace right away. Before Kron died, I had made this for him to wear. I have no use for it now, but perhaps you might.' WHERE `entry`=25193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I love all the little animals, mon. I love the big ones, too. I just hate to see you hurt them like that... but it\'s for the best.' WHERE `entry`=25194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Something happened to Screamslash when the cataclysm hit, Zen\'Taji thinks. He wasn\'t always so violent and irrational. Thank you for your help, $N. Zen\'Taji gonna get back to his studying now.' WHERE `entry`=25195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re the one who handled the Burning Blade to the south?  I\'ve got ears in all kinds of places, boy, and word travels fast.' WHERE `entry`=25196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve ventured all the way here from Honor\'s Stand? Excellent, we could use your experience here. They may have breached the walls, but Northwatch isn\'t going down without a fight.' WHERE `entry`=25197;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You made it through in one piece? You have more gears then I thought, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Cheer with the Drill Sergeant',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Dance with the Drill Sergeant' WHERE `entry`=25199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can\'t say that I was ever much of a footbomb fan, but you\'re giving me an appreciation for the game!' WHERE `entry`=25200;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yeah, these will do nicely. You did good, kid. I\'ll see to it that you get the best footbomb uniform ever made. In the meantime, you\'ve got other bombs to drop on the Trade Prince\'s lackeys.' WHERE `entry`=25201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='He got just what he deserved. There, there, don\'t cry. You\'ll find someone else that\'ll treat you right. Here, let me take that... we wouldn\'t want people to think that you\'re crazy.' WHERE `entry`=25202;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There\'s no two ways about it... he got exactly what he deserved.' WHERE `entry`=25203;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='All of the lights and indicators on the control panel are going crazy!' WHERE `entry`=25204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Valve #3 released',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Valve #4 released' WHERE `entry`=25204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The moral of the story: hasty, lazy actions have ruinous results. We mustn\'t take shortcuts... we must work for our rewards. I\'ve been trying to tell this story to the "Enforcer", but I fear his Hellscream-worshipping skull is a little bit too thick.' WHERE `entry`=25205;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='See?  The shaman\'s tales are nothing but that... a youngling\'s bedtime stories. The new Horde takes what it wants, and doesn\'t waste time with such frivolity. If you get a chance, I recommend you tell Shin... and those like him... not to waste any more of your time.' WHERE `entry`=25206;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I felt the heat from the explosions all the way over here!' WHERE `entry`=25207;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re back. What did Estulan say?' WHERE `entry`=25208;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have proven yourself to be a trustworthy and dependable ally, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25209;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, $N. I will study the horns, but the situation has become even more dire since you left.' WHERE `entry`=25210;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'ll show \'em!  Nice work!' WHERE `entry`=25211;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fantastic work!$B$BThe data I received shows the radiation levels are fully within safety range of our suits. That is excellent news!' WHERE `entry`=25212;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I was wondering where you were! Don\'t worry, Hobart will get that footbomb uniform converted into the most Ultimate Footbomb Uniform ever!' WHERE `entry`=25213;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oops. Well, what goes up must eventually come down.' WHERE `entry`=25214;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It shouldn\'t take long to cleanse the water. Thank you for your help.' WHERE `entry`=25215;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Another fan of the Great Sambino! Come all this way for an autograph perhaps? I\'m far too busy to be signing anything... move along now.' WHERE `entry`=25216;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Another sample. Brilliant! The rocky riches of the sea shall soon be mine!' WHERE `entry`=25217;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ya know, I should have given you a weight belt so that you wouldn\'t just float away, air balloon and all. Lucky for me you came down here with armor and all! Hah!' WHERE `entry`=25218;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you. Seriously. If I would have had to endure another shipwreckee laughing at me, I swear I would have gored someone. I\'ll let you know if I come up with anything.' WHERE `entry`=25219;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $C. There are still much bigger predators we\'ll have to keep an eye out for, but this will at least give us a bit of peace of mind around the cave.' WHERE `entry`=25220;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Rundown',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Swift work. Very impressive. That Fathom-Lord got away... I don\'t see him anywhere. He\'s most certainly the key to finding our captured friends. I will hunt him down. He cannot stay hidden for long.' WHERE `entry`=25221;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A friendly face! Welcome! Very kind of you to come check on us. We\'re fine. A naga scouting force did find us, but I\'m pretty sure none escaped. We should be safe for now.' WHERE `entry`=25222;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I suppose your abilities are... suitable. Color me impressed.' WHERE `entry`=25223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you managed to pass this part of the test without getting yourself eaten by Smolderos or being incinerated by the fire elementals? I suppose I should congratulate you on ascending the lowest rung of our ladder. Well... congratulations, recruit!' WHERE `entry`=25224;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Thonk',`details_loc6`='$G Oh, sweetie, I just remembered!: Sorry if I\'ve been mean to you. Sometimes I get a little jealous when other women come into town, as I\'m a little insecure about my appearance.;$B$BMy VERY good friend Thonk works in the guard tower on that cliff, just to the northwest of Razor Hill. He said something about a river overflowing, lots of work to be done, and so on. I wasn\'t really paying attention... I was staring into those deep brown eyes of his.$B$B$GWhat, we can\'t see other people?: Thanks.;',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Gail sent you?  Did... did she say anything about me?' WHERE `entry`=25227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Find Misha',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Find Zen\'Taji' WHERE `entry`=25227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Torek reads over the scrolls you collected.>$B$BWhoever these people are, they really mean to gain a following. It looks like they\'re having quite a bit of success. They can\'t be allowed to incite the citizens of Ogrimmar to panic and hysteria. We must discourage interest in this group and learn as much about it as we can.' WHERE `entry`=25228;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Our engineers have been working on getting our battle machines ready for our assault on Gnomeregan, but we\'re out of pilots!$B$BWe\'ve developed a device called the Motivate-a-Tron, which prevents distraction from other sources and gives the gnome the courage to enlist.$B$BAfter motivating a few Gnome Citizens, lead them out to Captain Tread Sparknozzle out at Steelgrill\'s Depot, just south of Ironforge.$B$BOh, and be careful. The device is still a little experimental.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is the best group of potential pilots you could find?$B$BOkay, well, I\'ll see what I can do. I\'ve been known to turn even the biggest pile of gnarled gears into a smooth-runnin\' fightin\' machine and I expect no less with this lot.$B$BWell, I guess it\'s time to work!' WHERE `entry`=25229;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These events disturb me greatly. My study of the antlers while you were gone has revealed little. We must find some way to fix this...' WHERE `entry`=25230;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is quite interesting. These rites aren\'t all that different from the spells which are taught to Horde warlocks. This merits further investigation!' WHERE `entry`=25232;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done! The chaos we sow back here will be felt up and down the chain of command.' WHERE `entry`=25233;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Augh! Cursed - this metal is cursed - it bites! What demented workmanship is this? $N, I\'ve never fought any foe like this before.' WHERE `entry`=25234;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I saw you drop a few of them from here. Nice work. Here\'s your reward, on behalf of the Night Watch.' WHERE `entry`=25235;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Our army needs water, and luckily the elements gave us plenty of that when the Cataclysm hit. The water that filled up the canyon to the southwest should do the trick.$B$BUnfortunately, the corpses of thunder lizards still sit at the bottom of the canyon, and their electrical discharges are a bit too dangerous. I\'ve got grunts that can lift them out of the water, but we need someone agile enough to attach the other end of the rope. Are you my $G man: woman;, $N?',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='The electricity was only one of the dangers. If those carcasses rot too long under the water, that entire source becomes undrinkable. Well done, $C.' WHERE `entry`=25236;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you once again, $N. I will prepare these for our final task.' WHERE `entry`=25237;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You continue to prove yourself, $N. Accept this, not as a gift, but as a tool for the fight against the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=25239;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You continue to prove yourself, $N. Accept this, not as a gift, but as a tool for the fight against the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=25240;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The spirits of these guardians will return in time, $N. You\'ve freed them to move on in nature\'s cycle.$B$BNow it falls to us to make sure that cycle is free of corruption and needless suffering.' WHERE `entry`=25241;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are a true champion of our cause, $N. None can claim to be more dedicated to the struggle than you. It is rumored that the minions of the Scourge fear you more than they do the Lich King himself. You are might incarnate. Accept this humble gift as a reward for your many triumphs.' WHERE `entry`=25242;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m sure she deserved it, $N. She should never have betrayed you like that. It gives me the shivers to think that she might have kissed that monster, the Trade Prince!' WHERE `entry`=25243;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Serves her right for stealing your man in the first place.' WHERE `entry`=25244;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='May you find what you\'re looking for, $Gbrother:sister;.' WHERE `entry`=25246;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='May you find what you\'re looking for, $Gbrother:sister;.' WHERE `entry`=25247;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='May you find what you\'re looking for, $Gbrother:sister;.' WHERE `entry`=25248;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='May you find what you\'re looking for, $Gbrother:sister;.' WHERE `entry`=25249;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The corruption has been stemmed! The forest can begin to heal now. May you have the blessing of the Earth Mother wherever you go, friend.' WHERE `entry`=25250;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did it! You did it! We\'re saved, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! Even these fools will soon know that to stand against the Horde means death.' WHERE `entry`=25252;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Anton reads over the scrolls you collected.>$B$BWhoever put these leaflets together knows how to get attention and from the state of things in Old Town, there\'s no lack of interest. We must act before they can build a significant following in the city. I fear they\'ll use their influence to spread panic throughout the city, paralyzing us.$B$BWe\'ve got to get inside the organization and learn as much as possible.' WHERE `entry`=25253;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. Now we must focus our efforts on discovering more about this cult and freeing the people they\'ve conned into joining.' WHERE `entry`=25254;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. I worry that our actions here may be too little, too late, but nature always has a way of rebuilding itself that never ceases to amaze.' WHERE `entry`=25255;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Vek\'nag sent you?  Without telling you that I need wagon wheels, nails, and rations?  That idiot.' WHERE `entry`=25256;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Ghislania',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I watched you fight out there. How long you been a $C? You\'re alright, kid.' WHERE `entry`=25257;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Griswold Hanniston',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m at a crossroads now, $N... you defeated him easily in combat, but then again, I did get him for free, and he\'s pretty cheap to feed. Maybe we\'ll keep him around for a bit.' WHERE `entry`=25258;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fine, here\'s the money... but you\'d better make yourself scarce before I reconsider my policy on keeping Horde slaves.' WHERE `entry`=25259;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Fizzled',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I ask for an orb, and you bring half of the goblin\'s arm with you?  I like the way you work. Tell you what... you\'ve already given me a hand. Allow me to return the favor.' WHERE `entry`=25260;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome, $N. Word reached me of your coming, and of your exploits in Durotar.$B$BYou are a $C of growing skill and renown.$B$BStay on the pure path, and your future will be great indeed.' WHERE `entry`=25261;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good. Hiding within these collars is the secret behind the Burning Blade. And I will uncover that secret...' WHERE `entry`=25262;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, and where did you get this?  Good Margoz sent you to me, did he? Well, let me take a closer look...' WHERE `entry`=25263;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is not news to me. While I appreciate your efforts, the Burning Blade will have to wait. We have other matters to which we must attend.' WHERE `entry`=25264;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lok\'tar! Victory, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25265;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The goblins and orcs have accomplished too much together to part ways now, $C. I intend for the Bilgewater Cartel to become part of the Horde.$B$BI have something that I want you to deliver to the new warchief. Give this package to my Kor\'kron friend on the dock at Bladefist Bay in Durotar. He will help you to get into Orgrimmar safely.$B$BSpeak with Sassy Hardwrench on the ship when you are ready to set sail.$B$BUntil we meet again. Aka\'Magosh, a blessing on you and yours, $N!',`objectives_loc6`='Deliver the Sealed Package to the Kor\'kron Loyalist on the docks at Bladefist Bay in Durotar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I know who sent you. Did he give you something to deliver to me?' WHERE `entry`=25266;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='<The Kor\'kron loyalist opens the package, palming one object while reading a letter from within. As he finishes the note from Thrall, the barest hint of a fanged smile appears on his face.>$B$BYou are to take this directly to Warchief Hellscream inside Orgrimmar. Make certain that Garrosh knows that it is from Thrall.$B$BTake my battleworg. Hurry, little goblin, there is no time to waste for this message!',`objectives_loc6`='Deliver the SI:7 Emblem to Garrosh Hellscream at Grommash Hold in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thrall had you deliver this? I understand the meaning of this all too well, $R. This smelly thing was caught unattended in the city and seems to recognize you. I have already put others of your kind to work in Azshara. Take it with you when you leave. From this day forward, you and your Bilgewater Cartel will serve the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=25267;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re here to rescue me, $C? Thank you! No, no, don\'t worry about the cage for now. My life isn\'t important. We\'ve got to save the shrine, first.' WHERE `entry`=25268;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lok\'tar, $C! Don\'t worry about this cage - these animals will come to fear me before long. My first priority is to clear this filth away from my beloved shrine.' WHERE `entry`=25269;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Disgusting. This is like the incense we burn when we wish to commune with the spirits... but it\'s... befouled.' WHERE `entry`=25270;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' As I suspected. These reagents bear the marks of the Twilight\'s Hammer. And here, the name "Lycanthoth." I believe these are used in a summoning ritual...' WHERE `entry`=25271;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The actions of these feral dogs are beginning to make sense. The Twilight\'s Hammer fears the power of the ancients. They do not want Lo\'Gosh to return.$B$BSo they\'ve summoned their own wolf god - a perversion of what once was. "Lycanthoth," the corruptor.$B$B$N, Lycanthoth is but a shadow of Lo\'Gosh\'s power, but the beast must be destroyed so that the true ancient can return. Take this incense, and burn it in the maw of Lycanthoth east of here. Slay the monstrosity and free the spirit of Lo\'Gosh!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You were brave to face down Lycanthoth, $N. Like myself, he was a primal force of nature... but his origins were from a darker place. Those who birthed that beast reached deep into the blackness, channeling powers never intended for this world. Come, $C. Climb onto my back, and let us show these beasts the true face of ferocity!' WHERE `entry`=25272;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You were brave to face down Lycanthoth, $N. Like myself, he was a primal force of nature... but his origins were from a darker place. Those who birthed that beast reached deep into the blackness, channeling powers never intended for this world. Come, $C. Climb onto my back, and let us show these beasts the true face of ferocity!' WHERE `entry`=25273;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. I\'ll do my best to alter these documents.' WHERE `entry`=25274;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Your people are busy with the terraforming of Azshara. We will remake the land in the image of the Horde so that all will know that Kalimdor is ours!$B$BGo north through the city. On the far side of the Valley of Honor you will find the Orgrimmar Rear Gate. Report to Labor Captain Grabbit outside the gates, goblin.$B$BFor the Horde!!!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N? The $N?! The rumors are already flying about you. I don\'t know if I should be thankful or frightened that you\'re here. At least we don\'t have any volcanoes in Azshara! Honestly, I can\'t believe you\'re showing your face here... Trade Prince Gallywix has setup shop atop the mountain!' WHERE `entry`=25275;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Earthenfurydamus?  Let us hope your parents brought you into this world with more than just a ridiculous name.' WHERE `entry`=25276;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hah! So you really sent some heads rolling, did you? It was said during the War of the Ancients that Lo\'Gosh fought demons for ten days solid. Hopefully you weren\'t fighting that long...' WHERE `entry`=25277;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You really cleared that place out, didn\'t you? Well done! The night elves once told me a story about how Goldrinn fought and killed a dreadlord, even as three others clung to his flanks, burning his flesh. I wonder if you or I will ever have the strength to do the same?' WHERE `entry`=25278;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N, it was incredible! For a fleeting moment I saw Lo\'Gosh through the trees - a creature of both fury and light. My cage collapsed and the vandals melted like wax under the kiss of his claws, their screams and howls echoing through the valley... Was that your work?' WHERE `entry`=25279;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N, it was astounding! Goldrinn himself appeared to free us, his white fur bright like the summer moon. Our cages collapsed and the vandals melted like wax under the kiss of his claws. He was beautiful, $N. Beautiful!' WHERE `entry`=25280;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='While you were away, I was able to revive some of the fallen soldiers.$B$BWe\'ll need every hand if we are to survive here.' WHERE `entry`=25281;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. Now we must focus our efforts on discovering more about this cult and freeing the people they\'ve conned into joining.' WHERE `entry`=25282;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh my. Their reactions were that different?$B$BNot completely what I was expecting, but I think I have a speech that will do.$B$BJust let me find where I put it...' WHERE `entry`=25283;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, good. It\'ll take them many sleepless nights to figure out where we came from and where we disappeared to after the kills...' WHERE `entry`=25284;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey, look at that!  You weren\'t blown to bits!' WHERE `entry`=25285;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Toby is all done with the speech?  Let me see...$B$B<Reads the speech> Pumping pistons! What a fantastic speech! I knew Toby was a good writer, but this is perhaps the best he\'s ever written.$B$BI think it\'s time to get you out to the battle.' WHERE `entry`=25286;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is the final draft, then?  Let me have a look...' WHERE `entry`=25287;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome, friend. We are honored that you have decided to embrace the truth and join us. Come, there will be more time to talk later and you have much to learn.' WHERE `entry`=25288;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm... so the left leg servo was activating the right leg?  But I saw the left leg moving...$B$BEh, details. I\'ll get to that later, but two out of three things worked: That isn\'t half bad!$B$BThanks for checking this out for me, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25289;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Go to Stormwind\'s Old Town and either speak to a Doomsayer or take a robe from the crate near a Doomsayer to join the doomsday cult, then equip the Doomsday Recruit\'s Robe you receive.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome, friend. We are honored that you have decided to embrace the truth and join us. Come, there will be more time to talk later and you have much to learn.' WHERE `entry`=25290;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You think you\'re ready for the next step then, Earthenfurydamus? Let\'s see what you\'re capable of.' WHERE `entry`=25291;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Gann? Dead? I ... I should\'ve known. His temper... his recklessness. I knew someday it would get the better of him. But it sounds as though you\'ve already gifted him with vengeance. Thank you, $N! Turn your attention now to Dustwallow. If the Alliance finishes their cursed road through here, all your victories in the Barrens may have been for nothing.' WHERE `entry`=25292;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you found them? Why did the missing men and women not return with you? We cannot compel them to change their minds and return to their families. I will let the families know that the relatives have been found and that they are safe. After this cult is broken up, they will likely return to their normal lives.' WHERE `entry`=25293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Speak to Cultist Tokka',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Speak to Cultist Rokaga' WHERE `entry`=25293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. This little pup will grow to be strong and merciless like his father.' WHERE `entry`=25294;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm... so the bullets had quite a bit of spread?$B$BTo some people that may be a problem... me, though, I see it as a blessing in disguise!$B$BOur enemies will be running all over the place, so with a bit of a spread, the tank drivers won\'t need to lead the target!' WHERE `entry`=25295;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. Or should I say: "$N"damus? Give me a minute to read these.' WHERE `entry`=25296;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! Let\'s hope the damage wasn\'t permanent. Judging by the poor victims still in camp here, the Twilight\'s Hammer really messed with their heads.' WHERE `entry`=25298;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve succeeded, Earthenfurydamus. You\'re ready for the next step.' WHERE `entry`=25299;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Elementary!' WHERE `entry`=25303;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Crucible of Fire Activated',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Crucible of Water Activated' WHERE `entry`=25303;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These foul things will be driven back into the sea. I hope you\'re ready.' WHERE `entry`=25304;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent job, $N!  You\'ve outdone yourself this time.' WHERE `entry`=25308;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re on the fast-track to success. Let us hope you don\'t ruin your track record with such silly notions as compassion and humaneness. Come, then. Let us discuss your future.' WHERE `entry`=25309;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, Earthenfurydamus. We must show all would-be competitors that we are not ones to give up easily.' WHERE `entry`=25310;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Sharp as always. You do not disappoint me.' WHERE `entry`=25311;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello, yes? What? You? Oh, you\'re one of the ones I sent after the Eye of Twilight, aren\'t you? Good work, very good. I suppose that\'s a valuable lesson: Never to take orders from a big purple ball.' WHERE `entry`=25312;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Our plan\'s almost come together.' WHERE `entry`=25314;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You. You\'re clearly not with them. An ally then?' WHERE `entry`=25315;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='<Ysera\'s eyes look distant, as if not fully acknowledging you.>$B$BI feel it as well, $C. Ragnaros has arrived.$B$BWe must defeat his minions before he can join them and lend them his strength.$B$BSeek Malfurion Stormrage at the Tranquil Grove, west of here, and aid his forces in any way you can.$B$BI must seek answers from within the Emerald Dream. You must protect the world tree until I return.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve arrived just in time, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25317;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Make no mistake about this, $N. The outcome of this war will determine the very survival of our world as we know it.$B$BThe Twilight\'s Hammer has become more powerful than ever with Deathwing\'s return. Should they succeed in taking over the world tree, they might strike a blow from which we will never recover.$B$BIt is time we beat back the enemy. It is time we crushed the Twilight\'s Hammer.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well, $N. But I fear the battle is far from over.' WHERE `entry`=25319;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Help has arrived at last!' WHERE `entry`=25320;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am thankful, $N. I will deliver my findings to our people.' WHERE `entry`=25321;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Speak to Hamuul Runetotem in Hyjal.' WHERE `entry`=25322;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Flamebreaker',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. This will help us turn the tide against the enemy.' WHERE `entry`=25323;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The dragon might be right. The Twilight\'s Hammer has breached our security and this is our most dangerous prisoner.' WHERE `entry`=25324;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did well, $N. I will take Fandral to Moonglade myself. His prison will be far enough from the battlefront there.' WHERE `entry`=25325;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' It\'s about time! ...Can I get a little help here?' WHERE `entry`=25328;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'ve done it! Cho\'gall himself has been utterly humiliated by you. His minions are dead, the Gordok are scattered, and now all will know the might of the Horde! Lok\'tar, $N. You\'ve more than earned your reward.' WHERE `entry`=25329;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, Earthenfurydamus. I\'m having the servants you chose for me briefed on their new duties.' WHERE `entry`=25330;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Kristoff, Kristoff... Oh yes, I remember now. I recall sending him on what amounted to a suicide mission. He survived? I suppose that means he failed. Still, you deserve at least some coin for the trouble.' WHERE `entry`=25332;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome back from the battle! The Twilight\'s Hammer have been disgraced in the eyes of the Gordunni, and driven from Feralas.$B$BWe\'ve shown the glory of the Alliance in full force today! Be proud!' WHERE `entry`=25333;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'d all suspected da naga, but I knew nothin\' of the Twilight Cult bein\' beneath the waves. Somehow dey are corruptin\' and pervertin\' the elements, makin\' demselves into dese horrors. We goin\' ta have to be fightin\' both of dese threats to stand a chance of bringin\' peace ta Vashj\'ir. We don\'t have da men ta do that yet. Come, $C, we got much ta do.' WHERE `entry`=25334;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='As my master told me... Upon a violent death, the muisek of a creature may escape and seek revenge. Shrinking the creatures, as you did, $N, prevents the muisek from escaping. Now we may use it as we please!' WHERE `entry`=25336;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Master always said "after killing an animal, if we allowed the muisek to escape, it may take the form of an even greater creature." This is dangerous stuff. Thanks for helping me with my studies.' WHERE `entry`=25337;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. This is my first time working with treant muisek...' WHERE `entry`=25338;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. You have put an old tauren\'s mind at peace.' WHERE `entry`=25339;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now I know that Edana is truly dead. This heart, I will keep it in memory of what you did here for me, $N. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25340;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done. Let me have a look at this.' WHERE `entry`=25341;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What\'ve you got for me here? You said the Gordunni had this? Disgusting...' WHERE `entry`=25342;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now that you understand the master\'s plan, you must prepare yourself to play your part.' WHERE `entry`=25343;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahh, I can feel the whelp in there. Let\'s get him out and ask him some questions...' WHERE `entry`=25344;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. Now the spiritual powers of the faerie dragon will be available to us.$B$BI hope you willing to perform another task for me.' WHERE `entry`=25345;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just imagine the possibilities of what we now possess, $N. Along with the materials that you have collected, I will be able to forever trap the muisek of these creatures into whatever I wish.' WHERE `entry`=25346;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<You hand Blood Guard Torek the devices that the overseer gave you, explaining the cult\'s plans. Torek\'s eyes go wide.>$B$BCho\'Gall is in charge of the cult? There can be no question then, this is the work of the Twilight\'s Hammer! You won\'t be the only one they\'ve sent into the city to deploy these devices.' WHERE `entry`=25347;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Twilight\'s Hammer will think twice before trying to turn our own people against us again. I\'m sure I\'m not the only one troubled by just how many citizens were taken in by their message. Times aren\'t exactly easy, but if you have no honor or loyalty, you have nothing.' WHERE `entry`=25348;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, $N, but the tale of your hunt troubles me. There should not be so many. The sickness is still spreading...' WHERE `entry`=25349;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='You have successfully defended Orgrimmar from the threat posed by this Twilight\'s Hammer cult, $N, and without shedding the blood of our own people. Our enemy will not rest for long. I cannot imagine that Cho\'Gall will accept defeat so easily.$B$BGarrosh Hellscream is a well-known hero of the Horde and he will know how to deal with this matter. Go to the Valley of Wisdom and speak to him in Grommash Hold. Tell young Hellscream that our enemies have shown themselves and we must be prepared for their return.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak with Garrosh Hellscream at Grommash Hold in Orgrimmar\'s Valley of Wisdom.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The warchief listens as you tell of your investigation into the Twilight\'s Hammer plot to destroy Orgrimmar.>$B$BYou are a dutiful member of the Horde, $N. You have done well in bringing this news to me. I will personally see to it that our enemies get what they deserve!' WHERE `entry`=25351;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You should\'ve seen the battle from here! Bodies were falling off of the cliff! Spectacular!' WHERE `entry`=25352;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='When I prayed at the shrine, Goldrinn granted me another vision. I saw you standing astride the Lightning Ledge, with lightning in your hands. Goldrinn seems to feel that this is of the utmost importance, but I don\'t understand what the Ancient has planned...$B$B$N, go to the Lightning Ledge. Twilight\'s Hammer has been running experiments with something called a "Lightning Channel." Investigate these channels, then use this totem to summon the Spirit of Goldrinn and see what he has in mind...',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, it is true! You indeed carry lightning in your hands. You are the chosen one, $N. You will be my champion, and carry my vengeance to realms where I cannot tread...' WHERE `entry`=25353;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Impressive, $N. Very impressive. You embody all of the strength of the Wolf Ancient, and possess the wisdom to use your powers well. I salute you.' WHERE `entry`=25354;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Lo\'Gosh granted me a vision while you were in the hovel, $N. I saw you striding across the Lightning Ledge, with lightning bolts in your hand. The vision was powerful: Lo\'Gosh feels this is of utmost importance. We must not fail the Ancient.$B$BUpon the Lightning Ledge, Twilight\'s Hammer has been experimenting with devices they call "Lightning Channels."$B$BInvestigate one of these channels, then use this totem to summon the Spirit of Lo\'Gosh and learn what the Ancient is planning...',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, it is true! You indeed carry lightning in your hands. You are the chosen one, $N. You will be my champion, and carry my vengeance to realms where I cannot tread...' WHERE `entry`=25355;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Jawn sent you? Good! We need your help, now!' WHERE `entry`=25356;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let\'s hope your efforts prove to be enough of a diversion...' WHERE `entry`=25357;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I trust we both know what\'s been going on inside these crates... That\'s right... ferrrmenntation! Here y\'are. My personal secret recipe. You wouldn\'t get this from any other guy!' WHERE `entry`=25358;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I remember you. You were there when they attacked us back in the cave. Good to have you with me, $C. Ready for a little vengeance?' WHERE `entry`=25359;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Does everything down here only come in jumbo size? Oooh! That\'s a thought. Maybe there are some hunky sea goblins around here somewhere. Thanks, by the way.' WHERE `entry`=25360;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful, $C! These will do nicely. There are enough here to make a cloak for Korrin, and possibly even more! Thank you.$B$BI hope the trip wasn\'t too dangerous? The area of Feralas is not known for being forgiving, but you\'ve obviously done well enough.$B$BThank you again, $C.' WHERE `entry`=25361;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Traitors to the Horde and traitors to their own people... I guess they\'re not all bad. They\'ll make fine drinking flasks.' WHERE `entry`=25362;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is proof of a good start, $N. Your skills as a soldier are to be commended. You are not the only one I ask that task of. Many before you have fought them, and in times past, our efforts have kept them at bay. Recently though, their attempts to push northward into our area of influence have increased dramatically. Their attacks have also become more savage... almost as if they were desperate. I have a plan though, $N, that might settle things once and for all against them...' WHERE `entry`=25363;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done as I have asked, and for that I salute you. Take this small reward as compensation for your efforts, $N.$B$BWith their numbers thinned and their leaders slain, the gnolls will think twice about storming the camp. This doesn\'t conclude the issue at hand, however...$B$BThere must be some reason why the gnolls have been whipped into such a frenzied state. Before they have a chance to regroup, I want to find out what is causing it.' WHERE `entry`=25364;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Examining the map reveals it to be the battle plans that Hadoken Swiftstrider wants. Numerous arrows that perhaps represent troop movements are drawn on the map, though most seem to be headed toward the south rather than to the north where Camp Mojache lies.$B$BAnother section of the map has a picture of what you think is a large insect of some kind, with various tick marks under it. From the looks of the gnolls, it perhaps represents their losses against the unknown bugs...' WHERE `entry`=25365;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, this is exactly what we needed. While I am not so skilled at ciphering what most of the scrawling on this map is, I\'ve seen enough battle plans in my day to understand what is happening with the gnolls. It looks like they are currently fighting a two front war. One is with us... but it seems that their main energy has been against a foe to their south.$B$BThere\'s more at hand here than meets the eye. Perhaps it is time to figure out who this other foe they face really is.' WHERE `entry`=25366;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $C. Though the extensiveness of the Zukk\'ash presence will not be thwarted with anything less than a full-scale invasion, you have bought us some time so we can devise a proper strategy.$B$BI will be sure to have these carapaces analyzed; we\'ll need to learn everything about them before we deal with what has unfortunately turned into a much larger issue than we had anticipated.' WHERE `entry`=25367;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The other spirits and I are bound here by a cruel demon named Verinias. He is our captor, a twisted, mindless beast who devours our souls over milennia.$B$BThe lure of the souls and arcane magic you\'ve brought me should let you draw him out. Take this condensed essence to the dead tree at the far north of the ruins. Use it to lure Verinias and slay him, that I may finally be free...',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m free...finally! Oh, it feels so good to be free... Oh, you saw, didn\'t you?' WHERE `entry`=25368;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Impressive, $C... most impressive!  If Stinglasher is indeed one of their strongest creatures, the study of the beast will prove to be quite valuable in time. It\'s now my charge to make sure we defend ourselves long enough to take advantage of it.$B$BPlease accept this coin bounty as a token of the entire camp\'s thanks, $N. Well done.' WHERE `entry`=25369;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='This is no mere natural occurrence, $N. There must be a twilight presence behind our lines that we haven\'t accounted for.$B$BIt\'s possible that whoever is instigating the elemental disturbance is using foul magic to hide themselves from our sight.$B$BSeek the aid of the faerie dragons that roam near the world tree; they can see through any of our enemy\'s illusions.$B$BFeed them the juniper berries that grow nearby to gain their trust.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well, $N. We cannot allow the Twilight\'s Hammer spies this close to the world tree!' WHERE `entry`=25370;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Amazing! You look exhausted. She must have really made you work for it. Life should be a lot easier down here going forward with a mount that swift at your beckoning. Congratulations, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25371;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is the key, $N! With the seedlings you collected for me earlier, the animals you\'ve saved from around Hyjal, and the Heart of the Forest you\'ve just discovered, we can rejuvenate this land right from under the feet of Twilight\'s Hammer. Imagine their astonishment to see their work undone, as life triumphs over chaos... I will begin the ceremony at once!' WHERE `entry`=25372;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, $N, but there is more work to be done to keep the camp safe. Listen further.' WHERE `entry`=25373;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I will be able to rest easy now, $N. You\'ve saved our camp from a terrible menace.' WHERE `entry`=25374;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, good. Let\'s hope the ogres are at least smart enough to realize we\'re sending a message!' WHERE `entry`=25375;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve discovered lost treasure! Your mind reels at the thought of what else might be hidden in the depths of the sea.' WHERE `entry`=25377;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve come.$B$BI am ashamed to ask this of you, $C, but I\'ve ran from him long enough. Taerar must be stopped.' WHERE `entry`=25378;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is done.$B$BThis land that has suffered so much can rest now.' WHERE `entry`=25379;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. It might be awkward at first, but you will get used to advocating our beliefs in public. It is one way of remembering our obligation to bring the truth to others. We must save as many as we can.' WHERE `entry`=25380;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. You\'ve given us the opportunity to try to reclaim the upper hand.' WHERE `entry`=25381;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dead? Good! But it seems there\'s still so much to be done... fires to quench... and the soil to heal... I hope you\'ll stay close and help us reclaim Hyjal!' WHERE `entry`=25382;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are truly blessed by the Earth Mother, $N, to have the honor of fighting with the guardians of nature, and to also survive it.$B$BKnow that you have kept safe every living soul in this camp, and possibly this entire forest. Take these gifts with my deepest thanks.' WHERE `entry`=25383;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Squueeeee! Did the nice Mr. $C pull you from the flames, little friend? You\'re safe now! Hooray!' WHERE `entry`=25385;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve been tussling with drakes, eh? I like it. We need someone who can pull their own weight around here. Are you ready to fight for the Horde?' WHERE `entry`=25386;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am thankful you\'ve come, $C. Our camp is beset by many perils, and yet we must tend to those fleeing the devastation of the cataclysm. If there is to be any refuge here, you must help us.' WHERE `entry`=25387;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Why, $N! What a surprise! If anyone ever calls your character into question you be sure to send them my way. I\'ll tell anyone who\'ll listen that in my moment of need, you gave me a case of crabs...' WHERE `entry`=25388;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, my! That\'s some of the biggest, juiciest tail I\'ve ever seen!' WHERE `entry`=25389;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, you\'ve found them! I was sure they were lost forever... Here you are, $N. I hope this is ample payment.' WHERE `entry`=25390;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='As promised, you have your choice, $N. The muisek of the creatures has been forever sealed into the power of these weapons.$B$BYou may now wield their energy as your own. Use it well.' WHERE `entry`=25391;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh yay! Happy little deer! Now they can grow up and have ADVENTURES. You\'re swell.' WHERE `entry`=25392;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Curses! We had to fall back. But Thermaplugg\'s lost, and he knows it... he\'s only bought himself time. We hold the surface, and when the radiation clears we\'ll assault and recapture Gnomeregan with a force twice this size.' WHERE `entry`=25393;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This development worries me greatly. This has happened before...' WHERE `entry`=25394;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='You\'ve got to help us, $G:lad:lass;. We were tasked with escorting a precious cargo to our fellow dwarves...a keg full of the finest ale you can get out here!$B$BUnfortunately, bird-brain over here fell asleep on the job! Those blasted orcs took our keg, and hauled it up into Dun Algaz where they\'re hiding.$B$BThis can\'t stand! Now, while I stay here and try to convince this idiot that it was his fault, I\'d like you to go in there and get our keg back. For Khaz Modan!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank the Makers! It\'s downright pristine. Those orcs couldn\'t figure out the tap-lock, it seems...and couldn\'t hack through the mastercraft work of Ironforge\'s keg-crafters with their crude weapons!' WHERE `entry`=25395;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The mountain giants are precious allies of our race. We must stop this corruption before it claims any more creatures of the forest.' WHERE `entry`=25396;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The spirits of these guardians will return in time, $N. You\'ve freed them to move on in nature\'s cycle.$B$BNow it falls to us to make sure that cycle is free of corruption and needless suffering.' WHERE `entry`=25397;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your bravery has seen us through! The Emerald Nightmare has been shut out from this land.$B$BThe fate of the dragon Taerar worries me...but there is much work still to be done. I cannot afford to dwell on it.' WHERE `entry`=25398;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your valor was mentioned in my briefings, $N. I commend you.' WHERE `entry`=25399;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It sounds like there were more than we thought! Thank you for your brave work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25400;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Is that it? Let me see here...' WHERE `entry`=25401;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahh, the orb I mentioned before. A decent reason to disturb me.' WHERE `entry`=25402;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you\'ve brought him. Now I merely have to suffer the fate of speaking to him.' WHERE `entry`=25403;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very well, $R. I will help you mortals, even from within my bonds. But don\'t sicken me by claiming it\'s my redemption. I do this for my own ends.' WHERE `entry`=25404;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hear you, $R.$B$BI understand the urgency, but these men are in no condition to fight.' WHERE `entry`=25405;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful! Everything\'s going according to plan. Lady Shandris will be pleased.' WHERE `entry`=25406;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wisps have always lived in harmony with night elves, and we depend on them for many things. These little guys you sent back, for example, will be helping us with some new construction and repairs.$B$BReady for more?' WHERE `entry`=25407;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very good. Please crush the berries into a pulpy liquid. That\'s quite an aroma isn\'t it? Now now, don\'t gag. It\'s beneath you.' WHERE `entry`=25408;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A properly trained squadron of hippogryph riders can take on nearly any opposing force. Feathermoon Stronghold will be much safer with these noble beasts on our side.' WHERE `entry`=25409;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They may not look it, but some treants grow to be ancient protectors. We could use a few more of those around here...' WHERE `entry`=25410;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Yes, master?' WHERE `entry`=25411;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, yes! Show me the runes you discovered. "Vol\'talo Thol\'embaar." That\'s the name of your real enemy. Presumably you\'re dealing with one of Ragnaros\'s generals, sent here to scorch the mountainside and pave the way for his conquest. I will show you how to crush him.' WHERE `entry`=25412;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you found them? Why did the missing men and women not return with you?$B$B<You tell the captain that they seemed determined to stay for various reasons.>$B$BThen we cannot force them to come home. I can only hope that in time, the cultists will realize the harm their actions have caused and decide to return to their normal lives.$B$BThank you for your efforts, $N. I will tell the families what you found.' WHERE `entry`=25414;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Speak to Cultist Wyman',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Speak to Cultist Orlunn' WHERE `entry`=25414;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. It might be awkward at first, but you will grow accustomed to advocating our beliefs in public. It is one way of remembering our obligation to bring the truth to others. We must offer hope to everyone, for we all face the end of this world together.' WHERE `entry`=25415;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now that you understand the master\'s plan, you must prepare to play your part in making it a reality.' WHERE `entry`=25416;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<You hand Captain Anton the devices that the overseer gave you, explaining the cult\'s plans.>$B$BCho\'Gall is in charge of the cult? Then, it has to be Twilight\'s Hammer! We suspected that they would try to strike again, but no one knew what form the attack would take.$B$BYou\'ve done an excellent job uncovering this plot. Unfortunately, you won\'t be the only one they\'ve sent into the city to deploy these devices.' WHERE `entry`=25417;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Twilight\'s Hammer will think twice before trying to turn our own people against us again.$B$BWhat worries me is how many citizens joined their movement without thinking about the cult\'s empty promises. Are times so dire that people will abandon the Light for promises of power and immortality?' WHERE `entry`=25418;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, $C. We\'re that much closer to the secrets of Uldum.' WHERE `entry`=25420;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is amazing. These hieroglyphs are undoubtedly titan, but the markings below it... If I had to hope, this is the same passage written over and over again in an entire assortment of ancient languages. We might be able to use this to decipher the hieroglyphs! If the antechamber was covered in them as you say, who knows what else we\'ll learn. I\'d like to grant you a fine reward, $N. We\'ve made the find of the century!' WHERE `entry`=25421;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you! Thank you... I feel much better. With just a bit more...' WHERE `entry`=25422;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You can feel their anguish, can\'t you? My poor friends. At least we can use you to fix things...' WHERE `entry`=25423;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This development is troubling, $N. We must act swiftly.' WHERE `entry`=25424;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The king\'s face takes on a look of concern, and then anger as you describe the Twilight\'s Hammer plot to destroy Stormwind.>$B$BHow dare they strike Stormwind? How dare they try to manipulate the people of this city against us and the Alliance! If not for your valor this day, $N, our city would not have discovered this Twilight\'s Hammer scheme. You are a true hero of Stormwind and the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=25425;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. I didn\'t think those gnolls would give you much trouble.' WHERE `entry`=25426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect. Any gnolls left will be simple prey, lost in the woods.$B$BHeh...here, soldier, take your reward before I get distracted. We\'ve got other threats to deal with.' WHERE `entry`=25427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There it is! Such a trophy! Born in the fires of another plane... Go ahead, $R. Crush it. Crush his charcoal heart in your hands and let the winds scatter the ashes... yes, yes.' WHERE `entry`=25428;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are silithid after all...I wasn\'t sure, having never seen one in person. Gilneas had its problems, but at least we didn\'t have these monstrosities running around!' WHERE `entry`=25429;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My duties are here, viewing the enemy\'s movement from above, commanding our armies where they\'re needed. Your aid would be most welcome.' WHERE `entry`=25430;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N! You\'re proving very valuable to securing this area for the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=25431;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='We dealt the Gordunni ogres a large blow at Dire Maul, but we haven\'t quite finished the job. My scouts have reported a group of them amassed in the hills to the north, gathering for some reason.$B$BIt\'s possible they\'re interested in the Horde settlement nearby, but I don\'t want to take any chances. Scout the area, kill any ogres you come across, and report back.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to see you back. We\'ve learned more about the ogre situation.' WHERE `entry`=25432;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done once again, $N. Yet another threat removed from Feralas.' WHERE `entry`=25433;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, and good riddance. I hope we never have to see another ogre here again!' WHERE `entry`=25434;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I didn\'t want to scare you, but this is a grave situation. If the portal at Dream Bough was sealed, and the corruption is still spreading...' WHERE `entry`=25436;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve come.$B$BI am ashamed to ask this of you, $C, but I\'ve ran from him long enough. Taerar must be stopped.' WHERE `entry`=25437;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='To be drawn into a fight between dragons...I don\'t know if you\'re blessed or cursed.$B$BLady Shandris has heard of all you\'ve done, and has personally sent this reward for your bravery. I\'m glad you came back in one piece to receive it.' WHERE `entry`=25438;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good to have a real warrior at my side. Too often, my shaman brethren can\'t seem to stomach the work.' WHERE `entry`=25439;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='And with this, hopefully their attacks on us will calm for a while.' WHERE `entry`=25440;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Too often, we are mistaken for druidic types. Perhaps that\'s true for some shaman, but do not let yourself be plagued by the ignorant belief that we are always peaceful. Nothing about what I do is harmonious. I command the elements to my will. There is nothing offered in return. I would have it no other way.' WHERE `entry`=25441;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What is this? A pearl? Much more I think.$B$BThis is exactly what I was looking for, thank you for bringing it to me.' WHERE `entry`=25442;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, yes! Show me the runes you discovered. "Vol\'talo Thol\'embaar." That\'s the name of your real enemy. Presumably you\'re dealing with one of Ragnaros\'s generals, sent here to scorch the mountainside and pave the way for his conquest. I will show you how to crush him.' WHERE `entry`=25443;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These be enough for me purposes. Now comes de hard part.' WHERE `entry`=25444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N, you\'d be a mighty warrior and a fierce commrade to da Darkspear trolls. De Echo Isles are OURS now and we couldn\'ta done it wit\'out ya.$B$BTake dis cloak. Wear it wit pride. You\'d be a member of da tribe now!$B$BIn no time, da trolls will have a home again and we have you to thank for dat.' WHERE `entry`=25445;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m already beginnin\' to see what de frogs are seein\'. Ya done it perfectly, $N. Now Vol\'jin and I will see what Zalazane be plannin\'.' WHERE `entry`=25446;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='At the very least, these creatures\' suffering has ended. Let us hope their sacrifice will bring a stop to further pain.' WHERE `entry`=25447;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $C. That\'s one less distraction for me.' WHERE `entry`=25448;
