UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Splendifimous!  Not only am I glad to see that you\'ve returned with the residue, but also with all your major appendages intact!  That is, well, there was never any danger in using the Ultra-Shrinker, now was there!$B$BI do appreciate your effort on my behalf, $N. Truly, you are a friend to goblins everywhere. Accept this as a token of my appreciation!' WHERE `entry`=25465;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Scrumdillyriffic!  These cores will keep me working for some time. Add to that the benefit of there now being fewer elementals along the coast, and I might no longer cry myself to sleep at the prospect of having set up shop in perhaps the worst place imaginable!$B$BThank you, $N, for your efforts on my behalf. While it certainly straps me financially to do this, allow me to show you some gratitude you may understand and appreciate... loot!' WHERE `entry`=25466;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The satisfying sound of a chest unlocking is followed by the sight of once-hidden treasure.' WHERE `entry`=25467;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Aren\'t they adorable? The babies are even cuter.' WHERE `entry`=25468;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent!$B$B$N, you\'ve helped bolster our forces here, and you\'ve saved many of these forest creatures from the Horde as well. With our army now ready, Feathermoon will stand against all threats, Horde or otherwise!$B$BOn behalf of Lady Feathermoon, I\'d like to award you with this weapon, fit for a Sentinel.' WHERE `entry`=25469;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Vanira\'s frogs be tellin\' de truth, den? Dis tiger be a druid and an ally? We couldn\'t be hopin\' for a better outcome. Dis be a good omen for de coming battle.' WHERE `entry`=25470;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ello, mon! You look a bit more capable then most of dem coming through here. Come rest a bit. Make yaself at home.' WHERE `entry`=25471;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent, $N. This will be a great weapon against the enemy forces.' WHERE `entry`=25472;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just so you know, you\'ll find Kaja\'Cola all over town. It\'s the Bilgewater Cartel\'s best-selling product of all time! Just remember, image is everything if we\'re going to get you promoted to Trade Prince! No, wait, profits are everything! Explosions are a close second! Then, image!' WHERE `entry`=25473;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You place the egg... distress beacon... inside the chicken... homing robot.$B$BHums and whirs are heard from inside the robot as it struggles to stand up. After the robot comes to life, Oglethorpe\'s voice is heard once more, but now from inside the robot:$B$B"OOX-22/FE is working at least, but it needs major repairs! It is much too heavy for you to carry it... but I think I have an idea. Are you up for watching over it some more?"' WHERE `entry`=25475;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, YOU\'RE the great savior of OOX-22/FE! I cannot even begin to express my thanks for your assistance! My homing robot series needs more development, but your recovery has saved me countless hours of extra rebuilding time, as well as many gold pieces in manufacture costs!$B$BPlease, take your choice of any of these items I have. Thank you again for your generous assistance $N, my robots and I are in your debt!' WHERE `entry`=25476;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='How unfortunate... Well, all things considered, it is good to see that you made it back unharmed.' WHERE `entry`=25477;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nyse sent you? Good! We need your help, now!' WHERE `entry`=25478;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thyssiana sent you? Good! We need your help, now!' WHERE `entry`=25479;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I will take de spirits\' advice to heart. Wit\' dem behind us and de power of de ancient loas of de Darkspear Tribe, we be ready to reclaim what\'s ours!' WHERE `entry`=25480;
