UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='This is going to take a while, but I\'m sure we\'ll beat them back.$B$BYou\'re more good to Thousand Needles elsewhere. We have reports that the gnomes and goblins out on the flooded salt flats somehow survived on a giant barge! Rendow is on the dock. He\'ll get you a boat to go there.$B$BMind helping us out a little on your way to him?' WHERE `entry`=25486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You want a canoe to go out to the salt flats? But, surely the race track has been destroyed?! Nonetheless, for your bravery, you will have the last one!' WHERE `entry`=25487;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='YES?! Do you see me interrupting your fascinating argument? No... no, please, go ahead. I\'m sure that your interruption is about something very important. More important than dealing with the survival of everyone here, in fact.' WHERE `entry`=25488;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Are you ready to go, $C?$B$BOne of our braves will row you out to the Mirage Raceway. If anyone has survived out there, they\'ll desparately need your help.$B$BMay the Earth Mother smile upon you.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Heya, kid, I\'ll be right with ya. Just gotta shut this gnome twerp up first.' WHERE `entry`=25489;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='$N, these fiends from the Twilight\'s Hammer are attempting to scourge this whole mountain clean of all life. Even now they trail behind this inferno, leaving death and ash in their wake.$B$BArch Druid Hamuul Runetotem is behind the fires, trying to salvage the wilderness before it\'s blotted permanently from the map. Travel southeast, through the inferno and down the road beyond. Find and aid the Arch Druid.$B$BOn your way there, clear the roads by killing any Charbringers that you find.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very good. The Twilight\'s Hammer must be sent the message that we will never give up.' WHERE `entry`=25490;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='This land has been scourged by fire, but it may yet renew itself.$B$BSome seeds deep in the soil may have withstood the scorching heat here in the flamewake. These durable plants are the key to this forest\'s regrowth. Please, collect some of these seedlings for me.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' These seedlings have survived an apocalypse. Even a handful hold great power. Life always replenishes itself, often stronger than before. Once the way is clear, we will use these to perform a miracle on this mountain, $N. You will see.' WHERE `entry`=25491;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Firebreak',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, $N. There\'s a chance the forest will recover from this yet. Now, there\'s something else I need you to take care of for me...' WHERE `entry`=25492;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very good. We will need these to act as bait while they are still warm. Here is my plan...' WHERE `entry`=25493;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent!  Our pup is ready for a fight.' WHERE `entry`=25494;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='At last, everythin\' be ready. Now, we show Zalazane what happen to dose who defy de Darkspears!' WHERE `entry`=25495;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Our situation is growing a bit desperate, r.$B$BWe must focus our attention on the naga and their prisoners, but it would be folly to do so without being prepared, and down here that means finding a way to travel more quickly.$B$BThese sharks are clearly fond of sea turtle. Let\'s see if we can turn that into our advantage.' WHERE `entry`=25497;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh. You\'re still alive. Not bad.' WHERE `entry`=25499;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is the speech from Toby?  Fantastic!$B$BRecruit, you\'ve done all we could possibly ask for and the Gnomeregan Army thanks you!$B$BWe\'ve got a strike team heading to Gnomeregan now and that wouldn\'t have been possible without your assistance. For all of your help, we\'d like you to join the Gnomeregan Reserves!$B$BIt doesn\'t pay very well, but you do get this snazzy helmet. Hang on to that, you might need it someday!' WHERE `entry`=25500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s good! Between your work and the work of a few others, that valley is secure from a counter-attack. I\'ve done all I can. It\'s all up to you and the Arch Druid now.' WHERE `entry`=25502;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This item was highly prized by the local gilblin population - even coveted by King Gurboggle, himself!' WHERE `entry`=25503;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I don\'t have even half of that stuff!' WHERE `entry`=25504;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Heya, pal, mind if I take a look at that list? What\'s Pozzik thinking? He knows that I don\'t have even half of that stuff!' WHERE `entry`=25505;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Fresh and stinking, these innards will prove to be irresistible for Nemesis, the befouled turtle god created by Twilight\'s Hammer.$B$BNemesis must eventually be destroyed, but first, we must collect a piece of his fiery armored shell. With it, we\'ll be able to work some magic to free the true Ancient.$B$BGo into the Flamewake and drop this bait near Nemesis. It will distract him. Pry off a piece of his shell... then run, if you hope to survive the encounter.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Nemesis is an instrument of evil, but he was forged from a shell fragment of the true Ancient. We will exploit this connection.' WHERE `entry`=25507;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very well. You\'re at least competent enough to figure out which way the pointy end of the pick goes.' WHERE `entry`=25509;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='<The Arch Druid fills the shell fragment with water, which boils instantly. He adds a bundle of herbs and closes his eyes in a silent prayer.>$B$B$N, Tortolla the turtle ancient is ageless, a part of this world since the time of the titans. He speaks a language older than our understanding.$B$BDrink this and find a place of calm within yourself. You will be able to understand the language of Tortolla. Go to him now, in the ashen lake. Earn the ancient\'s trust. The fate of Hyjal hinges on this.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='$R. This tongue. Is not yours. What do you want ... tormentor?' WHERE `entry`=25510;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fantastic. I might challenge you to a duel myself someday.' WHERE `entry`=25513;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You... Are not like the others. I am free once again. The others... Will pay.' WHERE `entry`=25514;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='<Jinky rolls up her sleeves and slicks back her hair while eyeing you up and down.>$B$BFine, if Fizzle wants you to have your own boat, the first thing we\'ll need is parts. Guess who gets to go get them?$B$B<Jinky smiles as she points downward and then grabs you a spare diving helm and flippers.>$B$BThat\'s right, $G brother : sister;. You get to go down into the deeps and salvage what rocket car parts you can find at the Raceway Ruins.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='This\'ll do for a start.' WHERE `entry`=25515;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is a great start!' WHERE `entry`=25516;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s the spirit! You\'re a real credit to the Alliance! You know, you can go back in there and do that anytime you feel like it. I highly encourage you to do so!' WHERE `entry`=25517;
