UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not another one! $N, these devices have been springing up all around Azeroth. We know that they can instigate elemental disturbances in the area, including causing tears in the elemental planes. The devices stink of Twilight\'s Hammer. The engravings covering the surface and the captured elemental essence implicate Cho\'gall and his minions are behind this. If you find more of these, please bring them to me or one of my associates. We need to learn more about what\'s behind this attack!' WHERE `entry`=25572;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent, $N. That should put a stop to the attacks once we finish these elementals off.' WHERE `entry`=25574;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The weapons the Twilight\'s Hammer uses against us are crafted by Forgemaster Pyrenduis within these very halls. The metal slices through armor like cheese in the hands of its wielder. Yet, when captured, the steel turns brittle and shatters.$B$BSo be it, $N. I\'d rather see those cursed arms smashed than delivered to our enemy.$B$BSeek out the crates of twilight arms in these caverns and smash them to pieces.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, good. I like nothing more than to see the works of our enemy destroyed.' WHERE `entry`=25575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Here we are deep within the realm of the fire god and what do we find? The little puppets of Ragnaros, scurrying around to do his bidding.$B$BThese Dark Iron laborers are finishing and packaging the weapons Twilight\'s Hammer hopes to use in their conquest of Hyjal. I don\'t care if they\'re here of their own free will or if they\'ve been brainwashed or kidnapped... They\'re a foe of our beloved Wolf Ancient and they should pay the ultimate price.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dead? Good. They sealed their fate when they threw their lot in with Ragnaros and his kingdom of flame. Leave their bodies down here to crumble into ash.' WHERE `entry`=25576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great work! There was a time when adventurers would collect these cores in order to craft mediocre fire-resistant equipment. But for now, I\'m glad just to destroy these fiends once and for all.' WHERE `entry`=25577;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Alysra\'s decision might not have been the wisest, $N. Yet there is little time to worry about that now. I bring important discoveries from the Emerald Dream.' WHERE `entry`=25578;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $C. I will get some of our own patrols out to make sure that no more naga get within sight of this cave. We should have the area secured within the hour.' WHERE `entry`=25579;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N, and just in time too. The Admiral just started sending more men out. Strong sword arms to be sure, but I doubt they possess quite the same awareness and finesse that you do. We were lucky to have you here when things went south. I suspect you will have a large role to play in things to come as well.' WHERE `entry`=25580;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you so much for taking this seriously.$B$BThis is some of the first definitive proof of other members of the Vashj family. Very interesting. And I\'d never even heard of either of the other two figures you mentioned until now.$B$BSo much of our history was lost during the sundering - it\'s exciting to have a chance at reclaiming some of it.' WHERE `entry`=25581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Ranger Valarian statue',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='High Priestess Siralen statue' WHERE `entry`=25581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is good intel. You have a sharp eye, $C. It sounds like the building tucked under the terrace at the far end of the ruins will make a suitable forward post. I will send some men immediately to start defensive preparations and we will reposition there as soon as possible.' WHERE `entry`=25582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Interesting indeed. The remains you describe sound much like the sea vrykul we encountered in Northrend. I highly doubt we will be striking any alliances with their sort, no matter the cause. Still, this information may prove useful in the future. I will think on it further if time permits. Thank you for bringing it to my attention.' WHERE `entry`=25583;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='It\'ll be crucial to reclaim each of the Ancients\' shrines, $N.$B$BFollow the road west of the Verdant Thicket, into Wolf\'s Run.$B$BWe have operatives stationed there. Aid them in any way that you can and work your way to the first shrine.$B$BThe wolf god was known to the elves as Goldrinn and to the orcs as Lo\'Gosh. He will be a fierce ally in our fight against the enemy.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ysera sent you? Good! We need all the help we can. We\'ll never be able to recover the shrines to the ancients so long as Twilight\'s Hammer controls the roads. Somehow we\'ve got to stem the flood.' WHERE `entry`=25584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They\'re still shooting, but not nearly as much! Yeeeeeeeeeaaaaaaaaaaah!' WHERE `entry`=25585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They\'re still shooting, but not nearly as much! Yeeeeeeeeeaaaaaaaaaaah!' WHERE `entry`=25586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I cannot thank you enough, $R. I just hope this whole nightmare has a happy ending.' WHERE `entry`=25587;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'ll teach those scurvy dogs! You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25588;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'ll teach those scurvy dogs! You have my thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25589;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey! Get me out of here!' WHERE `entry`=25590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fantastic. I might challenge you to a duel myself someday.' WHERE `entry`=25591;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You know what it is to carry yourself with honor, $C. You do Hellscream proud.' WHERE `entry`=25592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $C. You\'ve proven very useful.' WHERE `entry`=25593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Glad you know a quick buck when you see one. Pleasure doing business with you, $G buddy:gorgeous;.' WHERE `entry`=25594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now to hold up my end of the bargain. I\'ll get this cooked and passed out immediately.$B$BYou and I will have to have a talk later. I\'m going to need help that these soldiers just can\'t offer.' WHERE `entry`=25595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey! Get me out of here!' WHERE `entry`=25596;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Only once has there been a leader capable of commanding demigods and mortals alike.$B$BHis name was Jarod Shadowsong and his ability to lead in battle was such that Cenarius and the other Ancients placed themselves under his command.$B$BHe disappeared for years and his whereabouts were unknown. Until now.$B$BHe is being held captive inside a Twilight camp in Darkwhisper Gorge.$B$BYour job is to infiltrate their ranks and free Jarod. Speak to the one known as Ortell at Darkwhisper Pass to the southeast.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey there. I\'m glad to see they sent someone of your caliber for this operation. This here\'s going to call for some subtlety. We can\'t risk Commander Shadowsong getting killed.' WHERE `entry`=25597;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Where would we be without you, $R! I don\'t want to even imagine!' WHERE `entry`=25598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is the tome we\'ve heard about? I see... I guess it\'s good that I can read some of the elemental script. I\'ll work on translating this. Meanwhile, there\'s one final problem to take care of.' WHERE `entry`=25599;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is done! We\'ll seal this fiery hole up behind us and let the minions of the Twilight\'s Hammer discover the corpses we left behind. We couldn\'t have done it without you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25600;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There you are, Earthenfurydamus. I\'ve been meaning to talk to you about something. I heard about the unfortunate incident that befell our poor friend, Okrog.' WHERE `entry`=25601;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Outstanding! Let\'s see if this does the trick.... Stand back, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not another one! $N, these devices have been springing up all around Azeroth. We know that they can instigate elemental disturbances in the area, including causing tears in the elemental planes. The devices stink of Twilight\'s Hammer. The engravings covering the surface and the captured elemental essence implicate Cho\'gall and his minions are behind this. If you find more of these, bring them to me or one of my associates. We need to learn more about what\'s behind this attack.' WHERE `entry`=25604;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not another one! $N, these devices have been springing up all around Azeroth. We know that they can instigate elemental disturbances in the area, including causing tears in the elemental planes. The devices stink of Twilight\'s Hammer. The engravings covering the surface and the captured elemental essence implicate Cho\'gall and his minions are behind this. If you find more of these, please bring them to me or one of my associates. We need to learn more about what\'s behind this attack!' WHERE `entry`=25606;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, ze junk haz arrived! Zit is ze last piece of ze puzzle! Now to zet it up! Standby, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25607;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. We might win this one yet.' WHERE `entry`=25608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh yeah! Look at all that booty. Wait a minute... bring it closer!' WHERE `entry`=25609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh yeah! Look at all that booty. Wait a minute... bring it closer!' WHERE `entry`=25610;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They\'re moving supplies to Hyjal straight from the elemental planes? That explains so much. You\'ve made Goldrinn proud by sealing that flamegate, $N, but there may be more portals to seal. You should check with the other shrines!' WHERE `entry`=25611;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They\'re moving supplies to Hyjal straight from the elemental planes? Devious. You\'ve made Lo\'Gosh proud by sealing that flamegate, $N, but there may be more portals to seal. You should check with the other shrines!' WHERE `entry`=25612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' We use guns just fine, friend. CANNONS, on the other hand, I take issue with...' WHERE `entry`=25613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. The gnome technology, while somewhat obnoxious, is highly effective. We should now have a clear path to Windshear Hold.' WHERE `entry`=25614;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With the airways clear our hippogryphs will be able to move into Stonetalon freely. Well done, $N! Now on to more pressing matters. What you witnessed at Trueshot Point was a small sampling of the decimation left in the wake of Hellscream\'s legacy. As Warchief of the Horde, Hellscream has declared Kalimdor as the Horde\'s sovereign territory. All that would oppose the Horde are destroyed. We are Kalimdor\'s last line of defense. Should we fall, Kalimdor will also fall. The Horde must be stopped!' WHERE `entry`=25615;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With the Krom\'gar incinerators dealt with, the forest may be allowed to regrow. Only time can heal the wounds left by the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=25616;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you are the champion Lo\'Gosh promised! Your eyes don\'t deceive you: you have entered the Firelands, an elemental plane of molten stone and fire. We\'ve got our work cut out for us here. Put aside your differences with the Alliance, there\'s plenty of danger to go around. And take this: the Fang of Lo\'Gosh will allow you to channel the ancient\'s power here within the Firelands. Use it well!' WHERE `entry`=25617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you are the champion Goldrinn promised! Your eyes don\'t deceive you: you have entered the Firelands, an elemental plane of molten stone and fire. We\'ve got our work cut out for us here. Put aside your differences with the Horde, there\'s plenty of danger to go around. And take this: the Fang of Goldrinn will allow you to channel the ancient\'s power here within the Firelands. Use it well!' WHERE `entry`=25618;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Reoccupation',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hah! It seems you were right. That broken trident is serving you just fine. I suppose I don\'t get to see you claw anything to death today after all.' WHERE `entry`=25619;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, my battlemaiden, you\'ve come to me. The warrior caste whispers of nothing but your victories on the battlefield, and we\'ve only just begun our assault to take the city.$B$BYou have served me proud thus far. May the Queen favor you that you might continue to do more of the same.' WHERE `entry`=25620;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Come in, $N. Can you hear me? Zis iz Professor Xakxak! *POP* *CRACKLE* PERFECT! Viz ze Gnomecorder I vill be able to direct you about Stonetalon vile staying out of harmz vay! Now, onto our next order of buziness!' WHERE `entry`=25621;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Vonderful! As promised, VOILA, your reward! Now, I have a bit of news that you might find interesting.' WHERE `entry`=25622;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you are the champion Goldrinn promised! Your eyes don\'t deceive you: you have entered the Firelands, an elemental plane of molten stone and fire. We\'ve got our work cut out for us here. Put aside your differences with the Horde, there\'s plenty of danger to go around. And take this: the Fang of Goldrinn will allow you to channel the ancient\'s power here within the Firelands. Use it well!' WHERE `entry`=25623;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you are the champion Lo\'Gosh promised! Your eyes don\'t deceive you: you have entered the Firelands, an elemental plane of molten stone and fire. We\'ve got our work cut out for us here. Put aside your differences with the Alliance, there\'s plenty of danger to go around. And take this: the Fang of Lo\'Gosh will allow you to channel the ancient\'s power here within the Firelands. Use it well!' WHERE `entry`=25624;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Minions of the Old God? Two very potent foes have joined forces then. Their hope to defeat the Tidehunter may not be so foolish after all.$B$B$N, we can\'t let that happen. If Azshara defeats the Tidehunter and takes his power for herself, I\'m not sure any number of us could ever hope to oppose her on the seas.$B$BThe first step is clear at least - we need to hunt down the fiend that destroyed our ships. The navy was confident enough to bring in a new fleet, perhaps they have a plan.' WHERE `entry`=25626;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yeah, yeah, yeah... I\'m sure that your little adventure into the cave was very interesting. How about we talk about it over drinks back on the Speedbarge once you get me out of this cage?' WHERE `entry`=25627;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yeah, yeah, yeah... I\'m sure that your little adventure into the cave was very interesting. How about we talk about it over drinks back on the Speedbarge once you get me out of this cage?' WHERE `entry`=25628;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, Battlemaiden.$B$BI will attend to the eastern bridge. I need you to attend to the temple itself. The ritual must not be interrupted.' WHERE `entry`=25629;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Can this wait, $C? The battle is not going well. Oh, you\'re here to help. I hope you don\'t mind a little heat...' WHERE `entry`=25630;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is good of you to join me, Battlemaiden. The echoes of your combat graced your approach. It was a beautiful sound to behold.' WHERE `entry`=25637;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Take the Soggy Note to Erunak at Shallow\'s End.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='If he still lives, I may be able to locate this poor soul.' WHERE `entry`=25638;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good to see you again, $N. Thanks for the rescue in Ashenvale. Damn shame about all the gnomes we lost. You ready to get down to business?' WHERE `entry`=25640;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done indeed... I\'d expect nothing less from my own daughter. She\'ll make a fine witch doctor someday.' WHERE `entry`=25641;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not too much trouble, I hope. With these samples we should be able to figure out what they plan to do with the ore and the big bomb.' WHERE `entry`=25642;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Take the Pure Twilight Egg to Aronus at the Gates of Sothann in Hyjal.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You were right to come to me with this, $N. This represents a great threat to us if we do not act swiftly and boldly.' WHERE `entry`=25644;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am a fool...I was misled. This is nothing more than a rusted trinket, and my visions have no doubt been fulfilled. Forgive me, $N. But should you meet this demoness again, I pray you will triumph over her as you did Verinias.' WHERE `entry`=25645;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice job, I could hear their shrill screams from out here. You\'ve turned the whole place on its head! Did you happen to find any other information about the mining operation?' WHERE `entry`=25646;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Interesting. Hrm... Troubling... Can\'t understand a damn thing written here - if that is writing. Could just be toilet paper. Sure smells like it.' WHERE `entry`=25647;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, you\'re here. Welcome to Azshara, the stage for the next act of the Horde\'s glorious future. Now get to work.' WHERE `entry`=25648;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Uh oh... Disgusting! The good news is that this isn\'t toilet paper. The bad news is that the ink on this paper is a mixture of kodo poop and blood. That\'s not the worst of it, though...' WHERE `entry`=25649;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This is bad. Really, really bad. You have to warn Lord Fallowmere at Windshear Hold. What in the... It\'s MOVING! The goblin balloon is taking off! We\'re too late!' WHERE `entry`=25650;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My gunpowder! You found it! I\'m not crazy after all!' WHERE `entry`=25651;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Amazing story, lad. I\'d have never believed you had I not seen it with my own eyes. You did enough damage to that balloon to make those fiends pull back! Alas, the threat is far from over. We have only delayed the attack. There is much work to do if we are to stop the Horde from destroying Stonetalon!' WHERE `entry`=25652;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='By relieving Tortolla of his final burdens you have acquired for us a formidable ally... and the final piece of the puzzle. Steel yourself, $N. The most difficult part of our journey is to begin. We will bring the fight to their stronghold.' WHERE `entry`=25653;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These lands will finally be free of the foulness of the harpies. I cannot thank you enough.' WHERE `entry`=25654;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Feels great to be off the leash, doesn\'t it?' WHERE `entry`=25655;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, that\'s a start. The birds who laid these eggs will never accept them again, so we\'ll have to raise these birds as orphans in the shrine here. Were Aviana here, she never would\'ve let this travesty happen. But, on to business...' WHERE `entry`=25656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Amazing! You watch the great white beast swim off into the depths and wonder to yourself if anything could ever take him down...' WHERE `entry`=25657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Nar\'shola Wards are performing perfectly. I will inform the Mistress of the Tides of your aid immediately.$B$BThank you for your assistance, my lady.' WHERE `entry`=25658;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The Kvaldir General crumples to the ground, defeated.>$B$B<With this, the ruins of Vashj\'ir have been claimed for Lady Naz\'jar. Her ultimate goals remain uncertain, but it is clear that the naga came here with purpose.>$B$B<If only you could continue, you are sure that the answers to defeating the naga lie within this vision, but the Wavespeaker\'s magics are waning, and you are losing your connection with the Battlemaiden.>' WHERE `entry`=25659;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Haunted',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='What ya be wantin\'? Oh no you don\'t. I can see ya got Tony\'s spirit with ya, and I want nothin\' to do with it!' WHERE `entry`=25660;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Fine, I be helpin\' ya. He not gettin\' outa payin\' me alimony that easy! \'Sides, there be the baby he had with me sistah ta take care of!$B$BFirst thing we needin\' is the innards of his closest friends. That\'d be his cap\'ns.$B$BGo down there an pay the three of them a visit.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' They\'s gonna have ta do. It not be like he had many friends. Ain\'t that right, Two-Tusk?' WHERE `entry`=25661;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We don\'t have much time. To get me out of here you are going to have to take out Warlord Roktrog. He holds the key to this prison.' WHERE `entry`=25662;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' To be born again, but in darkness... I have been stolen away.' WHERE `entry`=25663;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That was nasty work, $N, but it had to be done. And if Aviana is truly to be resurrected, then perhaps your actions have enabled Blaithe to someday come back as well? Now let\'s see if we can contact our long lost guardian...' WHERE `entry`=25664;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Slow down, $C! You look as though you\'ve seen a ghost...' WHERE `entry`=25665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now that you\'ve dealt with the wendigos, we should be able to focus our efforts on the Frostmane trolls to the east.' WHERE `entry`=25667;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. The mountaineers will be glad to hear that half-rations are at an end. They\'ll need all their strength to continue fighting the Frostmanes.' WHERE `entry`=25668;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A hero thwarted their plans to destroy Windshear Hold, eh? That hero was you, $N. You are the pride of the Alliance! It seems that you have bought us a little bit of time. I must plan for the battle that lies ahead of us. Seek out the other inhabitants of Windshear Hold and lend them your assistance. I will call for you when I am ready to initiate our defensive strategy.' WHERE `entry`=25669;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='DUN-dun-DUN-dun-DUN-dun',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='This really ain\'t as bad as it looks...' WHERE `entry`=25670;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good. Their blood is on Hellscream\'s hands. Send enough of them back to Orgrimmar in a body bag and the populace of the Horde might react. Who am I kidding? They\'re monsters!' WHERE `entry`=25671;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, that\'s disgustin\'! We almost there, mon. Just need ta do one more ting!' WHERE `entry`=25672;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Mr. P you\'re gonna be ok! Hooray! Oh, Mr. P! I knew it!' WHERE `entry`=25673;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $R. You\'ve proven that you can take down an ogre... no small feat. Now let\'s see if you can take down an Alliance iron mine...' WHERE `entry`=25674;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well today, $N. Not only have you purchased more time before the next ogre attack, but I think you scared some of the captives into working harder.' WHERE `entry`=25675;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Heartstrike',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Finally... another operative shows up. I hope you\'re loosened up... it\'s time to tango, partner.' WHERE `entry`=25676;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There\'s nothing quite like a big fat kick in the wallet, is there, you Alliance lunkheads?!' WHERE `entry`=25677;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, friend. I like the way you do business.' WHERE `entry`=25678;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, you here already. Stick around for a bit, little $R. We gonna mess with the Alliance. I love my job, mon.' WHERE `entry`=25679;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So it was a demon?  Those miners never seen a demon before?  We\'re in the Blasted Lands, mon!  Demons are everywhere! Ah well... let\'s get on to da good stuff, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=25680;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice work, mon!  Without Hondo, these guys are helpless. Dis mine\'ll be ours soon enough!' WHERE `entry`=25681;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Impressive, $N. I wouldn\'t have hidden in that box, but otherwise, you have performed bravely and admirably. The battle we won today may not win us any immediate spoils, but the damage you\'ve done to the Alliance will last for a long time.' WHERE `entry`=25682;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Okrilla sent you?  Okrilla the killa\'? Loramus was his name?  I\'m sorry to say that we have not seen your demon hunter... but we have ways of finding him.' WHERE `entry`=25683;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. Now that that\'s out of the way...' WHERE `entry`=25684;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' More than enough, and still warm!  Now, let\'s get this ritual started, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=25685;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The blood ritual was a success; I can clearly see where Loramus is right now. That is, I can see where the pieces of his body lie...' WHERE `entry`=25686;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see... yes, we can work with this. Loramus Thalipedes, demon hunter. I look forward to meeting you.' WHERE `entry`=25687;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You... you fool!  What have you done?' WHERE `entry`=25688;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What?  LORAMUS?! Oh blast, keep it down, would ya?  If my boss gets word that I worked for Loramus, do you know how quickly I\'d be on my rear end?! Well, you weren\'t lying. Let\'s get to work.' WHERE `entry`=25689;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are perfect, $N. Lynnore and I will eat well for the next several days.' WHERE `entry`=25690;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hope this is what he needs. We probably don\'t have time for you to return and mine any more.' WHERE `entry`=25691;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There\'s no doubt about it, you found demon blood. Loramus\' requests aside, I\'m sure Dar\'toon is thankful for your efforts. They\'ve been struggling to deal with these demon distractions for some time now.' WHERE `entry`=25692;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is sufficient. If you see Wazzik again, you may tell him that he performed satisfactorily. I will get the bloodmages to work on fashioning the stone knife of sealing. There is no need for questions now. All will be revealed in time. While they work, I have another task for you to complete. Actually, make that three tasks.' WHERE `entry`=25693;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your work is appreciated, soldier. $R... if you\'re still interested, I have one more small task for you...' WHERE `entry`=25694;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re certain nobody saw you?  Good. Hmph... fairly harmless stuff. Either the Alliance are foolish enough to NOT be planning something against us... or they\'re hiding their information better than I expected. Either way, well done, soldier.' WHERE `entry`=25695;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Report to Rohan Sunveil at the Sunveil Excursion in the Blasted Lands.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome, traveler. Thank you for responding to my summons.' WHERE `entry`=25696;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' He was an archmage, I can feel it. I will hold the amulet for you while you collect the rest.' WHERE `entry`=25697;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' A warlock... and a powerful one at that. I will hold onto this until the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=25698;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' He was a powerful warrior, this one. I will keep the amulet until Loramus is ready to proceed.' WHERE `entry`=25699;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It would seem that we are prepared to face our demon, $N. We have the amulet\'s blessing, we have the stone knife, and I alone know the demon\'s true name: Rakh\'likh. Together, this may be enough to defeat the Defiler.' WHERE `entry`=25700;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see. So this was Loramus\' plan all along. I suspected correctly, but I suppose I refused to believe it. And now, his final instruction for me makes much more sense: He asked me to let you choose from one of these.' WHERE `entry`=25701;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Salt-Flop did not shame himself by running away. Look behind me, and see for yourself. The Rockpool had no hope against the naga\'s attack.' WHERE `entry`=25702;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Atrocities',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, brave $C. I am pleased... but I am not yet satisfied.' WHERE `entry`=25703;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now we gonna bring Tony Two-Tusk back ta life. You both ready, mon?' WHERE `entry`=25704;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You make an old murloc proud, $R. Thank you, and may the waves ever lap at your feet.' WHERE `entry`=25705;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The last Rockpool may be taken hostage today and killed tomorrow, landwalker... but they will pass into the underworld knowing that a brave $R avenged their death. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25706;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Aye, you\'ve done well, lad. You do the Alliance proud.' WHERE `entry`=25708;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s a tragedy, what happened on the Shattershore. They weren\'t even soldiers... just people looking for a new home. I think we\'ve done all we can, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25709;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm... not bad. You\'re quicker than many of my men. Stick around, $N... I may have use of you yet.' WHERE `entry`=25710;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re an excellent asset to the Alliance and the Kirin Tor, $N. Well done. With time, our forces will retake the mine and press these Horde dogs out of the Blasted Lands.' WHERE `entry`=25711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. Thanks to your efforts, I am confident that with time, we will take back the Nethergarde Mine.' WHERE `entry`=25712;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahh, the sound of things going boom makes my heart pitter-pat. You\'ve made this gnome\'s day, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25713;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My associates were correct to send you to me. I have a problem which may threaten the sanctity of Nethergarde, and I need someone more capable than most.' WHERE `entry`=25714;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You saw worgen?  That\'s bad. Worgen ghosts?  That\'s even worse. Those weren\'t Horde ships... they were Gilnean. And they must have been headed down to Surwich, at the bottom of the Tainted Forest. That makes a lot more sense. We\'ve got to try to help them, $N!  The worgen are our allies!' WHERE `entry`=25715;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ably done, $N. Now we see if my suspicions are correct.' WHERE `entry`=25716;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. I should be a bit more up-front with you. The demons were a nuisance, but they are not the real problem. That worgen druid is our problem.' WHERE `entry`=25717;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Rohan\'s sending YOU to slay his druid?  Very well. You should know: Marl Wormthorn is as much demon as he is druid. Even a druid of his power doesn\'t have a chance against the demonic energies that run so deeply through this land. That does not, however, make him any less of an obstacle.' WHERE `entry`=25718;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Brilliantly done, $N. We have what we need to break the worgen\'s trance.' WHERE `entry`=25719;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hopefully, with this druid out of the picture, we can get back to our digging. The world is full of powerful artifacts, $N. You just need to be willing to do what it takes to get to them. Feel free to take one of these. The Reliquary is always happy to share some of its trove with fellow members of the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=25720;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well I\'ll be. There\'s someone around here that isn\'t a disgrace to Magni, bless his poor gravelly heart.$B$BJust for that, you get first crack at the ale, $Glad:lass;. But don\'t let it get to your bloody head! We\'ve got more gorram work to do, and I won\'t tolerate you lettin\' up early!' WHERE `entry`=25721;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, well. The good news is, these will do perfectly. The bad news is I can tell they\'re the wrong color for topsoil here, even drunk as I am.$B$BThat means things aren\'t looking good for the area, $N. But we\'ve got more tests to run before we hang up the towel.' WHERE `entry`=25722;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The local wildlife\'s all messed up from the flood, it seems. This fen used to be full of crocolisks, but I haven\'t spotted a single one.$B$BWhat I have spotted are threshadons. Never used to be any here, so the flood must\'ve swept them all right out of Loch Modan.$B$BLucky for us, because they\'re tastier than crocolisks, and I\'m running low on provisions. Bring me back some Threshadon meat for the camp, and I\'ll gladly pay you for it.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lovely. These\'ll fry up nice, and the camp\'ll be spared a week of mushroom biscuits.' WHERE `entry`=25723;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Kill 5 Frostmane Seers and 7 Frostmane Snowstriders on Shimmer Ridge',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='We should be able to focus our efforts on the rest of the trolls to the east, but there\'s still the matter of the wendigos in the Grizzled Den.' WHERE `entry`=25724;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These\'ll do nicely. I\'ll have the lads back on their feet as soon as I make these somewhat edible.' WHERE `entry`=25725;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh good, it\'s undamaged! Thanks a lot.$B$BYou ah, you might want to wipe yourself off a bit there.' WHERE `entry`=25726;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good riddance to bad rubbish! I\'ll burn the foul thing later so it doesn\'t stink up the camp.' WHERE `entry`=25727;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This is awkward... Good job out there with the robot. You caught me a little off guard. I didn\'t realize the little girl was so... Special... Well, whatever gets the job done, right? Am I right? Probably. Have some ice cream.' WHERE `entry`=25728;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Vonderful! That\'s von more name I can scratch off of my list! I vill be in touch. Xakxak, out!' WHERE `entry`=25729;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well I\'ll be a monkey\'s uncle. You actually got the beast, eh? Well, a deal\'s a deal! Here\'s your reward!' WHERE `entry`=25730;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='It\'s time to get to the bottom of this. We need to interrogate the matron of these beasts, Marion Wormwing. We\'ll capture her alive. Here\'s the plan:$B$BThe Harpies communicate across the ridge using a series of signal fires. If we extinguish one, Marion is sure to come investigate.$B$BYou fight her as a distraction while I sneak up behind and grab her. I\'ll leave the questioning to you. Let\'s get her, $N!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='So the Harpies are tools of some sort of dragon - "Sethria." But what are the dragons doing to those eggs? And what\'s this \'special\' egg that Sethria wanted so badly? This is beyond me, $N. I\'ve given a report to Skylord Omnuron - he\'ll know what to do next.' WHERE `entry`=25731;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is it? How is this gunna remove - wait a minute...' WHERE `entry`=25732;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good job. I wouldn\'t be surprised if the horrid things had eggs in there somewhere, but it\'ll do for now.' WHERE `entry`=25733;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful, $Glad:lass;. This should be all we need. Let\'s have a look.' WHERE `entry`=25734;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Glorious! Beautiful stuff, this ore.$B$BGood on you for not droppin\' your pick. Last person I sent out let the butt end hit the floor, and that part\'s not sparkproof.' WHERE `entry`=25735;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The thing\'s still got some fight in it! Amazing!$B$BYou\'re a tough one, $N. It\'s much appreciated. I\'d say a reward is in order before you head out.$B$BKeep doin\' your best for Ironforge, you hear? And if you ever see my sister, say hello for me.' WHERE `entry`=25736;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Don\'t worry about me. Should be ok now that big hero killed the spider queen. Can get reinforcements through safely now.' WHERE `entry`=25739;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The dragon Sethria must be stopped. We know that her roost is south of here, along the southern cliffs of Hyjal, but beyond that we know little else.$B$BI have sent Thisalee on a fact-finding mission to Sethria\'s roost. She specifically requested your help - evidently you made quite an impression with the young druid.$B$BMeet Thisalee just beyond the tunnel leading to Sethria\'s Roost. And remember, this is a fact-finding mission - don\'t do anything crazy!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, $N! I was hoping to see you out here. What, Omnuron calls this a \'fact-finding mission?\' Bah! Facts are best found on corpses. Let\'s do some damage.' WHERE `entry`=25740;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This will keep us stocked on anti-venom for the foreseeable future. Thank you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25741;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Bring The Pewter Pounder to Harrison at The Accursed Reef.' WHERE `entry`=25742;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, what might have been...' WHERE `entry`=25743;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Negotiations',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I\'ve got Kravel Koalbeard up there talking to one of their chiefs, but now that you\'re here, we\'ll have the rights to pump up their oil in no time!' WHERE `entry`=25744;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Negotiations',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I\'ve got Trackmaster Zherin up there talking to one of their chiefs, but now that you\'re here, we\'ll have the rights to pump up their oil in no time!' WHERE `entry`=25745;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re good at this. I like you.' WHERE `entry`=25746;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good to see you again, $C. I almost thought we\'d lost you to the Wavespeaker\'s fool errand.$B$BDid anything come of it?' WHERE `entry`=25747;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='More naga are amassing to the south than reported too it seems. We shall have to move quickly then.' WHERE `entry`=25748;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are perhaps the most dependable person I\'ve ever met. I wish I could have more men half as thorough as you.' WHERE `entry`=25749;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are brave indeed! I\'ve seen you battling all manner of murloc, naga, and pointy-toothed fish, but that was nothing! The way you just sling those kelp bulbs under your arm like that is a whole new kind of fearless. BOOM! You could blow up at any second.$B$BYou\'re my kind of $R.' WHERE `entry`=25751;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did great up there! You devastated their ranks, but there were far more than we accounted for, and most of our men went down out there in the masses of naga. We\'ll need to hold this position as long as possible to buy them time. Hopefully some of them will still make it to the rendezvous.' WHERE `entry`=25752;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you. Truly.$B$BWe need to get these men moving as soon as possible. I\'ll meet you back at the forward post soon, I\'m sure.' WHERE `entry`=25753;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Still so many? They must want something very important here to come in such numbers.$B$BI will be honest with you, $N, because you deserve at least that: I don\'t know how much hope there is. We will retreat shortly, but we won\'t be able to defend ourselves when they strike back. We don\'t have anywhere to run... we\'re running out of options.$B$BI\'m sorry, I should keep such thoughts to myself. Do me a favor and don\'t mention any of that to the men. I\'ll figure something out.' WHERE `entry`=25754;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re finished! Just in time. I don\'t think we could have held them much longer.$B$BAn artifact? Could this be something we can use against the naga? I suppose that would require finding it.$B$BWe may have to attend to more pressing matters first, until an opportunity to pursue this further presents itself.' WHERE `entry`=25755;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What?! How\'d they get that much gold to offer? We don\'t have that kind of money!' WHERE `entry`=25756;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What?! How\'d they get that much gold to offer? We don\'t have that kind of money!' WHERE `entry`=25757;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Look at these things. Ugh, the runes make my eyes hurt. This one here is meant to sear flesh? Seriously? Ouch! Wait a minute... These plates are designed to be riveted directly into flesh. The pain must be unbearable!' WHERE `entry`=25758;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not another one! $N, these devices have been springing up all around Azeroth. We know that they can instigate elemental disturbances in the area, including causing tears in the elemental planes. The devices stink of Twilight\'s Hammer. The engravings covering the surface and the captured elemental essence implicate Cho\'gall and his minions are behind this. If you find more of these, please bring them to me or one of my associates. We need to learn more about what\'s behind this attack.' WHERE `entry`=25759;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Disassembly',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='That was some fancy bladework, $N! There\'s one less threat for us to worry about in Hyjal.' WHERE `entry`=25761;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did this favor to ingratiate yourself with me, but I will not sing your praises. I know what is to come. Where the sea failed, the great air spirit will strike you and your people down for your many transgressions against the elements. Begone from my sight!' WHERE `entry`=25762;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They\'re doing what? They\'re cloaking something? Of course - so our aerial scouts can\'t see anything with our eagle-eyes!' WHERE `entry`=25763;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We did it, $N! Aviana\'s Egg should soon be tucked safely in the boughs of her shrine. Do you think this means she\'ll really return to us?' WHERE `entry`=25764;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Kosak sent you, eh? Surprising. I thought for sure that he\'d be dead by now. Well if you made it past the blockade then you definitely have something that we can use. Now, do you have any news of the Horde? What are they doing? Where are they going? Tell me everything.' WHERE `entry`=25765;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Use the Highborne Prison to bind 5 Highborne Spirits.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I assure you, simpleton, the spirits you captured are at rest. Do not let their protests move you.' WHERE `entry`=25766;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful! Arcanist Valdurian will be most pleased.' WHERE `entry`=25767;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m assuming you saw the Krom\'gar hot air balloon on your way here. If not, get your eyes checked. It\'s hovering directly over the oil platform.' WHERE `entry`=25768;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good to see you again, $N. I have some news from Mirkfallon Lake.' WHERE `entry`=25769;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hah! Nice to see those addlebrained mountaineers knew to hand the ale off to a real man to get the job done. Welcome to my survey. If you\'re of the mind to help Ironforge by takin\' over the intended jobs of some useless, lazy sods that call themselves dwarves, you\'re in the right place!' WHERE `entry`=25770;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just a shard?  Pfuh!  This gets me nothing!  Take your reward and get out of my sight. Sounds familiar?  It should, because I say it a thousand times per day. Oh how I loathe this world.' WHERE `entry`=25771;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Simply amazing. I had doubted that anyone could find another sphere, yet here it is, pulsating in my hands. Well done, $N! Should you find anymore--and I believe this to be an impossibility--return them to me and I shall reward you again.' WHERE `entry`=25772;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, $N, this shard does explain the occurrence of the rift. The elemental planes have been in chaos in Outland ever since Draenor was destroyed. These shards cause a weakness in the already damaged elemental planes and allow the elementals to cross into our world We\'re still looking into how these rifts are appearing in Azeroth. Keep bringing us the shards. Every shard we get brings us closer to understanding how these rifts are appearing.' WHERE `entry`=25773;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Genius! Now, where\'s that gold paint? I know it\'s around here somewhere.' WHERE `entry`=25774;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Genius! Now, where\'s that gold paint? I know it\'s around here somewhere.' WHERE `entry`=25775;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Sethria is slain! I knew it was worth the risk. I\'ll stay here to look for survivors, but I imagine they\'ll want to see you back at the shrine.' WHERE `entry`=25776;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let\'s take a look here.$B$BOh, this is just lovely. "Significant geological instabilities"? "Threat of sudden, massive topological destabilization"?$B$BNice to hear that somethin\' bad might happen around here. I guess we\'ll just pick up our flooded town and fly it off somewhere safe!$B$BBah!' WHERE `entry`=25777;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just put it down on the ground, $R.' WHERE `entry`=25778;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just put it down on the ground, $R.' WHERE `entry`=25779;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='He\'s dead! Thank the Makers...$B$BI don\'t like the looks of them, lad. The Dark Iron I\'ve tussled with were never this crazy. Something\'s getting to these sods...' WHERE `entry`=25780;
