UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'ll teach them. You\'ve softened the Splithoof up enough that we should be able to govern them now with a minimal guard presence from the Speedbarge. That is, once we\'ve dealt with their supposed air elemental leader.' WHERE `entry`=25797;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oil! Black gold! Tanaris Tea! We\'re rich! We just have to clear out the remaining pesky centaur. I\'m sure with all the money we\'re going to make, we can relocate them to some other bluff.' WHERE `entry`=25798;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oil! Black gold! Tanaris Tea! We\'re rich! We just have to clear out the remaining pesky centaur. I\'m sure with all the money we\'re going to make, we can relocate them to some other bluff.' WHERE `entry`=25799;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A hearty seafood dinner will lift everyone\'s spirits and help us get the town back in shape again. Thanks for the help, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25800;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, well done $N.$B$BAccept this as payment for fulfillment of your contract with the Merchant Marines.' WHERE `entry`=25801;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This crate is covered with clawed scratches, and the marks of water damage. Prying it open reveals soggy and rotted straw, as if something of value was stored in the crate. You search through the straw...$B$B...and find an armload of red-colored bottles.' WHERE `entry`=25802;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This barrel is largely untouched. Prying it open...$B$B...you are assaulted by the pungent odor of cheese. It\'s a little wet, but still tasty!' WHERE `entry`=25803;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This barrel is halfway buried amidst the mud and grass ...' WHERE `entry`=25804;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The captain of the Blind Princess will be relieved to hear this precious cargo has been recovered. You\'ve well earned this payment for services rendered.$B$BIt\'s good to see dependable folk like you, especially in trying times such as these.' WHERE `entry`=25805;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Hey, this thing on? Anybody there?' WHERE `entry`=25806;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I ... live. Those that tried to corrupt me and kidnap my children will soon feel the rake of my talons, $C. Believe it. Continue to push forward across Hyjal. I will collect myself and assemble with the other Ancients.' WHERE `entry`=25807;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='<The Gnomecorder crackles with energy. You can hear Lieutenant Paulson on the other end.>$B$BStupid gnome junk... Is ANYBODY there? $N, are you there?$B$BMaybe $G he\'s:she\'s; dead.$B$BListen, if you can still hear me, we just got word that a Horde master assassin is in the mines, directing the other assassins. Find her, kill her, report back to me.$B$BPaulson, out.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nicely done, $N! You worked the mines like a pro. Now how about returning my goggles.' WHERE `entry`=25808;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Horde monsters!$B$B<Corporal Wocard spits.>$B$BLook at this place! They\'ve wiped out innocents! Civilians!$B$BListen, $N, you\'ve got to help us. Go into the Deep Reaches and look for surviving miners. If any are still alive they\'re probably scared witless! Check in the nooks and crannies of the mine. Maybe in mine carts! There are bound to be some left alive and in hiding.',`objectives_loc6`='Rescue 8 Frightened Miners.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank the Light! You truly are a righteous instrument of power! The Alliance is lucky to you have, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25809;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So it\'s true - Aviana has returned, with you as her herald. There\'s much to be done here. We are deep in the heart of the Firelands. Sethria smuggled stolen eggs from Mount Hyjal here to hatch her own hideous creations - birds of prey, trained for war. I hope you\'re ready to fight back!' WHERE `entry`=25810;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Plant Explosives at Third Beam',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Plant Explosives at Fourth Beam' WHERE `entry`=25811;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Spelunking',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='A... a $R? Here? I must be mad...' WHERE `entry`=25812;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well then, let\'s see them get any kind of magical hocus pocus air support now when we take over!' WHERE `entry`=25813;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well then, let\'s see them get any kind of magical hocus pocus air support now when we take over!' WHERE `entry`=25814;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah!  That hits the spot, and loosens the tongue. Thanks, mate!' WHERE `entry`=25815;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fitzsimmons sent you, didn\'t he? It\'s been so long...' WHERE `entry`=25816;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The cries of anguish have been stifled...but the source of the curse still lurks.' WHERE `entry`=25817;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The key is rusted but it fits the lock neatly.' WHERE `entry`=25818;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Eye of Paleth? You say Fitzsimmons sent you out? By the light...not again. Fitzsimmons is dead, lad. You\'ve not the first to come to me like this, either.' WHERE `entry`=25819;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, bless your heart, to do such a thing for a married woman like me. You\'re too kind.' WHERE `entry`=25820;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew that you\'d be a special snowflake when I first set my eyes upon you, $N. So special, in fact, that I\'d trust no one else here with what I\'m about to ask of you.' WHERE `entry`=25821;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This should be enough to supply a hundred Grimtotem! Now to present the weaponry to their chieftain.' WHERE `entry`=25822;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I will call for the infantry to move in and clear up whatever might be left over. If only we had ten-thousand more like you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=25823;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Debriefing',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, it\'s not encouraging, but it\'s something...' WHERE `entry`=25824;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is oil! You\'re really proving yourself to be invaluable, $N! Too bad I\'m going to have to send you off now.' WHERE `entry`=25825;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is oil! You\'re the best, $N! Too bad I\'m going to have to send you off now.' WHERE `entry`=25826;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I ... have not yet ... perished.' WHERE `entry`=25830;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' They stole my eggs, $C. They took them to that foul place. Corrupted them. My children stolen, tormented, killed in a vat of flame... Yes, we will make Twilight\'s Hammer pay. But I confess, part of me wants to fly up and simply watch this whole... world... burn.' WHERE `entry`=25832;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='For ten thousand years I drifted without form within the Emerald Dream. I awake to a nightmare.$B$B$R, seek out the dreamer - the dragon aspect you call Ysera - and let her know that I have returned and will aid the Guardians of Hyjal as they crush the Twilight\'s Hammer.$B$BI will fill their skies with suffering.' WHERE `entry`=25833;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The name be "Cookie," lad: greatest cook \'cross Azeroth. Now the Commander\'s told me what we be needin\' to do. To gain audience with the Grimtotem chief we\'re gonna have to cook up the finest of tauren cuisine. Ye get me the ingredients and I\'ll put together an offerin\' no tauren could refuse. Not even a grim tauren or whatever them things be.' WHERE `entry`=25834;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m glad that Fizzle finally sent you here. We\'re helping the tauren to retake Freewind Post and push back the Grimtotem.' WHERE `entry`=25835;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Well, it looks like it\'s time for us to part ways, at least for a while. To the northwest, the tauren of Freewind Post are in desparate need of your assistance in pushing back the Grimtotem clan!$B$BYou know, you\'ve been such a great help around here, I bet you\'re going to be their $G hero : heroine; in no-time!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am honored that you have come to help, $C. It was kind of Pozzik to send you.' WHERE `entry`=25836;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Stand back, $N, there\'s about to be a flavor explosion and I wouldn\'t want ya gettin\' hurt.' WHERE `entry`=25837;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you must be the $R that Captain Tharran said he\'d be sending. I\'ve already used the deploy-a-tron to get most of the covert ops team into position at Frostmane Retreat. They\'re just waiting on your arrival.' WHERE `entry`=25838;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Don\'t worry, the feeling of being zapped won\'t stay with you for more than a few minutes. All in all, it\'s not a bad way to get where you\'re going. That parachute system needs some work, though. Very late deployment, indeed. Sometimes, too late. Anyway, we have a mission to carry out.' WHERE `entry`=25839;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. With Battok dead, I\'ll send the signal to Captain Tharran. This should be the end of the Frostmane threat.' WHERE `entry`=25840;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Both you and the air wing performed admirably. There\'s no way that the Frostmanes will remain here now. All that remains is to begin mopping up the survivors.' WHERE `entry`=25841;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Firefight',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $R. I am ready now. All that I am, and all that this forest once was... it is now yours.' WHERE `entry`=25842;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The mountain blooms again! If we act quickly, we can press our advantage.$B$BOur old friend Tortolla, the Turtle Ancient, is already on the move. At his own pace, of course...$B$BFind Tortolla east of here, at the head of the path leading down into the scorched plains. Our strongholds there fell early in the campaign, but perhaps now we can reclaim them.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='$R. I remember you. Savior of my children. The time has come. For vengeance.' WHERE `entry`=25843;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This... this is the greatest thing I have ever tasted. You may prove to be a valuable ally, but before the Grimtotem agree to work with the Alliance, you must agree to our terms. I will now give to you those terms as told to me by my leader. Take them back to your commander and see if he accepts.' WHERE `entry`=25844;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Weapons, eh? I\'m about to make an executive decision here, $N. Let\'s hope this pays off, else King Wrynn will have my head!' WHERE `entry`=25845;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are fine weapons! Powerful steel! My warriors will be unstoppable armed with such weaponry. Magatha smiles down upon you, $N. There is but one thing I ask of you, perhaps two.' WHERE `entry`=25846;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The fight is far from over, $N. The Horde generals still live...' WHERE `entry`=25847;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Yes, ally, you have done it! It will take Hellscream weeks to recover from this blow. Southern Stonetalon belongs to the Grimtotem... and the Alliance, of course.' WHERE `entry`=25848;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='See? Not bad, eh? Why, I almost wish all my finds decided to dig themselves up for me. It\'d make my job a lot easier! Of course, you made it easier too, $N. Much obliged.' WHERE `entry`=25849;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s showin\' em what for! Good on you.' WHERE `entry`=25850;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Outstanding work, $N! Now our forces only need to worry about the Horde as they enter Stonetalon.' WHERE `entry`=25851;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You say the Grimtotem are no longer a threat? That\'s great, but we\'ve got Horde all up our keesters!' WHERE `entry`=25852;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s a relief! Maybe we can dig our way out of the hole we\'re still in, eh? No, nevermind, just a bad joke.' WHERE `entry`=25853;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful! These should be ready to hatch within the day... Now I just need to cobble up a raptor pen before they all hatch nigh-simultaneously. What could go wrong?' WHERE `entry`=25854;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, wonderful! I\'ll be able to start reassembling these right away. Thank you so much!' WHERE `entry`=25855;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m much obliged, $C. This\'ll go a ways towards getting my family back on their feet.' WHERE `entry`=25856;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Amazing! You\'re a true hero, $N. I\'ll never forget what you\'ve done for me and my family. I know it\'s not much, but please, take this with my blessing.' WHERE `entry`=25857;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Reinforcements have begun to circle the waters around the ledge, preparing for the attack. They await only your lead.' WHERE `entry`=25858;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not one slipped through to the bridge. Not one.$B$BIt was very boring. I\'d appreciate it if you shared a little next time.' WHERE `entry`=25859;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Azjentus is to be taken at his word. Lady Naz\'jar\'s Honor Guard should be sufficient to see the rest of the ritual through.' WHERE `entry`=25860;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My scythe is sated. Thank you, my lady.' WHERE `entry`=25861;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The crucible looks far too heavy to carry on your own, but more than enough naga forces remain to prepare it for transport.' WHERE `entry`=25862;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, my Battlemaiden.$B$BThis crucible will serve as a font of power for our summoning ritual. With it, Sira\'kess will beckon our allies from the depths to bolster our already swelling forces.' WHERE `entry`=25863;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A job well done. Consider this reward not from me, but from Ironforge; the preservation of Khaz Modan is a matter that concerns every dwarf.' WHERE `entry`=25864;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='You seem trustworthy enough to help me out with my real problem, $N. I was sent here by Ironforge to recover a shipment of gold ingots.$B$BThe ingots are part of the Ironforge Royal Treasury, stamped with the royal seal... only an idiot would steal them for profit, far too easy to trace. Oddly enough, this area is full of idiots: Mosshide Gnolls.$B$BI don\'t know how many gnolls you\'ve fought before, but they\'re foul and brutal beasts, and dangerous. I need you to slay them and recover the missing ingots.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done! The Ironforge Guard appreciates this, $N. You\'ve done our city a fine favor. But something new has come up...' WHERE `entry`=25865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I don\'t suppose they agreed to come along quietly? Didn\'t think so.' WHERE `entry`=25866;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That should do it! The more gnolls those fools have to chase after, the easier it\'ll be to keep them in line.' WHERE `entry`=25867;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A job well done! You\'ve brought one of Ironforge\'s most wanted to justice today, $N. I\'d say you\'ve earned a mighty fine reward.' WHERE `entry`=25868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Grim business, that. No pun intended.' WHERE `entry`=25869;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s a good start. Normally, I wouldn\'t wish harm on any of the Earth Mother\'s creatures. But attacking us at our most vulnerable moment?! They deserve to die!' WHERE `entry`=25870;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for freeing her, $N. Those Grimtotem monsters would have killed her in cold blood.' WHERE `entry`=25871;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for freeing him, $N. Those Grimtotem would have killed him in cold blood.' WHERE `entry`=25872;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A traitor amongst the tauren? I\'ve never heard of such a thing. Clan rivalries and warfare are one thing, but killing your own in cold blood.' WHERE `entry`=25873;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The cliffwatcher was a Grimtotem spy?! No wonder we had no warning! I don\'t want that damned thing. Throw it into the water and let the Longhorn name never be spoken again!' WHERE `entry`=25874;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Get in here and hug a wall! I can\'t risk blowing my cover!' WHERE `entry`=25875;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='OH NO! They plan to "test" the bomb at Thal\'darah Grove! That\'s the school for young druids located in the heart of Battlescar Valley. You\'ve got to return to Barus with this information! Master Thal\'darah must be warned!' WHERE `entry`=25876;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Blasted Horde! I\'ve got friends at that grove. Hopefully you know how to ride a hippogryph. We\'ve got to get you to Master Thal\'darah at the overlook immediately!' WHERE `entry`=25877;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I could see the explosions from here, $N! The Horde won\'t be refueling from Mirkfallon anymore, thanks to you!' WHERE `entry`=25878;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Slowly, but surely, we pick away at the Horde\'s numbers. They won\'t have a leg to stand on when this war really opens up.' WHERE `entry`=25879;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are dire times, indeed, $N. Our outpost in Stonetalon Peak has been overrun by fiendish creatures from the depths and the Horde seeks to destroy us. We need a hero, $N; a soldier of the Alliance strong enough to guide us through these trying times.' WHERE `entry`=25880;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve assembled the survivors? Good, good. And the rest of the mountain - healed? Haha, strike me down! We\'re on the front lines again!' WHERE `entry`=25881;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you\'re the one who\'s been helping Captain Tharran beat back the Frostmane trolls? I\'ve seen your name in the reports. It\'s good to finally meet you. You might be just the $C we need to help secure the ranch.' WHERE `entry`=25882;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re confident that your assault on the naga armaments has made an impact on their effectiveness.' WHERE `entry`=25883;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The waters surrounding the Holding Pens are red with the blood of the naga. Rendel would be proud!' WHERE `entry`=25884;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, yes. This is the stuff. Maybe I can gradually eat less of it and avoid that side-effect. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25885;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Terrific! Twilight\'s Hammer will no doubt try to re-take the mountain, but they\'ll have to do so without the leadership of those fat-for-brains thugs.' WHERE `entry`=25886;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is as it should be. Now the way is clear to deal these naga a crippling blow.' WHERE `entry`=25887;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Decompression',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let us hope for the safety of those released prisoners. In return for your noble efforts, please accept this gift.' WHERE `entry`=25888;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Praise you, $N. The hero we have been searching for has finally arrived, and not a moment too soon.' WHERE `entry`=25889;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Erunak trusts this task to me?  Very well, let\'s see what we can learn from the ancient one.' WHERE `entry`=25890;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Do you know why the Horde destroys? The Horde destroys because they cannot comprehend beauty. They fear it and that which they fear they must destroy. Why else would they destroy Thal\'darah Grove? Together, we will make them understand. They will know that what they do comes at a great cost.' WHERE `entry`=25891;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You made it! After the attack at the forward post, I thought we might be the only ones left. I\'m very glad to see you.' WHERE `entry`=25892;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Impeccable timing. Like clockwork! Trouble comes. You come. Save the day. Clockwork! We\'ve devised our brilliant plan. Gloriously simple, barring the hostility of local life. Simpler yet with a you available!' WHERE `entry`=25893;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Less gill goblins is good! I\'m glad that they\'re so primitive. I don\'t think I\'d want to be dealing with a race of aquatic tech-freaks right now. Not at all.' WHERE `entry`=25894;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let me see, let me see... flare gun... balloon... no rope. Never any rope. Terribly impractical if you do ask me. Rope should be mandatory.' WHERE `entry`=25895;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Kvaldir have proved a greater threat than we anticipated, but our plans are not hindered in the least. As our allies arrive, we will have a force more than sufficient to usurp the Tidehunter.$B$BAll that remains is to ensure that the ritual of summoning is completed.' WHERE `entry`=25896;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is great! I love it. It should work per... ewww! Is this stuff braided with hair?$B$BDoesn\'t matter. Almost done. This thing will be ready in the twist of a rope.' WHERE `entry`=25897;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect! There\'s no way they missed that, fighting or not.' WHERE `entry`=25898;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Breakthrough',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You killed how many? Well, well. Quite a show. I guess my men don\'t have any more excuses.' WHERE `entry`=25899;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That didn\'t go well. For some reason, the beast won\'t speak back to me.$B$B<Duarn is clearly frustrated.>$B$BIf only Erunak had not left us!  He would know what to do.' WHERE `entry`=25900;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful! Still sharp. A little blood on the fletching, but they\'ll fly true. Thank you, $N. Our defense of Hyjal can continue.' WHERE `entry`=25901;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This power is ancient. Primitive. Easy. We will use it against them.' WHERE `entry`=25904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The rams you rescued have made their way back into the pen. I\'ve got members of the family on a day and night watch now. Those trolls won\'t take us by surprise again!' WHERE `entry`=25905;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You were sent by the turtle god? Bless his almighty shell! I thought I was trapped down here forever.' WHERE `entry`=25906;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N... although I\'m afraid I haven\'t been nearly as productive as you have.' WHERE `entry`=25907;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Can you sense it?  If you have an ounce of shaman\'s blood in you, you must feel the sense of relief in the air.$B$BNespirah is pleased. Perhaps she will finally speak with us.' WHERE `entry`=25908;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' It doesn\'t look very impressive, does it?' WHERE `entry`=25909;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So it is done. Knowing that Twilight\'s Hammer is in league with creatures of malice such as these... it really curdles the blood.' WHERE `entry`=25910;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That is the best news I\'ve heard in what seems like an eternity. We\'ll get the survivors moving over there to the surface as soon as possible. Perhaps we can forget that this whole nightmare ever happened. Thank you, $N. I\'m not sure there\'s anything I can do to repay you for everything you\'ve managed to accomplish in this ocean, but I will try to find a way. You should consider meeting us at the ships later, when you finish saying your goodbyes to the naga.' WHERE `entry`=25911;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve found it! Elune bless you, child! Perhaps this book will give me the strength to carry on.' WHERE `entry`=25912;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. Each glaive has the name of the sentinel it belonged to imprinted upon its blade. We can now send word to their families and put their souls to rest.' WHERE `entry`=25913;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m afraid that the death of Harbinger Aph\'lass has not ceased the tendril attacks. You\'ve done all that you can, $N, and for that I thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25914;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah yes, yes... the secret strength of Nemesis, unearthed here in these caverns. We know all that we need to know, $N. It is time to finish this.' WHERE `entry`=25915;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I had assumed that the naga were only here for those pearls. No, this makes much more sense. If they had Nespirah\'s power under their control, the amount of damage the naga could do would be catastrophic!$B$BSomething must be done.' WHERE `entry`=25916;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Oh, I\'m sorry. I was just imagining what these will look like with little bits of naga stuck to the ends of them. Thank you, $N. We\'ll put these to good use.' WHERE `entry`=25918;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hopefully we made some progress. I\'m not sure how we\'ll know when the creature wakes up, but something tells me that it will be pretty obvious when it does.' WHERE `entry`=25919;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Brilliant work! Now I just need you and Captain Taylor to get me safely out of here. I can handle the studies from there on.' WHERE `entry`=25920;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='No need to bring me up to speed... Nespirah has been narrating your adventures as they happened, and Captain Taylor filled me in on the rest. Nespirah says that she is quite grateful, and that she has a small surprise ready for the naga.' WHERE `entry`=25921;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It appears that I owe you my life, yet again. Thank the Light that you found me before you and your shaman activated those bio-defenses.' WHERE `entry`=25922;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The usurper has perished! Twilight\'s Hammer dreamed of creating their own pantheon of twisted ancients to rule over the land, sea, and air. With your help, they\'ve all been executed. We must tell Tortolla at once!' WHERE `entry`=25923;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not exactly the battle you had anticipated, I\'ll wager. But a battle nonetheless, as you shall soon see....' WHERE `entry`=25924;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We witnessed the detonation of the bomb. Terrible, terrible destruction... Farwatcher Glen, for better or for worse, is still intact. Unfortunately we\'ve nowhere to run.' WHERE `entry`=25925;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahhh... yes. The swamp suffers less now. More threats, though. More lurk. I can see them!' WHERE `entry`=25926;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes... the flames die. There is peace now. Peace for the land.' WHERE `entry`=25927;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve been to the firelands? Nemesis is dead? So it is finished. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=25928;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Here you are, $C. With this you should find maneuvering in the sea to be nearly effortless. $B$BNow we must get to work. There is much to be done in little time.' WHERE `entry`=25929;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I say, are you there, $N? It would appear that you are in the center of a dragon\'s lair.' WHERE `entry`=25930;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A smashing success! Perhaps only a minor victory against the brood of Deathwing, but a victory nonetheless!' WHERE `entry`=25931;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With your help, we\'ve managed to weaken the raiders considerably. They haven\'t suffered such losses since the raids began. Now is the time to press our advantage.' WHERE `entry`=25932;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Sergeant Flinthammer? I\'m not familiar with the name, but, aye, there is a Flinthammer among the miners. He\'s one of the ones lucky enough to make it out of the mine, but most of my men are still trapped down there.' WHERE `entry`=25933;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. This will allow me to finish my last task and hopefully gain the form of the wolf!' WHERE `entry`=25934;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. The dogs will be well fed and ready to defend our outpost for weeks!' WHERE `entry`=25935;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='While you were away, I was able to revive some of the fallen warriors. We\'ll need every hand if we are to survive here.' WHERE `entry`=25936;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for recovering these artifacts. I will see to it that they are displayed in the Ironforge museum along with the story of those who died to recover them.' WHERE `entry`=25937;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hold there, stranger!' WHERE `entry`=25938;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='In sparing the land further suffering, you\'ve also helped us soothe the Greenwarden. Many thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25939;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The forest is being devoured!' WHERE `entry`=25940;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hear you, $R.$B$BI understand the urgency, but these men are in no condition to fight.' WHERE `entry`=25941;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let us hope that your work has bought us the time we need...' WHERE `entry`=25942;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good grub. Soon we\'ll be back to fighting strength.' WHERE `entry`=25943;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $R. Our chances of survival are increasing.' WHERE `entry`=25944;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='While you remain in Stonetalon and fight as a Krom\'gar soldier you will remain suited up! Am I clear? DO you hear me, grunt? If I see you without Hellscream\'s beloved tabard I will put my foot so far up your backside that you\'ll be spitting up laces.' WHERE `entry`=25945;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Take the Alliance S.E.A.L. Equipment to Legionnaire Nazgrim at The Immortal Coil.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Blood and Thunder! This changes everything, $C!' WHERE `entry`=25946;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done! Now, more than ever, we are prepared to face the naga!' WHERE `entry`=25947;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='No time to address the Vanguard. Just as well...' WHERE `entry`=25948;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Earthen Ring has received my distress message and sent help - just in time it would seem. Hopefully more can be sent soon. We are but few against a great many.' WHERE `entry`=25949;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Chicken and rice, $N! That will show those sorry and sad snakes who\'s the ol\' pitch and toss! Now it\'s bird lime for that tiddlywink. Finger and thumb or plink plonk?' WHERE `entry`=25950;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Get to the bridge on the east, quickly. Lady Naz\'jar and the Fathom-Lord should be there with whatever forces remain.$B$BFollow our Lady\'s direction, as always. Hold the bridge until we can complete the ritual.$B$BOnce our allies arrive, the Kvaldir will be doomed.',`objectives_loc6`='Hold the bridge on Quel\'Dormir Terrace until Lady Sira\'kess\' allies arrive.$B$BThis task is part of a Naz\'jar Battlemaiden vision. If needed, use the Blade of the Naz\'jar Battlemaiden at a time focus to return to the vision.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I could ask for no more proficient a Battlemaiden than you. You have done yourself a great honor this day.' WHERE `entry`=25951;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $C.$B$BI will get some patrols out of our own to make sure that no more naga get within sight of this cave. We should have the area secured within the hour.' WHERE `entry`=25952;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N, and just in time too. The Captain just started sending more men out. Strong axe arms, but I doubt they possess quite the same awareness and finesse that you do.$B$BWe were lucky to have you here when things went south. I suspect you will have a large role to play in things to come as well.' WHERE `entry`=25953;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you so much for taking this seriously.$B$BThis is some of the first definitive proof of other members of the Vashj family. Very interesting. And I\'d never even heard of either of the other two figures you mentioned until now.$B$BSo much of our history was lost during the sundering - it\'s exciting to have a chance at reclaiming some of it.' WHERE `entry`=25954;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Ranger Valarian statue',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='High Priestess Siralen statue' WHERE `entry`=25954;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is good intel. You have a sharp eye, $C.$B$BIt sounds like the building north of the gardens will make a suitable forward post. I will send some men immediately to start defensive preparations and we will reposition there as soon as possible.' WHERE `entry`=25955;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A shard of metal?$B$BThe remains you describe sound much like the sea vrykul we encountered in Northrend. We\'ll not be striking any alliances with their sort, no matter the cause. Still, this information may prove useful in the future.$B$BI will think on it further if time permits. Thank you for bringing it to my attention.' WHERE `entry`=25956;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good to see you again, $C. I almost thought we\'d lost you to the Wavespeaker\'s fool errand.$B$BDid anything come of it?' WHERE `entry`=25958;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='More naga are amassing to the south than reported too it seems. We shall have to move quickly then.' WHERE `entry`=25959;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are perhaps the most dependable $R I\'ve ever met. I wish I could have more men that showed half as much pride as you do.' WHERE `entry`=25960;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Brilliant! I can\'t have expected much more with the tools I gave you. I should be able to fill in the blanks and get this all written out shortly. There\'s no knowing if we will make it out of this place, but if it comes down to it, I will find a way to float this to the surface in hopes that it will one day be found. Thank you again, $N. You\'re not bad.' WHERE `entry`=25961;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are brave indeed! I\'ve seen you battling all manner of murloc, naga, and pointy-toothed fish, but that was nothing! The way you just sling those kelp bulbs under your arm like that is a whole new kind of fearless. BOOM! You could blow up at any second.$B$BYou\'re my kind of $R.' WHERE `entry`=25962;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did great up there, soldier! You devastated their ranks, but there were far more than we accounted for, and most of my men went down out there in the masses of naga.$B$BWe\'ll need to hold this position as long as possible to buy them time. Hopefully some of them will still make it to the rendezvous.' WHERE `entry`=25963;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you. Truly.$B$BWe need to get these men moving as soon as possible. I\'ll meet you back at the forward post soon, I\'m sure.' WHERE `entry`=25964;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Still so many? They must want something very important here to come in such numbers.$B$BI will be honest with you, $N, because you deserve at least that: I don\'t know how much hope there is. We will retreat shortly, but we won\'t be able to defend ourselves when they strike back. We don\'t have anywhere to run... we\'re running out of options.$B$BI\'m sorry, I should keep such thoughts to myself. Do me a favor and don\'t mention any of that to the men. I\'ll figure something out.' WHERE `entry`=25965;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re finished! Just in time. I don\'t think we could have held them much longer.$B$BAn artifact? Could this be something we can use against the naga? I suppose that would require finding it.$B$BWe may have to attend to more pressing matters first, until an opportunity to pursue this further presents itself.' WHERE `entry`=25966;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You made it! After the attack at the forward post, I thought we might be the only ones left. It\'s good to see you in one piece, $C.' WHERE `entry`=25967;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Look at you, a regular aquatic hero! Trouble comes. You come. Save the day. You must be proud of yourself!$B$BWe\'ve devised our brilliant plan. Gloriously simple, barring the hostility of local life. Simpler yet with a you available!' WHERE `entry`=25968;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Less gilblins is good.$B$BI\'m glad that they\'re so primitive. I don\'t think I\'d want to be dealing with a race of aquatic tech-freaks right now.' WHERE `entry`=25969;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let me see, let me see... flare gun... balloon... no rope. Never any rope. Terribly impractical if you do ask me. Rope should be mandatory.' WHERE `entry`=25970;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is great! I love it. It should work per... ewww! Is this stuff braided with hair?$B$BDoesn\'t matter. Almost done. This thing will be ready in the twist of a rope.' WHERE `entry`=25971;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect! There\'s no way they missed that, fighting or not.' WHERE `entry`=25972;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That is the best news I\'ve ever heard. We\'ll get the survivors moving over there to the surface as soon as possible. Perhaps we can forget that this whole nightmare ever happened.$B$BThank you, $N. You\'ve shown your worth down here. There will be a glorious spot in the Horde for you.$B$BYou should consider meeting us at the ships later, when you finish saying your goodbyes to the naga.' WHERE `entry`=25973;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice, $N! That will show those naga who\'s the boss!$B$BNow it\'s time for that drink. You want rum or wine?' WHERE `entry`=25974;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That should be enough for now. We know where there\'s more should the need arise.' WHERE `entry`=25975;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s a lot! And we know where there\'s more should the need arise.' WHERE `entry`=25976;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice Uncle Bob of pokin\' their general.' WHERE `entry`=25977;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done it! The mountaineers are returning to camp and our medics will have their hands full. We are all in your debt, $N.' WHERE `entry`=25978;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is never easy to countenance violence against the very elements whose powers I wield, but sometimes there is no other solution. Our duty to the people of Dun Morogh comes first.' WHERE `entry`=25979;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Stuck him right through, did you? I would have loved to have seen that!' WHERE `entry`=25980;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, they\'re ugly, but they mostly look harmless. Smelly though. Here, let me clean the gilblin stuff out of these. I\'ve got an idea....' WHERE `entry`=25981;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, they\'re ugly, but they mostly look harmless. Mostly. They\'re almost cute in a way.$B$BHere, let me clean the gilblin stuff out of these. I\'ve got an idea....' WHERE `entry`=25982;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s very disturbing news, but I believe our Earthen Ring friends here have a plan. And now that you\'re here....' WHERE `entry`=25983;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='If it weren\'t you saying it, I wouldn\'t believe what that troublesome goblin has to say. This is troubling indeed, but I think our Earthen Ring friends have a few ideas.$B$BAnd now that you\'re here....' WHERE `entry`=25984;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, you were sent here by Tiala? A wonderful student, she\'ll do many great things. Although I sense even greater potential from you. Please, stay a while in our shrine. There\'s much to do, but you can\'t accomplish anything with a troubled mind.' WHERE `entry`=25985;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s a good thing the Senator didn\'t come out here on his own. It\'s dangerous, and we\'re going to need all the help we can get to get the situation under control.' WHERE `entry`=25986;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What happened? That thing wasn\'t completely dead! Maybe I should stick to mechanical stuff. It gave you a vision? Of killing all of us?! That doesn\'t sound good. Well, in any case, that Earthen Ring fellow, Erunak Stonespeaker, wants these specimens all taken out to him. I\'ll make sure he gets them. I don\'t want them anywhere near me.' WHERE `entry`=25987;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My bad. My name is Fiasco for a reason. I should have known that thing wasn\'t completely dead when it wiggled a little.$B$BYou say it gave you a vision? Of killing all of us?! That doesn\'t sound good.$B$BHrm, well that Earthen Ring fellow, Erunak Stonespeaker, wants these specimens all taken out to him. I\'ll make sure they get out there. It\'s not like I want them stinking up the place around here.' WHERE `entry`=25988;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Duarn looks at the crab and disguises a frown.>$B$BIt doesn\'t look very impressive, does it?' WHERE `entry`=25989;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I had assumed that the naga were only here for those pearls. No, this makes much more sense. If they had Nespirah\'s power under their control, the amount of damage the naga could do would be catastrophic!$B$BSomething must be done.' WHERE `entry`=25990;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Captain Vilethorn admires the polearms you present him.>$B$BOh, I\'m sorry. I was just imagining what these will look like with little bits of naga stuck to the ends of them. Thank you, $N. We\'ll put these to good use.' WHERE `entry`=25992;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hopefully we made some progress. I\'m not sure how we\'ll know when the creature wakes up, but something tells me that it will be pretty obvious when it does.' WHERE `entry`=25993;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Brilliant work!$B$B<Tulra tucks the pearls away beneath her armor.>$B$BNow I just need you and Legionnaire Nazgrim to get me safely out of here. I can handle the studies from there on.' WHERE `entry`=25994;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='No need to bring me up to speed... Nespirah has been narrating your adventures as they happened, and Legionnaire Nazgrim filled me in on the rest.$B$B<Duarn closes his eyes and nods.>$B$BNespirah says that she is quite grateful, and that she has a small surprise ready for the naga.' WHERE `entry`=25995;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It appears that I owe you my life, yet again. Thank Hellscream that you found me before you and your shaman activated those bio-defenses.' WHERE `entry`=25996;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew they weren\'t here to see the sights. This is more serious than we thought! This is no mere raid. The Dark Irons intend to cripple the defense of Ironforge itself!' WHERE `entry`=25997;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank goodness you\'re here, $N. The airfield\'s been attacked by the Dark Irons and I don\'t think we can hold out much longer.' WHERE `entry`=25998;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You have all of your limbs intact. This is a first.' WHERE `entry`=25999;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Spelunking',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='...$R? Here? I must be mad...' WHERE `entry`=26000;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Blastgineer Fuzzwhistle is definitely dead. It\'s probably for the best. It looks like he\'s holding a note in his hand.' WHERE `entry`=26001;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Damn shame... He was a good goblin. As for you, $N, you\'ve done well. These attack plans will help us prepare. I want you to deliver the plans to Overlord Krom\'gar personally! There\'s sure to be a promotion in it for you.' WHERE `entry`=26002;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, brother! Now they will know that they cannot sneak up on the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=26003;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Hmm. Perhaps this grunt is more than he would appear. Perhaps this grunt is in actuality a sergeant. Look now upon Krom\'gar Sergeant $N, soldiers. He has come to serve warning of a cowardly Alliance attack. An attack that we will CRUSH!' WHERE `entry`=26004;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Find Captain Taylor aboard Voldrin\'s Hold, on the surface above the Ruins of Vashj\'ir.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You made it out! Good to see you, $N. It\'s good to be out of the water for a bit, and to have some resources at our disposal again. I\'m sure many of the boys would give anything to turn around and head home after what we\'ve been though, but we still have a grim task ahead. What about you? Want to stick it through to the end with us? I wouldn\'t blame you if you\'ve had your fill.' WHERE `entry`=26005;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Find Legionnaire Nazgrim aboard the Stygian Bounty, on the surface above the Ruins of Vashj\'ir.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Looks like you make it out in one piece, $C!$B$BIt\'s good to be out of that foul pit of water for a moment, and to have some resources at our disposal again. Don\'t get too comfortable though, we still have a grim task ahead.$B$BWhat about you? Had enough honor for one day, or do you want to get back in there and make Hellscream proud?' WHERE `entry`=26006;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Debriefing',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, it\'s not encouraging, but it\'s something...' WHERE `entry`=26007;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Decompression',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let us hope for the safety of those released prisoners. In return for your noble efforts, please accept this gift.' WHERE `entry`=26008;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Much more blood shall be spilled upon this soil before this war is over. Alliance blood...' WHERE `entry`=26009;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lok\'tar! Alliance pigs! Enjoy the victory for it shall be short lived. Your bravery has given us more time to prepare, nothing more.' WHERE `entry`=26010;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Did you find any suspicious documents at Paltrow\'s camp? Perhaps on his rotting corpse? Any insight into the Alliance\'s attack patterns would be extremely helpful in the battle for Stonetalon.' WHERE `entry`=26011;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for heeding Rhonin\'s call, brave adventurer. Let me share with you what we know regarding recent events, and any assistance you might offer would be greatly appreciated.' WHERE `entry`=26012;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you again, $C, for rescuing me from Baltharus\'s clutches! There is still much work to be done, however....' WHERE `entry`=26013;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Of course we haven\'t returned yet!  We\'ve had our fair share of setbacks... not the least of which was the passing of my dear brother Oskar. He lost his grip and floated away, the poor lad!  He thought he\'d grab some fish to bring back to the captain, but he floated off, and was eaten by one o\' those... those great-eels!  Bwaaaah ha ha haaaah!' WHERE `entry`=26014;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' There ya go. It\'s beautiful!  Oskar would be proud.' WHERE `entry`=26015;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Gnomish flying machines? Our anti-air cannons are still not functional! We will be sitting ducks. I require time to plan... to think... The hot air balloon and its payload cannot remain at Krom\'gar Fortress. I must make arrangements to move the balloon to another location. Our plans to destroy Windshear Hold with it are foiled.' WHERE `entry`=26016;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ya did good, $N!  Ya did real good!' WHERE `entry`=26017;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Hmm... they sound like regular ol\' murlocs... just underwater. That\'ll make Cap\'n Glovaal happy.' WHERE `entry`=26018;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Whaaa... an egg?  An EEL egg? We can definitely do something with this!  Get ready kid, \'cause it\'s time for some good ol\'-fashioned Digsong revenge!' WHERE `entry`=26019;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Properly motivated? Wha... what does that mean? Listen, Sergeant, I have a built in mechanism for survival called self-interest. That is, it\'s in my best interest to NOT DIE. With that said, there\'s no fixing these guns without the right materials.' WHERE `entry`=26020;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oskar\'s alive?  Wait... what did ya say?  Ya let him FLOAT AWAY AGAIN?! Well... ya held up your end of the bargain, and I appreciate everything ya\'ve done, $N. Here... take this. I\'ve only been hanging onto it as ballast, but it doesn\'t seem to be doing much good.' WHERE `entry`=26021;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is but a prelude to the slaughter we will visit upon these lands. All will know our name. You have done well, $N. Victory for Sylvanas!' WHERE `entry`=26022;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes... I was once Prince of the fallen kingdom of Stromgarde. I was cut down by the one seeking Trol\'kalar. I rue my foolish life now. I serve...only Sylvanas.' WHERE `entry`=26023;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You took down Marez Cowl?  Well done, $N. Well done indeed!$B$BMarez menaced our Stromgarde defenders, and it is rumored she was an emissary between the Syndicate and some other, darker power. We are glad to see that she\'ll no longer ply her powers against us.' WHERE `entry`=26024;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My restless nights will turn to peaceful slumber when I have destroyed this orb. Thank you, $N. It is a chilling reminder of the terrible power the demons held over the orcs before Hellscream released them from their curse.' WHERE `entry`=26025;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Mr. D you\'re gonna be ok! Hooray! Oh, Mr. D! I knew it!' WHERE `entry`=26026;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Cleared out properly? Good. I doubt we\'ll even bother to lurk in Stromgarde. That ramshackle hole needs to be razed into dust. The land would make a decent spot for a new Undercity in its place.' WHERE `entry`=26027;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I am - perhaps for the first time in my life - at a loss for words. I am really not sure where Clarissa even came from...' WHERE `entry`=26028;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is the fate of all who would stand in our way.' WHERE `entry`=26029;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hated the Syndicate in life as much as I do in death. To see the sigil again is a small comfort. But we have much more work to do... for Sylvanas.' WHERE `entry`=26030;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thoradin was the founder of Arathor. Just as I join these fragments together, he joined the scattered tribes of humans into their first great nation. But I\'m sure you\'re not interested in such drivel. Forgive me. Old memories are often hard to bury.' WHERE `entry`=26031;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Valorcall was loyal to me in life. His death will not be something I bear lightly. But bear it I must. I am Forsaken. My old existence means nothing. The sigils are ours; Trol\'kalar awaits.' WHERE `entry`=26032;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Trol\'kalar, my father\'s blade... it seems like it\'s been an eternity since I saw it.' WHERE `entry`=26033;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' We owe you a debt of gratitude, mortal, for driving the invaders from the Sanctum. But this news of the Destroyer is troubling beyond words. I have much to discuss with the other members of the Accord. Take these as a token of my thanks, as you gird yourselves for the coming storm.' WHERE `entry`=26034;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not bad. Since it\'s clear you\'ve got your head on straight, I was hoping you could help us with a more pressing job.' WHERE `entry`=26035;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Brilliant, $N. One item down an\' three more to go, based on my list. The other three items are all in Stromgarde.$B$BTake a rest an\' get your strength back--the next phase of my plan\'ll require a little more time an\' effort. Come back to me after you\'ve gotten a warm meal an\' some rest.' WHERE `entry`=26036;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You amaze me, $N. Well done again. Give me a moment to cast the proper spell an\' you\'ll be ready.' WHERE `entry`=26037;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Malin couldn\'t\'ve asked a worthier person to come here an\' aid us, $N. You\'ve done a grand job!$B$BHe\'ll be pleased to see what an overwhelming success our mission\'s been.' WHERE `entry`=26038;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah! You activated these shards. Already I feel more myself!$B$BBut alas, I am still far from free...' WHERE `entry`=26039;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, yes. This is the stuff. Maybe I can wean off of it and avoid the side-effect. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26040;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You have done it!  You opened the Stones of Binding!  I can feel the shackles about me loosen, and freedom draws ever closer. You are a noble $C, $N. My rescuer!' WHERE `entry`=26041;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You place the rod in the keystone. And a shudder is felt beneath you...' WHERE `entry`=26042;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A testament to the might of the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=26043;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Um... Well you see, it\'s quite simple... THIS CAVE IS SWARMING WITH SOULLESS KILLING MACHINES!' WHERE `entry`=26044;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ll be damned! You managed to get the parts and not die. How are you only a sergeant?' WHERE `entry`=26045;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Get the parts, kill the elementals and rescue the peons... We get all of that done and we\'re as good as promoted!' WHERE `entry`=26046;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew it! You are a hero! If I have anything to do with it, you\'ll be promoted to legionnaire!' WHERE `entry`=26047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just in time! The flying machines are starting to mass. Attack is imminent!' WHERE `entry`=26048;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='As the eldritch shackles are placed around the Shards, an unhuman wail is heard from far below. The scream is followed by a roar.$B$BThe Shards of Myzrael no longer invoke feelings of warmth and security as they once did. Now they pulse with an open menace... as if the thing beneath them holds ill will toward the surface.' WHERE `entry`=26049;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The goggles work perfectly now! Well done, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26050;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Most superb, $N! The Captain will be very pleased! And just wait until word gets back to Fleetmaster Seahorn!' WHERE `entry`=26051;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So the little gnomes proved their worth after all? I knew we kept those ankle biters around for a reason!' WHERE `entry`=26052;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. The march of the Forsaken continues.' WHERE `entry`=26053;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Sandfury trolls and the Cult of Twilight\'s Hammer, you say? And they meant to send some giant monster into the heart of the city?! Well done! Stormwind is in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=26054;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice work out there, $N.$B$BThose scum deserved what they got. While nothin\' will ever bring me ship or me crew back, the death of those naga gives me some solace.' WHERE `entry`=26055;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I sure am glad you\'re here!' WHERE `entry`=26056;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I sure am glad you\'re here!' WHERE `entry`=26057;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I have never seen such an act of bravery. You saved the base, sergeant - or should I say legionnaire! Lok\'tar!' WHERE `entry`=26058;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see that Krom\'gar has sent his best! Good, we have much work to do. The filth that is the Alliance have entered into a treaty with the Grimtotem. Now we fend off attacks from both forces. We are spread thin across the Greatwood Vale and will soon fall beneath the concerted effort of our enemies. There is only one hope: VOODOO!' WHERE `entry`=26059;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. Once I have everything I need I will mix it all together and unleash the voodoo! Woe unto our enemies!' WHERE `entry`=26060;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. Once I have everything I need I will mix it all together and unleash the voodoo! Woe unto our enemies!' WHERE `entry`=26061;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Finally! Now I will create the charm that will hold the voodoo enchantment!' WHERE `entry`=26062;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Darn still not very happy, but Darn will reward you for what you have done.' WHERE `entry`=26063;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. These eggs should get us through the week.' WHERE `entry`=26064;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N.$B$BThese nightmarish creatures that rise from below give me pause. I fear that our efforts will be for nothing.' WHERE `entry`=26065;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Reinforcements...',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='In times of crisis, a desperate act may be all that is needed to secure victory. Sending a swarm of kobolds at the enemy may be the edge that we need to win.' WHERE `entry`=26066;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Victory, at last! Though it stands to reason that without a stable supply line this victory will be short lived. Enjoy it while it lasts, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26067;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Fascinating tale, friend. It would seem that our newfound kobold allies might be somewhat useful after all!' WHERE `entry`=26068;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The situation is grim, $R. We need all of the help that we can get!' WHERE `entry`=26069;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good enough for me. Don\'t get too complacent, $N. The hard part\'s about to come.' WHERE `entry`=26070;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done.$B$BDon\'t get too full of yourself, $N. The hard part\'s about to come.' WHERE `entry`=26071;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, $R, can you feel them seething with a desire to break free and destroy us?$B$BThis is good! They will be the perfect lure for their leader.' WHERE `entry`=26072;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lok\'tar ogar! You are the embodiment of what it means to be a Horde soldier, $N. If only we had more like you, this war would be over and Kalimdor would belong to the Horde - UNCONTESTED! Rise now as a champion of Krom\'gar!' WHERE `entry`=26073;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Krom\'gar has sent his champion! Well you haven\'t a thing to worry about, Champion. We\'ll get the balloon all fueled up in no time. How about you lend a hand around here while you wait?' WHERE `entry`=26074;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I sure hope you didn\'t miss any. I don\'t think I can take much more of this!' WHERE `entry`=26075;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='And they called me crazy. I knew this place was crawling with spies. Poop too.' WHERE `entry`=26076;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Chieftain Cliffwalker and his tauren seek to commit treason against the Horde! They claim that the ancient tree at the heart of Battlescar Valley is merely a school for druids. They are blind to the fact that desperate measures are taken during war time. My scouts have assured me that the night elves hide a weapon of great power within that tree. We\'re going to end this now!' WHERE `entry`=26077;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done! My men are working hard on getting our flying machines and steam tanks back into the fight.' WHERE `entry`=26078;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Falconcrest and Otto? Wonderful!$B$BHere is your reward, $N. I am happy to pay it.' WHERE `entry`=26079;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see. Yes, I am rememberink now... Humphrey and Oskar vere not the strongest svimmers. The reconnaissance is helpful, and the extra fish look very tasty. If you are seeink Mister Digsong before he returns, please send him my thanks.' WHERE `entry`=26080;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The news of your victory satisfies me, $C... a rare sensation. The Dark Lady herself has mused that our conquest of Lordaeron may be the only way the Forsaken can find true satisfaction, and pehaps even relief. But it matters not. Our victory is inevitable. For your loyal service to the Forsaken, I award you in the name of Sylvanas.' WHERE `entry`=26081;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You possess quite a talent for destruction, $N. Whatever Alliance remain after your rampage across Battlescar Valley will be dealt with by the bomb.' WHERE `entry`=26082;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You friends with Goutgut! Him weird ogre. Smell funny.' WHERE `entry`=26083;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Throm\'ka, $C. If your deeds for the undead are as great as you claim, I am honored to help you serve the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=26084;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The men are finding hidden reserves of strength and courage to deal with the Dark Iron onslaught. The airfield will not fall on our watch!' WHERE `entry`=26085;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Orako',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Gah!  These fish are impossible to hit!$B$B<Orako looks at you.>$B$BMy wolf got eaten by a fish, and I\'m not going back until I find her.' WHERE `entry`=26086;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Shooting fish in a barrel is easy. Shooting fish in an ocean is a little harder.$B$BHave you seen the murlocs down in the canyon, $C?  They don\'t shoot at all!  They have little balls full of glow-juice on their heads that make the fish come to THEM. Hey, we should try that!$B$BGo south, and kill the crabs and groupers in the canyon. They have lots of glow-juice in their skin. I\'ve seen it!',`objectives_loc6`='Obtain 6 gobs of Glow-Juice from Pyreshell Scuttlers and Luxscale Groupers in Underlight Canyon.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey, look at how glowy it is!$B$B<Orako looks wistfully off into the distance.>$B$BMy wolf loved things that were glowy...' WHERE `entry`=26087;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm... you got a lot of fish, but none of these are the ones that ate my wolf. I think it was probably a bigger fish.' WHERE `entry`=26088;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I know, murlocs aren\'t fish. I thought that killing them would make me feel better, but I still feel sad about my wolf.$B$B<Orako sighs.>' WHERE `entry`=26089;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That is a big egg.$B$B<Orako sniffs it.>$B$BIt is big, and it smells like fish. Maybe the big fish that made this egg is the big fish that ate my wolf!' WHERE `entry`=26090;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Orako is busy playing with Wolf.>$B$BOh, thank you, $N!  I knew Wolf was alive!$B$BHere, take one of these. I don\'t need them anymore.' WHERE `entry`=26091;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is his report?!  That idiot...$B$BI suppose we can use the food. Thanks, $N. You\'ve done as well as can be expected.' WHERE `entry`=26092;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very good, $N. The last thing we need with the undead looming is a gang of common thieves distracting us.' WHERE `entry`=26093;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The momentum is starting to shift, $N, largely due to your efforts. Now, it is time to strike at the Dark Iron leadership.' WHERE `entry`=26094;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. We will inform the families of these fallen soldiers that they were killed in battle.$B$BIt will be grim news to bear, but it is better than the uncertainty of a missing loved one.' WHERE `entry`=26095;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I will use the mushrooms as a reagent to treat the corpses. We will have one ready for you soon.' WHERE `entry`=26096;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Orthus is dead. He is clutching something in his hand.' WHERE `entry`=26097;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You saw with your own eyes, $N. General Grebo attacked us! Now what will we do? Surely the Warchief will have us all executed for treason.' WHERE `entry`=26099;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='WHAT? My General has been killed by the tauren? This is treason! HIGH TREASON! They will pay for this grievous error.' WHERE `entry`=26100;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The traitorous tauren will now stand by as we destroy his precious grove and burn his village to the ground!' WHERE `entry`=26101;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'ve done it! Without your help, Ironforge Airfield would surely be occupied by the enemy and the Dark Irons would have a clear road to Ironforge itself. The Council of Three Hammers must be informed of what happened here.' WHERE `entry`=26102;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Bio-Fuel',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Yes, I think this will do.' WHERE `entry`=26103;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did well, $N. We need to be especially wary of Horde attacks right now. The Pincer X2 has plenty of firepower at sea, but in the back of this cave, she is exceptionally vulnerable.' WHERE `entry`=26105;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Have you considered a career in science, $N?  If you ever get tired of this $C nonsense, come see me!  I could use an assistant with your devotion to experimentation and the scientific method.' WHERE `entry`=26106;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The lethargy that overcame me even after the camps fell was so strong, I refused this gift when it was first given to me. Now, I am proud to do my part in the name of the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=26107;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='As Tor\'gan taught me, I transfer the power and the spirit of the raptors into this orb. It will imbue our warriors with the fiery strength and intelligence of the raptor. The guile of the raptor is yours now as well, $C. Take it with pride, for the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=26108;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='It\'s funny. Kin and I have been through so much together, and here we find ourselves back in Arathi, like so many years ago.$B$BWe broke up a plot to create a new plague right here, her and I. It doesn\'t look like the horde learned their lesson, because they\'re all over this farm yet again.$B$BTheir undead courier is shuffling around as obvious as daylight. If you want to help, find the courier and bring back whatever they\'re carrying.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Apothecaries yet again. You think they\'d get the message. Let\'s see what it is this time...' WHERE `entry`=26110;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='And now we will see if we can get you into L\'ghorek to speak with it before it dies.' WHERE `entry`=26111;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='And just what is this? This is impossible!' WHERE `entry`=26112;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The Horde have held Go\'shek farm to the east for a long time; it\'s never been of much concern compared to the rest of our problems here. But there\'s been reports of undead activity in the area.$B$BAnything more alarming than shuffling peons over there warrants investigation. This isn\'t the first time the undead have been up to no good at the farm, so I\'ve sent my best scouts there to check it out. Report to Quae and Kinelory and they\'ll fill you in.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Refuge Pointe sent you? Good to know they\'re still there. We\'ve got some interesting things to check into here, $C.' WHERE `entry`=26113;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The plague took our friends and family, but it was the Forsaken that took Phin. They\'re just as bad as the Scourge. I\'ll destroy every one of them with my own hands if I have to. When you\'re prepared, come let me know. We\'ll get started right away.' WHERE `entry`=26114;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now you truly know what it means to be a member of the Horde, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26115;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done a great service for us, $N. Thank you.$B$BI hope Kin wasn\'t too much of a handful down there. She\'s very friendly, but can be just as deadly when you\'re her enemy.' WHERE `entry`=26116;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I admit I\'m impressed, $C. It\'s a small comfort amidst all that\'s happened here. You have fought the undead, struck back against the Horde, and honored the memory of the victims of Southshore. On behalf of the kingdom of Stromgarde, I present you with an official commendation, and this reward.' WHERE `entry`=26117;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The ambassador will trouble us no more. He is not the only Dark Iron $R whose heart still belongs to Twilight\'s Hammer. We must remember that and remain vigilant against their schemes, else my son will inherit only ruins and ashes.' WHERE `entry`=26118;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The orcs will know better than to press further west now. Well done.' WHERE `entry`=26120;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did well, $N. We need to be especially wary of Horde attacks right now. The Pincer X2 has plenty of firepower at sea, but in the back of this cave, she is exceptionally vulnerable.' WHERE `entry`=26121;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Fiasco sticks a finger into each sample and sniffs it.>$B$BYes, I think this will do.' WHERE `entry`=26122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did well, $N. We need to be especially wary of Alliance attacks right now. The Verne\'s got plenty of firepower out at sea, but in the back of this cave, she\'s far too vulnerable.' WHERE `entry`=26124;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did well, $N. We need to be especially wary of Alliance attacks right now. The Verne\'s got plenty of firepower out at sea, but in the back of this cave, she\'s far too vulnerable.' WHERE `entry`=26125;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s it. Starting today, I\'m shifting the Verne over to bio-fuel. I\'ll send some men up to harvest more oil.$B$BThink of all the sea creatures that we\'ve saved today, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26126;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good show, lad, but we\'ve no time to celebrate. Thandol Span\'s in danger!' WHERE `entry`=26127;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='And good riddance! Thandol Span\'s safe thanks to you, $N, and hopefully Calamoth is down for good this time.' WHERE `entry`=26128;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Rebel arsenals?  In my own city? What in the bloody hell was Crowley up to?' WHERE `entry`=26129;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now that you have unplugged L\'ghorek, we must attempt to make contact with it. I can sense that the ancient yet lives, but only barely.' WHERE `entry`=26130;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You don\'t know how glad I am to see fresh faces from Ironforge. Perhaps sending Mountaineer Barleybrew wasn\'t a waste after all.' WHERE `entry`=26131;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The last thing we needed was a bunch of summoned creatures swarming our forces during the final assault.' WHERE `entry`=26132;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s one less thing we need to think about during the final assault.' WHERE `entry`=26133;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Minions of the Old God? Two very potent foes have joined forces then. Their hope to defeat the Tidehunter may not be so foolish after all.$B$B$N, we can\'t let that happen. If Azshara defeats the Tidehunter and takes his power for herself, I\'m not sure any number of us could ever hope to oppose her on the seas.$B$BThe first step is clear at least - we need to hunt down the fiend that destroyed our ships. The navy was confident enough to bring in a new fleet, perhaps they have a plan.' WHERE `entry`=26135;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, well met, $C. Stormpike sent you? About the keg? Hoo boy...' WHERE `entry`=26137;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I suppose I owe Thargas a favor for sending such a bold hero my way. Or perhaps he just wanted to keep all the clean-up for himself. Regardless, you\'ll find much to do here for the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=26139;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='WISE OF... YOUR ERUNAK TO... HAVE... YOU USE... THE FACELESS\' BRAIN. I SEE... YOU NOW.$B$BI WILL DIE. THERE IS NO... STOPPING... THE INEVITABLE.$B$BBUT... YOU WILL HELP... ME DEAL WITH... THESE PARASITES FIRST.' WHERE `entry`=26140;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='WE WILL USE... THESE... RUNESTONES TO ALLOW... YOU TO POSSESS... ONE OF... THE WATER ELEMENTALS.' WHERE `entry`=26141;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='THEY SHALL ASCEND... NO MORE!' WHERE `entry`=26142;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='YOU HAVE DONE... MYSELF AND... THE TIDEHUNTER GREAT... SERVICE.' WHERE `entry`=26143;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Prisoners' WHERE `entry`=26144;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am quite impressed, $N. You have done the Dwarven race a great favor by defending our lands. King Magni Bronzebeard himself would be proud!' WHERE `entry`=26145;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N!  You demonstrated uncanny courage on the battlefield. Our war against the Troggs will be won with efforts such as yours. You have served King Magni well.' WHERE `entry`=26146;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew the second I laid eyes on you, $N, that you would make Ironforge proud. You have served our people well. I salute you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26147;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Most excellent, $N! You have brought hope to Loch Modan. With Grawmug dead, we stand a better chance of seeing the Troggs eliminated from the land.' WHERE `entry`=26148;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Prisoners',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='A job well done. Now you don\'t need to worry about what would have happened to them if you hadn\'t been around.$B$BThe last one was even appreciative enough to give you a reward they\'d kept hidden on their person.' WHERE `entry`=26149;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='William sent you? Bless his soul. I... I\'m ok... It\'s just... Well...' WHERE `entry`=26150;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice job, $N! Penny will be very excited for breakfast tomorrow!' WHERE `entry`=26153;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='THEIR DEVOTIONS ARE... SILENCED.$B$BNOW THAT... YOU HAVE... THEIR POWER... YOU MUST DESTROY... THEIR LEADER.' WHERE `entry`=26154;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Kasim Sharim',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hah!  You Nethergarde nincompoops are always two steps behind me, and I\'m nowhere near as fast as I used to be. I don\'t need Mahar\'s note to know what\'s going on. Why do you think I\'m cooped up in the back of this cave?  What I do need, however, is a strong $R like you.' WHERE `entry`=26157;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent!  You\'ve managed to complete the simplest of tasks without dying. Now that that\'s out of the way...' WHERE `entry`=26158;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' More than enough, and still warm!  Now, let\'s get this ritual started, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=26159;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The blood ritual was a success; I can clearly see where we are going next. I\'m sorry, I misspoke. What I meant to say is, I can see where YOU are going next...' WHERE `entry`=26160;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see... yes, I can work with this. Loramus Thalipedes, demon hunter. I look forward to our reunion.' WHERE `entry`=26161;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You... you fool!  What have you done?' WHERE `entry`=26162;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='No, no, no... not Kasim again!  This is madness! Please, remain quiet. If my commander learns that I still work for the short one, do you know how quickly I will be removed from the watch? I see you speak the truth. Let us begin our business quickly, so that it may end even quicker.' WHERE `entry`=26163;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hope this is what the gnome wanted.' WHERE `entry`=26164;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There is no doubt about it, you have found demon blood. Kasim\'s requests aside, I am sure that my Watch Commander is thankful for your efforts. They have been struggling to deal with these demon distractions for some time now.' WHERE `entry`=26165;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is sufficient. If you see Grimeo again, you may tell him that he performed satisfactorily, but no... his debt is not yet cleared. I will get to work on fashioning the stone knife of sealing. There is no need for questions now. All will be revealed in time. While I work, I have another task for you to complete. Don\'t look so upset!  This task will be fun... it involves collecting body parts.' WHERE `entry`=26166;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' He was an archmage, I can feel it. I will hold the amulet for you while you collect the rest.' WHERE `entry`=26167;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' A warlock... and a powerful one at that. I will hold onto this until the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=26168;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' He was a powerful warrior, this one. I will keep the amulet until we are ready to proceed.' WHERE `entry`=26169;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It would seem that we are prepared to face our demon, $N. We have the amulet\'s blessing, we have the stone knife, and I alone know the demon\'s true name: Rakh\'likh. Together, this may be enough to defeat the Defiler.' WHERE `entry`=26170;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Loramus, resurrected!?  And then he trapped the demon inside his own body... by the Light... I see. So this was Kasim\'s plan all along. I suspected correctly, but I suppose I refused to believe it. Ah, one last thing!  Kasim left one more instruction for me within his rune. I did not understand it at first, but given the events that have taken place today, it now makes much more sense: He asked me to let you choose from one of these.' WHERE `entry`=26171;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are perfect, $N. I will eat well for the next several days.' WHERE `entry`=26172;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your work is appreciated, soldier. $R... if you\'re still interested, I have one more small task for you...' WHERE `entry`=26173;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re certain nobody saw you?  Good. Hmph... fairly harmless stuff. Either the Horde are foolish enough to NOT be planning something against us... or they\'re hiding their information better than I expected. Either way, well done, soldier.' WHERE `entry`=26174;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome to Surwich, $R. Please, have a look around.' WHERE `entry`=26175;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Glad to hear you\'ve been clearing out the troggs. Let\'s have a look at this report, and... ...Is that a beer stain?' WHERE `entry`=26176;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Collect 10 Canal Crabs. Deliver them to Robby Flay in Stormwind City.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='These crabs look great!  I will clean these up and make sure that the King hears about your contribution. Thanks!' WHERE `entry`=26177;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I don\'t think there could be too much misinterpreting or ignoring of that signal, hm? The Venture Co. will know not to take the $R lightly, or to be so arrogant as to believe we would allow them to steal the natural resources around us without protest.' WHERE `entry`=26179;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My anger is somewhat lessened at the news that the villain Fizsprocket is dead. I will go through his personal effects and see if there is any additional information about what the Venture Co. has planned for the future. Thank you for your efforts, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26180;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello again, $C.$B$BI felt L\'ghorek die. A shame that such a magnificent being is gone.$B$BIf we do not assist Neptulon, we will all meet the same fate.' WHERE `entry`=26181;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello again, $C.$B$BI felt L\'ghorek die. A shame that such a magnificent being is gone.$B$BIf we do not assist Neptulon, we will all meet the same fate.' WHERE `entry`=26182;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These will do nicely $N. I will get to work right away on the cider.' WHERE `entry`=26183;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You say the demons were all worshipping the tree? It is as I feared, then.' WHERE `entry`=26184;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='While I\'m surprised that Connisport is willing to go forward with his plan, I\'m also relieved. I\'ve seen the demons rallying around Maldraz, and I share his fears.' WHERE `entry`=26185;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Very well, $N. We have what we need to break Marl\'s trance and put an end to both him and his experiment.' WHERE `entry`=26186;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. I, and the people of Surwich, are in your debt. Feel free to take one of these. While we haven\'t got much, we\'re happy to reward those that protect us.' WHERE `entry`=26187;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, thank you, $N. Using the items you brought me, I will be able to create the remedy I need to stop the spread of the infection and, eventually, cure it completely. I owe you my life in thanks.$B$BBut I\'ll never forget that screeching call when Mazzranache came upon me, the blaze of color as its beak descended...$B$BBe wary on your travels.' WHERE `entry`=26188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good to see you back in one piece, $N! You\'re quite a piece of work. I\'ll be tellin\' Captain Stoutfist how you took care of those orcs!' WHERE `entry`=26189;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. I will get to work scaling these for the King right away.' WHERE `entry`=26190;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With every day, more warriors arrive at Azshara\'s command. Soon, Neptulon the Tidehunter will hear of our preparations, but too late to stop what we have set in motion. Our numbers will be too great and our allies too powerful. Victory is only a matter of time.$B$BIn Azshara\'s name.' WHERE `entry`=26191;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These sacks look like just enough, $N. Can\'t wait to see the smiles on the orphans faces.' WHERE `entry`=26192;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The whispers of the elements are crowding my thoughts, $N...$B$BThe Throne of Tides is under siege!$B$BWe cannot stand idly by while the naga threaten Neptulon\'s realm.$B$BMake ready! With this submarine and its armaments, perhaps we can make a difference.$B$BSpeak to me when you are prepared for battle.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Erunak in Darkbreak Cove to enter the battle for the Abyssal Breach.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='NO! This is NOT over!' WHERE `entry`=26193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The whispers of the elements are crowding my thoughts, $N...$B$BThe Throne of Tides is under siege!$B$BWe cannot stand idly by while the naga threaten Neptulon\'s realm.$B$BMake ready! With this submarine and its armaments, perhaps we can make a difference.$B$BSpeak to me when you have made your preparations.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Erunak in Tenebrous Cavern to enter the battle for the Abyssal Breach.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='They may think they\'ve won, but my axe and I have something to say about that!' WHERE `entry`=26194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The greenwarden was a local legend. Many thought him a myth... the plant-man, protector of the wetlands. The night elves came here just to find him, and after they succeeded they ended up settling down to the east.$B$BThey\'ve got a whole grove over there to watch over the Greenwarden, and I\'ve heard he\'s been acting up, enraged by the flooding and damage to the land.$B$BThe elves are good people. They could use the help of someone like you. If you get a chance, go tell the head druid what you\'ve done here.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome to the Greenwarden\'s grove, $C. I am glad Whelgar has told you of us. If you are able to lend us your assistance, I will be most grateful.' WHERE `entry`=26195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Supplies from Ferilon? Bless his heart. We\'re good on food, but we\'re runnin\' out of bullets!' WHERE `entry`=26196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N, isn\'t it? It\'s a pleasure to finally meet you. While you were getting cleaned up, Nevin\'s team told me about your escape from Gnomeregan.' WHERE `entry`=26197;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I want to show you a simple technique. It will allow you to focus and channel bursts of arcane power toward an opponent.$B$BAs you grow in power, you\'ll learn how to add more and more missiles to each volley.$B$BFind one of the training dummies setup in the middle of town. You won\'t always be able to cast arcane missiles right away. First, you\'ll need to cast other spells at the dummy until you\'ve created an opportunity to use arcane missiles. Try it out for yourself.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Bipsi Frostflinger to train Arcane Missiles. Once you\'ve learned the spell, successfully cast Arcane Missiles twice at a Training Dummy in New Tinkertown.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You picked that one up quickly. I can\'t wait to show you some of my other favorite tricks.' WHERE `entry`=26198;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. I\'m sure your time in Gnomeregan afforded you ample opportunity to practice your arts. Things are somewhat safer here, but your talents will never go to waste.' WHERE `entry`=26199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I have a simple technique I want to show you. It\'s pretty straightforward, but it\'s still one of the most useful things I know.$B$BYou can use it to heal yourself or a wounded ally very quickly. It\'s handy for when you need to treat someone promptly and don\'t have time for something more complicated.$B$BGive it a try for yourself and let me know when you think you have it mastered.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to "Doc" Cogspin to train Flash Heal. Use Flash Heal 5 times on Wounded Infantry in New Tinkertown.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, $N. You have a natural talent for our arts.' WHERE `entry`=26200;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I\'m not at all surprised that a warlock like you fought your way out of Gnomeregan. Few people, even among the gnomes, truly understand the nature of the power we wield.$B$BLet me show you a conjuration that I find handy. This spell, called Immolate, sets your target aflame, causing damage immediately and over time. Use it well, $N, and your enemies will come to fear you.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Alamar Grimm and learn Immolate, then cast Immolate on a Training Dummy in New Tinkertown 5 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='As you continue to gain power, return to me and I will teach you new spells and techniques.' WHERE `entry`=26201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, another one of Nevin\'s "rescued" survivors, eh? More than likely, you saved his life from the troggs down there. Did he stumble over his words when he mentioned me? The man has a healthy respect for the demonic powers we channel.' WHERE `entry`=26202;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='For a $R who has spent so much time inside Gnomeregan, you look positively fit and healthy, $N. That\'s good. Before we can complete what Operation: Gnomeregan began, we\'re going to need more warriors like you.' WHERE `entry`=26203;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I want to show you a simple but useful technique.$B$BAs I tell all my recruits, a warrior who strikes first can use that momentum to gain the upper hand. This is a technique to use from a distance, before engaging your opponent. It will allow you to charge in, taking your enemy by surprise and stunning him.$B$BTry it out. Let me know when you think you\'ve mastered it.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Drill Sergeant Steamcrank to learn Charge. Locate a Training Dummy in New Tinkertown and use Charge on it.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work! Keep practicing your charge and you\'ll have an instant advantage at the start of battle.' WHERE `entry`=26204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wow, I never expected it to work on the first trial! Uh, I mean, we\'ve succeeded! I wonder what other uses I we can find for this handy little guy.' WHERE `entry`=26205;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. Nevin tells me that you managed to survive the dangers in Gnomeregan by using your wits. That\'s exactly what we need up here. Clever minds and quick blades.' WHERE `entry`=26206;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I have a technique I want to show you.$B$BOne of a rogue\'s most potent abilities is to chain together moves in a combination, exploiting your enemy\'s weakness and opening up the opportunity to use stronger maneuvers. The technique I want to teach you is called Eviscerate. It is intended for use at the end of a combination to provide a strong finish to your assault.$B$BTry using it after a landing a couple of Sinister Strikes.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Kelsey Steelspark to learn Eviscerate, then find a training dummy in New Tinkertown and practice using Eviscerate 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m not surprised to see you\'re such a quick study. I look forward to showing you more of our tricks of the trade.' WHERE `entry`=26207;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Even now, only the S.A.F.E. teams dare to venture far into the city to search for survivors. Meanwhile, Thermaplugg has sent one of his followers, Crushcog, to distract us and buy time for him to dig in.' WHERE `entry`=26208;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Gnolls and murlocs? Horse poopy, pal! Gnolls and murlocs didn\'t kill these people. I\'ve seen what gnolls and murlocs do to people that they kill and this... isn\'t it. Too pretty. Too... perfect. Furthermore, the Furlbrow\'s had been squatting on this farm for 5 years. No, whoever wiped them out had a reason. This is murder, plain and simple and we\'re gonna get to the bottom of it...' WHERE `entry`=26209;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Clue #3 obtained',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Clue #4 obtained' WHERE `entry`=26209;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='MON! This is fantastic! With my best lure and the snapjaw population down, the fish will pile up.' WHERE `entry`=26210;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, mon! I can\'t thank you enough! Hopefully this here fishing pole will be reward enough for the job.' WHERE `entry`=26211;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Dis hit da spot! Tanks little one. Lard make you special picnic basket for help Lard.' WHERE `entry`=26212;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Is this supposed to be some kind of joke, because I\'m not laughing. Bits and pieces of red cloth? What the hell is this supposed to mean?' WHERE `entry`=26213;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice find, rookie. I think I have a stack of these on my desk back at the station. We\'re basically back to square one. What do we know? Someone that likes to write fiction about the past sent the Furlbrows a letter. Looks like we got ourselves a real history... mystery.' WHERE `entry`=26214;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Look, we ain\'t got no room for no more... Horatio sent you? Right then... um, how can I help you? He\'s not here is he? Heh, he knows I wasn\'t hidin\' from him, right? Was just tryin\' to lay low and all that, ya know?' WHERE `entry`=26215;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Vell done, Private $N. The cavern is ours, but the beast escaped. Should it raise it\'s ugly head again, ve vill make with blastink it out of the vater.' WHERE `entry`=26219;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, $N. These will do nicely.' WHERE `entry`=26220;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $C.$B$BThat slippery beast got away! I\'ll be making a few upgrades. It won\'t be so lucky next time.' WHERE `entry`=26221;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are fantastic! Let\'s see what we can put together. Would you be interested in testing out the prototype once I\'m done?' WHERE `entry`=26222;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A job well done, $R. The Revantusk thank you for your contribution.' WHERE `entry`=26223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have proven a worthy ally to the Revantusk, $N. Well done.' WHERE `entry`=26224;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect! I don\'t know where I\'d get this stuff if it wasn\'t for drunk humans repeatedly crashing their ships. Normally I\'d settle down and get ready to haggle with you for an hour, but you\'re in luck; I\'m too eager to crack these open. Cheers!' WHERE `entry`=26225;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ugh, I never liked cooking these slimy things. Thanks for the help $N.' WHERE `entry`=26226;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let me see your hands... Aha!  Your not any better at collecting these wretched things than I am!' WHERE `entry`=26227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' STOP! STOP! STOP! I don\'t wanna hear it! I don\'t wanna know and I don\'t care! That kind of information is liable to get you killed \'round these parts. I got one more bit of information for you and then we\'re done!' WHERE `entry`=26228;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Back before those damned kobolds gave me a permanent limp I used to be William Pestle\'s number one candle supplier. Hell, I even came up with the line "I TAKE CANDLE!" Yea, that was me. Kobold would say "You no take candle!" and I\'d just respond "I TAKE CANDLE!" and then bash their brains in!$B$B<Jimb drifts off for a second.>$B$BGood times... The best times.$B$BNow? Can\'t even use the bathroom without assistance. You want to help me? Kill me some kobolds. You\'ll find a good load of \'em in the nearby mine.',`objectives_loc6`='Kill 12 Kobold Diggers.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh SWEET justice! Killin\' those kobolds won\'t make me walk like a normal person and it sure won\'t get me a job, but damn does it feel good. Here, I think I got somethin\' for you from my kobold huntin\' days. Maybe you can put it to good use.' WHERE `entry`=26229;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just smellin\' you comin\' got my stomach rumblin\'! We\'re gonna eat like kings tonight!' WHERE `entry`=26230;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'re dealing with an organization here, rookie. You don\'t just off the richest bum in Westfall in broad daylight and leave no witnesses. Someone with a lot of power is behind these murders. What have you learned so far?' WHERE `entry`=26232;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='As you know, $N, Garrosh has relegated the Trolls of Orgrimmar to the western outskirts of the city. Fortunately, that means that we have easy access to their supplies. I am working on a large batch of jambalaya for the infantry and I need as much rice as possible. Lucky for us, the Trolls keep it stored in barrels near their structures. Retrieve these barrels of Darkspear rice for me and I should be able to finish up.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see you are a skilled thief as well, $N. Don\'t worry, we will return the rice once we are done... or not.' WHERE `entry`=26233;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='As you know, $N, Garrosh has relegated the Goblins of Orgrimmar to the western outskirts of the city. Fortunately, that means that we have easy access to their supplies. I am working on a large batch of jambalaya for the infantry and I need as much rice as possible. Lucky for us, the Goblins keep it stored in barrels near their structures. Retrieve these barrels of Kezan rice for me and I should be able to finish up.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see you are a skilled thief as well, $N. Don\'t worry, we will return the rice once we are done... or not.' WHERE `entry`=26234;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice work $N!  I will see that these rations are returned to the troops immediately.' WHERE `entry`=26235;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Horatio Laine? That man is a scumbag. Dirty as my underwear. Listen, friend, I don\'t often give out advice like this, but you seem like a good man. GET OUT OF WESTFALL. You\'re already in way over your head. All you\'re doing now is putting your neck on the chopping block.' WHERE `entry`=26236;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, brother. You\'ve done Salma and I a great service and I promise that it won\'t soon be forgotten. I don\'t have much money, but you\'re welcome to what I do have.' WHERE `entry`=26237;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That will show the Wildhammer to stay away from our lands! Crazy dwarves should\'ve stayed in the mountains...' WHERE `entry`=26238;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Makes all the difference, doesn\'t it? That\'ll teach those dwarves a lesson.' WHERE `entry`=26240;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Bless your heart, dear. These poor orphans haven\'t had a hot meal in days. It looks like we will have enough left over to help feed many more of the homeless of Westfall.' WHERE `entry`=26241;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did what was necessary, $N. I can tell you\'re the sort of $C I\'ll get along with well.' WHERE `entry`=26244;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The clues point to an obvious conclusion. Too obvious perhaps.' WHERE `entry`=26245;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Why would the Alliance attack the Horde just as they\'re about to deliver a fragment of the World Pillar to us.' WHERE `entry`=26246;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oi, $N!  I was told I\'d have company soon.' WHERE `entry`=26247;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We were bound to run into the Twilight\'s Hammer sooner or later, $N. If they\'re behind this, it\'s quite likely that the World Pillar fragment is in their possession.' WHERE `entry`=26248;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This ship is filled with rats...' WHERE `entry`=26249;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oi, this was a heavy one!  He nearly broke me gryphon\'s back! Are you ready to interrogate the ogre, $N?' WHERE `entry`=26250;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. The Twilight\'s Hammer is an evil that we must fight anywhere we find them.' WHERE `entry`=26251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Is that... Is that the heart of one of the watchers? I\'ve heard stories about using one of these to power up a watcher for personal use. Of course I\'m really in no shape to try such things myself.' WHERE `entry`=26252;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We have our answers, $N. Let\'s report back.' WHERE `entry`=26254;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We must investigate your findings further, but we must not lose track of the fragment.' WHERE `entry`=26255;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They\'re keeping slaves here?  We ought to free them regardless, but perhaps they might also aid us in finding the forgemaster.' WHERE `entry`=26256;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='From what I\'ve heard, all you really need to do is find a suitable harvest golem and drop in the heart. Once you\'ve done that you should be able to take full control of the creature.$B$BI think there\'s a whole field of overloaded harvest golems west of here, at the Molsen Farm. Look for the arcs of electricity.$B$BShould you manage to get it working, use the golem to destroy the energized harvest reapers at the old Molsen farm. Those monsters are much more destructive than the ones on our farm.',`objectives_loc6`='Use the Harvest Watcher Heart on an Overloaded Harvest Golem and then use the Overloaded Harvest Golem to kill 25 Energized Harvest Reapers.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='It actually worked? That\'s incredible, $N. Hopefully that takes care of the harvest golem problem here in Westfall.' WHERE `entry`=26257;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This must be where the world pillar fragment was brought. Let\'s have a closer look.' WHERE `entry`=26258;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There is still great power present in his blood, $N. I can sense it even now. Yet there is also much corruption. I am not sure we can salvage the Earthwarder\'s essence from this.' WHERE `entry`=26259;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There is an entry for an upcoming meeting at the Upper Silvermarsh. This must be where the Forgemaster is.' WHERE `entry`=26260;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let us find this journal. We\'re getting close to the World Pillar fragment, I can sense it.' WHERE `entry`=26261;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, mon. A fine hero of the Horde you are.' WHERE `entry`=26263;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can\'t wait to give this new technology a try! We\'ve lost more gnomes to radiation than we can count. It\'s time to turn that around!' WHERE `entry`=26264;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What a relief! Thank you for your help. I hope that gadget Engineer Grindspark was working on helps get the airfield cleaned up permanently.' WHERE `entry`=26265;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I smell Westfall stew! Mother sent you!?' WHERE `entry`=26266;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Years ago, there used to be a Horde base deep within Skulk Rock. It\'s been abandoned since then, but it\'s still prime territory, worth reclaiming.$B$BThe problem is, it\'s full of oozes by now. They\'re nasty things... mindless, corrosive, eat anything they find.$B$BI need someone brave to go to Skulk Rock and get rid of those slimes. Are you brave enough, $N?',`objectives_loc6`='Kill 10 Jade Oozes.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to see you back... and not missing any limbs, either.' WHERE `entry`=26267;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They\'re still intact! There\'s a lot of memories in these crate. Let\'s see what we\'ve got in the first one... Hey, banana bread! And it\'s still fresh! Here, mon, I\'ll take this and you can pick something else.' WHERE `entry`=26268;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve certainly saved me a heap of trouble, $N!  I can\'t thank you enough. It shouldn\'t be long now until we see Master Nesingwary\'s book in libraries throughout the world! I\'ll leave a copy of the book right here, if you ever want to take a peek at the finished product. Thanks again, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26269;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Speak with Salma Saldean at the Saldean\'s Farm in Westfall.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak with Salma Saldean at the Saldean\'s Farm in Westfall.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Of course, dear. Our little girl works at Sentinel Hill and is very close with the homeless of Westfall. Perhaps she has overheard something. Before you go, let me wrap up the Westfall Stew and tell you a little bit about our dear little girl.' WHERE `entry`=26270;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have a kind heart, $N. You have done a good thing, today, and that act will reflect back upon you when judgment day comes.' WHERE `entry`=26271;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Anotha newblood, eh? Ya actually have an intense look about ya though. Fiery eyes. You might have the makings of a real $C. Lets not waste anymore time \'den.' WHERE `entry`=26272;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not bad, mon. Ya have a deep power in ya spells - you may have a talent for dis. Some rough edges ta be sure, but we\'ll get dose ironed out here and I\'ll teach ya a few new tings as we go.' WHERE `entry`=26273;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I tink I have something I can show ya. It\'s pretty simple really, but it should help.$B$BOne of da most basic forces we can be drawin\' upon is da ability to unleash demonic fire on our enemies, viciously burnin\' them and leavin\' them on fire for a time afta.$B$BTry it out. Let me know when ya tink you have it down.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Voldreka to train Immolate. Practice using Immolate 5 times against a Tiki Target.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, mon! Dis stuff come easy to ya.' WHERE `entry`=26274;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dese are some fine pelts, boy. We could make some hefty cloaks outta dese.' WHERE `entry`=26275;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ya handle yerself quite well. Ya gonna be quite powerful some day.' WHERE `entry`=26276;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ya tha new recruit everyone\'s talkin\' about, eh? Welcome ta tha Darkspear.' WHERE `entry`=26277;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Keep up the good work, $C. Hellscream\'s eyes are upon you.' WHERE `entry`=26278;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see you are good for more than simple egg-smashing duty. Good. The Horde can use a capable $R like you.' WHERE `entry`=26279;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work. Hopefully the raids will stop for now. I have one more task for you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26280;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' The Horde thanks you, $N. Grom\'gol is protected, if only for today.' WHERE `entry`=26281;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fascinating... How large did you say it was? I wonder if others could be found intact... This sample is excellent. I\'ll be sharing it with my fellow researchers.' WHERE `entry`=26283;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Fer a job like this, I normally bring me whole crew o\' demolitionists. With some help in settin\' up th\' powder, th\' charges, and th\' rest o\' th\' gear, the job gets done a lot faster.$B$BThose blasted troggs have me men caged all around Frostmane Hold. Now I\'m \'ere all alone without th\' personnel I need to finish th\' job.$B$BYou look like a capable $C, though. Would you find th\' demolitionists th\' troggs captured and break them out o\' their cages?',`objectives_loc6`='Free 6 Captured Demolitionists from their cages around Frostmane Hold.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have me own thanks and th\' thanks of th\' men you rescued. I\'ve already had th\' boys start setting up the gear down inside the cave. It should be ready to go soon.' WHERE `entry`=26284;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, now, that\'s more like it. We may get around to blowin\' up somethin\' after all.' WHERE `entry`=26285;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Helix? I\'ve heard that name before. Recently as a matter of fact, but who is this admiral?' WHERE `entry`=26286;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='We were once known as the People\'s Militia. These days, though, we fight under the banner of Stormwind, with the full support of King Varian Wrynn. Our goals here in Westfall are many: to clean up the mess left behind by the Defias, to expand the reach of the Alliance and to maintain order. So far we are failing on all fronts.$B$BTimes are worse now than when the Defias ran amok. Now with the indigenous gnolls of the region up in arms, we find ourselves backed into a corner. Help us, $N!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. You have provided us a temporary reprieve from the onslaught of gnolls, but there is more work to be done.' WHERE `entry`=26287;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. It will take the Riverpaw weeks to recover from the blow you just dealt. Please take an item of your choosing as a reward for what you have done.' WHERE `entry`=26288;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Helix is the one responsible for the gnoll attacks? He\'s inside. He\'s been there for days. I\'ve just been waiting for an excuse to bust him.' WHERE `entry`=26289;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What could possibly be going on in Moonbrook? I don\'t like this one bit, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26290;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Who IS this Shadowy Figure? We have to get to Moonbrook.' WHERE `entry`=26291;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The natives are restless, $N. I don\'t know what\'s going on, but homeless activity in this area has quadrupled in the past two days. If I didn\'t know any better I\'d say they were planning something...' WHERE `entry`=26292;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The "Worldbreakers" hide in a highland wilderness, squatting behind the Alliance kingdoms in the east. We will crush them, and we will do so with the mightiest army ever assembled since our victories in Northrend.$B$BI tasked our new goblin allies with the assembly of a host of war machines. Reports from the field reveal that their workmanship is sometimes... lacking.$B$BI will not go to battle with faulty machines. See Foreman Glibbs here in Orgrimmar and ensure my war machines are battle-ready!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Busy now. Go away. Wait, what? Hellscream sent you? What - uh - what can I do for you? Him? Us?' WHERE `entry`=26293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='<Glibbs mops sweat from his brow with a greasy handkerchief.>$B$BHellscream isn\'t happy with our work? Oh - we even NAMED the "Hellscream Demolisher" after him. This is very bad. My boys need to step it up.$B$BMaybe you can help set an example. A set of Hellscream Demolishers just rolled off the blocks and are ready for inspection. Give them a thorough going-over, and if you find any problems, give the Chief Engineer a good thrashing. Remind them that the eyes of Hellscream are upon them!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Instilled a little discipline in them, did you? Good, good! Everyone pulls their weight in my Horde, from the smallest peon to the proudest warrior. I tolerate nothing less. Our preparations for the invasion are almost complete.' WHERE `entry`=26294;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Propaganda',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='V? The only V I know is VanCleef, but he died many years ago.' WHERE `entry`=26295;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I haven\'t seen a red bandana in five years. Could this shadowy figure be attempting to reform the Defias Brotherhood?' WHERE `entry`=26296;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I could hear the cheers from here. It seems as if we\'ve got a huge problem on our hands, $N. We have to discover the identity of this shadowy menace before we enlist the aid of Stormwind. Perhaps there is another way...' WHERE `entry`=26297;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are good tusks, $N. You prove that you have the strength to hunt the Bloodscalps.$B$BAnd that is good, because you are not done hunting them.' WHERE `entry`=26298;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. I will inspect these heads to ensure poor Yenniku was spared the headhunter\'s axe.' WHERE `entry`=26299;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You place the head of Nezzliok within the cauldron...' WHERE `entry`=26300;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes. These will serve me well. When my spirit is freed, I will enter the Nether with some fine servants indeed! You are a credit to your $R clan, and you have appeased me.' WHERE `entry`=26301;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Zanzil the Outcast?? If Yenniku is held by that troll, a vile and powerful witchdoctor, then I fear that only a faint hope remains. Faint. And tiny as the smallest insect. Fortunately, I have some suspicions of my own. Suspicions which may lead to Yenniku\'s salvation.' WHERE `entry`=26302;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You retrieved the eye!  Your might is the stuff of legends, $N! And in getting the Eye, you must have defeated Mai\'Zoth and sent him to the Nether. That is why the spirits would not mention him before. It is good that he is gone from the world of flesh and bone, but now that he is in the realm of spirits...I fear he will begin a new reign. But that is a worry for another time.' WHERE `entry`=26303;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My mother\'s spirit rests well tonight, $N. As will I.' WHERE `entry`=26304;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done it!  You freed Yenniku from the will of Zanzil and the tyranny of the Skullsplitter, and completed the mission I had thought was so hopeless. Zanzil still looms a threat in the Cape of Stranglethorn, but for now, I at least know that the soul of my chief\'s son is free. Our tribe will remember your name in songs, $N, and we will etch your tale in stone so that it will live forever.' WHERE `entry`=26305;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N! Let the Vilebranch flee in terror from the sight of you!' WHERE `entry`=26306;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It won\'t be long until we\'re the only trolls left breathing on these walls.' WHERE `entry`=26307;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There are none left to oppose the Revantusk! Any stragglers will be quickly taken care of. You\'ve done my people a great honor, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26308;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='First the spiders and now this. I can smell the venom in this blood... it\'s the same as the skitterlings, but stronger. The Vilebranch and spiders... there\'s some potential here.' WHERE `entry`=26309;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh yes... I was wise to ask you to get these. How fascinating. Come here, my pretties. Into the bag you go.' WHERE `entry`=26310;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Twilight Assassins followed you to the bar? Here, in Orgrimmar? The Warchief won\'t be happy about this. Continue your preparations for the invasion and I will investigate.' WHERE `entry`=26311;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $C. Many Earthen Ring owe dere lives to ya dis day.' WHERE `entry`=26312;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dese are in surprisingly good condition - good work, mon.' WHERE `entry`=26313;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dat will slow their assault a bit while Norsala be findin\' a way to calm\'m. We\'ve no desire ta be remainin\' enemies of Therazane the Stonemother.' WHERE `entry`=26314;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yeah, mon... dat\'s about the reaction we were expectin\'.$B$BHe mentioned Diamant though? If da two don\'t get along, perhaps this Diamant be a bit less brash den Boden. At least it\'s somethin\'.$B$BLet me see if I can get da earth to tell me where we might be findin\' dis Diamant.' WHERE `entry`=26315;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It won\'t be tough to collapse th\' tunnel, but I\'m goin\' to need my team an\' my equipment \'afore I can get to th\' task.' WHERE `entry`=26316;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Bring the Lashtail Hatchling to Far Seer Mok\'thardin at Grom\'gol Base Camp.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, the little one seems to have taken a liking to you. I suppose that one raptor alone and raised among orcs is much less deadly than a whole pack of them. Keep her, $N... she may come in handy. In fact...' WHERE `entry`=26317;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I could feel th\' explosion way up here! My boys did a fine job riggin\' up that blast, but it wouldn\'t have happened without your help. It\'s only fair that I split my contract payment with you for helpin\' me finish th\' job.' WHERE `entry`=26318;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm, yes, perhaps I could be of some assistance. When I was in Northrend I helped the people of Valgarde uncover some of the mysteries of the vrykul by delving into the spirit world. Perhaps the same could be done here.' WHERE `entry`=26319;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='WHAT? VanCleef had a daughter?' WHERE `entry`=26320;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='She looks bigger already!  You can see, these raptors grow quickly. You are lucky to have found such a strong companion. Keep her by your side as long as you can, $N. I\'m sure she will prove to be an asset in the future.' WHERE `entry`=26321;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I will deploy a battalion of soldiers to Westfall at once! With the Defias Brotherhood reborn, an old threat to the kingdom is renewed.' WHERE `entry`=26322;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Return to Nimboya at Grom\'gol Base Camp and show him your Lashtail Hatchling\'s new skull.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='What do we have here?  A young raptor, and her pet $R. Hah! More importantly, what is that skull you have there?  This was no ordinary troll. He was big... ... and strong, too. Let\'s see what we can do with this one. Don\'t go anywhere.' WHERE `entry`=26323;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='We have a map of the Highland approaches. The plan is clear: we will show ourselves in force. The Dragonmaw orcs, on seeing the might of our combined forces on their shore, will have no choice but to ally with us in our crusade to destroy the Twilight\'s Hammer.$B$BThe fleet is assembling at Bilgewater Port in Azshara. I grow impatient with their progress.$B$B$C! You have a knack for greasing the wheels of my war machine. Seek out Warlord Krogg in Azshara and find out what\'s taking so long.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='What, another message from Hellscream? His patience is thinner than calf\'s hide. Have you ever worked with goblins before? Everywhere is another hidden cost! Our ships lie half-assembled and the air fleet is scattered to the winds. If this invasion is going to happen, I\'m going to need your help.' WHERE `entry`=26324;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Yes... yesss... My spirit is strong again, $R, and I am ready to return to the world. Now I need a body.' WHERE `entry`=26325;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey, mon! Thank ya for comin\'.$B$BWe weren\'t ready for dis kind of attack. We been expectin\' da Twilight Cult, but not elementals... we\'ve got no idea what upset dem so much that dey would turn on us like dis.$B$BYou haven\'t been out dere killin\' them, have you?' WHERE `entry`=26326;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well met! If you\'ve got a weapon on you, I\'ll take any help I can get clearing out these crazed fools!' WHERE `entry`=26327;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah... you must be the $R that I was expecting.$B$BYou have come on behalf of the Earthen Ring then?' WHERE `entry`=26328;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Splendid news! With the troggs taken care of, we should be able to turn our attention to Crushcog\'s troublemaking.' WHERE `entry`=26329;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $R. Only one more step remains before I may return.' WHERE `entry`=26330;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That should set back Crushcog\'s plans a bit, but we can\'t rest until he is defeated and Chill Breeze Valley is secure.' WHERE `entry`=26331;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Excellent work, $R. You and your raptor have done a great thing. Hakkar would be most pleased...' WHERE `entry`=26332;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Mekkatorque will be pleased to hear that you\'ve ruined Crushcog\'s plans to use our old weapons for his followers. Without the mechano-tanks under his command, he\'ll be weak and vulnerable.' WHERE `entry`=26333;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='$R. $R, $R, $R... you didn\'t think I was a friend, did you, $R?  Ah, ha ha haaaa!$B$BYou\'ve served your purpose. I\'ve returned to the realm of the living, and it\'s all thanks to you. So, instead of killing you, I\'m going to make you a deal instead.$B$BGive me the raptor.$B$BYou must already know that she\'s no normal raptor, and I need a replacement for Ohgan. Do it, or both you and the witch doctor will taste my rage.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m glad to see you\'ve come to your senses. Come and visit us in Zul\'Gurub sometime, $R. I\'ll be watching...' WHERE `entry`=26334;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahoy, $C. Any friend of Skuerto is a friend of mine. You\'ll find plenty of work needs doin\' around here. We\'re not sittin\' in this cove twiddlin\' our thumbs by choice.' WHERE `entry`=26336;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So they were trying to skimp on production costs? Unacceptable! I\'m glad you knocked some sense into them. If that foreman makes good on his word, our fleet will be ship-shape in time for the invasion.' WHERE `entry`=26337;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Balance is restored - for now. We may call on you again in the future, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26338;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, yes, Kelsey told me to expect you. There\'s still much to do before we can take on Crushcog.' WHERE `entry`=26339;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm?  Barnil\'s the name. And you are...?' WHERE `entry`=26340;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I\'ve scouted all over these highlands, $N, and there\'s one thing I\'ve found I haven\'t been able to explain.$B$BTo the northeast of here, there\'s a circle of stones, like the others you\'ll find everythwhere in Arathi... but the largest and most imposing of them, built into the mountainside itself.$B$BJust between you and me, I heard voices while I was there. Whispers of the earth. If you\'re the curious type, you could go see for yourself...',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Help...' WHERE `entry`=26341;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve given us just the opening we\'ll need to get the drop on Crushcog. Excellent work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26342;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These skins should do. Their quality isn\'t too important, given that they\'ll make up the inside layer of the boots, but it\'s still important that they\'re comfortable.$B$BIf they\'re a bit too rigid, I\'ll use some tiger blood to soften it up. Tricks o\' the trade, you know?' WHERE `entry`=26343;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My boots... they\'re like sausages, $N. Look great, taste great. I tell you they\'re filled with nothing but the finest ingredients and meats, and you eat it, and you love it.$B$BIt\'s safer--and more enjoyable--if you just trust me, and don\'t ask too carefully what\'s really inside.' WHERE `entry`=26344;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great! Thanks to your help I\'ll have this order filled and sent off to Director Riddlevox on the next boat to Undermine. Ahead of schedule, even!$B$BFor all your hard work, here, I made some extras, so take a pair. It\'s on Drizzlik.$B$BAnd remember, there\'s no boot so fine as one of Drizzlik\'s Excelsior line!' WHERE `entry`=26345;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Say no more, $N. I followed up with an... "old friend" while you were gone. I should\'ve known better than to send you to those shards. We\'ve both made a grave mistake in involving ourselves in this. Luckily, I "persuaded" my boy Gerrig to tell me what to do if this happened.' WHERE `entry`=26346;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Praise you, brave $C. The rocks of the Westfall Coast shall be lit thanks to your hard work. Many lives will be spared so long as the torch is kept lit.$B$BI died needlessly on this very shore. My afterlife plight is to see that no others follow my destiny.' WHERE `entry`=26347;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. You have quite a knack for combat. Thanks to you the Coast of Westfall is a safer place.' WHERE `entry`=26348;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So the foul heathen, Murk-Eye is dead. Well done, $N. By your hands one life was laid to rest but perhaps many more were saved. The Great Sea, wrought with danger as it is, shall be a wee bit safer this night thanks to your heroics.' WHERE `entry`=26349;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Mandokir is alive, yes. You are responsible, yes. You may be able to stop him still, yes.' WHERE `entry`=26350;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You bring feathers, yes. You can follow directions, yes.' WHERE `entry`=26351;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A fuel regulator?  This seems important. At least, I hope it is. We may not have ended the Venture Company\'s operations, but we at least slowed them down. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26352;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The footlocker slowly creaks open. Sand and water seem to be its only contents. But wait! A small crab scurries out with a clue to the treasure in his claws!' WHERE `entry`=26353;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, treasure hunter!' WHERE `entry`=26354;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re on your way to the jackpot, treasure seeker!' WHERE `entry`=26355;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The hinges on the old chest are rusty but they still work. You force the chest open and take the booty.$B$BCongratulations!' WHERE `entry`=26356;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Such a pretty site ta see the enemy\'s hopes burnin\'...' WHERE `entry`=26357;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' What? The Captain said WHAT? It\'s HIS fault this big beast of an engine is delayed.' WHERE `entry`=26358;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What did Priestess tell you? The raptor is daughter of Ohgan, heir to Mandokir\'s seat. Hah!' WHERE `entry`=26359;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! I should have this here engine samophlanginated within the hour.' WHERE `entry`=26361;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Speak with Chiyu',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Escape from Zul\'Gurub' WHERE `entry`=26362;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dead? All of them, around the altar? And you found these spider idols on them... A mass sacrifice. They threw their lives to Shadra.' WHERE `entry`=26363;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'re finally free of Razlo Crushcog and his interference! With the defeat of Crushcog and his forces, Thermaplugg can\'t afford to send any more of his followers to the surface. I can\'t wait for the day when we defeat him for good!' WHERE `entry`=26364;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Heard Westfall was in some deep doody. Well, we got our own set of problems here. See them gnolls out there? Looks like they\'re actin\' up again. I don\'t like it. Don\'t like it one bit.' WHERE `entry`=26365;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The look of fear and confusion on his face... this is what he deserved! Let\'s make sure all the Vilebranch wear the same look.' WHERE `entry`=26366;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I wish I could have been there to see it, $N! I\'ll have to hear the story from Ongo\'longo himself when this is over.' WHERE `entry`=26367;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Mmm, yes... that old nostalgic smell. You\'ve done well for the Forsaken, and the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=26368;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The parts scattered, the keepers separated... I see. This is a ritual to summon Shadra. They must not have gotten far. It should be destroyed...' WHERE `entry`=26369;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Five years of work burned to the ground in five minutes. Damn the Defias! And this is only the beginning, $N! We have a long, hard road ahead of us.' WHERE `entry`=26370;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Aye... I used to be flesh and blood, just like you, lad. That is, until that fateful day when the murlocs attacked the lighthouse...' WHERE `entry`=26371;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My airship has engines? At last! Now we can rip the heavens a new one! Once the ground and naval forces are ready, we\'re going to light up the skies over the Twilight Highlands.' WHERE `entry`=26372;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='If Gnomeregan Covert Operations is recommending you, then you must have made quite an impression. Your help will be most welcome here, as we\'ve a wealth of enemies and few enough mountaineers to face them.' WHERE `entry`=26373;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N! Most of my soldiers have already reported for duty, some a little worse for the wear. One night in Bilgewater makes a hard orc humble. Still, fresh fighting in the Twilight Highlands should restore discipline.' WHERE `entry`=26374;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are a generous $R. You give back to the earth that offers you so much. You have my respect. You shall surely have the respect of the Stone Lords with time.' WHERE `entry`=26375;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I have observed you, $R.$B$BYou do not fear shedding Twilight blood.$B$BIn this, I am willing to extend you some degree of trust.$B$BIt is a start.$B$BAll things in time.' WHERE `entry`=26376;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Time brings respect to all.$B$BThe smallest pebble.$B$BThe largest mountain.$B$BThe most stubborn cultist.' WHERE `entry`=26377;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Murder, rookie. That\'s what you\'re looking at on the ground in front of us.' WHERE `entry`=26378;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These look promising. I\'ve heard great things about the Short and Stout Brewery, but I haven\'t had the chance to try their ale until now. While you\'re here, relax a little. If you need a spare hearthstone or wish to make Kharanos your home, just speak to me and I\'ll be happy to help.' WHERE `entry`=26380;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m pleased, $N. That was quicker than I expected.' WHERE `entry`=26381;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, good. Just put them over there, I\'ve got my hands full.' WHERE `entry`=26382;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Did the sentinels send you? Thank Elune. We need everyone we can get.' WHERE `entry`=26383;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Bring the Tablet of Shadra to Darkcleric Marnal.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, what have we here... Fascinating. Quite fascinating.' WHERE `entry`=26384;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='It seems you have your first charge. You must travel back down to Rut\'theran Village, where we first arrived, and speak to Vesprystus to secure a ride to Lor\'danel.$B$BOnce in Lor\'danel, aid the night elves in any way that you are able. I am trusting you to treat them with the reverence that they deserve in light of all that they have done for us.$B$BI must travel to the distant city of Stormwind to meet with King Varian. I hope to see your face again very soon, $N. Until then, a fond farewell.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Our allies have come to our aid? Thank Elune. Tyrande was wise to extend open arms to your people. We need help. We need everyone we can get.' WHERE `entry`=26385;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Surkhan',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' It would seem that Jin\'do has survived, and he is rallying his brothers to once again summon Hakkar into this world. It was good of you to come to speak with me. There is not much we can do now but to wait, and watch. Jin\'do is weak, and prime for striking, but I must wait for word from Rastakhan before issuing orders. Until then, you and your raptor will have to wait.' WHERE `entry`=26386;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now we\'ve got a win-win situation. The spiders are going to either starve off, or find some dwarves and elves to replenish their larder, since my colleagues and I would make a poor meal.' WHERE `entry`=26387;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is a disaster, $N! Our air fleet was decimated. And reports are coming in that our navy was attacked - unprovoked - by the Alliance in open water. And what of Hellscream? Is the Warchief dead?' WHERE `entry`=26388;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Blackrock orcs will surely fall now that their main force has been defeated! Only one task remains.' WHERE `entry`=26389;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With Kurtok slain we are safe once again from the orcish hordes. I will send peasants to the pass in an attempt to seal the passage so that no more orcs may come through into our territory. You have the thanks of Stormwind and of the Alliance, hero!' WHERE `entry`=26390;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Bless your heart, $N. You truly are a hero of the Alliance! Though the land is completely incinerated and there is nothing left of the vineyard but ash and debris, I still might be able to recover. Right? How bad can it be?' WHERE `entry`=26391;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have to get this note to Stormwind? That\'s not a problem, you can take one of my gryphons!' WHERE `entry`=26393;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, a note from Smith Argus?  I\'m not surprised he needs more gear. There are so many new recruits these days. Well thank you, $N. Here\'s some money to cover your travel costs.' WHERE `entry`=26394;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A crate for Goldshire, eh?  People sure are getting lazy. Have you been to Goldshire before?  If so, then it\'s no problem, my friend. I have plenty of gryphons trained to fly that route!' WHERE `entry`=26395;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great, you brought the armor!  We\'ll get this divvied to those who need it immediately. Thank you, $N. Your efforts have been a great help to us. And now that you\'re no stranger to gryphons, I hope you\'ll come and lend your aid to Goldshire often!' WHERE `entry`=26396;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Much has changed outside of Mulgore, $N. The world is torn, and our Horde allies have turned down dark paths. We must guide them. Even in the darkest hour, we will bravely hold our heads high, and honor the Earth Mother in all we do.$B$BYou must go, $N, and be this example. Go to Orgrimmar. Tell Warchief Hellscream how the Grimtotem were driven out. Let him know our pride and discipline, our strength and sorrow.$B$BTal at the Skytower will send you on your way. Go in peace, and never forget your people.',`objectives_loc6`='Take the Mark of Bloodhoof to Garrosh Hellscream, located in Grommash Hold in Orgrimmar.$B$BYou may speak with Tal the Wind Rider Master to travel there, or wait for the zeppelin.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Grimtotem forced from Mulgore... if Baine speaks for this, you are indeed a fierce warrior. From this day, your strength is no longer your own. It belongs to me, and the Horde, as a weapon of war. Hellscream\'s eyes are upon you, $N. Victory or death!' WHERE `entry`=26397;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='You have fought bravely alongside me, $N, and done much for my people. If every $R could be as noble, the future of the Horde might not disturb me so much.$B$BI would ask you to ease my worries further. Go to Orgrimmar. Tell Warchief Hellscream how the Grimtotem were driven out. Let him know our pride and discipline, our strength and sorrow.$B$BTal at the Skytower will send you on your way. Go in peace, friend.',`objectives_loc6`='Take the Mark of Bloodhoof to Garrosh Hellscream, located in Grommash Hold in Orgrimmar.$B$BYou may speak with Tal the Wind Rider Master to travel there, or wait for the zeppelin.' WHERE `entry`=26398;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Say... have you heard about the ogres?  I got a hot tip from some fella\' named Mok\'thardin that some $R schmuck in a ridiculous $C getup found this ogre hand, and...$B$B<Skeezy trails off as he looks you over.>$B$BWhat was I just saying?  Oh yes... some $G SWASHBUCKLING HERO: BREATHTAKING HEROINE; found this ogre hand, and Mok\'thardin thinks it means that the ogres have some special artifact. I\'ve seen them guarding a chest up in some ruins behind their mound. Care to fetch it for me?',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Those ogres really know how to close a treasure chest, I\'ll tell you what. A box is useless to me, hero. We\'re going to need to find a way into this crate.' WHERE `entry`=26399;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Whaaaaaa?!? I\'m... I\'m going to have to send this to... to Flem... in the south. He\'ll know what to do with it.' WHERE `entry`=26400;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='How horrible... for someone so young and full of promise to fall to demons! I beg your forgiveness for sending you into danger as well, $N. I hope you don\'t cross paths with that demoness again...' WHERE `entry`=26401;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Telaron has already sent word of you, $N. I\'m interested in seeing if you\'re half as skilled as he claims.$B$BI am fighting a war on multiple fronts, while keeping our currently held areas properly defended, as well as overseeing the instruction of our youngest sentinels. If you\'re a decent fighter, there will be plenty for you to do.' WHERE `entry`=26402;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great!  Wonderful!  I can get a bundle for these!! That Venture Company sure picked the wrong jungle to mine in, didn\'t they?  We\'d all be in better shape if they moved out of here.' WHERE `entry`=26403;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Skeezy sent you to the right place. Welcome to Hardwrench Hideaway!' WHERE `entry`=26404;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='As promised, your reward. You do the troll nation proud.' WHERE `entry`=26405;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There it is... only one left.' WHERE `entry`=26406;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Strange indeed. I will pass this on to my contacts in the east, near the Mosh\'Ogg\'s main camp. I have a feeling that they\'ll be interested in these strange scars. You have my thanks, $R.' WHERE `entry`=26407;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good to see a new face around here! The forest crawls with Horde, but my assignment requires that I keep this outpost safe. I could really use someone who might be up for a good fight.' WHERE `entry`=26408;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hiya! Lend a hand, would ya, bub?' WHERE `entry`=26409;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good thing that I just happen to be a grand master of all things explosively alchemical. This won\'t ignite on its own, though.' WHERE `entry`=26410;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Looks like that did it. He should come to any moment now. I told you I was a grand master of alchemy! I\'ve got some extra resin leftover. I can make it into all kinds of explosively wonderful stuff. What do you want?' WHERE `entry`=26411;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We are honored by Flint Oremantle\'s presence. I am given to understand that the Stonefather is in possession of a fragment of the World Pillar. It is imperative that we recover all of the fragments. The instability between worlds is increasing. Soon it may become too great even for mighty Thrall to hold at bay.' WHERE `entry`=26413;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice work $N!  I see you are quite the fisherman these days. Might just have to take you out on the boat soon and see what you can really do!' WHERE `entry`=26414;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hah!  That Cromula cracks me up. Oh, right, Stranglethorn. You\'re really going?' WHERE `entry`=26416;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Glad you could make it!  Let\'s get to work, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=26417;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes... it\'s finally time. Shadra will be ours!' WHERE `entry`=26418;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellently done. You have served the Dark Lady well today, $N. This virulent blood will supply our armies with all manner of powerful weapons against the disgusting Alliance. We will wipe them from these lands. For the Horde, of course... and all thanks to you.' WHERE `entry`=26419;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Those look like some nice bass, $N. Let\'s fry em\' up and see how they taste!' WHERE `entry`=26420;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. You\'ve probably heard others speaking of Operation: Gnomeregan. Let me tell you a bit about what happened and why we left the dwarven city of Ironforge.' WHERE `entry`=26421;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. You\'ve probably heard others speaking of Operation: Gnomeregan. Let me tell you a bit about what happened and why we left the dwarven city of Ironforge.' WHERE `entry`=26422;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. You\'ve probably heard others speaking of Operation: Gnomeregan. Let me tell you a bit about what happened and why we left the dwarven city of Ironforge.' WHERE `entry`=26423;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. You\'ve probably heard others speaking of Operation: Gnomeregan. Let me tell you a bit about what happened and why we left the dwarven city of Ironforge.' WHERE `entry`=26424;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to meet you, $N. You\'ve probably heard others speaking of Operation: Gnomeregan. Let me tell you a bit about what happened and why we left the dwarven city of Ironforge.' WHERE `entry`=26425;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The ground rumbles slightly as you approach the cave. This looks to be the entrance that Diamant and Felsen spoke of.>' WHERE `entry`=26426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='All right, help me get tied to the wheel.' WHERE `entry`=26427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You stand before me as a figure of vengeance, and I bow down before you in thanks.$B$BWith that cow\'s death, and knowing that their seed will no longer spread over the face of Azeroth, I can put my energy into something more lucrative. I hope you looted their farmstead after you finished them off.' WHERE `entry`=26428;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The signs of war are upon your garments, and sweat drips from your brow. Good, very good indeed.' WHERE `entry`=26429;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Not all forest trolls are foul nuisances like the Witherbark. North of here in the Hinterlands is Revantusk Village, home to the only forest troll tribe still allied with the Horde.$B$BEven they cannot escape the cruelty of their bretheren. The Vilebranch tribe wars with them, distracting them from our battle with the Alliance.$B$BYou have fought well here. Speak with Urda if you wish to fly to Revantusk. Their village will have use of your strength.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome to Revantusk, $C. I hope fighting the Witherbark hasn\'t exhausted you; the Vilebranch are even worse.' WHERE `entry`=26430;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome, $C. We\'re gonna make the Vilebranch regret ever crossin\' us.' WHERE `entry`=26432;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Ahh... do you know how hard it is to get fresh water in Stranglethorn?  It\'s no wonder that the nagas guard their shrine so ferociously! Oh, right... your artifact, and clarity. Clarity... I\'ve got it!' WHERE `entry`=26433;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Excellent work, $N!  These reagents will serve perfectly.' WHERE `entry`=26434;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fascinating! I\'ll need some time to study this. Why don\'t you have a look around Booty Bay and come back later?' WHERE `entry`=26435;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Entrenched',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Diamant says you are to be trusted. Diamant is patient and wise, so I shall allow you to prove yourself.$B$BAs it happens, I could use hands that are more... mobile.' WHERE `entry`=26436;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahh... invigorating. Thank you, fleshling.' WHERE `entry`=26437;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Intervention',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve proven useful, $R.' WHERE `entry`=26438;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='$R. If you act in the service of the Stone Lords, there are those that might aid you.$B$BWatch for the Stonebound. They lie dormant all around the Shuddering Spires. It should not take much prompting to rebind them to service against the flayers.' WHERE `entry`=26439;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Clingy',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The stones in Pebble\'s body bounce up and down happily. He seems very appreciative.>' WHERE `entry`=26440;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve made a friend, have you?$B$BAre you certain you want to feed him? He might become attached.' WHERE `entry`=26441;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Looks like the traps are working!  Thanks $N!' WHERE `entry`=26442;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='By the Seven Crystals of Ata\'mal, this cannot be! They plan to attack Forest Song?! Not on my watch! No. We will not allow this to happen!' WHERE `entry`=26443;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have my respect and thanks, $C. Perhaps we\'ll be able to create a new home here without having to worry about the Burning Legion yet again.' WHERE `entry`=26444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Never again will the Burning Legion threaten Ashenvale! You have delivered us from a fight we very likely would have lost, $C. I give you thanks, $N, and the deepest gratitude of the Hand of Argus. It honors me to have you at our side!' WHERE `entry`=26445;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good. Though it may take a great deal of your years for the seedlings to grow into ancients, in the fullness of time they will aid us in our fight against all of the enemies of Ashenvale.' WHERE `entry`=26446;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dreadlords!  They plan to attack us here at Splintertree Post?! Not while I still draw breath! No. We will not allow this to happen!  They are a blight upon our world!' WHERE `entry`=26447;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s better!  There\'s nothing quite like ridding our world of a demon. And they make for worthy opponents as well, unlike the weak races of the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=26448;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Never again will the Burning Legion make slaves of the orcs, or any other race of the Horde!$B$BBravely fought, $C! You have the true heart of the Horde beating inside of you! You give us much honor!' WHERE `entry`=26449;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice work, $N. Now I\'ve just got to decide what to do with all of these...' WHERE `entry`=26450;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $R!  Did you feel it?  The rush of the melee?  The true risk of free-for-all combat? As today is your first day here, I\'ll let you perform in one more competition for another reward. If you return in the future, you may compete again, once a day. Your rewards will, of course, improve as you become stronger.' WHERE `entry`=26451;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $R!  I look forward to seeing you fight again soon.' WHERE `entry`=26452;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to see another new arrival here at Forest Song.$B$BVindicator Palanaar is sending as much help as she can muster and each set of hands is appreciated.$B$BTake a look around, $C. It may not be much now, but with time and help from our night elf allies, we\'ll build a settlement worthy of calling home. There is much to be done here and any help you can provide would be welcome.' WHERE `entry`=26453;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wood warped by foul demonic magic is of no use to the draenei at Forest Song. Nothing sound can be built with it, but I shall purify it and return it in good time to Architect Nemos and his people for their use. Some good will come from this tragedy, after all.' WHERE `entry`=26454;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. There is certainly a latent power here, one that not even constant exposure to the corruption of the satyr can dim. Do you see how it still shines, after all these years?' WHERE `entry`=26455;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for delivering this report, $C. From what Sentinel Melyria writes, it seems our worst fears have come to pass. With each advance we make, the Horde appears more determined to do as much damage as possible. We can\'t afford to back down; the fate of our ancestral lands hangs in the balance. With more people like you on the frontlines, I\'m certain we could triumph. Will you join our fight? A new front has just opened in Warsong Gulch to the south.' WHERE `entry`=26456;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='At last we have sent a message that the orcs won\'t dare ignore. Any overseer or foreman who sets foot within the camp to replace Gorthak will feel my wrath! We must press our advantage, $N, and never rest until the Warsong Lumber Camp is a distant memory and a glade of trees stands upon that ground. Now what was this about explosives...?' WHERE `entry`=26457;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not bad for a city-dwellin\' $R. Good show, aye!' WHERE `entry`=26462;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='A friend of mine from Astranaar, Raene Wolfrunner, asked me to send a scout west to Lake Falathim. Teronis left days ago, just before the Horde attacked.$B$BHe was searching for an item he thought could slow the furbolg attacks on our people--a rod created by a now-dead, evil wizard.$B$BBefore he left, he mentioned a gem for the rod. Unfortunately, we know that the lake has been invaded by some evil force.$B$BPlease, $N, find my friend.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Teronis\' body lies broken atop the small rise next to the Keeper. Deep slashes crisscross his corpse.' WHERE `entry`=26463;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is terrible, $N. Teronis is dead?! The time for mourning will come, but for now we must focus our efforts. I will send some of the Sentinels to recover Teronis\' body and to assist the keeper. You have the gem that Teronis was seeking? It must be delivered to Astranaar.' WHERE `entry`=26464;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s quite a few that you have found! Thank you, $N! The old city of Zoram holds many secrets, and these statuettes may be the key to many of them.' WHERE `entry`=26465;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You found the ring! Thank you, $N. Please take this as payment, and know that your deeds today will remain forever in my memory.' WHERE `entry`=26466;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Judging by the gaping wound in her side, Anilia is on the verge of death.' WHERE `entry`=26467;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Anilia died? No... that can\'t be! It was just yesterday that we were running and playing together in the woods.$B$BI guess those days are over...' WHERE `entry`=26468;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, kind $R. My sister\'s spirit is gladdened by your efforts.' WHERE `entry`=26469;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N! With the befouled elemental numbers thinned and Tideress put back into the lake, we should be able to launch a counter-offensive on Silverwind Refuge. Just as soon as we\'re done with defending the spire....' WHERE `entry`=26470;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Rest in peace, my friends. I felt the anguish of the Dor\'danil Barrows lessen, and knew that you had completed your task. It was grim work that you did, $N, for the spirits you destroyed were merely victims of the Horde\'s evil. But with their destruction, let us hope the maddened spirits will finally find peace.' WHERE `entry`=26472;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you have the hair! This is a good first step. There are other ingredients that we will need, but the hair of the fallen Ancient could well be the most important. I only hope that whatever the Forsaken are devising from the plant will not be turned into a weapon. We simply do not have the numbers to remove them right now, especially with Maestra\'s Post under attack!' WHERE `entry`=26473;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is from Orendil? His skill with herbs and healing is great! This cure gives me hope, when before I had little....' WHERE `entry`=26474;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, you found it! Odd... it looks tarnished somehow. I will place the tear in a stew, and pray that it will cure her. Thank you! Thank you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26475;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, Raene sent you? It must be serious indeed. What can I help you with?' WHERE `entry`=26476;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m pleased to see you\'re back, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26477;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The last piece of the rod is held by druids of the claw. I asked their leader, Oso Bramblescar, to give it to me, but he and his guardians nearly killed me! Clearly they too were affected by the Horde\'s corruption of the Forest Heart.$B$BBut, I have an idea for how you can get into Oso\'s cave and grab the pommel.$B$BEver since I was a faun, I\'ve been pretty good at playing possum. It works great against bears! I can teach you! Go east to the Shady Nook, and if they try to get you, just use my technique.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You got it? Wonderful for you... and for Raene! I guess we\'ll have to see about reassembling it, won\'t we?' WHERE `entry`=26478;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve recreated the rod Teronis had set out to find? That\'s wonderful to hear. Shael\'dryn has been indispensible in her assistance. Teronis would be proud to see his quest is continuing even after his tragic passing. Now it is time for us to make use of its power to eliminate the enemies of Ashenvale!' WHERE `entry`=26479;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Use Dartol\'s Rod to be able to communicate with Krolg at Krolg\'s Hut in Ashenvale.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, yes... you appear as one of my kind, but I care not what you truly are if you can help the furbolg. The night elves and now the orcs have visited many atrocities upon my people. Corruption runs through our veins, corruption brought down upon us by the prideful night elves and the warlike orcs. They are the ones who did this to our people... They are the ones I blame for being cast out of my tribe. At night I can still see the campfires burning in the darkness.' WHERE `entry`=26480;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, my friend. Now quickly, hand me Ran\'s skull. While his essence yet taints it, we shall fashion it upon Dartol\'s Rod giving you the power to influence my brethren and deliver them from evil!' WHERE `entry`=26481;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, you used the skull of the furbolg king to modify the power of Dartol\'s Rod? You then used that power to convince the captured furbolg to rise up and attack the Horde at Silverwind Refuge? I am more than pleased and impressed with your abilities, $N. The Sentinels cannot thank you enough. It should be a simple matter for us to sweep away the orcs and retake the refuge now! Teronis would be proud. You have my deepest respect.' WHERE `entry`=26482;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Gan\'dranda',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now that\'s what I like to hear! Good on ya.' WHERE `entry`=26483;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Stonefather\'s son, Flint, sent you? No time to talk. We must prevent a second front from opening up on the war!' WHERE `entry`=26484;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, nice an\' fresh. I\'ll get those going while you fetch me some more goods then...' WHERE `entry`=26485;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s the stuff! Wouldn\'t want any trolls or goblins gettin\' pleasure out of these, now would we! Maybe I can work a bit of this into my next brew...' WHERE `entry`=26486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey hey!  Not bad, not bad at all!  You may have a future in resource acquisition. Or hotel management.' WHERE `entry`=26487;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Arnold and I used to relax down at the moat in the Valley of Heroes. One day, I lost my locket in the lake and I have never been able to find it. Rumor has it that huge royal monkfish live in that moat and that they eat anything!  I know its a long shot, but do you think you could catch a few monkfish and look for my locket?$B$BPlease let me know right away if you find it, it\'s very precious to me.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You found it!  I can\'t believe it was down there all those years!  You have no idea how much this means to me $N.' WHERE `entry`=26488;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew you had it in you, boss-man. You know what they say: You can take the $R out of the islands, but you can\'t take the murderous tendencies out of $N.' WHERE `entry`=26489;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Look at it! That\'ll put some oomph into the mix!' WHERE `entry`=26490;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Years ago, there used to be a Horde base deep within Skulk Rock. It\'s been abandoned since then, but it\'s still prime territory, worth takin\' for our allies!$B$BProblem is, it\'s full of dwarf-eating slimes and oozes. Those things are slightly less disgustin\' than trolls, but they\'ll still give us a hassle.$B$BWith our boys tied up fightin\' the Revantusk, I need you to go to Skulk Rock and clear the place out for me.',`objectives_loc6`='Kill 10 Jade Oozes.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to see you back... and not missing any limbs, either.' WHERE `entry`=26491;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Looks like it\'s still good inside! Huh... is that banana bread? Still fresh! Here, lad, take your share of goods.' WHERE `entry`=26492;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great!  These look... disgusting. But probably pretty valuable. Let\'s get to splitting these up. Some for me, some for Jasper, some for Chabal...' WHERE `entry`=26493;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ll file these away for now. Maybe we can experiment later. Yeah, you\'ll do.' WHERE `entry`=26494;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Chabal',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You have my thanks. I have been waiting for you to approach me, $R. I have identified you as the most promising $R here in this strange town. I have a task for you, if you would be willing to take it.' WHERE `entry`=26495;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well met, $N! We\'ve got a lot of trolls to kill and only so many hands to do it with!' WHERE `entry`=26496;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Aye, we\'ll have these trolls cleared out yet.' WHERE `entry`=26497;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It won\'t be long until we\'re the only dwarves left breathing on these walls.' WHERE `entry`=26498;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have my thanks, $N. You\'ve made all the difference, and the fate of these cowardly stone trogg ambushers is set in stone. Now we must get about the business of retaking Stonehearth.' WHERE `entry`=26499;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not a bad start, though you\'ll have to destroy more of them than that if you\'re going to rescue the Stonefather. A lot more.' WHERE `entry`=26500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is good. We no longer need to worry about stone trogg attacks from the rear. Let\'s see what you can do for us on the front.' WHERE `entry`=26501;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Barracks sealed',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Shrine sealed' WHERE `entry`=26501;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Those\'ll do. Just put them down over there. I\'m going to have something for you to do in a moment. Maybe.' WHERE `entry`=26502;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew it! Looks like Yowler is behind this uprising - which is incredible, because we keep killing gnolls named Yowler. I don\'t know how many sons the original Yowler had, but it\'s got to be close to a hundred. Well, looks like we got ourselves another Yowler to kill. Magistrate Solomon must be notified.' WHERE `entry`=26503;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A job well done deserves a reward, wouldn\'t you say? Don\'t spend this all in one place, $C. Better to spread it around, if you catch my drift.' WHERE `entry`=26504;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Oh, you\'re not Conacher. What have you got there? Oh for pity\'s sake. Yowler? AGAIN?' WHERE `entry`=26505;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='PERFECT! I\'ll put these in the pot right away. Dinner should be ready in a few hours. Thank you, darling!' WHERE `entry`=26506;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Pebble leaps upon the pile of petrified bats and rolls around in them, seeming to forget that you exist entirely. Perhaps for the best, if Kor\'s warnings are to be trusted.>' WHERE `entry`=26507;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for finding my necklace mister $C... you are very kind! My kitty thanks you too - isn\'t that right Effsee?' WHERE `entry`=26508;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Finally the menace is laid to rest!  Thank you, $N, you have done me a great service. The garden shall be in full bloom this season!' WHERE `entry`=26509;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! Let me make a few adjustments here and we should be good to go.' WHERE `entry`=26510;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That ought to teach those murlocs a lesson. Hopefully the next time they decide to raid our town they\'ll think twice. We both know that won\'t happen.' WHERE `entry`=26511;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Can you hear me, $N? Is this thing on? Ah, yes, I see you there now. Let\'s get to work!' WHERE `entry`=26512;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, citizen. Without you, we would have starved or worse, been forced to go out and get food for ourselves.' WHERE `entry`=26513;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Good work, $N. I\'ve just been handed some important information. It would appear that our most hated enemy, the Blackrock orcs, have wised up... I\'ve transferred a few silver over to you for the gnome, erm, gnoll kills.' WHERE `entry`=26514;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ain\'t that a hoot! Wish I could\'ve seen it myself.' WHERE `entry`=26515;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'ve cleared straight through \'em! Jintha\'Alor is as good as wiped out!' WHERE `entry`=26516;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dead? All of them, around the altar? And you found these spider idols on them... It\'s Shadra. The Spider Loa! They\'re trying to tap her power!' WHERE `entry`=26517;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s one ugly mug. Maybe he was takin\' other heads tryin\' to find a prettier one!' WHERE `entry`=26518;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='<Upon touching the orb you hear a faint click.>$B$B<You remove the orb from the pedestal.>$B$BYou now control the orb, therefore you now control the ettins. Maybe you can use an ettin to remove the huge boulder currently crushing Foreman Oslow over at Lakeshire. Find an ettin and use the orb on the ettin. Then head over to Lakeshire.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You used an ettin to remove the boulder that was crushing Foreman Oslow? Incredible work, $N! Oslow will be grateful once he regains his composure.' WHERE `entry`=26520;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The elements dance, and fire consumes. Let the flame show \'em the cost of their wickedness!' WHERE `entry`=26521;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='By Kurdan\'s beard... these don\'t look like any spiders I\'ve seen before. Dark magic\'s at work here.' WHERE `entry`=26523;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This isn\'t just blood... it\'s venom! Spiders... venom... I hope I\'m wrong about my hunches here, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26524;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good riddance. May those horrid things never walk these lands again.' WHERE `entry`=26525;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A tablet! If I can read this... this is a ritual to summon Shadra herself into this world, and a list of the idols needed. You\'ve done a good job slaying the keeper and getting ahold of this, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26526;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. We\'ll be knockin\' on this bug\'s door in no time.' WHERE `entry`=26528;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There it is... only one left, lad.' WHERE `entry`=26529;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is it, lad! We\'re ready!' WHERE `entry`=26530;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Talonaxe and the boys are right behind. Let\'s do this!' WHERE `entry`=26531;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done a great thing for the Wildhammer today, $N. I wish Falstad could\'ve been here for that. On behalf of the whole clan, I\'d like to repay you for keeping these lands free from that foul shadow. You\'ve earned this reward.' WHERE `entry`=26532;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This mixture is... I don\'t understand it. Perhaps we need to run some clinical trials.' WHERE `entry`=26533;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You don\'t say!  Well, that certainly is interesting. In that case... Forget understanding how the stuff works!  I gotta get my hands on that recipe!' WHERE `entry`=26534;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is fascinating!  Just think of all the applications! Just so we\'re clear, I\'m not thinking about using this to make an army of slaves or anything like that. No, no... I\'m much more interested in the ogre explosions!' WHERE `entry`=26535;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These perch look great $N. Why don\'t you join us for a fish fry tonight?' WHERE `entry`=26536;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s a good dent, but it\'s clear to me that we\'re going to have to handle this a slightly different way.' WHERE `entry`=26537;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' If it is Zaela\'s wish, then you shall have your supplies. Just don\'t tell the Dragonmaw Warchief...' WHERE `entry`=26538;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m glad you\'re here, $C. Perhaps a seasoned veteran of the Horde\'s campaigns in Northrend and elsewhere can talk some sense into the Dragonmaw leadership...' WHERE `entry`=26539;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dragon\'s Blood!? We best not tell our red dragon allies that we\'ve used these. Still, it\'s powerful magic... We\'ll have our fighting force back in no time.' WHERE `entry`=26540;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='By order of his royal highness, King Varian Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Gryphon Master Talonaxe at the aviary in Aerie Peak.$B$BOur new brothers in the Alliance need your help to fend off the aggressive Horde offensive in their beloved homeland. Travel north from the Arathi Highlands, through the dwarven mountain pass and follow the road northwest to Aerie Peak.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome to Aerie Peak, $N. On behalf of High Thane Falstad, I thank ye for comin\' to help us.' WHERE `entry`=26542;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Looks like you found the clams, $N. These will do nicely.' WHERE `entry`=26543;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Just put the missive in the little compartment and I\'ll read it. I am fluent in orcish. It looks like these orcs are here under the direct command of Yowler. That means Yowler must have the orc invasion plan.' WHERE `entry`=26544;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Shadowhide army!? Damn those orcs to hell! These invasion plans speak of a massive build up of orcish and gnoll forces in the east. Looks like Gath\'Ilzogg, the Blackrock general, is preparing to march his armies across Lakeshire and attack Stormwind directly!' WHERE `entry`=26545;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Treat them with respect, and they\'ll treat you with it as well. Give \'em guff and you\'ll be out an eye!' WHERE `entry`=26546;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Much appreciated, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good to see you out here! Let\'s get to it.' WHERE `entry`=26548;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Madness',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wake up, $N! We don\'t have much time. I rescued your gear for you. At least now you\'ve seen the foolishness of our leader first-hand. His blood is contaminated, his rage is unquenchable -- and he\'ll destroy us all trying to defeat the Horde!' WHERE `entry`=26549;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is as I suspected. Zanzil is too haughty to interfere with the squabbles between the Bloodscalps and the Skullsplitters. No, he is playing a part in a grander scheme... Jin\'do the Hexxer is using him to help bring Hakkar back to Zul\'Gurub. It\'s good that we found this out now, because it offers us a simple solution.' WHERE `entry`=26550;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I ask you to slay Zanzil the Outcast, a lowly, hermetic exile of the Gurubashi, and what do you do?  You dash headfirst into the Gurubashi capital and eliminate one of their High Priests!  Very nearly two!  Only one word suffices to explain such a rash and foolhardy endeavor: Heroism. Jin\'do the Hexxer still walks within Zul\'Gurub\'s walls, but he lost one of his legs when you crushed Jeklik. Today\'s battle is ours.' WHERE `entry`=26555;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice work $N. These samples will help us figure out what is going on in that toxic soup over there.' WHERE `entry`=26556;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Outstanding!  Those sandy carp are picky eaters aren\'t they?' WHERE `entry`=26557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Marnal draws close... and Shadra even closer. Prepare for bloodshed.' WHERE `entry`=26558;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Jorgensen',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I know where they\'re holding Krakauer and Danforth. We gotta hurry. They were prepping those two for a sacrifice!' WHERE `entry`=26560;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Krakauer',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wha... Where am I? What happened? Messner? Jorgensen? OH MY GOSH! We have to get to Danforth! It might already be too late!' WHERE `entry`=26561;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='About damn time you sissies showed up. My arms were gettin\' tired.' WHERE `entry`=26562;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Unbelievable work, $N. You\'ve managed to rescue the entire Bravo Company from the clutches of the Blackrock orcs? With Keeshan\'s team rescued and Keeshan\'s belongings returned, there\'s no way Keeshan could refuse us.' WHERE `entry`=26563;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well then. Maybe you\'re okay after all. Alright, alright... don\'t get all bent out of shape. Just give me a few moments with these parts.' WHERE `entry`=26564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So the high tinker himself has heard of my little project? Splendid! I\'ve almost finished my latest prototype, but maybe you can help me chase down those last few parts.' WHERE `entry`=26566;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='John J. Keeshan',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Help you? Help these people? These people that would rather spit on me than crack a smile?' WHERE `entry`=26567;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I\'m not giving up on him, $N, and I\'m not giving up on Redridge. We need to boost his spirits... Rouse the slumbering monster within him!' WHERE `entry`=26568;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fantastic work, $N! These will come in handy for our next project, the Lakeshire SUPER BRIDGE, meant to traverse the length of Lake Everstill. It should be done in 20 or so years. Give or take a decade or two.' WHERE `entry`=26569;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve probably bought us another day, maybe two. Nice work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26570;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Come in, $N. Do you copy? Troteman here! Great job on getting Keeshan\'s weapons back! Now there\'s one final mission you have to run. Are you up to the challenge?' WHERE `entry`=26571;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='You heard of the golden stonefish, $N?  The thing with these fish is that they can\'t be caught by normal means. They have jaws so strong that they snap right though any hooks or lures you try to use on \'em.$B$BYou can find a number of them in Thunder Ridge, south of Orgrimmar. That ridge used to be full of thunder lizards, but they all drowned in the flood.$B$BTake my knife, swim down there and cut off their tails. You should be able to use the tail to zap any stonefish you find.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice one, $N!  I tell ya, golden stonefish are not easy to come by so this is a nice treat.' WHERE `entry`=26572;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hope with these items and with his crew all rescued he\'ll have a change of heart. We can\'t do this without Keeshan.' WHERE `entry`=26573;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome to Shadebough, $N. Lady Shandris sent word of you.' WHERE `entry`=26574;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $R. You\'ve done all that I can ask of you. I shall impart my favor for you to the Stonemother.$B$BMay the stone beneath your feet hold you steady during your quest for the World Pillar.' WHERE `entry`=26575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Greetings, $R. I have been told of your coming. If you wish to aid me, then perhaps I can be of aid to you as well.' WHERE `entry`=26576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are Diamant\'s chosen. So small. So fragile. Do you realize that your actions shall be the basis by which your entire, "Earthen Ring" is judged? You truly think you can stand for so many? You are a fool. A confident fool. We shall see if you are a capable fool as well.' WHERE `entry`=26577;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Doomshrooms',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have appealed to Diamant. He is patient. Trusting. Perhaps too much so. You have much to prove if you wish my favor, $R. Still, this is a start.' WHERE `entry`=26578;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You carry with you a certain degree of potency. I can find some respect for such strength, especially in your kind. My concerns are not yet abated. Not for the source of the overgrowth, and not for you.' WHERE `entry`=26579;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is good to see you again, brother. I see that your efforts go well. The Stone Lords appear to be showing you some degree of trust. We\'ve come to help. We might be of some aid in tracking down the source of this sudden growth. I highly suspect your giant friend\'s aggressions are focused in the wrong direction.' WHERE `entry`=26580;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You let the mist touch your skin? I hope there weren\'t any adverse affects.' WHERE `entry`=26581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The stone troggs? And I am to trust you at your word? I have no love for the Verlok anyway. Suspicion is more than enough reason to lay waste to them. We shall see if your word is true.' WHERE `entry`=26582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $R. Gorsik shall hear of your deed. Therazane shall hear of your deed. You are quite vicious for one so small... and so soft.' WHERE `entry`=26583;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done fleshling. Your presence complimented my brothers well.' WHERE `entry`=26584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So your words prove true. You have my gratitude, $R.' WHERE `entry`=26585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Keeshan? You mean JOHNNY\'S ALIVE? You bet your sweet behind I\'ll help, but first you gotta get me out of this damned cage.' WHERE `entry`=26586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Are you up for a challenge, $N?  Good, I was hoping you would be. The southfury river flows just west of Orgrimmar and your challenge can be found within its mighty flow.$B$BWe are looking for a giant furious pike. This esteemed fish used to be prevalent in these areas but ever since the floods hit, the big ones have been much harder to find. Head out to the river and let\'s see just how good of an angler you really are.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N, you got one!  It\'s a rare day that I get to see such a strong, beautiful fish.' WHERE `entry`=26588;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Peace, friend. I wish we could have met under less troubling circumstances.' WHERE `entry`=26589;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Ahh... do you know how hard it is to get fresh water in Stranglethorn?  It\'s no wonder that the nagas guard their shrine so ferociously! Oh, right... your artifact, and clarity. Clarity... I\'ve got it!' WHERE `entry`=26590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='If you ever get tired of your being a $C, come look me up. You seem very good with those fleshy hands of yours.' WHERE `entry`=26591;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Yes, these will do. Now to perform the analysis... Oh, you\'re still here?  You don\'t think I\'m a fraud or something, do you?' WHERE `entry`=26592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ack! Where\'d you get these? No, don\'t tell me. I don\'t want to know!$B$BWho sent you? Sea Wolf?' WHERE `entry`=26593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Heh heh, well done! And when you showed Shaky those giblets, how hard did he shake?$B$BHah! He\'s so easy to read, when I play cards with him I can\'t help but win!$B$BThanks for your help, $N. Now it\'s your turn to get paid...' WHERE `entry`=26594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Kill-Collect',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great! I can get a good price for these, especially for what\'s inside Maury\'s foot! Thanks much, $N!$B$BI hope those three learned their lesson: don\'t bet something you can\'t afford to lose.$B$BAnd maybe it\'s too late for them, but...they should be careful of who they gamble with.' WHERE `entry`=26595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yeah?  Whaddya need?' WHERE `entry`=26596;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='...feel strength returning.... Where might I be?  Booty Bay?  Oh my!  I had the strangest dream... ...the weakness has not completely left me....' WHERE `entry`=26597;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='temp text 02 - description',`objectives_loc6`='temp text 02 - log',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Witch Doctor Unbagwa like Gorilla Fangs!  For you I talk to spirits. Make Mokk the Savage come. You protect Witch Doctor Unbagwa from other Gorilla-beast though or no Mokk for you!' WHERE `entry`=26598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You found it!  What a glorious day for ol\' Hecklebury, this is. Getting back my chest cools some of the fire in me. But my revenge isn\'t complete...' WHERE `entry`=26599;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This wasn\'t expensive, was it?  Well, here\'s some pieces of eight to reimburse you. Now let\'s get onto this revenge, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=26600;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Mok\'rash... Negolash... Gorlash... they\'re all gone. I suppose I have no excuses now. I can return to the high seas and a life of pillage and booty!  And it\'s all thanks to you. Now I just need to get myself a ship...' WHERE `entry`=26601;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can\'t believe my fortune, $N!  Meeting you has turned my luck to the better, make no mistake there! If I ever get a new ship and you\'re looking to sail the seas, you would be my honored guest.' WHERE `entry`=26602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Have you come to free me?' WHERE `entry`=26603;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s about time you returned. I was beginning to worry that I was going to be eaten while you hunted. A cat eating a princess... wouldn\'t that be a fancy feast?' WHERE `entry`=26604;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Looks like it\'s all here. Alright, I think I\'m ready to be rescued now.' WHERE `entry`=26605;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N, you have saved me from a great dishonor. If it was within my power, I would offer you a place among my tribe. But for now, all I can only offer you is this token for the courage and nobility you have shown.' WHERE `entry`=26606;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' My bow... and knife! Where did you... Jade\'s amulet... My darling Jade. We got orcs to kill.' WHERE `entry`=26607;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Fel Orcs from Outland have laid claim to the Dragonmaw? Obscene! If Hellscream knew what was happening here, he\'d raze their city to the ground...' WHERE `entry`=26608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='On top of the barrel, you discover a map with some hastily written text on it, along with some coins.' WHERE `entry`=26609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Sure, I remember you, $C. Back from scouting I see....' WHERE `entry`=26610;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Bloodsail Buccaneers attacking Booty Bay?  This isn\'t the first time that those blaggards have tried something. Booty Bay is impenetrable! Sounds like they might be changing their strategies up, though. Wouldn\'t put it past Firallon to try something crazy. Very well, let\'s see what else they\'re up to.' WHERE `entry`=26611;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect, $N. Now that we know their plan, it\'s just a matter of time.$B$BAnd to think the fools have dropped anchor just off the cape....' WHERE `entry`=26612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good show, $N! And just before I need to ship out too! Can\'t thank you enough, old friend.' WHERE `entry`=26613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Shiver me timbers and timber me shivers!  Ye found me beautiful eye!  Let\'s see if she still fits. $N ho!  Blimey, I can see!!' WHERE `entry`=26614;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s orc killin\' time.' WHERE `entry`=26616;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That coin!  Where did you get it? Bruce... yes, I see. He was one of the Blackwater Raiders once. One of us, before Greymane closed the Gilneas ports and held his crew captive. I know that what happened in Gilneas changed the people there, but I never expected them to change their loyalties. Especially not Bruce. If you wouldn\'t mind, could I keep the coin?  I\'ll pay its worth in gold.' WHERE `entry`=26617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Don\'t go thinking that was too easy. Far greater dangers lurk deeper in the woods.' WHERE `entry`=26618;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N, what are your people doing? Are you attacking the Dragonmaw or are you here to rid us of Mor\'ghor\'s corruption? Ah, I see now. I like the way you think. Warchief Mor\'ghor won\'t even know what hit him. Let\'s do this!' WHERE `entry`=26619;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Mmm-mmm! The skirtsteak\'s the best part. It\'s not an efficient way to cook, though. Here, have this recipe. It\'s a little different, but flank meat\'s easier to come by when you really need a meal.' WHERE `entry`=26620;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Insurrection',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'ve lost a lot of good orcs, but the fight is going our way, $N. Mor\'ghor\'s regime is collapsing. All that remains is to destroy the beast himself.' WHERE `entry`=26621;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N! You have done the Horde proud in my absence. The Dragonmaw have joined us, with Zaela as their new leader. Blood was shed, but casualties were low, and we have their complete loyalty. Our Horde grows stronger!' WHERE `entry`=26622;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah yes, a nice lump you have there!  Let me just get this seasoned with my secret spices (no looking!) and get them to skittering on a skillet for a while... And, although Dusky Crab Cakes are my specialty and I won\'t give out the recipe, here\'s the recipe for a dish that\'s almost as good.' WHERE `entry`=26623;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yarr, ya made a good decision, lad.' WHERE `entry`=26624;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Finally, we can move forward and rescue the Stonefather.' WHERE `entry`=26625;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, welcome, stranger. I\'d offer you something, but there\'s not much here... Could I beg you to run some errands for a poor old hermit?' WHERE `entry`=26627;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We survived the attack!$B$BWe could not have done it without you, $N.$B$BWe\'ll be heading out as soon as the tide rises. If you weren\'t such a promising hero I\'d offer you a place on my crew. But I can tell you have bigger fish to fry.$B$BEven if you are a puny $R....' WHERE `entry`=26628;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well blow me down!  Now there\'s something ya don\'t see too often. Welcome aboard, $N. Plunder and booty await ye.' WHERE `entry`=26629;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That should fool that Bloodsail dimwit. This was fun, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26630;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes... yes... I see... well, everything appears to be in order. Slayer of the great Seahorn, eh?  That doesn\'t matter on MY ship. Only thing you\'re gonna be slaying is deck stains. Grab a mop.' WHERE `entry`=26631;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Word of your prowess has spread ahead of you, $R. Let\'s see if you can help us keep these fungal horrors off of the front.' WHERE `entry`=26632;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I heard the most furious mopping sounds from down here, mate. That\'s EXACTLY what your Captain likes to hear.' WHERE `entry`=26633;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ll distribute these right away, $R. And I\'ll see what I can do to put in the good word for you.' WHERE `entry`=26634;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks, $N. I\'d been hearing whispers about "Pretty Boy" and a "boo-box". I don\'t think I want to go in the boo-box.' WHERE `entry`=26635;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice job, rookie. I\'m gonna go ahead and put the camo in the box. We should be ready soon.' WHERE `entry`=26636;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect. Those orcs won\'t know what hit \'em - literally. I\'ll need a few minutes to get these in working order and then I\'ll put them in the Bravo Company field kit.' WHERE `entry`=26637;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great work, $N. We need to move quickly before they send for reinforcements.' WHERE `entry`=26638;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Brubaker is dead. It looks like the orcs are attempting to send a message with this grizzly display. Upon closer examination you notice something in Brubaker\'s pouch.' WHERE `entry`=26639;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' DAMN IT! This just got complicated. We\'ve got prisoners of war to rescue before we can blow up the valley. Not to mention the orcs have black dragons on their side. Are you ready, $N?' WHERE `entry`=26640;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ll see these are burnt to ash right away, and scattered to the winds for good measure.' WHERE `entry`=26641;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A fresh recruit from Orgrimmar is it? I\'ll take what I can get. Keeping the roads open has been a nightmare.' WHERE `entry`=26642;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A grim task for sure, $N, but it\'ll keep the spiders left alive from recovering. I thank you.' WHERE `entry`=26643;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So ye be the one that did ol\' Seahorn?  Yancey sent word, but I wanted to make sure he hadn\'t been telling his tall tales again. I\'ll make it brief. Ye did well on Keelhaul\'s crew, but I expect ye to do even better on mine. I\'ve got an entire fleet to attend to, so you\'ll be helpin\' to run the day-to-day of me ship. Welcome aboard the Crimson Veil, sailor.' WHERE `entry`=26644;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Splendid, $N. For your service to the people of Darkshire you shall be rewarded.' WHERE `entry`=26645;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Looks like the P.O.W.s are free. Time to initiate Operation: End All.' WHERE `entry`=26646;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I like the cut of your gib, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26647;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. The eternal battle wages on, but we\'ve tipped the scales in favor of the pirates today. Firallon will be happy to hear the news.' WHERE `entry`=26648;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahahaha!  Blasted \'em clear off their rigging!  I\'ll drink to that! You\'ve got a bright future, kid.' WHERE `entry`=26649;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You see a set of plans unrolled on the table. They explain everything! These are the details of the impending attack on Booty Bay. Battle formations, plans of attack, and something about a group called the "Brashtide Crew".' WHERE `entry`=26650;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='And now, we blow the whole damned thing up.' WHERE `entry`=26651;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What is this? A comb? It\'s lovely! And it glides through my hair as if it weren\'t the stiff, stringy horror that it is.$B$BOh, if only I had a mirror...' WHERE `entry`=26652;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, Ghost Hair Thread is what you need, is it? I\'m afraid I have none in stock, but I can make some for you...if you can supply the ghost hair.' WHERE `entry`=26653;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can make a spool of Ghost Hair Thread with this, and have a few strands to spare. Here are some coins for those extra strands.' WHERE `entry`=26654;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Delightful! This will do splendidly...$B$BHere, good $N, take this as payment for your honorable deed.' WHERE `entry`=26655;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done. Of my main strengths, speed is not one.' WHERE `entry`=26656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not just fast it seems. You have some bite in you.$B$BWell done, $C.' WHERE `entry`=26657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Glorious.$B$BNow we will deal a blow to the stone dragons that they will remember for the next hundred years.' WHERE `entry`=26658;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Impressive, fleshling. You are far more capable than I initially assumed.$B$BI will extend that sentiment to the Stonemother as well.' WHERE `entry`=26659;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You need some Zombie Juice, do you? Hmm...that\'s some strong stuff - I don\'t usually get requests for it.' WHERE `entry`=26660;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Gather 5 Rot Blossoms from Tranquil Gardens Cemetary.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, you got the rot blossoms. I\'ll whip up the zombie juice... it\'s strong stuff, I warn you.' WHERE `entry`=26661;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Brashtide Crew aren\'t just pirates... they\'re worgen pirates!  And they\'re joining in on the attack! Revilgaz is definitely going to want to know about this.' WHERE `entry`=26662;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve set the pirates back several days\' work. Hopefully this will delay their attack.' WHERE `entry`=26663;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The fewer Bloodsail Buccaneers that Booty Bay has to fight, the better. However, it might be best to stop slaughtering your supposed allies before you draw suspicion to yourself.' WHERE `entry`=26664;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Brashtide!?  I thought they were dead and gone YEARS ago! No, that absolutely makes sense. And it\'s not good news either. The Brashtide are formidable foes, and if their numbers are anywhere near what they were before they disappeared, we\'re in for a nasty battle.' WHERE `entry`=26665;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='By the light... you actually went and got it? I\'m shocked. I suppose I owe you thanks for returning it to the archives.' WHERE `entry`=26667;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Detonation',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Did you see those orcs explode? THAT\'S HOW WE DO IT IN BRAVO COMPANY! Now to clean up the rest of these jackasses.' WHERE `entry`=26668;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This was all you found? That\'s bad news, I\'m afraid...' WHERE `entry`=26669;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You actually went and got it?! I don\'t know whether to call you brave or insane. But once again, my archives thank you.' WHERE `entry`=26670;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can\'t thank you enough... I had hoped for this to be a joyous reunion, but the more I learn, the less glad I am to have asked. But I must know.' WHERE `entry`=26671;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='How interesting. It\'s been quite a while since I\'ve seen such a ring...' WHERE `entry`=26672;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='REUSE - BREADCRUMB' WHERE `entry`=26673;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I\'m afraid I cannot give Tobias the answers he seeks. But I can help you find the only person who can...$B$BStalvan Mistmantle.$B$BTake the ring into the woods to the east, to Manor Mistmantle, where Stalvan\'s body was buried. Enter, and hold the ring before you. Let the waning moon pour its light through the ring, and the spirits will answer your call.$B$BTake heed, $N. The questions of the living can offer more comfort than the answers of the dead.',`objectives_loc6`='Use the Mistmantle Family Ring at Manor Mistmantle, east of town.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Master Harris may have been right. I would have been better to leave the past behind. I\'ve got a new life now. Whether it\'s that of a monster or a man is up to me. As for you, I cannot thank you enough for your assistance, regardless of the outcome. Please, take this with my thanks.' WHERE `entry`=26674;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A thousand thanks, $N. You warm an old man\'s heart with your foolish-...I mean...with your kindness!$B$BHere you are, friend. Take this as a token of my gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=26676;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, thanks. These will do just the trick!' WHERE `entry`=26677;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This must be the doublerum. You pour a glass for Revilgaz, then consider pouring one for yourself...' WHERE `entry`=26678;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' AH!  Much better, $N. Now, let\'s get down to business. I believe that you and I have a town to save.' WHERE `entry`=26679;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank the Nec-...well, thank YOU, $N! You have more than earned your reward.$B$BAha! Happy! Happy nights ahead!!' WHERE `entry`=26680;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You fool! You\'ve doomed us all!' WHERE `entry`=26681;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. We\'ll be able to focus on greater threats here now.' WHERE `entry`=26682;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Why yes, I used to own a looking glass.' WHERE `entry`=26683;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Most superb! This will work perfectly. Many thanks!' WHERE `entry`=26684;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='At last!  The stargazing device is complete!  Thank you, $N. Now I can continue my research. . .' WHERE `entry`=26685;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The people of Darkshire thank you, $N. You have proven yourself to be a great ally of The Night Watch.' WHERE `entry`=26686;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What now, soldier? Reinforcements? For the Barrens? We\'ve been bleeding supplies and men there for months! Does someone need to remind Twinbraid of the attack on Northwatch? Our losses at Honor\'s Stand? What happened to the men I sent to Triumph Hold? We\'ve nothing to spare! Listen $N, if you want to help out our cause, you\'ll focus your efforts here in Dustwallow. Between the deserters and the Horde encroachment... we could use a hand.' WHERE `entry`=26687;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Impressive, $N. It would seem that you are capable enough to handle yourself. Perhaps a more suitable challenge could be found for one of your abilities.' WHERE `entry`=26688;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You performed well against the Shadow Weavers, $N. But even now, years after their first arrival, there seem to be so many to replace the ones we kill. I will put my faith in Master Carevin. No doubt he will get to the bottom of the problem.' WHERE `entry`=26689;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N, to be honest with you, I did not believe that you would get this far, but you are clearly a $C to be reckoned with. In fact, if you wish to formally join Master Carevin\'s struggle, I will gladly write for you a letter of recommendation.' WHERE `entry`=26690;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excuse me for my cold reception, $N, but as I\'m sure you can tell, I am an extremely busy man. I see that you have impressed Calor--and I assure you, that is no small feat--and that he has given his recommendation.$B$BThere are unsavory types afoot, $N, and we can use the help of all who have proven themselves. We battle against demons, the undead, and those who would provide them aid. Be vigilant, be wary, and trust none who would not give aid to our cause.$B$BGlory under the Light.' WHERE `entry`=26691;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'re closing in on the Blackrock high command. There\'s nowhere left for those dogs to run.' WHERE `entry`=26692;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Now that the easy part is over, it\'s time for phase two.' WHERE `entry`=26693;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='He teleported away? Mentioned Darkblaze? What the hell is going on here. Looks like it\'s time to strap in and finish this nonsense.' WHERE `entry`=26694;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You brought them!  I\'m beginning to think the tide is turning in our favor, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26695;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yeah?  What can I do for ya?' WHERE `entry`=26696;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hope those mongrels know how to doggy paddle! Actually, I take that back.' WHERE `entry`=26697;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I should have known these Brashtide were alive and up to no good. I\'d written them off years ago.' WHERE `entry`=26698;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We need to keep moving, $N. Booty Bay won\'t hold out for much longer.' WHERE `entry`=26699;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Attacking your former crewmen... You really have grown into a real pirate, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26700;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lok\'tar, $R. Welcome to Brackenwall.' WHERE `entry`=26701;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N!  You\'re awake!  We found you bobbing in the harbor, shortly after the remaining attackers had turned tail. We were worried about you for a while there... I\'ve been meaning to thank you, $N. Not only did you provide us with the intelligence to prepare for this attack, but you helped fight off the Bloodsail AND the Brashtide. Your name will always be remembered here in Booty Bay. We here in Booty Bay pride ourselves on our booty. Care to take first pick?' WHERE `entry`=26703;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Endgame',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='We did it, $N. We\'ve started the evacuation. If we leave soon we\'ll leave the Forsaken fleet in the dust.' WHERE `entry`=26706;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, $C... and I\'m sure the worgen that may be returned to sanity with the potion this will make would thank you too.' WHERE `entry`=26707;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='AHHHHHHHHHHHH! AHHHHHHHHH!!!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='The only thing left to deal with now are the orcs holding out at Stonewatch Keep.' WHERE `entry`=26708;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I am returning to my throne. I\'ve no desire to see any more of these Earthen Ring, but you remain welcome here, $R. If you wish to help us rebuild our realm, perhaps we can help you in return.$B$BAll things in time.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You returned. This is good. The Stone Lords have been asking after you.' WHERE `entry`=26709;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well. Now that these are rocklings are free to learn our ways, they will grow tall and strong. One day, we will extinguish the gyreworm infestation from our realm, and these rocklings shall no longer be plagued in their youth.' WHERE `entry`=26710;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, it\'s you, ma\'am! Sorry, I didn\'t recognize you at first with all of these commoners milling about. You people cool your heels! $N is here! Here are your macaroons, ma\'am. Come back anytime if you need more.' WHERE `entry`=26711;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, it\'s you, sir! Sorry, I didn\'t recognize you at first with all of these commoners milling about. You people cool your heels! $N is here! Here are your macaroons, sir. Come back anytime if you need more.' WHERE `entry`=26712;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Come in, $N. Are you there? If you can hear me: Blackrock has the upper hand. I repeat. Blackrock has the upper hand. GET BRAVO COMPANY OUT OF TH...' WHERE `entry`=26713;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' They died in defense of the Alliance. In defense of our kingdom! Heroes, all of them, and they will be laid to rest as such.' WHERE `entry`=26714;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Sounds like a close call! But he ran off without harming you further... He might be still fighting it. Master Harris must know!' WHERE `entry`=26717;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome to our humble camp. I wouldn\'t call it pleasant, but it\'s at least somewhat private. Beg your pardon? A worgen at the farm?' WHERE `entry`=26719;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve got him! No time to lose, then. We\'ll prepare to administer the serum right away. JITTERS! Get ready!' WHERE `entry`=26720;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh thank you, thank you! You\'ve saved me from having to go out in the woods with those awful things! At least for a day, that is...' WHERE `entry`=26721;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='His clothes and bloodstains? If it\'s not tricks, it\'s something worse...' WHERE `entry`=26723;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s heartening to see one so recently recovered be so concerned with the plight of others. Sven spares himself suffering by not dwelling on his own misfortune.' WHERE `entry`=26724;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They will never be forgotten, $N. What you and the rest of Bravo Company sacrificed in order to save Redridge will be a tale told for ages to come. While I can in no way make up for the loss of your friends, I feel that you must be rewarded for such a heroic deed. These are Keeshan\'s possessions - the only things we found when we dredged the lake for his body. Troteman has informed me that Keeshan would have wanted you to take something as the lone surviving member of Bravo Company. Remember them, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26726;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank the light, he\'s gone... I\'ll say you\'ve made amends by helping save the lives of those here, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26727;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are the help that we requested? I suppose you will have to do.' WHERE `entry`=26728;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These will do for my purposes. Though we can\'t activate the altar with bracers alone...' WHERE `entry`=26729;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We have what we need. Are you ready to activate the Altar of Naias, $N?' WHERE `entry`=26730;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My colleagues within the Kirin Tor will be happy to learn that the heart is ours. Thank you for your assistance, $N. I couldn\'t have done it without you.' WHERE `entry`=26731;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. Now, let\'s see what they\'ve got in this elixir of theirs...' WHERE `entry`=26732;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This will do. Please hold on for a moment while I test this out.' WHERE `entry`=26733;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I knew they\'d have some more of this substance. I\'m going to send this to my contacts at Fort Livingston, to the south. Hopefully they\'ll have some more luck with it. Thank you for everything, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26734;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They KILLED him?  And all this time, I thought he had them underneath an iron bootheel...' WHERE `entry`=26735;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. It looks like my suspicions were correct... the three prisoners seem to have escaped the affliction that gripped Kurzen and the rest of his men. Before you arrived, Emerine teleported them over to Stormwind to get cleaned up after their ordeal. They promised to return soon.' WHERE `entry`=26736;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Marvelously executed, $N. My men and I can handle the rest. With Kurzen out of the picture, we may be able to continue our original expedition here in Stranglethorn, which was... ahh... No matter. Please, feel free to peruse our armor stores. You may find something that fits you well.' WHERE `entry`=26737;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Bring the Lashtail Hatchling to Corporal Sethman at the Rebel Camp in Northern Stranglethorn.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, the little one seems to have taken a liking to you. You\'re lucky... at this age, the raptors are calm, peaceful, and easily trained. Keep her, $N... she may come in handy. In fact...' WHERE `entry`=26738;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='She looks bigger already!  You can see, these raptors grow quickly. You are lucky to have found such a strong companion. Keep her by your side as long as you can, $N. I\'m sure she will prove to be an asset in the future.' WHERE `entry`=26739;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh I see, it\'s a Krazek\'s Crock Pot! An ingenious piece of work, but it can break a spring or throw a gear now and then. Let me see what\'s wrong with this one...$B$BAha! Its steam charger is rusted out, it has a cracked knuckle-gasket and its fobulator is missing teeth. I\'m surprised the pot could even boil a turnip in this state!$B$BCan I fix it? Of course I can fix it!$B$BBut there\'s a price. Oh yes, there is always a price...' WHERE `entry`=26740;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I think I can read this text... Fascinating! Tsul\'kalu, Mahamba, Pogeyan... what are these names?' WHERE `entry`=26742;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='First you save me from the madman\'s jail cell, and now you bring me some keys to understanding trollish shamanism. This is turning out to be a pretty good week! Thank you again, $N. I will see to it that you have the support of the Wildhammer clan as you continue on your journeys.' WHERE `entry`=26743;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='To be honest, I\'m sending this information home to Stormwind, for my wife and son. They love to hear about what I\'ve been doing out here in the jungle, and I only get to visit so often. Every little bit helps. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26744;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Report to Osborn Obnoticus at the Rebel Camp and show him your Lashtail Hatchling\'s new skull.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='What do we have here?  A young raptor, and her pet $R. Hah! More importantly, what is that skull you have there?  This was no ordinary troll. He was big... ... and strong, too. You know, I\'ve been meaning to try my hand at some troll magic. How hard could it be?  Let\'s use this strong fellow as a test subject, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=26745;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These will provide a bit of... what\'s the troll word?  Voodoo?  Juju?  Tiklabang? It doesn\'t matter. If we\'re going to re-build a troll, we need troll magic, and these fetishes are full of it.' WHERE `entry`=26746;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $R. We have a head, a body, and some juju-voodoo-mojo nonsense. Now, just a little shock of electricity to get things started, and...' WHERE `entry`=26747;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='$R. You just resurrected your worst nightmare. You didn\'t think I was a friend, did you, $R?  Ah, ha ha haaaa!$B$BYou\'ve served your purpose. I\'ve returned to the realm of the living, and it\'s all thanks to you. So, instead of killing you, I\'m going to make you a deal instead.$B$BGive me that raptor.$B$BYou must already know that she\'s no normal raptor, and I need a replacement for Ohgan. Do it, or both you and the gnome will taste my rage.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m glad to see you\'ve come to your senses. Come and visit us in Zul\'Gurub sometime, $R. I\'ll be watching...' WHERE `entry`=26748;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Mandokir is alive, yes. You are responsible, yes. You may be able to stop him still, yes.' WHERE `entry`=26749;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you\'ve come. Fleshlings just like you killed my daughter... my only daughter. With no provocation. Not sated at stripping me of my family, more of you flocked to Deathwing to serve him in ravaging my home. You\'re quite arrogant to come before me asking for MY help. I\'m tempted to crush you where you stand.' WHERE `entry`=26750;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Balance is restored - for now. We may call on you again in the future, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26751;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ya\'ve done well, brotha. Da Stonemother be listenin\' and da World Pillar is not far from our reach.' WHERE `entry`=26752;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='May the disgusting monster stay dead this time! I\'ll head down there and scatter his remains to ash myself, $N. You\'ve done a great thing; perhaps in time Duskwood can return to its former peaceful state.' WHERE `entry`=26754;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s a great start, $N, but we\'re going to need you to fly over into the town and stir up some trouble.' WHERE `entry`=26755;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Success... Finally! I can\'t thank you enough for giving me the chance to work the cure myself. Our new friend may be in need of some help as well. You might want to speak with him.' WHERE `entry`=26760;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I heard about the Defias making a return. Terrible news. I wish I had better news, but it would appear that Lakeshire is under attack! We are losing citizens left and right. Our own guards are spread far too thin to handle the situation. We need a hero to step up!' WHERE `entry`=26761;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That was a nice bit of work, $N. With our constructs back up and running behind their main lines, it\'s only a matter of time now before we make the big push through and rescue the Stonefather.' WHERE `entry`=26762;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These will work fine. Just a moment please. All fixed!' WHERE `entry`=26763;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s fixed!  This is great, now I can get dinner started!  Thanks so much, $N. I hope Krazek didn\'t give you too much trouble.' WHERE `entry`=26765;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That should be enough to lure the beast, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26766;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let\'s see if the snare can ground something larger than a drake.' WHERE `entry`=26768;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Gazlowe calls this 10%? You tell him I\'m going to weigh these! I suppose he expects me to pay you a delivery fee, as well? Fine, fine. Have some spoils!' WHERE `entry`=26769;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A few less stone troggs is always a good thing. Glad to see that you\'re a decent $C after all. We\'ll soon know the exact location where they\'re keeping my father captive. Hope you survive until then.' WHERE `entry`=26770;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. Here\'s to hoping the trap performs as well when we try it on Abyssion.' WHERE `entry`=26771;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You bring feathers, yes. You can follow directions, yes.' WHERE `entry`=26772;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What did Priestess tell you? The raptor is daughter of Ohgan, heir to Mandokir\'s seat. Hah!' WHERE `entry`=26773;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Speak with Chiyu',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Escape from Zul\'Gurub' WHERE `entry`=26775;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Ghaliri',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' It would seem that Jin\'do has survived, and he is rallying his brothers to once again summon Hakkar into this world. It was good of you to come to speak with me. There is not much we can do now but to wait, and watch. Jin\'do is weak, and prime for striking, but I must wait for word from Rastakhan before issuing orders. Until then, you and your raptor will have to wait.' WHERE `entry`=26776;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have brought peace to those who knew only misery, $N. Be proud.' WHERE `entry`=26777;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The cries grow softer for now. Light bless you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26778;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='As promised, your reward. You do the troll nation proud.' WHERE `entry`=26779;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can see the difference already. I can\'t wait until later tonight, when I get to perform my observations again!' WHERE `entry`=26780;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You retrieved the eye!  Your might is the stuff of legends, $N! And to think my brother and sister said we wouldn\'t find anything of worth here in the Vale. Hah!  And I\'m just getting started!' WHERE `entry`=26781;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This... this is not like what I expected. I had thought it would be a... a... Ahem!  I\'m sorry. I\'m not sure what came over me. I\'ll be sending this south, to the Explorers\' League Digsite in the Cape. Maybe they\'ll know what to do with it...' WHERE `entry`=26782;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This... this is not like what I expected. I had thought it would be a... a... Ahem!  I\'m sorry. I\'m not sure what came over me. I\'ll be sending this south, to the Explorers\' League Digsite in the Cape. Maybe they\'ll know what to do with it...' WHERE `entry`=26783;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are perfect! The restless waters of that troubled river will now do much more than move silt or stone... They\'ll move you across continents. Finish up the rest of your business here in Dragonmaw and then we should be able to proceed.' WHERE `entry`=26784;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Tobias is staying in town still? Master Harris warned him not to pursue his brother\'s fate. We all lead new lives now, after all. But the past is hard to let go of...' WHERE `entry`=26785;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Something troubles me, $N. The twilight dragons knew just where and when to strike our airfleet. It\'s as if they knew our plans.$B$BTwilight spies cower within our midst!$B$BI\'m going to take one of our remaining ships back to Orgrimmar to roll some heads. I need you to stay behind and secure this front. The Dragonmaw shaman are powerful; I have asked them to open up a portal to Orgrimmar, and I need you to help.$B$BSo. Start helping!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your Warchief is decisive, $N. He makes things happen. I like him. Let\'s talk about this portal that he wants!' WHERE `entry`=26786;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you! Oh, thank you. I never thought I\'d be happy to smell those brains, but I am now that I didn\'t have to get them! Here\'s your reward as promised...' WHERE `entry`=26787;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Now that\'s the stuff! I\'ll start mixing and diluting this with gravel and water. Just a few handfuls of this can enhance enough cement for an entire stone tower. We\'ve got big plans for this port, $N. You\'ll see!' WHERE `entry`=26788;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They won\'t have any more of those fungal giants to throw against us!' WHERE `entry`=26791;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. We\'ve never had such a problem in Deepholm before the destruction of the World Pillar. Your Earthen Ring must repair the damage before it\'s too late.' WHERE `entry`=26792;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Morgan Ladimore?$B$BAhh, yes, of course. His was a long and sorrowful tale. I knew him, well, before he left for the war, but that was the last time I saw him. A noble and good man, he was, but he suffered a bad end.$B$BHere, I should have something here that can tell the tale better than my own recollections...' WHERE `entry`=26793;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Morgan Ladimore? Never heard of... Oh, you mean Mor\'Ladim! I guess you haven\'t heard the story? Well, I\'ll give you the short version. A powerful undead calling itself Mor\'Ladim has been wandering Duskwood. From what we\'ve gathered, it appears to be the undead body of Morgan Ladimore, of whom you apparently know. He\'s been causing us all sorts of problems, attacking Watchmen on patrol and killing people. You seem to be capable enough, maybe you could lay him to rest.' WHERE `entry`=26794;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You killed him? That\'s no small accomplishment, $N! On behalf of the people of Darkshire and the Night Watch, I thank you.$B$BAh... there is one small matter, however...' WHERE `entry`=26795;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes? My father... I wish... there was something I could have done for him... If only I had talked to him before he...' WHERE `entry`=26796;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This is...? Sarah? Could it be she\'s still alive? The weight is removed from my shoulders... $N. Take my sword, Archeus. As my soul is put to rest, I have no more need for it. It was forged to do good, and though I have proved myself unworthy to hold it, perhaps you will carry on the Light through it. Lys, my love...' WHERE `entry`=26797;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The portal is ready!$B$BIt\'s not powerful enough to transport an army, but we can maintain the connection long enough to allow important individuals to pass back and forth.$B$BThe Warchief will want to know about our progress here. Walk through the portal to Orgrimmar, then deliver the news to Garrosh Hellscream.',`objectives_loc6`='Use the portal in Dragonmaw Port to go to Orgrimmar and report to Garrosh Hellscream.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='$C, you\'ve returned from Dragonmaw. The portal is functioning then? Good. Before you return to your work there, we\'ve got some dirty business to clean up right here in Orgrimmar...' WHERE `entry`=26798;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not even the power of the val\'kyr was enough to save these creatures. They were doomed from the beginning. I have obtained some equipment for you, $N. It\'s not much, but it will help. Please, take your pick.' WHERE `entry`=26799;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Recruitment',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great work $N. I knew you weren\'t useless. Here, take one of these. We deathguards have piles of these things just sitting around.' WHERE `entry`=26800;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re growing in strength, $N. I\'ve seen your type before. You will be moving out of Deathknell and on to greater things before long. Just make sure you don\'t lose sight of where you started. You have much to accomplish, $C.' WHERE `entry`=26801;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. This armor should help you out.$B$BHopefully, it should do you more good than the last one to wear it...' WHERE `entry`=26802;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Garrosh is brash and speaks harshly, but his intentions are good. In time, he will grow to see your people as a valuable ally.$B$BI am awaiting reports about recent Alliance activity in Durotar, but they haven\'t arrived yet. Would you be willing to visit Razor Hill and ask him for the reports in person? The easiest way to get there is by wind rider. Doras, Orgrimmar\'s wind rider master will let you use one of his wind riders for a small fee. Look for him on the rise north of the Valley of Strength.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you need to get to Razor Hill in a hurry? That\'s no problem at all. One of my wind riders will get you there very quickly and it only costs a few coins to hire one.' WHERE `entry`=26803;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Eitrigg sent you? The warchief must be getting anxious to read my reports. I\'d\'ve sent them long ago, but each day we discover more about the Alliance\'s plans for invading Durotar.' WHERE `entry`=26804;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wulfred has a good eye. I think you\'ll do just fine here at my camp.' WHERE `entry`=26805;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ready to return to Orgrimmar with those reports? I can arrange a flight for you right away.' WHERE `entry`=26806;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' The Alliance has grown bolder than we\'d thought! I\'ll talk to the warchief about sending reinforcements right away. Thank you for getting these reports to me so quickly. I hope this coin is enough to cover your travel expenses.' WHERE `entry`=26807;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Maywiki',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You have my thanks. You may tell your young dwarven friend that I am not sad. I am waiting. For you. I have identified you as the most promising $R here in this strange town. I have a task for you, if you would be willing to take it.' WHERE `entry`=26808;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is as I suspected. Zanzil is too haughty to interfere with the squabbles between the Bloodscalps and the Skullsplitters. No, he is playing a part in a grander scheme... Jin\'do the Hexxer is using him to help bring Hakkar back to Zul\'Gurub. It\'s good that we found this out now, because it offers us a simple solution.' WHERE `entry`=26809;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I ask you to slay Zanzil the Outcast, a lowly, hermetic exile of the Gurubashi, and what do you do?  You dash headfirst into the Gurubashi capital and eliminate one of their High Priests!  Very nearly two!  Only one word suffices to explain such a rash and foolhardy endeavor: Heroism. Jin\'do the Hexxer still walks within Zul\'Gurub\'s walls, but he lost one of his legs when you crushed Jeklik. Today\'s battle is ours.' WHERE `entry`=26814;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This mixture is... PERFECT!  Let\'s see what it does to your potentially-titan artifact here!' WHERE `entry`=26815;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is fascinating!  Just think of all the applications! Thanks again, $N. Remember, if you ever need anything mixed for you... and I mean ANYTHING... you can always ask The Flask.' WHERE `entry`=26816;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Do you know how hard it is to get fresh water in Stranglethorn?  It\'s no wonder that the nagas guard their shrine so ferociously! Alright, let\'s get this mix started!' WHERE `entry`=26817;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' These are so nice and cushy!  I think my customers are going to LOVE them!' WHERE `entry`=26818;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hooray!  It\'s been days and days since we last had Akiris reeds!' WHERE `entry`=26819;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These statues are beautiful... Wow, I had no idea the naga were so talented. Thanks, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26820;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Airwyn Bantamflax',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fascinating! I\'ll need some time to study this. Why don\'t you have a look around Booty Bay and come back later?' WHERE `entry`=26821;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahem!  Ahhh... right... Well done!  And, congratulations, on killing them, I mean. Here you go.' WHERE `entry`=26822;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Alright!  Step one - getting ingredients - is all done. Time for the next step: getting more ingredients.' WHERE `entry`=26823;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew that alchemist was all talk. Well, thanks for your help, $N. I know you tried.' WHERE `entry`=26824;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Hey - you must be that $G fella\': lass; that Wulfred was talkin\' about!  The one who found the ogre artifact, and helped him test out those strange stones from up north. Welcome to the digsite, $N!$B$BWe were actually working on identifying those samples right as you got here. Would you mind bringing the sample over to Dask?  I need him to help me find out how old it is.',`objectives_loc6`='Bring the Opened Mosh\'Ogg Bounty to Dask "The Flask" Gobfizzle at the Explorers\' League Digsite in the Cape of Stranglethorn.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='So once again, it falls upon tiny Dask to get the Explorers\' League work done!  Alright... let\'s see what you\'ve got in there.' WHERE `entry`=26825;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Hey - you must be that $G fella\': lass; that Wulfred was talkin\' about!  Welcome to the digsite, $N.$B$BWe were actually just starting a project when you arrived. Would you mind bringing this sample over to Dask?  I need him to help me find out how old it is.',`objectives_loc6`='Bring the Opened Mosh\'Ogg Bounty to Dask "The Flask" Gobfizzle at the Explorers\' League Digsite in the Cape of Stranglethorn.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='So once again, it falls upon tiny Dask to get the Explorers\' League work done!  Alright... let\'s see what you\'ve got in there.' WHERE `entry`=26826;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done what I thought not possible. Quite impressive, $C.' WHERE `entry`=26827;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='And so you arrive, fleshling. As promised.' WHERE `entry`=26828;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Their blood upon the earth is a sweet thing. I shall cherish every moment, slowly extinguishing the stragglers from my realm.' WHERE `entry`=26829;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I haven\'t given up my search for the Twilight\'s Hammer agents that lurk here in Orgrimmar. I need someone I can trust to collect the final evidence of treachery.$B$B<Hellscream pulls you aside.>$B$BSauranok the Mystic - my own most trusted advisor! - is under suspicion. Uncover the truth, $N, and you\'ll be rewarded.$B$BI understand Twilight\'s Hammer has infiltrated workers at the airship docks, to spread their lies all over the continent. Question them. If you discover Sauranok\'s guilt... Kill him.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Sauranok, Sauranok. His own visions worked against him. Twilight\'s Hammer probably corrupted him from afar. Bah! Weak! We\'ll speak his name no more. I told him you were investigating the airship docks, $N. To flush him out. Yes, I used you as bait. You served your Horde well, and deserve a reward for outing this viper from our midst.' WHERE `entry`=26830;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is good that you were here. I find my size to be inhibiting when it comes to dragon riding, strangely.' WHERE `entry`=26831;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You let Lorthuna escape? I warned you of this. Still, their forces are shattered and their resources cut off. There is little they can do to me or my allies.' WHERE `entry`=26832;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Gorsik has arrived. All of the pieces of the World Pillar are here, thanks to you. What you have done for us is immeasurable. These final moments shall be the most crucial. I hesitate to ask more of you, but I\'d like you to stay with us and see this through. The Twilight\'s Hammer was devastated by your attacks, but not destroyed. It\'s no stretch to assume they will try to stop us from completing our ritual.' WHERE `entry`=26833;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good to see you again, $N. Now we\'ll get somewhere.' WHERE `entry`=26834;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N, we have good news and a slight problem....' WHERE `entry`=26835;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N! You did it! How will we ever repay you?' WHERE `entry`=26836;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome to our camp, $C. You couldn\'t have arrived at a better time.' WHERE `entry`=26838;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N! I trust Orgrimmar fares well? As you can see, construction of Dragonmaw Port continues at a breakneck pace. If my people questioned the Horde\'s power before... the sight of this imposing edifice and the speed in which it was constructed leaves no doubt. A new day dawns for the Dragonmaw.' WHERE `entry`=26840;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I will be your mentor and guide for now. It is my duty to teach you the arcane arts and how you might best fit in among our people. As you learn and grow in power, you will learn an immense variety of spells that should allow you to deal with nearly any situation. But until then, return to me as often as you like and I will teach you what I can in the ways of our kind.' WHERE `entry`=26841;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nicely done, $Glad:lass;. I could use a $C like you around here.' WHERE `entry`=26842;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So I was right! Now the question is what the little freaks were plotting...' WHERE `entry`=26843;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, good. Now we can see what\'s going on down in that mine.' WHERE `entry`=26844;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s a gnoll head. Are you trying to pull some funny business, $N?$B$BIf you\'re not, I\'ve not the faintest idea what\'s going on here.' WHERE `entry`=26845;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m sure that only worked because the troggs aren\'t bright to begin with. But then again, us dwarves were once creatures of the earth as well.$B$BBeing bossed around by a kobold doesn\'t sound quite dignified, and I\'m glad we didn\'t get to find out if they could pull that off.' WHERE `entry`=26846;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Here is the corpse of a dwarf -- mauled, frozen, and picked clean by mountain scavengers. Clutched in its hand is a book containing the roughly scribbled notes of Mori Hildelve. And around its frame, still in superior condition, is a Brigadier\'s Vest.$B$BThis grisly scene must have been where the Siege Engine pilot met his end.' WHERE `entry`=26854;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is grim news, for Hildelve was a good friend. And I wish I could have been there with you when you found the beast, Mangeclaw!$B$BThank you, $N. Your deed will be remembered by the pilots of the Ironforge Siege Brigade.' WHERE `entry`=26855;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done it, $N! You\'ve upturned the Searing Blade\'s invasion before it could even start! Take this, as a token of my thanks.' WHERE `entry`=26856;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That ought to get the dragon\'s attention, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26857;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My children will sing songs of your glories, $N!' WHERE `entry`=26858;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Much obliged! The rump\'s part of my own secret twist on the recipe... but here\'s instructions on how to make it with any kind of bear meat.$B$BAnd here\'s a fresh batch of me own. Mind you eat them fresh!' WHERE `entry`=26860;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. When we make our move against Abyssion, we should be able to do so without reinforcements coming to his aid.' WHERE `entry`=26861;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $C. The Molten Elementals\' spirits are finally back to rest.' WHERE `entry`=26862;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Did you see a lot of kobolds in there? The thought of their grimy hands clawing around our mine makes my stomach rumble!' WHERE `entry`=26863;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Gnolls and kobolds, and troggs? Oh my.$B$BI\'d laugh if I didn\'t have another twist in the story for you.' WHERE `entry`=26864;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve been expecting your arrival, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve been expecting your arrival, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26866;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve been expecting your arrival, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26867;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Worked like a charm, didn\'t it? Maybe Kadrell will get off my darn back now what with savin\' the whole town and all!$B$BI suppose you\'ve done earned yourself some proper goods.' WHERE `entry`=26868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<This is it. This is the stone Diamant sent you for.>' WHERE `entry`=26869;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can already feel the balance returning! Quick, talk to Muyoh to help him awaken Naralex!' WHERE `entry`=26870;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, fleshling!$B$BThe gyreworms are among our most dangerous enemies.$B$BThe other Stone Lords shall have trouble not turning their head to this accomplishment.' WHERE `entry`=26871;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your efforts shall not go unnoticed, $N. Thank you for your dedication.' WHERE `entry`=26872;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $N. Hopefully we can use these to prevent further nightmares.' WHERE `entry`=26873;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Twilight forces continue to stream in, but it looks like the Earthen Ring defenders can handle them.' WHERE `entry`=26875;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your efforts in repairing the World Pillar are invaluable, $N. Once the Temple of Earth\'s structure is stable again, the rift between the worlds will begin to stabilize.' WHERE `entry`=26876;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, $C? What brings you to this place?' WHERE `entry`=26878;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='There\'s something sinister going on within this place, $N. We fear that the rumors of the Naga working with the Twilight\'s Hammer are true.$B$BI sent Thaelrid, one of our best scouts, further in to investigate the matter, but he hasn\'t returned.$B$BSeek him out. If he\'s still alive, find out all that he\'s learned.',`objectives_loc6`='Seek out Scout Thaelrid.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ashelan was good to send you. There is indeed a wicked plot underway in this corrupted place.' WHERE `entry`=26881;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Kelris has eluded us for quite some time.$B$BIt seems as though whenever evil made its presence known in these parts, Kelris had played a role. For some time we considered him either dead or missing.$B$BBut this makes perfect sense. By ending his reign you have spared the lives of many innocent people.$B$BTo sacrifice someone to a servant of an Old God for one\'s personal gain is beyond reproachful!$B$BYou have done a great deed, $N. I thank you on behalf of Ashenvale.$B$BIf only Thaelrid had survived....' WHERE `entry`=26882;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Obtain 10 Twilight Pendants.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are no doubt of brave and noble blood, $N. We and all of the people of Ashenvale commend you for your efforts against evil.' WHERE `entry`=26883;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have undoubtedly faced great peril to obtain these.$B$BYour actions have been selfless. It is for the good of all Azeroth that you help me with my research. I thank you, $N, for all that you have done.$B$BNow if you\'ll excuse me I have much work to do.' WHERE `entry`=26884;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You found the manuscript! What a joyous day this is! I will study it exhaustively and learn all there is to know.$B$BI\'ll make full sentinel yet!$B$BYour service to us is more than you know, $N. I hope that this gift shows you my gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=26885;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful! I hope you didn\'t get hit with too many cannonballs.' WHERE `entry`=26886;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I know we\'re here to make friends with the Steamwheedle goblins, but those awful Bilgewater goblins are so rude$B$BWhy, I just saw a bunch of them pulling gold fillings out of the teeth of the Southsea musketeers and strongarms. Do they think they can just take that for themselves?$B$BObviously, the nice thing to do is kill those pirates ourselves, take their fillings ourselves, and then give some of them to the Steamwheedle as a thank-you gift! Head on down there and beat those goblins to the punch.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='More gold! We\'ll be sure to give some of this to Mister Noggenfogger to smoothly ensure our continued relations. And only a little bit of it will go back to Gnomeregan for experimental weapons development!' WHERE `entry`=26887;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The beast is slain. I can feel his dark presence fading away forever.' WHERE `entry`=26888;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You know, I\'m usually not impressed when I see a $R, but I\'ve heard about what you\'ve been doin\' for the Steamwheedle. You\'re alright, kid.' WHERE `entry`=26889;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! These will do nicely. Here\'s a reward for your hard work.' WHERE `entry`=26890;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is exactly what I need! A fathom core is an incredible well of information that we will be able to draw much good from. Whatever the Twilight\'s Hammer is up to in there - and believe me when I say it is no good - my comrades and I will now uncover.$B$BYou\'ve done well here today; the Earthen Ring looks upon you warmly for assisting us. You\'ve also helped the Horde as a whole, and for that you should be proud.' WHERE `entry`=26891;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can hear their cries from here! Maybe this will show them how foolish it is to wish for the return of an Old God.' WHERE `entry`=26892;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='There\'s a task to be done that you\'re perfect for, $C. We need to secure the area around Blackfathom Deeps to help with that Alliance that are threatening Zoram\'gar Outpost west of here.$B$BGo to Blackfathom Deeps, north of Zoram\'gar Outpost, and speak with Je\'neu of the Earthen Ring. He will have plenty for you to do.' WHERE `entry`=26893;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The Naga mock us with their defiance. We will drive them and their allies out of this land for good.$B$BTravel north of here to Blackfathom Deeps and speak with Je\'neu Sancrea. He\'s already made his way inside.$B$BBe wary of Zeya, by the way. She can be a bit...temperamental at times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Did Commander Grimfang send you? I\'ve asked him to find suitable recruits to aid me here.' WHERE `entry`=26894;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Another proud $C, lured by the promise of fame! Of wealth! Of VIOLENCE! Yes, welcome, friend. Welcome... to THUNDERDROME!' WHERE `entry`=26895;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Another proud $C, lured by the promise of fame! Of wealth! Of VIOLENCE! Yes, welcome, friend. Welcome... to THUNDERDROME!' WHERE `entry`=26896;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Although our position is exposed, we are safe compared to our friends inside Blackfathom Deeps! They stand mere feet away from the most deadly Naga forces in the area. Speak with Sentinel Aluwyn and give them the aid they desperately need!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank Elune you\'re here! We could use all the help we can get.' WHERE `entry`=26897;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank Elune you\'re here! We could use all the help we can get.' WHERE `entry`=26898;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I spare your life for your help, $R. Leave now...before I change my...mind.' WHERE `entry`=26899;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Agamaggan' WHERE `entry`=26900;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done! This is just what we need, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26901;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks again, friend! I told you I\'d make it worth your while.' WHERE `entry`=26903;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Few people, especially among our allies, truly understand the nature of the power we wield. They shun us for pursuing knowledge that they are too weak to use properly.$B$BLet me show you a conjuration that I find handy. This spell, called Immolate, sets your target aflame, causing damage immediately and over time. Use it well, $N, and your enemies will come to fear you.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Saripal Smolderbrew and learn Immolate, then cast Immolate 5 times on a Training Dummy near the entrance to Anvilmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='As you continue to gain power, return to me and I will teach you new spells and techniques.' WHERE `entry`=26904;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Take this gift. You have earned my blessing this day.' WHERE `entry`=26905;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Agamaggan',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I\'ve been waiting for you to come here.' WHERE `entry`=26906;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Overlord Ramtusk and the Death\'s Head mobilize for war. It took many scouts\' lives, but we have learned of the weapon they intend to use to overtake the rest of the Barrens.$B$BIt is known as Agathelos the Raging, an immense boar outfitted with heavy armor and force-fed the rage-inducing Kraul bat guano.$B$B$R, you must stop them before they take innocent lives!',`objectives_loc6`='Kill Aggem Thorncurse, Death Speaker Jargba, Overlord Ramtusk, and Agathelos the Raging.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well this day. Agathelos would have taken many lives in its fury.' WHERE `entry`=26907;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Only a veteran like you could brave the dangers lurking here.' WHERE `entry`=26908;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Help...' WHERE `entry`=26909;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you received my note? Excellent. You\'ve proven yourself quite capable in dealing with those orcs. As you continue to grow in power, I will teach you some new techniques.' WHERE `entry`=26910;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I know, $N. I should not have sent you. Forgive me... the whispers of the past are sometimes too strong.' WHERE `entry`=26911;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='As the eldritch shackles are placed around the Shards, an unhuman wail is heard from far below. The scream is followed by a roar.$B$BThe Shards of Myzrael no longer invoke feelings of warmth and security as they once did. Now they pulse with an open menace... as if the thing beneath them holds ill will toward the surface.' WHERE `entry`=26912;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Now that you\'ve had the chance to test your abilities in battle, it\'s time to show you a new combat technique -- charge. As a warrior, it\'s important to use every advantage at your disposal to get the upper hand in battle.$B$BWhat better way to do that than by charging into battle and stunning your opponent? I\'ll show you how it\'s done, and then I want you to go try it on one of the training dummies south of the entrance to the abbey.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Llane Bershere and purchase the Charge ability, then practice using Charge on a Training Dummy south of the entrance to Northshire Abbey.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re a quick learner, $N. Return to me as you grow stronger and I\'ll show you other combat techniques.' WHERE `entry`=26913;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='We must take care in how we speak around the abbey and its environs, but don\'t let that deter you from the path of power.$B$BI want to show you one of my favorite spells. It will allow you to set an opponent on fire, damaging the enemy immediately and continuing to do more harm over time. I\'ll show you how it\'s done, and then I want you to go try it on one of the training dummies south of the entrance to the abbey.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Drusilla La Salle and purchase the Immolate ability, then practice casting Immolate 5 times on a Training Dummy south of the entrance to Northshire Abbey.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see you have already mastered Immolation! I look forward to instructing you in the future. Do not forget to return for further lessons as you grow in power.' WHERE `entry`=26914;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='By now, you know the basics of combat as rogue, but I want to teach you a new skill. As rogues, we are renowned for our ability to execute chains of combat techniques, often saving the most powerful strikes for the end.$B$BLet me show you the basics of Eviscerate. After using Sinister Strike a few times, you can attack with Eviscerate to hit your opponent even harder. I want you to go try it on one of the training dummies south of the entrance to the abbey.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Jorik Kerridan and purchase the Eviscerate ability, then find a Training Dummy south of the entrance to Northshire Abbey and practice Eviscerate 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve caught on quickly, $N, and a quick mind will serve you well. Return to me as you grow in power and I will show you new techniques.' WHERE `entry`=26915;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='As a mage, you will learn a variety of spells as your understanding grows. I want to show you a new technique that allows you to launch volleys of arcane energy at your opponent, Arcane Missiles. You won\'t be able to cast this spell all the time, but each time you cast another spell, there\'s a chance you\'ll create an opening to use Arcane Missiles. I\'ll show you how it\'s done, and then I want you to go try it on one of the training dummies south of the entrance to the abbey.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Khelden Bremen and purchase the Arcane Missiles ability, then practice casting Arcane Missiles 2 times on a Training Dummy south of the entrance to Northshire Abbey.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Have you mastered the use of Arcane Missiles already? You are a quick study in the arcane arts and you have a promising future ahead. Don\'t forget to return to me for training as you grow in power.' WHERE `entry`=26916;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I\'ve heard about your help in clearing out some of the orcs. You\'ve shown that you can handle yourself in combat.$B$BI want to show you a new skill. I\'ll show you how it\'s done, and then I want you to go try it on one of the training dummies south of the entrance to the abbey.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Ashley Blank and purchase the Steady Shot ability, then find a Training Dummy south of the entrance to Northshire Abbey and practice using Steady Shot 5 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew you would master Steady Shot quickly. I\'m looking forward to showing you other techniques as you get more experienced in the ways of the $C.' WHERE `entry`=26917;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I want to teach you a couple of techniques for using the Light\'s power to boost your combat skills.$B$BThe first technique is applying the Seal of Righteousness. While under the effects of the seal, all of your melee attacks will inflict additional holy damage.$B$BThe second ability, Judgement, can be use periodically to unleash the seal\'s power and inflict damage.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Brother Sammuel and purchase the Seal of Righteousness and Judgement abilities. Cast Seal of Righteousness on yourself and then use Judgement on a Training Dummy south of the entrance to Northshire Abbey.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re a quick learner, $N. Return to me as you grow stronger and I\'ll teach you more about using the Light to vanquish your enemies and strengthen your allies.' WHERE `entry`=26918;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='One of your responsibilities as a priest is caring for the wounded. With the power of the Light, you can save those who would otherwise die and speed the healing of wounds.$B$BI want to teach you a simple, quick technique you can use to heal an ally quickly.$B$B I\'ll show you how it\'s done, and then I want you to use this spell to treat the injuries of wounded trainees around the abbey.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak to Priestess Anetta and purchase the Flash Heal ability, then use Flash Heal 5 times to treat Wounded Trainees inside Northshire Abbey.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re a quick learner, $N, and the wounded are fortunate to have your aid. Return to me as you grow stronger and I\'ll teach you other spells.' WHERE `entry`=26919;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s about time you arrived, $C.' WHERE `entry`=26920;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You may not act quickly, but at least you do not fail me. Very well. I will have a more important task for you, $N, when the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=26921;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These grenades are all explosives, nothing more. Even as a member of the Royal Apothecary Society, I recognize that some problems are not solved by throwing more plague at them.' WHERE `entry`=26922;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With the behemoths out of the way, our victory against the Scourge is inevitable. Our current chances against the Alliance aren\'t quite as favorable... but that\'s no concern of yours. Not yet, anyhow.' WHERE `entry`=26923;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Scholomancer',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellently done, $N. And now, with the leader of the Scourge forces eliminated from Andorhal, we bide our time.' WHERE `entry`=26924;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Araj dead... this is good. The Royal Apothecary Society has done its part. As have you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26925;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Word arrived shortly before you did, $N. With the Scourge ejected from Andorhal, the Forsaken has cemented its foothold in Lordaeron.' WHERE `entry`=26926;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Murlocs? Sure, I\'ve hunted murlocs.$B$BAnd every single stinkin\' one of them deserved what they got! You hear me?' WHERE `entry`=26927;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Phew! Ain\'t that a stench.$B$BNow you prepare yourself, because I\'m about to wow you with what\'s left of my mental faculties.' WHERE `entry`=26928;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Mighty kind of you to help out an ol\' fool like me. Here\'s your reward as promised an\' all.' WHERE `entry`=26929;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Burning bodies?  No survivors?  I guessed correctly. All the better!  We\'re better off without the Scarlet taint upon Lordaeron. They epitomized all the worst things about humans.' WHERE `entry`=26930;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s a relief to have those hunters out of the way. We\'re not done killing Alliance, however...' WHERE `entry`=26931;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That should help prevent disease and illness from spreading into our remaining water. Many thanks, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26932;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ha ha!  I hope that they come back as zombies.' WHERE `entry`=26933;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Glorious!  This is the last bit I need. Actually, stick around, $N. Let me tell you a little bit more about our plan.' WHERE `entry`=26934;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome to Northridge, $C.' WHERE `entry`=26935;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am able to communicate with you through the Val\'kyr, $N. You have done well. Remain on Felstone Field. We must now teach these newly-converted Forsaken how to fight.' WHERE `entry`=26937;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='When Koltira gives his word, I will bring these val\'kyr into Andorhal. We will win. And yet another piece of Lordaeron will fall to the might of the Forsaken.' WHERE `entry`=26938;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hope that wasn\'t too much for you. The mission is far from over!' WHERE `entry`=26939;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='We are the heirs to a legacy of arcane magic and your path will not be an easy one. Many still hold us responsible for the actions of our forebears, but our talents are needed.$B$BI want to show you a new spell, Arcane Missiles. It allows you to fire volleys of arcane energy, but you won\'t be able to cast it all the time. Casting other spells has a chance to create an opportunity for you to use Arcane Missiles.$B$BI want you try it. Look for a training dummy near the southeastern edge of Aldrassil.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Arcane Missiles from Rhyanda. Look for a Training Dummy near, and practice using Arcane Missiles twice.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew you would master this lesson quickly. You are a credit to the highborn and to all our kin. Remember, as you grow in power, return to me and will instruct you further.' WHERE `entry`=26940;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Took you long enough. Get behind the pillar with me before you blow our cover!' WHERE `entry`=26941;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'d love for you to come aboard as a full G-Team Commando, but you have other adventures to pursue. I\'m sure we\'ll meet again, and I hope you\'ll have considered joining by then. Here\'s something for your trouble.' WHERE `entry`=26942;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I used t\' have quite the home back in Ironforge. That is, I did until I was booted out to make way for the Gnomes.$B$BThey couldn\'t stop a bunch of troggs with all them gizmos and machines! An\' I have to pay for their weakness?$B$BNo, sir. No longer.$B$BGo to Gnomeregan and talk to Commando Murd Doc. Sure, he\'s a Gnome, but his crew, S.A.F.E. I think they call \'em, are going to take Gnomeregan back.$B$BGo! I want my house back!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Never thought I\'d see a $R like you down here. Any particular reason you\'re risking life and limb?' WHERE `entry`=26943;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The Gnomish capital, Gnomeregan, hasn\'t been under their control for some time now. I know what it feels like to lose a home.$B$BPlease, venture inside Gnomeregan and speak to Commando Murd Doc, a member of S.A.F.E. If there\'s anything at all that you can do to help them take their home, I urge you to do so. There are dark secrets in those halls.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Never thought I\'d see a $R like you down here. Any particular reason you\'re risking life and limb?' WHERE `entry`=26944;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='There\'s no better time to get the upper hand in battle than at the start. Let me teach you a technique for charging into battle and stunning your opponent.$B$BI want you try it. Look for a training dummy near the southeastern edge of Aldrassil.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Charge from Alyissia. Look for a Training Dummy near, and practice using Charge.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve proven a capable student. When it is time to resume your training, return to me and I will show you other techniques.' WHERE `entry`=26945;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I\'m certain that by now, you\'ve mastered using Sinister Strike against your enemies, but I want to show you a technique you can use to follow a successful series of Sinister Strikes. It\'s called Eviscerate and it can be a strong way to end a combination of attacks.$B$BI want you try it. Look for a training dummy near the southeastern edge of Aldrassil.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Eviscerate from Frahun Shadewhisper. Look for a Training Dummy southeast of Aldrassil and practice using Eviscerate 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve learned quickly. If you are as sharp as you seem to be, you may prove to be one of my best students yet. Return to me when you are in need of further training.' WHERE `entry`=26946;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='When most people think of the kaldorei, they conjure visions of druids and sentinels, but the way of the hunter is just as ancient and just as venerable.$B$BI\'ve been observing you, and you\'ve had quite a bit of experience handling that bow. I want to show you a shooting technique that I often use in combat.$B$BI want you try it. Look for a training dummy near the southeastern edge of Aldrassil.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Steady Shot from Ayanna Everstride. Look for a Training Dummy southeast of Aldrassil, and practice using Steady Shot 5 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are a quick study in our ways. I look forward to continuing your training in the future. Return to me when the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=26947;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Druids play an important role in our society, but all too often we are seen as passive dreamers in a world that is changing around us. I want to teach you a basic healing technique and with it, I want you to go out in the world and aid the ailing and the fallen.$B$BUse your new knowledge to heal the wounds of sentinels who have been injured defending Shadowglen.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Rejuvenation from Mardant Strongoak. Use Rejuvenation to treat a Wounded Sentinel in Aldrassil.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have mastered the basics of the healing ways quickly, $N. I have no doubt that your healing skills will often come in handy. Return to me when you need further training.' WHERE `entry`=26948;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='As a priest, you will often be called upon to heal the wounds of injured comrades. I want to teach you a basic healing technique and with it, you will be able to ease the suffering of the wounded and hasten their recovery.$B$BUse your new knowledge to heal the injured sentinels recovering within Aldrassil.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Flash Heal from Shanda. Use Flash Heal 5 times to treat the Wounded Sentinels in Aldrassil.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You will find no lack of allies in need of healing. Return to me when you need further training.' WHERE `entry`=26949;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What do you mean Thalnos was an undead? That\'s impossible. This is a holy place, the Scarlet Crusade would never allow... Take this as a reward, and get some rest. The crypts must have gotten the best of your nerves.' WHERE `entry`=26950;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks, $C. The spirits can rest now. As long as we show them respect they will bless us and our new home for a long time. Spirits be with you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=26951;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome, $C. As you can see, our camp is a joint expedition between Argent Crusade members and Cenarion Circle druids, but we welcome all who wish to help heal the land.' WHERE `entry`=26952;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It looks like Zen\'Kiki is still having a little bit of trouble with his shapeshifting.' WHERE `entry`=26953;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now we\'re getting somewhere. How many birds did Zen\'Kiki end up killing? None?  You killed them all yourself? Alright, I suppose we\'ll have to find another use for him then. I will let you know when the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=26954;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='By the grace of the Earthmother, he\'s done it!  Thank you, $N! I admit, I had nearly given up hope on Zen\'Kiki. It is only due to your patience and diligence that he has come into his own as a druid and member of the Cenarion Circle. And that\'s without even mentioning the good you\'ve done for nature. You have my admiration and respect.' WHERE `entry`=26955;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='$R!  I\'m glad someone\'s here to help me out.$B$BWe Cenarion druids have re-cultivated Dalson\'s Farm, immediately behind me. The land has flourished and our crops have been successful... mostly.$B$BA few plants seem to still be infected by the plague that ran through this land. Perhaps their roots were too deep, perhaps the seeds were weak... I cannot say. All I can say is that I need an able $C like you to help me remove the bad plants from the good ones.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for your help, $N. I know that picking vegetables isn\'t the most heroic task imaginable, but even the humblest tasks have their rewards.' WHERE `entry`=26956;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It would appear that I arrived before you, $N. Field Agent Kaartish gave me the details about my old home. It seems my battles with the Scourge aren\'t quite over yet.' WHERE `entry`=26957;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Let\'s start your training right away. I want to teach you a combat technique that you\'ll find useful at the start of battle. By charging your opponent before the fight begins, you can stun the enemy and momentum will be on your side.$B$BI want you to try out this technique using the training dummies to the northwest of the Crash Site. Return to me when you think you\'ve mastered it.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Charge from Kore. Find a Training Dummy on the northwest side of the Crash Site and practice using Charge.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Keep that technique handy, $N. I find myself using it all the time. Return when you\'re ready for further training.' WHERE `entry`=26958;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I knew I could count on you! These fools will never know what hit them.' WHERE `entry`=26959;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent, Anduin will learn a lot by shadowing you. Remember, stay within the city\'s borders. Keep him out of trouble. And above all else, guard him with your life. Anduin, no adventures! Stay close to $N and return to the keep should you see any trouble.' WHERE `entry`=26960;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You got them! Nicely done, $N!$B$BAnd you don\'t look too worse for wear, even with those berserk Troggs about. I\'m going to keep my eye on you...you show some promise.' WHERE `entry`=26961;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Herod is slain! The Armory will fall!' WHERE `entry`=26962;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Let\'s start your training right away. It\'s going to be a struggle to survive here, and you\'ll play an important role in making sure our people are safe and well-supplied. I want to show you a shooting technique that I use all the time.$B$BTry out this technique using the training dummies to the northwest of the Crash Site. Return to me when you think you\'ve mastered it.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Steady Shot from Keilnei. Find a Training Dummy on the northwest side of the Crash Site and practice using Steady Shot 5 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Keep that technique handy, $N. I find myself using it all the time. Return when you\'re ready for further training.' WHERE `entry`=26963;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Most excellent! A new recruit has arrived. There is much to do... much to do I say.' WHERE `entry`=26964;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well that was unexpected. I am not one to doubt our Warchief, but... Nevermind! We have work to do. I\'m sure the Dark Lady and the Warchief will get this all worked out.' WHERE `entry`=26965;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='As a paladin, you\'re no stranger to the Light that touches all of us. But you also have the unique power to call upon the Light to help you in battle.$B$BWhile under the effects of the Seal of Righteousness, each melee attack will deal extra holy damage. From time to time, you can also use Judgement to unleash your seal\'s power for another attack.$B$BI want you to try out these techniques using the training dummies to the northwest of the Crash Site.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Seal of Righteousness and Judgement from Aurelon. Apply Seal of Righteousness, find a Training Dummy on the northwest side of the Crash Site and use Judgement.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve proven yourself a quick learner, $N. I look forward to training you again when the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=26966;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes! The Scarlet Monastery now belongs to the Forsaken! None can escape our wrath! You\'ve completed your task with the precision of a true champion. Take this as a reward, courtesy of the Banshee Queen.' WHERE `entry`=26967;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='In your future as a mage, you\'ll be expected to master a wide variety of spells. In fact, I want to teach you one right now. It\'s called Arcane Missiles and it allows you to throw volleys of arcane energy at your opponent. However, you won\'t be able to use it all the time. Each time you cast a spell, there\'s a chance you\'ll trigger an opportunity to use the missiles.$B$BI want you to try out this technique using the training dummies to the northwest of the Crash Site.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Arcane Missiles from Valaatu. Find a Training Dummy on the northwest side of the Crash Site and practice using Arcane Missiles 2 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve mastered the use of this new spell quickly, $N. I only wish all of my students were as talented. Return to me when you find yourself in need of further training.' WHERE `entry`=26968;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Your walk with the elemental powers will take you to many places. Let us start your journey with a simple, but useful, lesson. I want to teach you to a basic combat technique.$B$BOnce you have completed training, go practice your new skill using the training dummies to the northwest of the Crash Site. Return to me when you are finished.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Primal Strike from Firmanvaar. Find a Training Dummy on the northwest side of the Crash Site and practice using Primal Strike 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is a pleasure to teach such a capable student. As long as you continue the traditons faithfully, the shamanic arts will never be lost to our people again. Return to me when you need further training.' WHERE `entry`=26969;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='As a priest, one of your most important duties is to use the Light\'s power to aid the wounded. There are no lack of people here who could use your skills, $N. Allow me to show you a quick, simple heal that you can use to treat any ally.$B$BUse your newfound knowledge to help me treat those wounded in the crash.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Flash Heal from Zalduun. Use Flash Heal 5 times to heal the wounds of Injured Draenei at the Crash Site.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ll often find your skills as a healer in demand, $N. Do not hesitate to return when you need more training.' WHERE `entry`=26970;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Maruut said when all dis started dat he would gladly give his life ta see our task done. He would be proud of dis success... of dis death. Da rift be closed on dis side. Deepholm should calm down a bit. It\'ll be takin\' time for Thrall to mend da wound in Azeroth, and we\'ll be needin\' to remain until he finishes. Thank you for all ya\'ve done. I don\'t tink we could have been accomplishin\' dis so soon without you.' WHERE `entry`=26971;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What do you mean Thalnos was an undead? That\'s impossible. The entire mission of the Scarlet Crusade is to destroy the undead! There\'s just no way... You have muddied my thoughts. Please take this reward for your achievement and leave me to rest.' WHERE `entry`=26972;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work! I just know the Light shines favorably upon us for our work. Our cause is righteous!' WHERE `entry`=26973;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So he\'s really dead? That means...I, Joseph, am the new Scarlet Champion!!! Take this. I don\'t have a need for such possessions anyways! I\'m the Scarlet Champion, after all.' WHERE `entry`=26974;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Please understand your highness, the men are working double-shifts. The scale of your father\'s operation is enormous. But we will endeavor to wrap things up. I give you my word.' WHERE `entry`=26975;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes! The Scarlet Monastery is ours! You\'re a real friend. Take this as a reward, and feel free to visit again once I\'ve taken the Undercity too. It\'ll be a Scarlet Paradise!' WHERE `entry`=26976;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmmm, yes? My investigation of the Twilight\'s Hammer. Of course. Your assistance will be valuable.' WHERE `entry`=26977;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' The drums are placed?  In their positions? Very well then, I will give the word to the High Executor. When the time is ready, he will be the one to press the ignition switch.' WHERE `entry`=26978;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Leave Drum inside Ranch House',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Leave Drum inside Barn' WHERE `entry`=26978;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N. The Dark Lady watches over you.' WHERE `entry`=26979;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Stoutfist sent you, eh? He\'s a good captain, runs his men well. Just wish he\'d stop starin\' at my midriff. Don\'t let me catch you doin\' it either. We\'ve work to take care of here!' WHERE `entry`=26980;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well met, $C. We\'ve got raptor problems for sure... sort of. More like the entire dig site deciding to attack us. I\'ve never seen rocks and fossils get so upset!' WHERE `entry`=26981;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Captain Nials sent you? I haven\'t seen her in ages! How is she? Did she get my letter? Oh, you\'re not here for that. Well then, let\'s get down to business!' WHERE `entry`=26982;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You came here from Southshore, eh? I bet you hunger for revenge against the vile Forsaken that trashed the place. The Scarlet Crusade can help take care of that! Right after you help me realign their misguided souls, that is.' WHERE `entry`=26983;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You look pretty tough, $C. There are wrongs to be righted here. Let\'s get started.' WHERE `entry`=26984;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wait, you were sent here by THE Shandris Feathermoon? I can barely believe my ears! To know that my cause is supported by her massive army... Yes, yes, you will be perfect. You\'re the key to my future!' WHERE `entry`=26985;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Oftentimes the best way to ensure our men sustain as few injuries as possible is to cause great harm to our enemies in their very homes and prevent battles from ever occurring!$B$BTravel to the Scarlet Monastery and speak with Dark Ranger Velonara in their graveyard. She is leading a Forsaken assault there and could benefit from a seasoned $C such as yourself.',`objectives_loc6`='Report to Dark Ranger Velonara.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='It looks like Darthalia sent an able $C, as I requested.' WHERE `entry`=26986;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m surprised to see Huntsman Markhor working with me for once. He\'s usually quite stubborn. He does tend to a strong hatred for magic, though. I hope you do, too, $C, because we\'re going to strip the Scarlet Crusade of theirs.' WHERE `entry`=26987;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yayo\'jin is correct, you helping me here will aid her in the Hinterlands as well. All the more reason to get started immediately.' WHERE `entry`=26988;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Holyfiresnub has returned! And in one piece! Defender of Silverpine! Redeemer of the Horde! Holyfiresnub, your bravery must be rewarded!' WHERE `entry`=26989;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Sandfury trolls and the Cult of Twilight\'s Hammer, you say? And they meant to send some giant monster into the heart of the city?! Well done! Thunder Bluff is in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=26990;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nazeer is a strong warrior - his hatred for our enemies rivals my own. You are welcome help to my forces.' WHERE `entry`=26991;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Agony abounds, friend! The land itself threatens to devour us, and yet we persist. I wonder why that is? With this doomweed and the guts and gore that T\'Veen needs, we might have something suitable to send to the Forsaken front.' WHERE `entry`=26992;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done. How about I give you a nice reward for your work, and you don\'t tell a soul that you saw me here. Deal?' WHERE `entry`=26993;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very good. Yes, very good indeed. Your reward, as promised. No questions.' WHERE `entry`=26994;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! With these guts and the ferocious doomweed we\'ll be able to test out our new strain of blight. Now to select a suitable target...' WHERE `entry`=26995;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This doesn\'t make any sense, $N. Why was Samuelson sending us out here on a wild goose chase? Something doesn\'t feel right. We should poke around on our own...' WHERE `entry`=26997;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Potent enough to exterminate a thousand murlocs! I think I\'ll put that on the label. You\'ve done well, $N, and great work around here gets rewarded.' WHERE `entry`=26998;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This will be more than enough, $N. Now, I will need some time to perform my studies.' WHERE `entry`=26999;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, it sounds like they\'re certainly afraid of the mustang, but they\'re not leaving for good. I can\'t have you running around on a horse forever. Nor do I think you\'d want to. Fine. Bloodshed it is.' WHERE `entry`=27000;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s much more like it!  Now my lumberjacks can get to work again. Nice riding out there, $N. You cut a pretty impressive silhouette on that mustang.' WHERE `entry`=27001;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='$N. It is truly a pleasure. I know you are young, and still training, but I\'ve had my eye on you. We among the Argent Crusade are always looking for promising new recruits, and you have indeed shown great promise. I have no immediate tasks for you, but merely wished to meet you in person, and see for myself what type of $R you really were. For the time being, the amenities of Hearthglen are yours to enjoy. I look forward to our next meeting, $N. You are dismissed.' WHERE `entry`=27002;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Smells like someone else was in this cell recently. Gross!' WHERE `entry`=27003;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' But... but, this is just gibberish! What does this even say? What language is that?' WHERE `entry`=27004;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This is just gibberish! What does this even say? What language is that?' WHERE `entry`=27005;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A waygate?! The culties dug up a Titan waygate?' WHERE `entry`=27006;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is the place. Our scouts confirmed the presence of high-ranking Twilight officers nearby as well as potential trogg hunting parties. Be on the lookout, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27007;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A waygate?! They unearthed a Titan waygate. This is very interesting and potentially very bad.' WHERE `entry`=27008;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A job well done, $N. The Quilboar here can no longer be saved, but at least they are no longer organized for attack, or slaves under Amnennar\'s tyrannic rule. Leave quickly, please. Razorfen Downs is without hope. It must be purged.' WHERE `entry`=27009;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We have the information we need. Let\'s not tip our hand by engaging the enemy too soon.' WHERE `entry`=27010;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ll just put this back over in the lumber stores outside. Nathaniel probably won\'t even notice it was missing.' WHERE `entry`=27011;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. I\'ll be throwing these in the fire. We don\'t want those gnolls just sneaking in and stealing them back.' WHERE `entry`=27012;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I\'m happy for Nathaniel: he\'s spent so long trying to return to Northridge, and now with the Scarlet Crusade out of the way, he can finally move back home. It\'s just... even for such a seemingly-idyllic setting, it\'s not really the best place to raise a family.$B$BFor example: along this valley\'s edge, you will find rabid foxes searching for innocent prey. Every once in a while I catch a glimpse of one looking right at me.$B$BPlease, $C, remove some of these foxes. I don\'t feel safe with them near.',`objectives_loc6`='Kill 12 Rabid Foxes near Northridge Lumber Mill in Western Plaguelands.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I feel a bit more relieved, $N. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=27013;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have arrived at last. During your training in Camp Narache, I will guide you in the ways of the $C. You have much to learn and I look forward to counting you among my students.' WHERE `entry`=27014;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Just a moment ago a messenger was looking for you, $N. I believe she was sent by the paladin trainer, Sunwalker Helaku. If this note is from the sunwalker, I recommend going to see him immediately.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='We have much to cover. In time, the ways of the sunwalkers will be as plain and natural to you as the shaman\'s conversations with the elements.' WHERE `entry`=27015;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve killed ten already? H...hah! While you were out, I\'ve broken my previous record! To ten... hundred! Yes, ten hundred boars!$B$BA bet is a bet, I suppose... here\'s your consolation prize, $N!' WHERE `entry`=27016;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This... Gloria used to read from this prayer book every night!  How had I forgotten?  She was so devout, $N. Oh... This painting... my daughter, Andrea... she loved to... to paint...' WHERE `entry`=27017;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Fantastic, I thought you looked to be the heroic type!  We\'ve got our work cut out for us $N, I\'m not going to lie to you. If we stay focused on the task at hand, we should be able to come out on top.' WHERE `entry`=27019;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The time has come for your first lesson in the ways of the warrior, $N, and a fitting lesson it is. I will teach you a technique for gaining the upper hand at the start of battle.$B$BCharge into the fray, surprising your enemy, and stunning him. After we have completed our lesson, I want you to try it for yourself.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Charge from Harutt Thunderhorn. Locate a Training Dummy in Camp Narache and practice using Charge.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $N. Return to me when you are in need of further training.' WHERE `entry`=27020;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='It is time for your first lesson, $N. You have a long way to go to master the ways of the hunter, but each new skill is a step on that path. Let me show you a useful shot.$B$BWhen our lesson is concluded, I want you to try it for yourself.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Steady Shot from Lanka Farshot. Locate a Training Dummy in Camp Narache and practice using Steady Shot 5 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $N. Return to me when you are in need of further training.' WHERE `entry`=27021;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Belnistrasz\'s sudden departure has left behind a burning brazier. As you stare in to the flame, the image of a great-winged red dragon fills your mind. A more graveled version of Belnistrasz\'s voice speaks directly to you. "Indeed mortals, you are the heroes I had hoped you would be. Thanks to you the butchery these beasts were perpetrating is a thing of the past. My faith in your kind has been once more renewed. Take this as a reward befitting of a hero."' WHERE `entry`=27022;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='It is always a pleasure to meet a fellow Sunwalker. We are not as numerous as some of the more ancient orders, but our ways are no less powerful and our members no less respected.$B$BAllow me to teach you one of our most basic techniques -- seals and judgments. Using Seal of Righteousness allows you do deal extra holy damage with each swing and you may periodically use Judgement to inflict additional damage to your opponent.$B$BTry it for yourself.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Seal of Righteousness and Judgement from Sunwalker Helaku. Locate a Training Dummy in Camp Narache and practice using Judgement.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have made me proud, $N. You will make a fine Sunwalker. Return when you desire further training.' WHERE `entry`=27023;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done! Without their leaders, the Scourge will pose no significant threat.' WHERE `entry`=27024;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve been informed there\'s a bear warning active for the woodlands as well! They love those stabthistle seeds.$B$BIt\'s a good thing you gathered those so they don\'t attract more bears!' WHERE `entry`=27025;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Okay, yes, I have already been informed that bobcats are much smaller than I was assuming. But that\'s still pretty dangerous for gnomes! You\'ve done a good thing for the safety of this lodge, $N!' WHERE `entry`=27026;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I know you\'ve been busy helping the braves protect Camp Narache from the bristlebacks. We\'re going to need all the hammers and all the luck we can get. Allow me to teach you a simple combat technique to help you in battle.$B$BPrimal Strike should help you fell your enemies faster. Try it out for yourself.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Primal Strike from Meela Dawnstrider. Locate a Training Dummy in Camp Narache and practice using Primal Strike 3 times.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. I see you will have no trouble mastering our more advanced arts as you gain experience. Return to me when you need further training.' WHERE `entry`=27027;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lovely specimens you\'ve got there! Here\'s my wager, lad.' WHERE `entry`=27028;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I have faith that this substance will prevent many future headaches. Thank you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=27029;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahh, you see? Goods of the finest quality. Good work gettin\' these.' WHERE `entry`=27030;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Beautiful. you\'ve got an eye for quality!$B$BGreat minds think alike! It\'s clear you\'ve got an enthusiasm for flight and fowl, so maybe you can help me further...' WHERE `entry`=27031;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I\'ve actually nearly perfected my dream machine: The Skystrider! The world\'s first flying Mechanostrider! But, well$B$BWhen I was putting the finishing touches on it in my secret cavern lab, my other creations became, er, jealous. Giving mechanical birds a personality to begin with was probably a bad idea, but that\'s already done.$B$BI need the Supermechanical Robo-Widget from the original Skystrider if I want to rebuild it! Please, journey into the cave and retrieve it for me!' WHERE `entry`=27032;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect! Now that I\'ve perfected the wing balance and have all the parts I need, all we need is a pilot.' WHERE `entry`=27033;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I don\'t care about my father and his silly inventions! It\'s all just nonsense!' WHERE `entry`=27034;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did it? You did! You fought them and won! There\'s hope after all...' WHERE `entry`=27035;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Er... what\'s this? A bear\'s head, by the looks at it. Well, that\'s quite an interesting kill you have yourself there. Couldn\'t be that bear from back then... Oh, take that away take it away! Get that grisly thing out of here!' WHERE `entry`=27036;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks for helping me out with my little plan, $N. I\'ve been itching for months to get back at that snooty, stuck-up boy, and I\'d say we did a pretty good job! Here, have this, you\'ve earned it.' WHERE `entry`=27037;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Oh aye, \'ere\'s the stuff. But where\'s me powder? Everything\'s here but for the powder. I need explosives, man! You tell the King, no powder, no power. I need me some kersplosions or I ain\'t leavin\' port.' WHERE `entry`=27038;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Belmont gets a little nervous and sends some newbie to look for me? Listen, I\'ve been staking out the old Ivar cottage from inside this outhouse for three days. Your presence threatens the whole damn operation! There\'s no time to explain. We have to act now or this mission will be compromised.' WHERE `entry`=27039;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s the ol\' spirit! One less nasty in this world that the little ones will have ta worry about when they go ta sleep at night. Not ta mention that we won\'t have ta be worrying about him none no more neither! Now let\'s see here. I think we have somethin\' in our crates that\'ll make a fittin\' reward fer ya.' WHERE `entry`=27042;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='An excellent display of $C prowess. I believe that a reward is in order. Something appropriate for a powerful man such as yourself.' WHERE `entry`=27043;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Y- Y- Your highness!' WHERE `entry`=27044;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Alas, poor Yorick! I knew her, $N. An assassin of infinite courage... Now, tell me what\'s going on? What did you and Yorick discover?' WHERE `entry`=27045;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You wage a war that we cannot. Thank you for your help.' WHERE `entry`=27046;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Motes',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $R. These will do well.' WHERE `entry`=27047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well played! I\'ve got this pretty sweet deal going. A bunch of shmucks go up there to Therazane\'s Throne and give all kinds of gold to D\'lom for who-knows-what kinda crap. He forks all that cash over to me for these crystals. I go home freakin\' rich for a couple chunks of rock. Don\'t tell no one though. I don\'t want no competition springin\' up. Think you can come back later to help me get another load of crystals out?' WHERE `entry`=27048;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Once the growth starts, it is near impossible to stomp back into submission. Through persistence our realm will one day be cleansed.' WHERE `entry`=27049;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are proficient at stepping on things. You would make an excellent giant.' WHERE `entry`=27050;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $R. We will weed the rest out of their possession in time.' WHERE `entry`=27051;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Cauldron Lord Soulwrath\'s key disintegrates as it touches the lock on the access panel at the base of the cauldron\'s platform. A slight clanking noise is heard within, and the access panel swings open to reveal more viscous toxins within the cauldron\'s framework. There is a small spigot that the bottle fits well enough under, allowing you to draw a sample for Field Agent Kaartish back at the Menders\' Stead.' WHERE `entry`=27053;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The orders in Malicia\'s possession incriminate Darkmaster Gandling of the Scholomance, but they also conceal another important bit of information.' WHERE `entry`=27054;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have gone above and beyond, $N. Not only have we set back the Cult of the Damned in their crusade to re-plague the plaguelands, but you have uncovered another set of dire plans: they continue to re-animate the dead! Your name will definitely be mentioned when this information is presented to Highlord Fordring, $N. You have my thanks, and the blessing of the Argent Crusade.' WHERE `entry`=27055;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Crowley... A gnat. An insect, waiting to be crushed beneath my boot heel. So he thinks to rouse the feral worgen of Silverpine? We shall show him and his allies the might of the Forsaken! But first we must clean up the mess made by the Warchief\'s fleet. Without their aid we may lose this war.' WHERE `entry`=27056;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work. One moment please... Yes, this appears to be the same corruption that is affecting the wildlife. With this knowledge, and with your combat expertise, we may have the power to stop this.' WHERE `entry`=27057;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did it! You found out what the Twilight\'s Hammer were up to and you stopped them dead in their tracks! Now I\'m certain that I have something around here for you.' WHERE `entry`=27058;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did it! Excellent work, my boy. You found out what the Twilight\'s Hammer were up to and you stopped them dead in their tracks! Now I\'m certain that I have something around here for you.' WHERE `entry`=27059;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That was a close one! I can\'t believe you stood your ground against so many at once. It looks like this site was used for some kind of twisted Twilight\'s Hammer initiation ritual. They\'re definitely active in Stormwind. What\'s this? This badge shows a crossed axe and hammer. It looks old. If we keep poking around, we might figure out what it means...' WHERE `entry`=27060;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So we\'re going to have to take on Abyssion to get the fragment?  This operation just got a whole lot more difficult all of a sudden.' WHERE `entry`=27061;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You seem an able warrior. Perhaps you can help me put an end to the terrible evil here.' WHERE `entry`=27062;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You seem an able warrior. Perhaps you can help me put an end to the terrible evil here.' WHERE `entry`=27063;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is REALLY suspicious, $N! Samuelson doesn\'t have a shred of info here about the Twilight Hammer - it\'s almost like he\'s not investigating them. Yet he\'s got a complete catalog of the missing explosives. And I found this funny badge with a symbol on it: A crossed axe and hammer. It all means something, but what?' WHERE `entry`=27064;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This fiasco may go down as one of the biggest embarrassments in the history of naval warfare. How did this happen? Drunk happened. That\'s how.' WHERE `entry`=27065;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I want to teach you a versatile and quick healing technique, $N. This heal is one you will find yourself using often.$B$BThere is no lack of braves injured in our battles against the Bristlebacks, so you\'ll have a chance to put your new knowledge to use right away. Practice your new healing technique on the wounded braves around Camp Narache.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Flash Heal from Seer Ravenfeather. Practice using Flash Heal 5 times on Wounded Braves in Camp Narache.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for your help in seeing to the wounded braves. I\'m sure that you will often find your healing skills in demand. Return to me when you need further instruction.' WHERE `entry`=27066;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I want to teach you a basic healing technique, $N. This spell will allow you to aid wounded allies by healing their wounds over a short period of time.$B$BMany braves have been injured in our fight to defend Camp Narache, so your healing skills will be put to good use. Practice your new healing technique on the wounded braves around Camp Narache.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Rejuvination from Gart Mistrunner. Practice using Rejuvination on a Wounded Brave in Camp Narache.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have a knack for the healing arts, $N. Wherever you go, your skills as a healer will be in demand. Return to me when you are ready for more training.' WHERE `entry`=27067;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='He\'s gone? Did he have the sword? Nah...don\'t tell me. Don\'t matter no more. Mazoga don\'t care. I\'m off now, mon. De consequences of my actions await me. Take whatever I was holdin\'... I don\'t need it where I\'m goin\'...' WHERE `entry`=27068;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='We may not have to live down the shame of this defeat, $N. The Warchief will likely have us all executed instead.$B$BI\'ll be damned if we don\'t go down without a fight. Although the whole beachhead is overrun by Bloodfang worgen, there may still be hope. I want you to accompany one of our sea pups to the Beachhead, directly west of here, and recover our supplies. Return to me when the pup can carry no more.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Within these crates are held STEEL THUNDER! With our weaponry returned we might have a chance to redeem ourselves.' WHERE `entry`=27069;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I heard that a troll in here, Hydromancer Velratha I think she was called, has come into the possession of a very rare, beautiful, and powerful piece of jewelry called the Tiara of the Deep. She uses it to control the powerful demigod Gahz\'rilla, whose very scales are said to crackle with energy. Do you know what all of that means, $R?$B$BI need it! Kill Velratha, take the Tiara of the Deep, and kill Gahz\'rilla for one of his scales. Bring them all back to me pronto! I\'ll reward you handsomly.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! This Tiara will grant me complete control of the water around here, and the Electrified Scale will serve to power all the machines I need to use it all to my advantage! You\'re going to make me a very rich and powerful goblin! You can have this, it\'s nothing compared to what I\'ll have soon.' WHERE `entry`=27070;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You killed dem? All of dem? And you return alive? Take what you want off my body, den. It\'s mostly curse-free, Mazoga promises.' WHERE `entry`=27071;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' $C? What are you doing here? I\'m SI:7 Agent Jack Bauden. This is the longest day of my life.' WHERE `entry`=27072;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Looks as if you really gave those worgen a beating and, in the process, lifted the "shame haze" they cast over us. Perhaps the sea dogs will quit drinkin\' now. Who am I kidding? Hah!' WHERE `entry`=27073;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You hit the twilight camp at the center of the lake? Not bad, lad! If you\'re ready to take the fight right to their doorstep, I\'ve got your chance.' WHERE `entry`=27074;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It may look grim, but we\'ll win with your help, $N. They won\'t keep the dwarves down.' WHERE `entry`=27075;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wow! I knew I could count on you! Here\'s something for your troubles.' WHERE `entry`=27076;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Shame that these half-formed things are too brittle and warped to be used for some weapons of our own. But it\'s thanks to you that we had the chance to get them out before they set. I\'m not about to complain.' WHERE `entry`=27077;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Gor\'kresh',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done it! We may not have stopped the cult dead, but we\'ve shown them we\'re not easy pickings and given them a welt to prove it. Take this with my gratitude, and try not to blush if anyone in Thelsamar calls you "hero"!' WHERE `entry`=27078;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! Now to prepare the "meal."' WHERE `entry`=27082;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thassarian and the humans made their move. I thought I had an agreement with Thassarian... but I suppose this will do.' WHERE `entry`=27083;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Merely a dent in their numbers... but the sight of their fellow men falling from the skies surely weakened their resolve.' WHERE `entry`=27084;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You fight well, $N. I wish I had your ability... and your bravery.' WHERE `entry`=27085;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done. With them out of the way, I have no more excuses. Soon, I must battle Thassarian, for honor and for Andorhal.' WHERE `entry`=27086;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You won\'t be taking me anywhere, $N. While Koltira prances about with his playmate, Thassarian, I plan to win this battle. Then I\'ll make Koltira suffer for his weakness. Don\'t believe me?  Fine, I\'ll let you in on a little secret...' WHERE `entry`=27087;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Was there ever any doubt? An ettin is no match for science!' WHERE `entry`=27088;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='With the Enthralled Val\'kyr by your side, kill 5 Frightened Provincial Minutemen, then use your Call to Arms ability to turn them into Forsaken Troopers. Then find Thassarian in western Andorhal.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is the body of Lurid, Thassarian\'s trusted knight. With Thassarian nowhere to be found, it would seem that the Alliance forces have withdrawn. The Forsaken have won the battle for Andorhal.' WHERE `entry`=27089;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='See?  All it took was a little help from the val\'kyr. These creatures are turning to be much more helpful than I had first thought. Now, on to other matters.' WHERE `entry`=27090;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='And now, it is time for your first lesson.$B$BI will show you a  great way to start combat, $N. By seizing the initiative and charging in, you can stun your opponent and give yourself the upper hand.$B$BOnce our lesson has ended, find a training dummy and practice your new skill.',`objectives_loc6`='Learn Charge from Delios. Locate a Training Dummy outside the Sunspire and practice using Charge.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I think you\'ve mastered the basics of the charge, $N. Don\'t forget to return when you need more training.' WHERE `entry`=27091;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<3 ... 2 ... 1 ...> Underneath the powder kegs you find a heap of notes and papers. Apparently the cultists were trying to destroy the evidence behind them.>' WHERE `entry`=27092;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lok\'tar, $N! Once the ale wears off my orcs will be ready!' WHERE `entry`=27093;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You rescued our orcs and killed the Skitterweb matriarch? We owe you a great debt of gratitude. You\'ve saved us all from certain execution, $N. I\'m sure we can rouse these drunken idiots now.' WHERE `entry`=27094;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The root of this evil must be found and destroyed! The Skitterweb matriarch must be nearby. No doubt hiding in the nearby cave!' WHERE `entry`=27095;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='<Admiral Hatchet hands you an envelope sealed with the mark of the Horde.>$B$BThis is your commendation letter. It\'s the least I could do for you given the circumstances.$B$BReturn to Lady Sylvanas Windrunner with the letter and inform her of our status. Let her know that we will be ready to march on her command.$B$BGoodbye, $N. You are an excellent soldier.$B$BNortheast, $G lad:ma\'am;. To Forsaken High Command!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' So the orcs are in order? Recovered their supplies? Killed a dozen worgen? Toppled an ettin? Freed their soldiers and destroyed the Skitterweb matriarch? I say this rarely, $N, but I am impressed. Perhaps your ability matches your aspirations. We shall see, for now you will be tested!' WHERE `entry`=27096;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see everything, $N. Through Agatha all is known to me.' WHERE `entry`=27097;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Lordaeron',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Do you now understand the importance of our mission here? Crowley and his Alliance dogs must be stopped!' WHERE `entry`=27098;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='You must strike at their leaders, $N. You will find them holed up in the old keep. Battle your way inside and find the holdouts! Turn them for your queen!$B$BNone shall escape the mighty grasp of the Forsaken!',`objectives_loc6`='Find the Refugee Leadership inside Fenris Keep.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='It would seem that Crowley is more formidable than I anticipated. Still, he is a man - flesh and bone - full of secrets. Secrets that I know all about... You have served me well, $N. I could use someone of your ability at the Sepulcher. I have a plan to deal with Crowley and his insurgents once and for all. Will you help?' WHERE `entry`=27099;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The notes deal with High Cultist Maziel\'s research on the elemental properties of quicksilver. His obsession with the subject borders on the insane.' WHERE `entry`=27100;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Maziel\'s journal appears to be undamaged by the mercury.' WHERE `entry`=27101;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve disposed of an enemy before he could grow more powerful. By eliminating Maziel you\'ve also ensured that his powers will not be used against the Earthen Ring.' WHERE `entry`=27102;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done well, $C, and for that I am forever in your debt. Though the war is far from over, a great battle has been won against those who would bring about our doom. Please - accept this gold as a token of my enduring gratitude. If we ever cleanse Dire Maul, know that you will be welcomed here as a hero. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=27103;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, very well done indeed. You\'ve made an old spirit very happy this day. You deserve proper thanks for the risks you\'ve taken.' WHERE `entry`=27104;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is very troublesome that a water elemental was here, let alone one that powerful. Take this as my thanks for your efforts. I must examine this essence for any knowledge it may contain.' WHERE `entry`=27105;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Samuelson - corrupted by the Twilight\'s Hammer? This must have been going on for years. Right here in my very keep! I am grateful that you and my son were able to get to the bottom of this before my city was brought to harm. I\'ve underestimated how much Anduin has grown - his command of the holy light just saved my life, if not the entire kingdom. As for you - words alone can\'t do justice to your heroism this day. Thank you, $C.' WHERE `entry`=27106;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now you watch Master use book to kill stupid trees and stupid goat men! YAR!' WHERE `entry`=27107;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This web have lots of magic! Master will be very happy now! And you make Dagg\'thol happy, $R. Take this so you believe how happy you make Dagg\'thol!' WHERE `entry`=27108;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your work here was noble. Fret not, for Tendris\' soul was crying to be put to rest. He is thankful.' WHERE `entry`=27109;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We thank you, hero.' WHERE `entry`=27110;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You open the chest to find...' WHERE `entry`=27111;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your dedication will make this all that much easier.' WHERE `entry`=27112;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Our meeting is no coincidence, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27113;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s working! My father brought it!' WHERE `entry`=27115;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What in blazes WAS that? A flying mechanostrider? You know what, I don\'t want to know. I\'m just going to pretend that didn\'t happen, and we\'ll be all nice and businesslike.' WHERE `entry`=27116;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellently done, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27117;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yeah, this will do the trick. Just a slip here, and tuck here... heh - this is going to work out just fine!   Here you go, you\'re all set. Remember- this isn\'t the most securely fashioned item in the world. You\'ll have ten minutes of use before it falls apart, and then you\'re not going to fool anybody!  Try using it just before you approach him to make sure it lasts as long as you\'re going to need it.' WHERE `entry`=27119;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Here ya go $N - put this thing on, and you\'ll have ten minutes to do whatever. Good luck!$B$BOh, and if you happen to find a key to get me out of here, BY ALL MEANS LET ME KNOW!!!' WHERE `entry`=27120;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dark Iron dwarves and Ragnaros the Firelord, ye say? At the behest of the Cult o\' Twilight\'s Hammer? Well done! Ironforge is in yer debt.' WHERE `entry`=27122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve arrived just in time, $N. All our resources are tied up keeping the rift stable. We need someone like you to help us recover the fragments of the World Pillar.' WHERE `entry`=27123;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wow... you ARE da true king! Old king never even ask about da gauntlet! Look - this mark on da gauntlet an old old OLD timey magic mark, older than da Gordok they say. Well, I learn one thing as little ogre - how to make mark come to life and give power back to gauntlet! I do it for you, king!  Here, take da gauntlet and rule FOREVER!' WHERE `entry`=27124;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes! I can see that you were indeed successful. You have received your tribute, the Gordok advance will exist no longer, and the Gordok are blissfully ignorant! This is a true winner\'s scenario, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27125;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can\'t thank you enough, $C. Now, let\'s see if we can get this catapult moving again.' WHERE `entry`=27126;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dark Iron dwarves and Ragnaros the Firelord, you say? At the behest of the Cult of Twilight\'s Hammer? Well done! Orgrimmar is in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=27127;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Little $R did it! Now Horde more powerful than ever! YAR!' WHERE `entry`=27128;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Have you been in contact with a druid of the talon recently, $C? I can feel the lingering presence of one.' WHERE `entry`=27129;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your face shows signs of desperate conflict. I honor your presence, brave $C.' WHERE `entry`=27130;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I sensed your coming all the way from Dreamer\'s Rest. Your assistance would be most welcome.' WHERE `entry`=27131;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I sensed your coming all the way from Camp Mojache. Your assistance would be most welcome.' WHERE `entry`=27132;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Speak softly, $N. The Gordok may not be intelligent, but they are still dangerous warriors.' WHERE `entry`=27133;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These ogres no pushovers. I need you help me finish Orhan\'s task, $R.' WHERE `entry`=27134;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Uh oh. Sounds like he wasn\'t very happy about the situation. How was I to know? I\'m just an initiate after all. Anyway, I\'ll worry about Magmatooth later.' WHERE `entry`=27135;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. We need all the power we can muster to keep Deepholm stable.' WHERE `entry`=27136;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There you are, my boy. I have something very important for you to do!' WHERE `entry`=27139;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did it!  They are defeated!  And the Gambit... did it work? Very interesting. You\'ve done well, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27140;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Shake it off, kid. Happens to me all the time...' WHERE `entry`=27141;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ten thousand souls cry out in unison, $N! You have struck a mortal blow to the Scourge and their masters.' WHERE `entry`=27142;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $R. Alexi deserves nothing for his foolishness.' WHERE `entry`=27143;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I have nothing against the Knights of the Ebon Blade, but Koltira needs to be reminded who he works for now. His loyalty must lie with the Horde. Or, more specifically, the Forsaken. I wouldn\'t plan on seeing Koltira anytime soon. Now that I have him... you can rest assured that any bonds he may have had with that Alliance scum will be thoroughly broken.' WHERE `entry`=27144;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N!  It\'ll be a long time before they can grow another clutch of dragons.$B$B...At least, I hope it will!' WHERE `entry`=27145;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can feel my spirit healing, $N. You have done my husband and I a great service.' WHERE `entry`=27146;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Destroy Kirtonos.',`objectives_loc6`='Destroy Kirtonos.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='With the death of Kirtonos, a chapter in the horrible tale of Scholomance comes to a close. You have my deepest, everlasting gratitude for your bravery.' WHERE `entry`=27147;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Without a headmaster, the school will descend into chaos. It will not put forth any more of its vile \'students\' into the field. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=27148;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I must admit, $N... I have been using my mind vision spell to keep tabs on you. And I must say... the number of gnolls you found on the trail is truly staggering!' WHERE `entry`=27151;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Gnolls and necromancy... what a surprise!  And I thought that, here in the Western Plaguelands, we had put these dark days behind us. Wait... what is THAT?' WHERE `entry`=27152;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Did you notice, $N?  Many names were mentioned, but one name was mentioned far more than the others. Bisp.' WHERE `entry`=27153;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Speak with Bree Ironstock',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Speak with High Cleric Alphus' WHERE `entry`=27153;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I suppose that we can take his aggression as an admission of guilt. You alright, $N?' WHERE `entry`=27154;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m already aware of your actions, $N. I welcome you into my town, give you my blessing, and what do you do? You slay the traitor that we\'ve been hunting down for weeks. Well done. Your heroism is budding much earlier than even I had anticipated.' WHERE `entry`=27155;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m just looking over my paperwork here, and it says that we were expecting a FEMALE $R $C. You\'re not, umm... Never mind. It would appear that you are not the person that I originally hired, but you did a good job. So I\'m going to pay you anyhow.' WHERE `entry`=27156;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice work!  In retrospect, I\'m glad that other $R $C never showed up... you\'ve proven to be all the help I need.' WHERE `entry`=27157;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s about time you arrived, $C.' WHERE `entry`=27158;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You may not act quickly, but at least you do not fail me. Very well. I will have a more important task for you, $N, when the time is right.' WHERE `entry`=27159;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Abominations... strong. $N... stronger.' WHERE `entry`=27160;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These grenades are all explosives, nothing more. I may not be a goblin engineer... but I still understand the value of being able to just explode things every once in a while.' WHERE `entry`=27161;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Scholomancer',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellently done, $N. And now, with the leader of the Scourge forces eliminated from Andorhal, we bide our time.' WHERE `entry`=27162;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellently done, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27163;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Araj dead... this is good. That gnome has done his part in winning this war. As have you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27164;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Word arrived shortly before you did, $N. With the Scourge ejected from Andorhal, we are one step closer to retaking Lordaeron.' WHERE `entry`=27165;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I will have my fletchers get to work on these. I\'m glad to see you being so useful right away, $N. Perhaps later I will have some more exciting tasks for you.' WHERE `entry`=27166;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You hunt like a true $C. Even if we can\'t set up our homesteads... at least we can still eat.' WHERE `entry`=27167;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hopefully most of them passed on peacefully. I thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27168;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You and the humans at Chillwind Camp wish to re-take Andorhal?  I wish you luck.' WHERE `entry`=27169;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Scattered all over the bottom level of the crypt, you find shattered crates that once held weapons and armor. It appears that somebody got here before you did.' WHERE `entry`=27170;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Attacked by ghosts?  Strange. I suppose that crypt wasn\'t fully healed after all. You just missed Thurman Grant... you remember, that oaf of a farmer that was here earlier. He took his men with him and traveled to the nearest farm... against my orders.' WHERE `entry`=27171;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, now that you\'re here, we\'ll gladly take that armor off your hands. You can keep the weapons, though. These men wouldn\'t know which end to hold.' WHERE `entry`=27172;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You fight well, $R. My men could stand to learn a few moves from an experienced $C like you.' WHERE `entry`=27173;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We can handle things from here. I thank you for your help, $N. I assume that when we next meet, it will be in battle. Take care of yourself until then. We\'ll need all the help we can get.' WHERE `entry`=27174;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome, $C. As you can see, our camp is a joint expedition between Argent Crusade members and Cenarion Circle druids, but we welcome all who wish to help heal the land.' WHERE `entry`=27175;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Let\'s have a look at this. Shall we?' WHERE `entry`=27176;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Look at all this! You were able to recover more than I thought. We can outfit a whole squad of marines with this stuff. We have the gear. If we only had some way to bolster our numbers here in the Highlands...' WHERE `entry`=27177;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'ll send \'em packing, $N! Cho\'gall won\'t be able to count on the naga to back him up in this fight. From here on out, it\'s just us versus the Twilight\'s Hammer. ...And the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27178;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These tablets are covered with titan writings. There\'s never-before seen information here, $N! Missing pieces to an ancient puzzle... Good work!' WHERE `entry`=27179;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I will see to it that these insignias are returned to the Undercity at once. The registrar will place their names in our records so that their sacrifice may never be forgotten.' WHERE `entry`=27180;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You have avenged the fallen, $N, but there is more to be done.' WHERE `entry`=27181;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Have you come here to spy on me? No?$B$BPerhaps you have an appreciation for fine cuisine, then? Good, you can help!' WHERE `entry`=27182;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, that\'s the spice! Now here\'s some swampy good stew.' WHERE `entry`=27183;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You got the eyes! You got the eyes! Tasty, tasty spider eyes!$B$BSome eyes... when you stare at them they stare back. Eat those last. They keep you company... out in the swamp.$B$BHello, little spider eyes. Hello! You taste like chicken. Gooey, salty chicken!$B$BMmmh.' WHERE `entry`=27184;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nicely done, lad! Without them new weapons, they\'re just as easy t\' kill as they were when they were alive!' WHERE `entry`=27185;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s a good blade. It has a good swing. It\'s a good swing blade. Thank you. Thank you, thank you, thank you!!! Now I want to try it....$B$BLater. I\'ll try it later. But like I was saying... thanks.' WHERE `entry`=27186;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' From your findings, the spirits in this place must amount to everyone who ever lived on this land, not just the previous occupants. Something has been corrupting and killing them. Those who follow don\'t learn the truth until it\'s too late. We have to put an end to this, $N!' WHERE `entry`=27188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' These match the description exactly! I prepared the torch while you were out. All that remains is to fasten the herbs to the end here.' WHERE `entry`=27189;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It worked? I mean... it worked! Jarl and I are in your debt, $N. Now the only remaining problem is my friend\'s taste in furniture, and I\'m afraid that won\'t be solved as easily.' WHERE `entry`=27190;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonder what it\'s like to be an ogre. Big people have to eat more. Ogres must be even hungrier than me. That doesn\'t sound very fun.' WHERE `entry`=27191;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Recover a box of Fras Siabi\'s Premium Tobacco.',`objectives_loc6`='Recover a box of Fras Siabi\'s Premium Tobacco.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Truly, you have uncovered the snuff of legends. It is nearly impossible to place a value on this historical tobacco. Here, have a few coins.' WHERE `entry`=27192;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This book documents a recent meeting with Ivus Bloodfang. The location mentioned is the Deep Elem Mine. I know of this place. It has only one entrance. We shall corner and crush them!' WHERE `entry`=27193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I \'spose we\'re to corner them first then crush, eh?' WHERE `entry`=27194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='WHAT!? CROWLEY!!!!! Bastards. Those were some of our strongest soldiers. I have underestimated Crowley and Bloodfang for the last time. Clearly they are an enemy the likes of which we have never seen - willing to sacrifice their own to set a trap like this... unheard of in Alliance warfare.' WHERE `entry`=27195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Would you get a load of this place!' WHERE `entry`=27196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Word has it that you helped those farmers arm themselves. Well, now they\'ve initiated the attack without my order!  They\'ve forced my hand. The battle has resumed. This time, we fight the Forsaken... and I fight Koltira, my old brother of the Ebon Blade.' WHERE `entry`=27197;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You fight well, $N. I wish I had your ability... and your bravery.' WHERE `entry`=27198;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done. With them out of the way, I have no more excuses. Soon, I must battle Koltira, for honor and for Andorhal.' WHERE `entry`=27199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='She had me under her spell, $N. I wouldn\'t have made it out of there alive if it weren\'t for you. Thank you! Maybe the rest of the Alliance fleet can finally anchor here in peace...' WHERE `entry`=27200;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='For every val\'kyr you slay, you save dozens of our men... and prevent the Forsaken forces from growing. Still, they press on. We may not win this battle after all.' WHERE `entry`=27201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You fought valiantly, but we\'re getting nowhere. Every body that falls just fuels their forces.' WHERE `entry`=27202;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is good to see you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27203;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Aradne',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I watched your victory from below. Well-fought, but ultimately, it was for naught. The val\'kyr and the Forsaken press on; soon, they will overtake us. We have lost Andorhal.' WHERE `entry`=27204;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Val\'kyr?  Koltira brought val\'kyr to this fight?  Has he gone mad? No, this is not Koltira\'s work. This was Sylvanas.' WHERE `entry`=27205;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lost?  No... next, they\'ll be coming for Chillwind, I suppose. This was a major strategic blow to the Alliance\'s plans for Lordaeron. Very well. I will report the results of this battle to King Wrynn. I don\'t expect him to be happy.' WHERE `entry`=27206;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A massive prince of the wind, you say? The herald of Al\'Akir, the Windlord? Madness. All of it. Stormwind is in your debt, hero.' WHERE `entry`=27207;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good we stopped Balnazzar now. Before long, his army would have overtaken all of Stratholme, giving him a powerful center for his new unholy empire.' WHERE `entry`=27208;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A massive prince of the wind, you say? The herald of Al\'Akir, the Windlord? Madness. All of it. All of Thunder Bluff is in your debt, $C.' WHERE `entry`=27209;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. I think we managed to catch them off guard. Their agents probably thought themselves safe within the city walls.$B$BGiven time, the agitators will return and spread their lies again. We\'ll use the time you\'ve bought to shut out the deserters further.' WHERE `entry`=27210;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Excellent. All that remains is to discredit the deserters so that they\'ll never gain a foothold in Theramore again, and I have just the plan to do it.' WHERE `entry`=27211;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Just as I\'d hoped! I think it\'s safe to say any deserter agents who try to infiltrate Theramore will be laughed right out of town!' WHERE `entry`=27212;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Gavis\' request isn\'t as outlandish as it might sound. With the proper handling, Lady Jaina can return the deserters to the fold, but that is her decision, of course.$B$BIt\'s been a pleasure working with you, $N. Without your help, I doubt the operation would\'ve gone so smoothly. When I make my report in Stormwind, it will name you as the $C who ended the deserter threat.' WHERE `entry`=27213;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' So you\'ve heard about the recent shipwreck off the coast? Good, I could use some help confirming my suspicions about the survivors. Welcome aboard, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27214;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Get off my lawn... unless, that is, you want to help old "Swamp Eye" with a little bit of cooking. Whad\'ya say?' WHERE `entry`=27215;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good. I can use all the help you can offer. My first priority is to get that lamp re-lit.' WHERE `entry`=27216;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, I have my doubts, but this is the only solution available right now. Once we have it up and running, I\'m sure there will be time to look at other ways to fuel the lamp.' WHERE `entry`=27217;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, now, that was thoughtful o\' Babs to send that over. I don\'t know if you\'ve leafed through it or not, but there\'s a lot of truth to the tales in that book. Sailors didn\'t just make it all up, you know.' WHERE `entry`=27218;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you want to know about sea monsters? Hmm... well, I\'ll make you a deal, but it\'s going to involve a lot of alcohol and some embarrassment on your part.' WHERE `entry`=27219;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not bad at all, but you know, I think I\'d get a bath in as soon as possible, if I was you.$B$BNow, about your sea monster...$B$BHelp yourself to a brew or two in the meantime.' WHERE `entry`=27220;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Well, it sounds like we\'ve got our work cut out for us. I\'ll make the preparations.' WHERE `entry`=27221;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N! I\'ll admit, when I caught my first glimpse of that beast, I had doubts about our ability to defend the docks, but you held together the defenders brilliantly!' WHERE `entry`=27222;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You may have this as a suitable reward. I found it nestled in the armor of one of the scourge here.' WHERE `entry`=27223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to see that you received my message. I have something important I wish to discuss with you.' WHERE `entry`=27225;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A-HA! I knew it! Lesson learned, I suppose. We will not fail again. I will be sure to have some ale on hand at the front lines.' WHERE `entry`=27226;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Stratholme will become a paragon of all that is good in this world. You have my thanks for your part in this mission.' WHERE `entry`=27227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I respect the power you demonstrated in killing Ramstein. With proper rage backing your actions, I think even the Scourge can know fear.' WHERE `entry`=27228;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='By Grom, I\'m glad that\'s over with. If you read that sign you may have some idea how desperate I got after trying to communicate to these lumbering oafs.' WHERE `entry`=27229;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great! Without a steady flow of their weapons, we\'ll win through attrition!' WHERE `entry`=27230;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Those that survived your assault on Fenris managed to drink the blood of the wolf. They turned into ferocious worgen, hell-bent on vengeance. Now they paddle across Lordamere Lake and assault my sea dogs. Many have already been killed. The worgen monsters must be stopped!$B$BMake your way to the Decrepit Fields, east of here, and kill the Hillsbrad Worgen that infest the area. Once you\'ve killed them all, make your way to the Horde communication panel, located at the docks. I\'ll be in touch.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Hatchet here, are they all dead?' WHERE `entry`=27231;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Though you killed a large number of the newly turned worgen, many more are sure to appear. Still, their assault will have softened. Well done, $N!' WHERE `entry`=27232;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome, $C. As you can see, our camp is a joint expedition between Argent Crusade members and Cenarion Circle druids, but we welcome all who wish to help heal the land.' WHERE `entry`=27233;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' What in the world could \'precious cargo\' refer to? The Defias have done some small time smuggling back in Stormwind, but this seems out of their league. The language of these orders suggests a wealthy or noble patron.' WHERE `entry`=27234;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' So there was valuable cargo on board! We have to locate it before the Defias recover it. These guys are no divers, but we\'re going to need some of their gear if you\'re to help me find the cargo.' WHERE `entry`=27235;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wow, this is in worse shape than I\'d thought, and these tools...$B$BWell, I said I\'d get this back into working condition for you, so I\'d better get to work.' WHERE `entry`=27236;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Good work. Now, let\'s see if our \'precious cargo\' is in here....' WHERE `entry`=27237;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You and Renn have done excellent work in bringing this information to light and reporting it immediately. Now, we must confirm your findings. The implications are too great if we are wrong.' WHERE `entry`=27238;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' A rune circle, dragonkin? The Defias have allied themselves with HER? The traitor?' WHERE `entry`=27239;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Speak with Jaina to travel to Stormwind and meet with King Varian Wrynn.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='So it was the Defias who served as the hands of Onyxia in this plot? You and Lady Jaina have done Stormind a great service this day. The traitors will not live long enough to regret their crimes.' WHERE `entry`=27240;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I have no doubt that the king meant every word when he told you he plans to destroy the Defias once and for all. He does not make promises lightly, and the enemies of Stormwind should know it.' WHERE `entry`=27241;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You look a little scratched up, but nothing major. You\'re certainly in a lot better shape than the Grimtotems will be when our new raptor friends get done with them.' WHERE `entry`=27242;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Good. That ought to forestall a raid or two.' WHERE `entry`=27243;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, $N. Our agent, Marg Nighteye, was stationed outside Theramore. He was charged to spy on the city. $B$BThis is his latest report, and it may be his last -- from your testimony, I fear that Marg met his end in the swamp...' WHERE `entry`=27244;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Collect Grimtotem Keys from the Grimtotem tauren in Blackhoof Village and use them to free 5 Theramore Prisoners.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='The freed captives have already begun returning from Blackhoof Village. The information the captain is receiving from the prisoners will give us an advantage in our next battle against the Grimtotems.$B$BYou have my thanks and that of the men.' WHERE `entry`=27245;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hm... I can\'t read orcish very well, but this looks like a report... written by an orc spy!' WHERE `entry`=27246;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A report from an orc spy! How did you find this? No matter -- let\'s see what it says...' WHERE `entry`=27247;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So Theramore is interested in doing business? Well, that\'s not an offer I\'d turn down. Supplies are pretty scarce here right now, so we need all the business contacts we can get!' WHERE `entry`=27248;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to see that Captain Vimes is finally assigning others to this investigation.$B$BI\'ve used a reflective powder to dust the area. It will reveal suspicious objects and markings, helping you to focus your efforts. Look over anything the dust illuminates.' WHERE `entry`=27249;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='REUSE - BAD COPY' WHERE `entry`=27250;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='James Hyal\'s his real name. He opened an inn at the edge of the Barrens. Wanted to make a nice place for travelers to stop over...$B$BMight be he was thinking too big, but the inn did do well for a while. Then we lost control of the roads in the marsh, and the ogres took over.$B$BJames was too stubborn to give up his dream for safety within our walls, and the Shady Rest Inn was burnt to the ground. We\'re investigating, but haven\'t had much luck. If you want to help out, see what you can find in the rubble.' WHERE `entry`=27251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hm, I\'m no expert with the construction of arms and armor. Their use, yes, but not their making.$B$BThis shield seems as ordinary as any, excepting the damage from the fire that engulfed the inn.' WHERE `entry`=27252;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Leave this place be, errand boy, or I\'ll be sure to bring a contingent of guard with me next time to sink the lesson home.' WHERE `entry`=27253;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I grant that humans have strange decorating tastes, but would they use a plain iron shield to adorn their fireplace? Perhaps this shield was placed there by the ones who burned the inn.$B$BA warning? A threat?' WHERE `entry`=27254;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is good shield. Very strong, heavy, good. But Do\'gol don\'t need it. I make shields, not buy them, $N.$B$BYou should know that.' WHERE `entry`=27255;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I don\'t like spiders that are so big I can\'t sit on them and squish them.$B$BThanks for getting them, $N. Now I rip them open and pour them onto the shield...' WHERE `entry`=27256;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Mosarn? Sounds familiar... I can\'t put my finger on it. Maybe it\'ll come to me later.$B$BIt probably isn\'t important. A shield can come from anywhere and not mean anything...' WHERE `entry`=27257;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, you are certainly correct. This is a shield that I made.$B$BI\'m afraid there\'s not much more I can tell you though, $N. I craft so many different shields and sets of armor, I can\'t keep track of them all.' WHERE `entry`=27258;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hoofprints... It could have been the quilboar, I suppose. Or maybe even the centaur. Their presence in the Barrens is not insignificant, and I would not think it a stretch to commit such an act.$B$BDid I tell you? It wasn\'t just that the inn was burned down... The owner\'s woman and pup were killed. Bad business, that.$B$BNonetheless, I will send Kagoro to find where the tracks lead.' WHERE `entry`=27259;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm... now this is interesting.' WHERE `entry`=27260;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmph. It is good that Reethe will no longer be lurking around the swamp, but it is a shame that humans are built so frail that he could not recover from a little arrow wound.$B$BIt seems that this thread of the mystery has led nowhere, and we must look elsewhere.' WHERE `entry`=27261;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hoofprints, eh? It is true that there is an extraordinary amount of centaur activity in the lands near the Dustwallow Marsh. In brief excursions into the Barrens, we found their camps and holdings dotting the area.$B$BI\'ll send out Falgran Hastil, one of our trackers, to see if he can find where the tracks lead.' WHERE `entry`=27262;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s never good news when a guard\'s badge is brought to me.$B$BSometimes it\'s a man or woman who\'s fallen in battle, and I\'m left to bring the news to the grieving family. Other times we never find out what happened to them. And other times it\'s even worse than that.' WHERE `entry`=27263;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello, $N. You\'d like information about a specific member of the Theramore guard? Reethe, was it?$B$BJust give me a moment to find the right book.' WHERE `entry`=27264;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It heartens me to see that my message found you, $N. We have much to discuss.' WHERE `entry`=27265;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you\'ve arrived. Make yourself at home, $N. We have much to discuss.' WHERE `entry`=27266;
