UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I will send Lieutenant Caldwell to deal with the deserters at Lost Point. In addition, I will instruct him to find Reethe. The marsh is not so big and trackless that he should be unable to find him.' WHERE `entry`=27288;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well if it isn\'t Mesnanub! I hope you\'re ready for battle, because that\'s all you\'ll find in this hellhole. We\'re at the heart of contested territory and these worgen mongrels won\'t give an inch!' WHERE `entry`=27290;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' It\'s good to know that they understand. You didn\'t tell them about James, did you? I\'ll deliver his wife\'s message to him, but I doubt he\'ll understand.' WHERE `entry`=27291;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='He actually said that the Grimtotems are his biggest customers? Mosarn gave us more help than he knows. With this much pointing toward the Grimtotems, I think we just found our first suspects.' WHERE `entry`=27292;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' There\'s no doubt in my mind that the Grimtotems are moving against the humans. What I don\'t understand is what their intentions are toward us. We knew nothing of these plans and we lost a good man because of it. I don\'t trust that we\'re not next on their list.' WHERE `entry`=27293;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This is unmistakably the work of Mosarn. Questioning him further may draw too much attention, but we have a bit more freedom in dealing with the Grimtotems.' WHERE `entry`=27294;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Krog wishes me to scry for the Grimtotems, eh? Well, I have no need of magic in this case. It seems we have a mutual enemy. The Grimtotems have built an outpost nearby and are a constant thorn in the side of me and my students.' WHERE `entry`=27295;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Use Tabetha\'s Torch to burn he North Tent, East Tent, and the Northeast Tent at Direhorn Post.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Grimtotems should have no trouble understanding our latest message. As for you, your contact at Brackenwall Village will want to know of your success. If I know him, he\'ll appreciate the taste of vengeance.' WHERE `entry`=27296;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I\'m impressed, $N. I would\'ve thought that the Grimtotem criminals would\'ve been more difficult to locate. The Alliance are truly incompetent. In truth, I just sought to answer the death of one of my men, but this situation has been more fortunate than expected. If the Grimtotem choose to retaliate, it will likely be against the Alliance. Perhaps we will soon have the manpower to drive the scum from these shores once and for all.' WHERE `entry`=27297;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ve heard much about you, $N. You have a bright future ahead of you in the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27298;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='It won\'t be takin\' much convincin\' to turn us against da Twilight - dat\'s already our goal. We\'ve already come to battle here though, so we may be needin\' ya help before we can turn towards dey\'re fortress.$B$BDa Twilight have already brought Iso\'rath up from da ground to the south, I\'m sure ya noticed. It\'s tentacles have been burstin\' from da ground all around us. We could use a hand beatin\' them down if you be willin\'.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Tank ya, $C. A bit of breathin\' room helps a lot.' WHERE `entry`=27299;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Revenge is bittersweet, but I\'m glad we be havin\' someone as powerful as you do see dis done.' WHERE `entry`=27300;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Unbroken',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank the elements that you\'ve come. Did my brothers send you?' WHERE `entry`=27301;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now that\'s what I\'m talkin\' about! Can you think of all the uses for this stuff? I definitely can\'t. But I can think of a lot, and I\'m liking the possibilities.' WHERE `entry`=27302;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. You are quite capable. I\'m extremely grateful that you\'ve chosen to aid us.' WHERE `entry`=27303;
