UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ander told me to expect you. It\'s quite an honor to be crafting a weapon for you, $N. With these materials, it will be a fine blade indeed.' WHERE `entry`=27337;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Keep your head down \'fore you lose it, $C! This is MY beach. The Horde WANTS my beach. They will NOT have my beach. Is the beach situation clear?' WHERE `entry`=27338;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This is absolutely perfect! He\'ll never know the difference.' WHERE `entry`=27339;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Good. Can\'t say I\'ll miss the company, if you can call it that. You\'d think at least in the middle of the swamp you\'d get some privacy, you know?' WHERE `entry`=27340;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s the lay of the land, soldier. If you\'re having trouble fighting here on the coast, you might consider pitching in and helping us take and hold that hill.' WHERE `entry`=27341;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Good. Now just do as Forward Commander Onslaught commands. Try your best to fit in with the rest of the soldiers. We don\'t want the Gilneas Liberation Front to get suspicious. Oh, you  didn\'t know they were watching us? Right now there are five different worgen spies looking down on our position. Just be calm and follow orders. I\'ll let you know when we are ready to proceed.' WHERE `entry`=27342;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lord Grayson has told me much about you and your dedication to the Light and the Alliance. It will be a great honor to craft a hammer for you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27343;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Who knew that cursed old keep hid such valuable items? I\'ll be honored to craft them into a fine weapon for you.' WHERE `entry`=27344;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With this device I will be able to communicate with you in the field. Now to check the rest of our frontline outposts.' WHERE `entry`=27345;
