UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, it does look a little cleaner out there...$B$BI suppose it\'s time to get down to the business of salvaging this wreckage.' WHERE `entry`=27347;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wow! You certainly found a lot more than I expected would be out there. I\'m not sure how much Drazzit thought we were going to find out here, but he\'s going to have to be happy with this for now.' WHERE `entry`=27348;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Dreadwatch is lost? This is bad, $N. Real bad. If Dreadwatch is compromised it means we\'ve lost Gilneas City.' WHERE `entry`=27349;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Th... Af... After we lost Gilneas City, the port fell. HU... HUM... HUMANS ARE HERE! Reinforcements from Stormwind! They slaughtered my men. Left me alive to witness their strength. To tell high command... To tell them that the 7th Legion are here...' WHERE `entry`=27350;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It was quite an honor to receive the commission for your weapon, $N. When Tony mentioned using so many exotic materials, I had my doubts, but it seems you managed to find them all. This will be a fine reward for all you\'ve done for the Alliance.' WHERE `entry`=27351;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! I think the holy water will prove devastating in large volumes.' WHERE `entry`=27352;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I have rarely had the chance to work with such exotic materials, but even I can sense the power residing within them. I will have the honor of crafting an incredible weapon for you, $N. The farseer did not underestimate your abilities when she told me about you.' WHERE `entry`=27353;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, I have been expecting you, $N. Maginor Dumas has spoken highly of you and the royal commission only confirms his words. It is an honor to be able to craft a staff for you.' WHERE `entry`=27354;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I won\'t ask what you had to do to come by such rare and powerful materials, but I\'m glad to have the chance to work with them. Your weapon will be magnificent!' WHERE `entry`=27355;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you must be the $C Loganaar was talking about. It is a pleasure to finally meet you. Loganaar and other members of the circle speak highly of you. It will be an honor to make a weapon for such a $C.' WHERE `entry`=27356;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is embarrassing to have been kidnapped by Arnak again. I heard the fighting outside. Did you kill him? I am happy to be free once more. Now, how can I help you, $R?' WHERE `entry`=27357;
