UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh my... the banshees are very tortured souls indeed. Merely holding their essence is emotionally painful... Enough of that for now. I\'ll get to work on counteracting their magic, then we\'ll have a portal up and running in no time. Stratholme will be ours soon, I just know it.' WHERE `entry`=27359;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Though we were shamed in battle, the enemy was not victorious. I will not soon forget this, $N. If I make it back to Silverpine I will likely retire from the service. War is not in my blood.' WHERE `entry`=27360;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can\'t believe you managed to get all those materials. I wouldn\'t think of venturing into Shadowfang Keep! The stories about that place are horrific. Enough of that, though. This is a time to recognize your achievements, not prattle on about my silly fears.' WHERE `entry`=27361;
