UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You saved many of my closest allies today, $N. I can only imagine what horrors you witnessed within Iso\'rath, but you have the thanks of all of the Earthen Ring.' WHERE `entry`=27380;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Argus Highbeacon... that old guy on the top of the tower?  Great! A man his age must have been in the Argent Crusade for a long time. Maybe he can put in the good word for us at Light\'s Hope.' WHERE `entry`=27381;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Of course a young $R like you would have no trouble taking care of a few wild animals. With the roads clear, my journey to the next tower will be much easier.' WHERE `entry`=27382;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello. I\'m Pamela, what\'s your name?' WHERE `entry`=27383;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You found it! You found my doll! Oh, thank you!' WHERE `entry`=27384;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve seen Pamela?  She\'s alive? She\'s dead?  No!  Oh, Pamela!  Why does your spirit still suffer in this world?  Why are you perished, while fortune keeps me alive?  In an instant I would switch places with you and wander dead Darrowshire, a ghost and alone! Ah, but this news cannot change fate. Thank you, $N. Now my duty, my duty to revenge, burns hot as ever. Say, what is that sword you have there?' WHERE `entry`=27385;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What is this?  A warsword?  A butter knife?  I\'m useless when it comes to blades. Let me see... Ah!  This sword was once in the hand of a great man, but there is much tragedy in that man\'s past. Are you here to help him?  It\'s far too late for him now... but perhaps we can help him in the past!' WHERE `entry`=27386;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You found them!  Well done, $N!  These relics hold within them the memories of the Scourge forces at Darrowshire. We will need these if we are to save your Joseph Redpath.' WHERE `entry`=27387;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have the relics?  Good. I will get to work on resolving any temporal discontinuities. Don\'t worry... that\'s not something you have to worry about. You just gather the reagents.' WHERE `entry`=27388;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. Are you certain you haven\'t done this before?' WHERE `entry`=27389;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The fighting is over!  I heard my daddy whisper to me. He scared away all the ghosts and he says he\'s coming home!  I\'m so happy!$B$BHe also said I should welcome you if came to our house, so I made some tea!$B$BI hope you like lots of sugar!' WHERE `entry`=27390;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The key fits the lock, and the chest opens...' WHERE `entry`=27391;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s my daddy\'s sword!  How did you find it?  Did you find the bad hunter?' WHERE `entry`=27392;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Wavespeaker was right. There\'s something here.' WHERE `entry`=27393;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Wavespeaker was right. There\'s something here.' WHERE `entry`=27394;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m honored that the warchief chose me to craft a weapon for you, $N. With such exotic materials, it will be a very fine bow.' WHERE `entry`=27395;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Gordul told me that you would be bringing a variety of unusual materials, but I didn\'t expect anything like this. Moonsteel is said to be very rare and there\'s only one place I know to get it. You have risked much for this weapon, $N, and I\'ll see to it that you receive a fitting reward.' WHERE `entry`=27396;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The elements and spirits speak to you with clear voices, $N. You have become a powerful shaman and an example to others wishing to serve the Horde.$B$BWord has even reached the warchief, and he has commissioned his personal smith to forge a special weapon for you.$B$BThe cursed Shadowfang Keep in Silverpine Forest is the only place to get the materials you\'ll need. Travel there and obtain Lord Walden\'s talisman, the Book of Lost Souls, and essence from the ghosts haunting the keep.',`objectives_loc6`='Go to Shadowfang Keep and obtain Walden\'s Talisman from Lord Walden, the Book of Lost Souls, and 5 Ghostly Essence.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you must be $N. Kardris said that you were venturing to Shadowfang Keep to find the materials needed for this weapon and I see that you have not disappointed. I will make you a mighty weapon worthy of what you have brought.' WHERE `entry`=27397;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your aid is most timely, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27398;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your aid is most timely, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27399;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you must be the $C that Uthel\'nay mentioned. I\'ve heard tales about the artifacts the Silverlaine family once kept, but I haven\'t ever seen one. This should make an excellent focus for your staff. Let\'s get started.' WHERE `entry`=27400;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' TORPEDOED! We had everything at the water line covered, but nothing below the line. They must have snuck in beneath our defenses and then blown our warships to smithereens. And now the rest of the Alliance fleet is nearly here...' WHERE `entry`=27401;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you are the $C who will receive this staff. It will be a fitting reward for one so dedicated to the pursuit of power and the ascendancy of the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27402;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I haven\'t worked with the Sunwalkers before, but from all I\'ve heard, the warchief holds you in high regard. It was a great honor to be asked to forge this weapon for you and I hope it will serve you well.' WHERE `entry`=27403;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, you must be the $C Loganaar was talking about. It is a pleasure to finally meet you, $N. I\'ve often heard members of the circle describe you as a talented and promising $C and I\'m heartened to see their estimations were correct.' WHERE `entry`=27404;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Forward Commander Onslaught fought until the bitter end, $N. It took a pack of bloodthirsty worgen to finally bring him down. We must not let his death, or the death of all of our soldiers in Gilneas, go in vain. Our mission MUST succeed. Now I will reveal to you why we are here.' WHERE `entry`=27405;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Here we are, $N. He is a little rotted, but no worse for the wear. We must hurry before the Alliance finds us!' WHERE `entry`=27406;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Brogg pleased with these feathers. Very strong magic. Brogg not know what raptors do to give feathers power, but raptor feathers always best for ritual.' WHERE `entry`=27407;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have Brogg\'s thanks, $N. Brogg has big plans for clan banner.' WHERE `entry`=27408;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have Brogg\'s thanks, $N. Once Brogg adds their magic to the totem, it will be able to redeem the spirits of Brogg\'s fallen friends.' WHERE `entry`=27409;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Brogg thanks you for your help, although he knows Overlord Mok\'Morokk never will. At least surviving Stonemaul can finally focus on problems with the living and leave dead where they belong. Only one thing remains for Brogg to do.' WHERE `entry`=27410;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Brogg know Onyxia dead. Brogg know her brood still there. Brogg not let them forget the Stonemaul. Brogg is grateful for your help, $N, and he will never forget what you have done for him. Brogg will never give up his quest to bring Stonemaul back where they belong.' WHERE `entry`=27411;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank goodness someone\'s finally taken me up on that offer. I was just thinking that I might need to triple the reward to get that stupid raptor killed, and our budget couldn\'t afford that!' WHERE `entry`=27412;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you! This will help keep our guys going out in the field until Moxie returns with the rest of the supplies from the zeppelin crash.' WHERE `entry`=27413;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='\'Twas a perilous affair, no doubt, collecting all of these hearts and tongues. I shall delve into the depths of the arcane to trace the origin of the black menace which has descended upon our former home.' WHERE `entry`=27414;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Splendid! It will be sometime before Onyxia can produce more eggs.$B$BOn behalf of my people, I thank you, $N.$B$BI have asked much of you so far. Perhaps you can do the Stonemaul Clan one last service.$B$BMok\'Morokk is not fit to lead us. Tharg would make an excellent leader but is hindered by his injuries and age. Drive Mok\'Morokk from this place by force. Only then can we appoint a new leader to return us to our proper home in the south.' WHERE `entry`=27415;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Why you tell me \'bout dragons? Me no like dragons. Me like it here. No dragons here.' WHERE `entry`=27416;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That lazy coward!$B$BMok\'Morokk displayed strength when Rexxar was our leader. But soon after Rexxar\'s departure Mok\'Morokk fell prey to temptations of power. Rather than lead, he demanded. He does not serve his people but rather expects us to serve him.$B$BSomething must be done.' WHERE `entry`=27417;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That cowardly fat mass Mok\'Morokk fled like a scared child. You have done a great service, $N.$B$BNow my people can appoint a new leader, one who will help us reclaim our old home once and for all.' WHERE `entry`=27418;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The sooner those Scourge are pushed out of the Fungal Vale, the sooner we can heal it. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27420;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Even if the flowers died out shortly after they bloomed, they proved our point to the Scourge: they are losing, and we are winning. Thank you for your assistance.' WHERE `entry`=27421;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What a relief it is to see an able-bodied soldier that\'s on our side! There\'s plenty for ye to do around here, $R.' WHERE `entry`=27422;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='No time to bask in the battle glory, $N. We have a job to do. I have no doubt more of those beasts are on the way.' WHERE `entry`=27423;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You good $R. Me miss things very much. Me like you now.' WHERE `entry`=27424;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Captain Vimes thinks the Grimtotems are behind the destruction of the Shady Rest Inn? They wouldn\'t have been first on my list of suspects, but if Captain Vimes sent you here to follow up on a lead, he must have his reasons. Regardless, the Grimtotems have been a thorn in our side for some time and we\'re always glad to have the extra help.' WHERE `entry`=27425;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I\'d say it doesn\'t get any clearer than this. They\'ve taken it upon themselves to fight back against human settlements in the area and I have little doubt Theramore is next on their list.' WHERE `entry`=27426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' There\'s no doubt about it. These match the description exactly, but there\'s just one problem -- these have never been used in battle. Blackhoof Village must not be the only Grimtotem post in the marsh.' WHERE `entry`=27427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you want me to scry for Grimtotems, eh? And what will you say when I tell you there\'s no need?' WHERE `entry`=27428;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hope the Grimtotems got the message. Any attempt to return will be met with far worse than a mere torch. My apprentices and I will see to that.' WHERE `entry`=27429;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' We have avenged James and his family, but not even that can restore what was destroyed.' WHERE `entry`=27430;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Talk about bringing the house down...' WHERE `entry`=27431;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Great, you got him!  And I hope you taught his gang a lesson too!' WHERE `entry`=27432;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Shredderectomy',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh aye, tha\'s the stuff! A good engineer can make anything outta just about anything. This here doo-jicker could recouple a busted cylinder casing... Oh! And who doesn\'t want a dongle? ...And you can fashion this jobby into a ... thing. Yep, perfect.' WHERE `entry`=27433;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I don\'t know how you came by such a large supply of moonsteel, $N, but I haven\'t worked with it in years. It will be both a challenge and a pleasure to create this weapon for you.' WHERE `entry`=27434;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Seer Liwatha mentioned that you were visiting Shadowfang Keep to find the materials for your new staff. I see now why she sent you there. Even the twisted magics gripping the keep could not extinguish the power of these items.' WHERE `entry`=27435;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Shadow-Walker Zuru mentioned that you were visiting Shadowfang Keep to find the materials for your new staff. Artifacts from the keep are reputed to possess much hidden power and your efforts are proof that the tales are true. Your staff will be a masterwork.' WHERE `entry`=27436;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dark Cleric Cecille mentioned that you were visiting Shadowfang Keep to find the materials for your new staff. I see now why she sent you there. Even the twisted magics gripping the keep could not extinguish the power of these items.' WHERE `entry`=27437;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I had no doubt that you would succeed, $N. I hope you can understand why I kept the true purpose of your mission a secret. Should Crowley and Bloodfang have found out about our plan, they would have surely gotten to Godfrey first and disposed of the body. Stand by, $N. The time of their rebirth is at hand.' WHERE `entry`=27438;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Tyelis mentioned that you were visiting Shadowfang Keep to find the materials for your new staff. Few would venture into the keep, even to retrieve such valuable things. Your new staff will be a fitting reward for your bravery.' WHERE `entry`=27439;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Pardon my saying so, but I am surprised you completed the task set out before you alive. Those monsters were responsible for the deaths of countless thousands, a great many of them heroes still spoken highly of to this day. You have earned my respect and a reward for your courage.' WHERE `entry`=27440;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You must be the $C that Brother Silverhallow mentioned. Welcome, $N. Let me see those materials you gathered from halfway around the world. They seem well worth the travel and you will not be disappointed with your staff.' WHERE `entry`=27441;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your aid is most timely, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27442;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your aid is most timely, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27443;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You saw Nefarian when you fought Rend?$B$B<Acride sighs.>$B$BI wish I had accompanied you, then. I could have faced him unaware, outside his lair...but no matter. Nefarian will die by my claw.$B$BYou\'ve done well.' WHERE `entry`=27444;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! It is only a matter of time before the son of Deathwing feels my claws.' WHERE `entry`=27445;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Greetings and salutations, friend. Welcome to Tanaris!' WHERE `entry`=27446;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well hello there, $C. Welcome to Tanaris!' WHERE `entry`=27447;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'ve enjoyed having you ride with us, $N. Hopefully, once Gidwin and Tarenar join the Argent Crusade, we can continue to travel together.' WHERE `entry`=27448;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, you are indeed strong... and I submit to you. I will join you and your friend, the worgen. My strength is yours.' WHERE `entry`=27449;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmm... they didn\'t survive the trip out of the water as well as I had hoped. Oh well!  Seafood salad for Frederick tonight!' WHERE `entry`=27450;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello!  It\'s me. Hope you don\'t mind a little home-brewed magic to allow me to communicate with you in the field. It\'ll save us both some time. We\'re going to incorporate that living rot into a mixture that\'ll ruin their next batch of plague. That\'ll show them!' WHERE `entry`=27451;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve got both pieces!  Good. These will help when trying to sneak into their death camp.' WHERE `entry`=27452;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Catalysm',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Uh oh... it looks like we may have gathered a little too much coagulated rot. Oh well, we\'ll just have to improvise, then! What could possibly go wrong?' WHERE `entry`=27453;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It should take them weeks to get their operation running again. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27454;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can\'t believe it. We\'re literally FEET away from becoming sworn members of the Argent Crusade. We\'d be in there already if it weren\'t for Tarenar\'s dallying. If he doesn\'t quit chatting with the locals soon, I\'m going to head in there myself.' WHERE `entry`=27455;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='May the Earthmother watch over you! Bless you, young one.' WHERE `entry`=27456;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You brought us a shaman!  From the Earthen Ring, no less! I have no idea how we\'ll fit him in the caravan, but we\'ll find a way. Welcome aboard, Rimblat Earthshatter!' WHERE `entry`=27457;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well well well!  Someone who goes and gets things done!  Here\'s your cut, chief. I\'ll be seein\' you around.' WHERE `entry`=27458;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The flare is fully assembled, and the matches lie unused next to the fuse. The fallen Argent centurion got much closer to setting off this flare than you had guessed.' WHERE `entry`=27460;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well met, $N. Can I trust you to assist me in taking this abbey away from these abominations?' WHERE `entry`=27461;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ll be handling things from here, $C. Fine, you want an assignment?  I suppose I can afford to send you in on a mission or two.' WHERE `entry`=27462;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome to Light\'s Hope Chapel. You wish to join the Crusade?  Very well. We have plenty of tasks for new recruits. But first, a test.' WHERE `entry`=27463;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Remember that your ancestors always watch over you. As a brother of the Argent Crusade, you will join a family that has a long line of such fallen ancestors. Their vigil and protection will be your strength as you press forward against the Scourge. Congratulations Tarenar, Gidwin, and $N. Welcome to the Argent Crusade.' WHERE `entry`=27464;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve returned sooner than I expected. Excellent. We will continue our path into the north. Next, you will be completing a similar task - this time, in Northdale.' WHERE `entry`=27465;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello, $N!  Glad to see you\'ve rejoined the caravan! Tarenar and Gidwin arrived here before you. Tarenar\'s just right there, and Gidwin\'s... well... he\'s in a little bit of a mood right now. I think he\'s in the tower.' WHERE `entry`=27466;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Our duty for the day is done. It is only a matter of time before we defeat the Scourge. Today, we made progress.' WHERE `entry`=27467;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yep, one more tank limpin\' back home for repairs. All these trees an\' stumps an\' mud an\' rock - you couldnae drive a golfball into this turf, much less a tank. We\'re gonna need a new approach.' WHERE `entry`=27468;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Oi, what\'re ye doin\' here in my camp? Bloody hell, why\'re ye in the Burnin\' Steppes at all? *hic*$B$BBah, it don\'t matter anyway.$B$BListen, I was adventurin\' the other day, as I often do, an\' I was ambushed by orcs from Blackrock Mountain! \'Cept one of \'em was different...dressed all funny an\' spoke all sophisticated like. Called hisself Acride, I think...$B$BYou ought to go to the Blackrock Spire and find that orc...just be watchin\', pretty much all of the others will want t\' kill ya. Tell him I sent ye!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello, what is your business in a place like this? I\'m sorry, who sent you? I\'m afraid I\'ve never heard of such a dwarf.' WHERE `entry`=27469;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello, what is your business in a place like this? So Overseer Oilfist sent you? Listen carefully, we have much to discuss in little time.' WHERE `entry`=27470;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hello, what is your business in a place like this? So you come at the will of Miss Brightwing, do you? Very interesting indeed.' WHERE `entry`=27471;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Today marks a new beginning for the Forsaken and the end of the Alliance in Lordaeron!' WHERE `entry`=27472;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is good that you\'ve come, $N. We need all the help we can get with the situation here.' WHERE `entry`=27473;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Clever mages. The codex is sealed by a magical ward. Pity that they weren\'t clever enough to realize that former archmages of Dalaran are now Forsaken.' WHERE `entry`=27474;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The magi of Ambermill have employed foul magic to keep us away. Elemental servitors created with immunities that we cannot breach protect their territory.$B$BVenture east to Ambermill and slay the unyielding elemental servitors that guard the town and recover their cores. Bring their cores back to me so that I may devise a method by which we are able to destroy them all!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. The praise the Banshee Queen lavishes upon you is apparently not unfounded.' WHERE `entry`=27475;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Dark Lady requires my expertise? Well of course! Give it here, boy.' WHERE `entry`=27476;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Keep this up and I may have to keep you here at Eastwall, $R.' WHERE `entry`=27477;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Perfect. I hope this wasn\'t too much trouble to come by, $N. Relios was a pupil of mine back when I was a mortal man thereby making him a competent and formidable adversary. I suppose I could have warned you ahead of time. Now, let us see the ring. There we are...' WHERE `entry`=27478;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, hallelujah, and praise, praise be to the Light, my brother!' WHERE `entry`=27479;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Smart boy! I can most definitely use these arcane remnants in my studies. Indeed, Dalaran was built upon a massive ley line. It\'s no wonder, then, that such things exist at the crater.' WHERE `entry`=27480;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My duty is not over yet. In many ways, this was the easy step.' WHERE `entry`=27481;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thought for sure that with the death of a dozen of my most hated enemies I would feel a great burden lifted from my shoulders. Sadly, I do not feel a thing. Perhaps I am a psychopath.' WHERE `entry`=27483;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Only one may enter? I know just the person for this mission. I will prepare our forces and have them at the ready.' WHERE `entry`=27484;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m glad Lira didn\'t scare you off. I won\'t say her concerns aren\'t warranted, but we have a common enemy. She is perhaps a bit overzealous.' WHERE `entry`=27485;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m glad Lira didn\'t scare you off. I won\'t say her concerns aren\'t warranted, but we have a common enemy. She is perhaps a bit overzealous.' WHERE `entry`=27486;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I couldn\'t stop him. While you and Tarenar were out, Giddy ran north all alone! Tarenar, you should have known better!  Gidwin gets so impatient sometimes, and you only egg him on. If Giddy gets into any trouble, I\'m blaming you for this.' WHERE `entry`=27487;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Impatience',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You didn\'t see him?  Where could he have gone then? His... his prayer book?  Why would he leave that behind? Oh... By the Light, what have I done?' WHERE `entry`=27488;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Time is wasting, $N. Every minute we waste gives the Scourge another chance to kill Gidwin. If he isn\'t dead already. Not that I think he is. Giddy may be a stick-in-the-mud, but when it comes down to it, he can swing the Light like a champion.' WHERE `entry`=27489;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That must have been deadly. While I don\'t approve of their methods, no one can question the effectiveness of Master Mathias Shaw and his SI:7. Not to mention that you\'re here. Our victory is all but assured.' WHERE `entry`=27490;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That must have been exciting. Despite any losses that the Kor\'kron may have incurred along the way, no one will be able to doubt their effectiveness, nor that of Garona. And with you in the mix, it\'s only a matter of time before victory is ours.' WHERE `entry`=27491;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='As with any offensive, you first need to soften them up. We\'ve been having a heck of a time getting in there. But someone like you... well, let\'s just say I have no doubt in my mind that you can get into the Twilight Gate to the southwest and teach the Bloodeye Clan ogres and ettins a thing or two!',`objectives_loc6`='Slay 10 ogres or ettins at the Twilight Gate.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s the spirit, lad! Today\'s already shaping up to be a good one.' WHERE `entry`=27492;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I want you to get in there past those boulders to the northwest at the Twilight Gate. Kill every Bloodeye Clan ogre and ettin in sight. Think you can handle that for me, $N?',`objectives_loc6`='Slay 10 Bloodeye Clan ogres or ettins at the Twilight Gate.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='And here I thought that today couldn\'t get any better. I enjoy being wrong, occasionally.' WHERE `entry`=27493;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks to you, our cannoneers hit their marks. Tell me about the situation within the Twilight Gate.' WHERE `entry`=27496;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Southwestern building targeted',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Southern building targeted' WHERE `entry`=27496;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I must say that I rather enjoyed the sight of their buildings being hit.' WHERE `entry`=27497;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Southwestern building targeted',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Southern building targeted' WHERE `entry`=27497;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' That\'s quite a gruesome trophy collection you have there. I would have believed you if you had simply said they were dead. Regardless, thank you for having the foresight to take care of them. The Twilight Gate will soon be ours. Time to move up to the Twilight Citadel.' WHERE `entry`=27500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' That\'s quite a gruesome trophy collection you have there. I would have believed you if you had simply said they were dead, though I do appreciate the extra effort. Thank you for having the foresight to take care of them. The Twilight Gate will soon be ours. Time to move up to the Twilight Citadel.' WHERE `entry`=27501;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Calen has become very trusting. It is not often that strangers are permitted within the redoubt.' WHERE `entry`=27504;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We will take Grim Batol back from the Twilight\'s Hammer and thier allies. It may take time, but this is one charge that we cannot forsake.' WHERE `entry`=27505;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='$R, I have a task for you.$B$BTake these ruby seeds and plant them at the corpses of any dragonkin that you come across. Twilight or Vermillion, whelping or dragon, it matters not. We need to see that their bodies are returned to the earth so that life can continue to flourish.$B$BIn death, there should always be new life. This may be our one consolation during times of war and great tragedy.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='In this, we deny Deathwing the destruction that he so passionately seeks. In this, life continues.' WHERE `entry`=27506;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have a talent for killing I see. In times like these, that has its place.' WHERE `entry`=27507;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I don\'t know if you did this for me or the young inside these eggs, but it doesn\'t really matter, either way it\'s clear that you want to be an ally of our flight. I appreciate that. I cannot forgive the attacks by your allies against my brood, but for now, it seems you have chosen the right side.' WHERE `entry`=27508;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done. Thank you, $R. I will not be so foolish as to let such an oversight happen again.' WHERE `entry`=27509;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I only hope that we don\'t end up getting beat down by inconspicuous birds, cats and trees next... or seals. Could you imagine it?' WHERE `entry`=27510;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Your exploration of the Chamber of the Stars has yielded more questions than answers...' WHERE `entry`=27511;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Yes, this is it. Now run the ring along the runes of the portal and you should become attuned for transdimensional travel.' WHERE `entry`=27512;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Excellent work, $N. Now to eject them into our waiting hands!' WHERE `entry`=27513;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Aw dang crap it all. You\'re just an Alliance $C. I was hoping for a rescue.' WHERE `entry`=27514;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh, that\'s the stuff all right! Hope ya didn\'t eat any. Gives you the cramps something awful but it does wonders for birds.' WHERE `entry`=27515;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N! Aiding that downed gryphon-rider has given us our first contact with the old Wildhammer clans. We\'ll be able to find out who\'s still left, and in what numbers. Our campaign is looking up!' WHERE `entry`=27516;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ahh, rope! Thanks, kid. Something tells me I\'m going to need this.' WHERE `entry`=27517;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Had I not witnessed what you did with my own eyes I would not have believed it, $N. Now, with the Ambermill magi on our side, there is but one thing left to do before we retake Gilneas and send those Alliance dogs running for Stormwind.' WHERE `entry`=27518;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, $N. Orsis was punished for not joining the forces of Deathwing. Prince Nadun has offered my people refuge in his city. I must go there and tend the survivors.' WHERE `entry`=27519;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You continue to prove to be a valuable ally, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27520;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='$R... please, I ask your help.$B$BSomething\'s happened to my people. Our commander, Ranger Lord Hawkspear, came upon an item of magical energy, and my friends, my family... they succumbed to its seductive power.$B$BThey\'re corrupted, $R. All of them.$B$BMy Ellaria wouldn\'t want to live like that, nor would any of my brothers. Please, put them out of their misery. Quel\'lithien Lodge is not far; it\'s just up the hill, to the northwest.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Do not feel sorry for me. Those were my friends that you saw at Quel\'lithien Lodge, but they were already as good as dead.' WHERE `entry`=27521;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It sounds like you were successful. Hopefully this is enough information to find Gidwin.' WHERE `entry`=27522;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I have seen many things in my day, $R. The peaks of Mt. Hyjal... the oddities of Outland... a wall of Scourge soldiers, proceeding into war. But I have never seen a bat as big, or as shockingly white, as Duskwing.$B$BHow he taunts me from his roost!$B$BThis albino demon bat circles to the southwest of here, due north of Blackwood Lake. Track him down and destroy him. If he flies too high for you to reach, use my flare to get his attention.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work. I can now continue my work without the distractions of that great white beast. I shall fashion this fur into something you can use.' WHERE `entry`=27523;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I haven\'t found anything but brainless undead, and plenty of them. I was just about to kill my way into Stratholme when you arrived. Did you have any more success?' WHERE `entry`=27524;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'ve got to keep moving!  We\'re getting so very close!' WHERE `entry`=27525;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have no idea how happy I am to see you two!  You\'re a sight for sore eyes... sore eyes that have been starin\' through a banshee for far too long now. I\'m sorry for causing so much trouble. Will you take me back to the caravan?' WHERE `entry`=27526;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Speak with Fiona at Light\'s Hope Chapel in Eastern Plaguelands.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve been more help than anyone expected of you, $N. The doors of my caravan are always open to you. The boys and I have even put together a little something special for you. Here, take your pick!' WHERE `entry`=27527;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A blessed fire cleanses even the most corrupt of flesh. They stood no chance in the face of the Light.' WHERE `entry`=27528;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is good to hear you found the tortured souls of my brethren and freed them. I find my strength renewed, knowing at least some of the defenders of Darrowshire no longer wallow in the vile subservience of the Scourge.' WHERE `entry`=27529;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are a true Champion of the Light, $N. I wish you luck in your future endeavors, wherever they might take you. If you need anything in the future, you can always find me here - knee-deep in the corpses of the slain.' WHERE `entry`=27530;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I love the smell of fresh foot scrapings, don\'t you? If we\'re going to find a cure to the plague, we need to get creative with our ingredients. Now, if you don\'t mind, I\'m going to get back to work.' WHERE `entry`=27531;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Whew. Every time Argus comes plodding through that Plaguewood, I fear it to be his last. It\'s good to see that he\'s wise enough to send a youngblood like you in his stead.' WHERE `entry`=27532;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see them!  Can you?  The little pig spirits, on their way to the great sty in the sky...' WHERE `entry`=27533;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There it is! And oh my! I forgot how full it was!$B$BThis is a glorious day, $N! Stupendous! Insanely good, I say!' WHERE `entry`=27534;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve come to the right place, mister!  No place better than Terrordale, yes siree, that\'s right!  The jewel of Lordaeron!' WHERE `entry`=27535;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What did I tell you, eh? Perfectly safe! I\'ll see about getting some of these over to to your friends, $N. At a discount.' WHERE `entry`=27536;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My word, $N. These elemental energies are so powerful, so chaotic - no wonder the Twilight\'s Hammer has chosen to build their stronghold here! I should be able to channel these energies into something more benign and productive though. Let\'s give it a try...' WHERE `entry`=27537;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh... mud. You brought me mud? Wow - this stuff oozes with power! I see what Thordun was saying, now. I\'ll distribute this to all of the healers. Our wounded will be on their feet in no time!' WHERE `entry`=27538;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='May my pile never stop growing.' WHERE `entry`=27539;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well met, $C. I am Gavan Grayfeather, emissary of the Wildhammer shaman. There is much work to be done. The leaders fear for their citizens, as many have turned to cults. We shaman are concerned with the elemental unrest. Our advice to you, $C, is to be vigilant. Help where you can, be it calming the people or putting the elementals at rest. There is plenty to do.' WHERE `entry`=27540;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Odd... It looks as if someone used gemstones as lenses. I should be able to fix them without too much trouble.' WHERE `entry`=27541;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I suppose I had better work on my stealth, if you were able to find me. Are you interested in helping me heal the Plaguelands?' WHERE `entry`=27544;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ho! I knew you were a $C I could count on, $N. Use that portal anytime you need to get from Stormwind back to the Highlands. Now then, time to get to business. We need to locate and unite the lost Wildhammer clans scattered around the Highlands. Talking with Thordun here is a good start!' WHERE `entry`=27545;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='King\'s honor, $C. I am Captain Anton. I am leading the investigation into the cultists that have appeared in Stormwind.' WHERE `entry`=27546;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What happened here today is between us. Say a word to anyone and you will find yourself in a corpse pit next to these poor fools.' WHERE `entry`=27547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I suspect we\'ll see fewer humans at the Battlefront. The risk for these cowards is too great.' WHERE `entry`=27548;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, kid, it looks like you\'ve done it again. This starlight is exactly what we were missing. Now we can get to work!' WHERE `entry`=27549;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The part of me that was Gilnean died at Tempest\'s Reach. Only vengeance remains, $N. To that end, we have work to do. Spare me your pointless queries.' WHERE `entry`=27550;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is it!  If this missive is to be believed, then he\'s literally right over this hill! What are we waiting for, $N?' WHERE `entry`=27551;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Tarenar has laid a few holy talismans inside the caravan. They appear to be unused.$B$BThey appear to be magical in nature. If Tarenar isn\'t using them, what\'s the harm in borrowing one for a while?' WHERE `entry`=27557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hope you\'re as tough as your gear suggests. The Twilight\'s Hammer have made their way within the redoubt somehow and I need someone to hunt them down.' WHERE `entry`=27564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I don\'t know how I\'m still alive. The patrols keep walking past me like I\'m not even here. ...Am I dead, $C?' WHERE `entry`=27565;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is good to see you, $N. Here at the Throne of Elements we may be able to uncover what ails Azeroth.' WHERE `entry`=27566;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see...she did not cooperate. Hopefully we can still stop them before something else terrible happens.' WHERE `entry`=27567;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I would stay away from Oralius. Far, far, far away. He isn\'t quite right in the head. Now, let\'s get onto business!' WHERE `entry`=27568;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m sure you are up to the task I have for you if you\'ve made it this far in one piece. Between you and me, you may want to enjoy yourself in the Grim Guzzler while you\'re there. It could be the last drink you ever have.' WHERE `entry`=27569;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Greetings, $C. The situation here is tense. The elements are restless and the people are scared and confused. The Warchief is trying to find a semblance of balance between leading the people and protecting Azeroth. Though it seems he will soon be leaving us to travel to Nagrand and gain insight about the elementals. Regardless of the Warchief\'s choice, we still must do what we can. Help calm the populace, scour the lands for rogue elementals. These tasks will surely help our cause.' WHERE `entry`=27570;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Dark Irons took our Thunderbrew. I\'ll never let them live after that. I\'d kill \'em all myself if I could! However, look ahead and you\'ll see we have slightly more dire matters to attend to at the moment.' WHERE `entry`=27571;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is good to see you, $C. Here at the Throne of Elements we may be able to uncover what ails Azeroth.' WHERE `entry`=27572;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I cannot proceed any further alone, regardless of my combat experience. The Lyceum has proven too difficult for me. If you are here, though...you might be the key to all of this.' WHERE `entry`=27573;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I know that face, $N. This head belongs to a former Gilnean known as Sean Dempsey. He was imprisoned with Crowley before the great outbreak. I wonder if it would be possible to put him back together. The rest of him must be in the belly of these crocolisks.' WHERE `entry`=27574;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now let\'s see if I can do this. ...leg bone connects to the thigh bone... ...arm bone to torso... ...sprinkle on a little Forsaken necromancy... TA-DA!' WHERE `entry`=27575;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You got the dragons in the game! Good on you. We\'d already laid out plans for our ambush by the time the dragons contacted us. They\'re helping by cutting off their retreat. It\'s not too late for you to join in on the fun though. We saved some for you.' WHERE `entry`=27576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' It looks like the reinforcements from the ships in Gilneas are marching soon. Crowley and Bloodfang have set up an encampment to the southeast for the Gilneas Liberation front.' WHERE `entry`=27577;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done it! You\'ve actually done it! Morgan\'s years of planning and waiting have finally come to fruition. She may have lost her land and family when Ragnaros tore this land asunder, but with the Dark Iron crippled we\'ll be able to safely build a new kingdom of our own in the Burning Steppes. Not even the Firelord himself will be able to breech the capital\'s walls! Make sure you come back someday when we\'ve finished, you\'ll be our guest of the highest honor. I thank you with all my heart, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27578;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Get over here. If you blow my cover, I swear to the Warchief I\'ll kill you where you stand.' WHERE `entry`=27579;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The rest of the Alliance fleet will arrive shortly, only to find their base camp decimated. Now for the second and most important part of our battle plan.' WHERE `entry`=27580;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Twilight\'s Hammer\'s presence only complicates our mission here further, but you\'ve done your part for now. You\'ve earned a reward for your efforts...and some rest. Let\'s get out of here.' WHERE `entry`=27581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Beyond this door lies the commander of the Dark Iron Army, surrounded by trained soldiers. Are you up for a little killing?' WHERE `entry`=27582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Warlord Zaela sent you? Good. If you Horde are as strong as your Warchief promised, I expect to see some bloodshed on these shores.' WHERE `entry`=27583;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You\'re a true fighter, $N. I liked watching you work. Perhaps the Dragonmaw really DO belong in your Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Up ahead is the Grim Guzzler. A disgusting bar full of all our enemies, intoxicated and therefore unfit for proper battle. Ripe for the slaughter.' WHERE `entry`=27585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh yeah. YEAH! These are DEFINITELY going to kill somebody. Probably naga.' WHERE `entry`=27586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I can see it now: our own famous Bogpaddle Lobster-Poppers! Made fresh from the sea! Oh, it\'s like this stuff writes itself... Your help is very much appreciated, my friend. I\'ll start seeing if I can\'t cut your people a favorable arrangement, eh?' WHERE `entry`=27587;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hear quite the commotion coming from the Grim Guzzler. I see you\'ve been hard at work. If you\'ll direct your attention opposite me, you\'ll notice that we have bigger issues to worry about than toying with drunkards.' WHERE `entry`=27589;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I cannot proceed any further alone, regardless of my combat experience. The Lyceum has proven too difficult for me. If you are here, though...you might be the key to all of this.' WHERE `entry`=27591;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Our ice-cold, refreshing Silversnap Ice! I can\'t thank you enough, "dawg", for this entirely spontaneous act of heroism! Here, have your very own bottle as a totally sincere gesture of thanks! Be sure to tell ALL YOUR FRIENDS how good it is.' WHERE `entry`=27592;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A true $C if I\'ve ever seen one! You\'ve done the impossible! I knew we could count on you. And with that, I\'d like for you to be the first to know that the Kargath Expeditionary Force is now officially back in business! I extend to you my personal gratitude for your efforts here. Remember always our motto: "First in, last out, always victorious. Remember always Kargath." You are dismissed.' WHERE `entry`=27593;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done it! Finally, everything is in place. Should Crowley not accept our terms, his daughter will be turned.' WHERE `entry`=27594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Who... who are you?  Sent here... to rescue my people and fight our enemies.' WHERE `entry`=27595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have the heart! Amazing! It is even more beautiful than I imagined!$B$BPlease, $N, take this as payment!' WHERE `entry`=27596;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Silversnap sent you?! I\'m DOOMED! Oh, he sent you to help me! That\'s different, haha!' WHERE `entry`=27597;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'ll show those fish-faced freaks! Good work!' WHERE `entry`=27598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='WOW! I don\'t know why I said that. I\'m excitable! But man, there was a lot of stuff on these guys, check it out! Here, you want this?' WHERE `entry`=27599;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My high-grade fuse! My imported blasting powder! And my--hello there! I\'ll just be taking that! Those are all worth more gold than what you\'re wearing, you know! Thanks for your help!' WHERE `entry`=27600;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' This... is not over. Godfrey and his traitorous allies will pay for what they have done as will the remaining Alliance forces occupying Lordaeron. Our work has only just begun.' WHERE `entry`=27601;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Though the chest is locked, there is a plaque bearing interesting hieroglyphs above it.' WHERE `entry`=27602;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Darn it! I simply HAVE to know what\'s behind that gate! This could be the discovery that makes my career, you know! Hmm....maybe a couple good explosions would do the trick...' WHERE `entry`=27603;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent! I suspect that without Jammal\'an\'s leadership, the trolls will fall to infighting and Hakkar will never set his eyes upon our world.' WHERE `entry`=27604;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You only defeated Eranikus\' Shade? This is most troubling... Let us hope that his full form does not still exist outside the Temple. Only Ysera herself is stronger than him in our flight.' WHERE `entry`=27605;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Boom baby, boom! What? You killed the Fathom-Lord already? I suppose we should stop shelling his corpse, then.' WHERE `entry`=27606;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good timing, $C. We were just about to unleash a counter-attack.' WHERE `entry`=27607;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' That\'s quite a gruesome trophy collection you have there. I would have believed you if you had simply said they were dead. Regardless, thank you for having the foresight to take care of them. The Twilight Gate will soon be ours. Time to move up to the Twilight Citadel.' WHERE `entry`=27608;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' That\'s quite a gruesome trophy collection you have there. I would have believed you if you had simply said they were dead, though I do appreciate the extra effort. Thank you for having the foresight to take care of them. The Twilight Gate will soon be ours. Time to move up to the Twilight Citadel.' WHERE `entry`=27609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, $C. Now you know the lay of the land. If you\'re ever having difficulty fighting here on the Twilight Shores, remember that capturing and holding the Beach Head will give all Horde forces here a combat advantage!' WHERE `entry`=27610;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, good. Let them reap what they sow!' WHERE `entry`=27611;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The abbey will fall shortly. We can soon move on, deeper into Tyr\'s Hand.' WHERE `entry`=27612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The death of Rohan eases my spirits a bit. I once fought beside him, you know. He was an emissary of the Scarlet Crusade; one of the few that deigned to join us in our battle against Kel\'thuzad, so many years ago. How quickly things change.' WHERE `entry`=27613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='This battle was won before it started. Right now, we\'re just shooting for style points.$B$BWithin these barracks, the sniveling Scarlet Crusaders cling to their priceless artifacts, even though some of the objects are too holy for their now-undead hand to touch. So they keep them in chests, hidden from the world.$B$BYou will find these artifacts, and bring them back to me. They belong to be among the Argent Crusade. They belong in the hands of the righteous.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. I will deliver these to Tyrosus when we return.' WHERE `entry`=27614;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are well on your way to becoming a true champion of the Light, $N. Well done.' WHERE `entry`=27615;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='One less thing to worry about. Nice work up there.' WHERE `entry`=27616;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, the abbey is ours. I never doubted Eligor\'s ability for a moment.' WHERE `entry`=27617;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It sounds like Korfax really cleaned house over at the barracks. It\'s very much like him to show off like that.' WHERE `entry`=27618;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, good. These barracks are as good as fallen.' WHERE `entry`=27619;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='While I can\'t agree with their methods, I can\'t argue with their results. In many ways, the Scarlet were well-intentioned, but their zeal grew too strong, and their hate blinded them to reason. I only hope that the same doesn\'t happen to our Brotherhood of Light.' WHERE `entry`=27620;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Come to join the patrol, lad? Glad to have ya. I need some bodies helpin\' to get our defenses under control here. Help me out and I\'ll see if I can\'t find some more prestigious work for ya.' WHERE `entry`=27621;
