UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='My bretheren are being butchered here. It\'s as I thought.$B$BI must ask your help further before I enter, $N. In the passageway outside this room, the hallway proceeds left and right. To the right, it goes down to the Chamber of Blood. Here the Atal\'ai perform their dark rituals.$B$BThey have expected and prepared for my kind for years, but not for you. Enter the Chamber of Blood and slay the Priestess Udum\'bra. She is one of three foul presences here that must be vanquished before I may enter.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good riddance. Another source of corruption in this world put to rest. I thank you for your bravery, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27705;
