UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent work, $N. The note you captured makes sense in light of this ritual the infiltrators mentioned. This city is infested with cultists and their sympathizers. We must act before their plans can come to fruition.' WHERE `entry`=27749;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Great! Did you get any for yourself?' WHERE `entry`=27750;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' So, $C. There\'s more to you than meets the eye. Maybe your Horde can stand with the best of my warriors. Let\'s try you out...' WHERE `entry`=27751;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh aye ... we get a few of these kegs out to the boys on the front and we\'re gonna see some fireworks. Thank you, $N!' WHERE `entry`=27752;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good - hardly a worm or weevil to be found! This is a lifesaver to the folk who fled here for survival.' WHERE `entry`=27753;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Look at that! That\'s quite a collection of trophies you have there. I\'ll spread the word. If a single Alliance $C can do this, imagine what the rest of your lot can accomplish!' WHERE `entry`=27754;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They couldn\'t be saved, $N. The ancient curse that fell upon them is irrevocable.' WHERE `entry`=27755;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Bzzzzzzzzzzzzt.>$B$BNicely done! A clean kill. Now continue on and see what else you can find! We\'ll crack this case wide open with you on our side, I just know it.' WHERE `entry`=27756;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh my. It sounds like you ran across quite a sinister being. I wonder what one of those was doing all the way out here...' WHERE `entry`=27757;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Bzzzzzzzzzzzzt.>$B$BHey, it\'s Horatio. That was intense! I\'m watching your progress on the Stormwind Communicator\'s Spyatron X3 application.$B$BThey sure are using a lot of heavily fortified doors to hide their work. Keep pushing forward and see what you find next. I bet it\'ll be a huge clue!' WHERE `entry`=27758;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Scanning subject... Cerebral cortex diagnostics indicate the absence of "tomb curse" phenomenon. Diagnostics did reveal frequent head trauma. The user would do well to exercise more caution around blunt objects in the future.' WHERE `entry`=27760;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done, $N. The expedition has already doomed itself. There is no need for it to endanger the rest of the world as well.' WHERE `entry`=27761;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Third Bomb Cluster disarmed',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Unstable Bomb Bot deactivated' WHERE `entry`=27761;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Nice landing!' WHERE `entry`=27762;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Use the Teleporter in the back of Fuselight-by-the-Sea to port up the mountain, then report to Dolph Blasto at Fuselight in the Badlands.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Welcome to Fuselight!' WHERE `entry`=27763;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $R. You may keep the goggles, as they have already served their purpose: they brought you to me.' WHERE `entry`=27764;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you for gathering these so quickly, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27765;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This grisly task was necessary, $N.$B$BAll will be revealed to you soon. For now, know this:$B$BI am no ordinary goblin.$B$BI serve a mistress of unimaginable power, and her motives here are not as dark as they might seem.' WHERE `entry`=27766;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You need to familiarize yourself with the portal ritual quickly. We need to send as many teams into Stormwind as we can. They\'re discovering and arresting more of our brothers each day.' WHERE `entry`=27767;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My true name is Rheastrasza, and I am an envoy of Alexstrasza herself, the Aspect of the red dragonflight.$B$BWith Deathwing currently occupied with other matters, we are going to find a way to redeem the black dragonflight.$B$BAnd you are going to help us.' WHERE `entry`=27769;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We will find a shred of good within these dragons, $N. Whether it is in the wild eggs you found, the bodies of the whelplings you slew, or the eggs that we have encouraged Nyxondra to lay... we will find an untainted black dragon.' WHERE `entry`=27770;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You have done everything that I have asked you, without question. Our job here in Lethlor Ravine is done.$B$BIt is now time that I revealed everything to you.' WHERE `entry`=27771;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ooh!  Science stuff!  Let\'s see what you\'ve got here...$B$BWild eggs?  Blech. Useless. These are never any good.$B$BOoooh, what\'s this?  Some sort of... pre-engineered egg?  This looks promising, but I don\'t want to know what Rhea had to do to get it.$B$BHmm... yes, some very nice corpses. Very nice indeed.$B$BAlright, I\'ll see what I can do.' WHERE `entry`=27772;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='He has escaped! I should have known it would not be so easy. The path is clear, $N. It is time to return.' WHERE `entry`=27773;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I wonder where all of these ogre-magi are coming from?  Curious times, indeed.' WHERE `entry`=27774;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A perfect fit!  My goat puncher is finally finished!' WHERE `entry`=27775;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done!  I have no doubt that those goats will be back, but they\'ll think twice before they nibble my cogs again!' WHERE `entry`=27776;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent job, user $N. We must obtain access to the fusion core now.' WHERE `entry`=27777;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I am in control, user $N. But I cannot keep the core temperature stable indefinitely.' WHERE `entry`=27778;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Gnomebliteration',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is done, user $N. I thank you for your assistance with this unfortunate task.' WHERE `entry`=27779;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done an excellent job tracking down and combating the cultists, but I fear they are right about one thing. We will never know if we\'ve gotten them all.' WHERE `entry`=27780;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Bzzzzzzzzzzzzt.>$B$BYou\'re nearing the heart of their domain. There will likely be an extremely fortified door protecting the inner sanctum of the entire Defias operation. See if you can find anything that might pry it open!$B$BI suggest a stealthy method!' WHERE `entry`=27781;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, you\'re back. We know where Cho\'gall\'s ultimate weapon is located!' WHERE `entry`=27782;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, you\'re back. It\'s about time. We know where Cho\'gall\'s ultimate weapon is located!' WHERE `entry`=27783;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Hammer of Twilight floats in the middle of the altar, unprotected....' WHERE `entry`=27784;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Bzzzzzzzzzzzzt.>$B$BYour exploits have gained quite the following in the intelligence community, $N. Many top members of SI:7 have been earnestly watching you infiltrate the Deadmines through their own Stormwind Communicators.$B$BMathias Shaw himself wants to speak with you! I\'ll transfer you over momentarily.' WHERE `entry`=27785;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Hammer of Twilight floats in the middle of the altar, unprotected....' WHERE `entry`=27786;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did it, lad! You beat that damned gronn and sent Cho\'gall packing into the Twilight Bastion. Don\'t you worry. With your help and that of your friends, we\'ll get in there and we\'ll kill Cho\'gall once and for all!' WHERE `entry`=27787;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did it, $N! You beat that damned gronn and sent Cho\'gall packing into the Twilight Bastion. Don\'t you worry. With your help and that of your friends, we\'ll get in there and we\'ll kill Cho\'gall once and for all!' WHERE `entry`=27788;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The results are in. I\'ve identified traces of corruption in all three samples you brought me. Rhea will be quite disappointed.' WHERE `entry`=27789;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Survive third wave',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Survive final wave' WHERE `entry`=27789;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You very well may have saved all of Stormwind with your efforts here today, $N. Vanessa may still be out there, but she is an insignificant threat now that the Juggernaut will be placed under our careful watch. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=27790;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Titans?  You wanna know about titans?$B$BYou came to the right place, $G lad: lass;. We\'re on the brink of somethin\' big.' WHERE `entry`=27791;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Chalice... worthless.$B$BVase... counterfeit.$B$BHieroglyph... interesting, but rather common.$B$BWhat\'s this?  I\'ve never seen trogg craftsmanship of this caliber!  You\'ve stumbled upon something rare indeed, $N.$B$BAlright, fine. Let\'s talk titans, shall we?' WHERE `entry`=27792;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With your inspection complete, the statues return to their original positions. Something seems different in the room, however...' WHERE `entry`=27793;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just one tiny little device? I never did understand those titans. Very well!  Let\'s see what this peeper can do.' WHERE `entry`=27794;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Going toe to toe with ogres is impressive, $N. I\'m glad I\'ve got soldiers like you out here.' WHERE `entry`=27795;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Find a use for the Warden\'s Pawn within the Tomb of the Watchers in the Badlands.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The statue clicks into place on the large stone slab.>' WHERE `entry`=27796;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<The statue slides into place on the cold marble slab.>' WHERE `entry`=27797;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Hammer of Twilight? And you say you got this information out of a drowned Wildhammer dwarf? You\'re kidding, right?' WHERE `entry`=27798;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve brought many of these traitors to justice, $N, and yet their numbers keep growing. I fear we won\'t be able to stomp out all these rituals in time...' WHERE `entry`=27799;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You need to familiarize yourself with the portal ritual quickly. We\'ve sent dozens of brothers into the city, but only so many can evade capture. We\'re relying on you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27800;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So there were more cultists waiting to be admitted to the city? It\'s a good thing that you caught them, $N. Reading over the note that you found, it seems they\'re planning something big.' WHERE `entry`=27801;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So they\'re preparing some kind of ritual all over the city? Orgrimmar city is infested with cultists and their sympathizers and the warchief is at wit\'s end. We must do something!' WHERE `entry`=27802;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, boy. Good to have another capable set of hands about.' WHERE `entry`=27803;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks for your help. Every little bit makes a difference. We\'ll keep the water going until we can push the Twilight back.' WHERE `entry`=27804;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are very generous. Thank you. There\'s a lot of darkness in our world these days. We appreciate the light that you\'ve brought here.' WHERE `entry`=27805;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Greetings, $R. Sent by Keegan?' WHERE `entry`=27806;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Iain sent ya? You don\'t look like a Firebeard to me. Why exactly should I be listenin\' to anything you say?' WHERE `entry`=27807;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It seems the Doyles suffered the worst of the attacking Twilight drakes. It\'s clear that they fought to the end: not a single rider\'s footprint more than a few yards from his gryphon. It\'s doubtful there were any survivors.' WHERE `entry`=27808;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Bout that time, eh? Help us wrap things up then.' WHERE `entry`=27809;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s the stuff! Not half bad. You\'ve got a bit of fight in ya after all.' WHERE `entry`=27810;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good on you. I always feel like a part of me is missing when my gryphon isn\'t nearby. I can\'t speak for Duglas or the rest of the clan, but I\'ll be ready to ride at Firebeard\'s call.' WHERE `entry`=27811;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ya got the Mullans. Good news! They\'re worth more than their weight in a fight, and they ain\'t exactly skinny.' WHERE `entry`=27812;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That\'s more like it. Let\'s finish gatherin\' up supplies and get back to Keegan.' WHERE `entry`=27813;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yer a good lad. Have me thanks and a little gold for yer troubles.' WHERE `entry`=27814;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hah! Looks like their raid went mighty well then. I\'ll have to buy ol\' Forgehammer a round once we finish with this mess.' WHERE `entry`=27815;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It seems you had some luck bringin\' riders back. Well timed too - we just pushed the elementals back, so we should have the arm room to lead an attack right away. Thank you, $N. You\'re a good $R.' WHERE `entry`=27816;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now that\'s how it\'s done, lad! With a real gryphon wing back together, we can take the fight to the rest of the Twilight. You\'re welcome to fly with us anytime.' WHERE `entry`=27817;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Let\'s have a look then... Mmm, oh dear. That\'s what I thought these were. They might still be usable, but it\'s horrid to have such things in my backyard.' WHERE `entry`=27818;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='More black on you than red... that\'s what I like to see. Looks like you\'ve got what it takes, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27821;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'ve had strikes on our own lumber line while you\'ve been gone. This should at least put us on equal footing for gathering rates. Good work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27822;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Wow, this stuff is strong!  I knew they had beer, but I never expected them to have shadowstout!  That\'s my favorite shadowbeer!' WHERE `entry`=27823;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now here\'s some treasure!  I was beginning to worry that these weren\'t titan ruins at all! I\'ll show these to Durdin. Thanks again, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27824;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I imagine those ogres weren\'t too much trouble for you. Here - some coin for your troubles.' WHERE `entry`=27825;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'ll take that egg out of your hands now. We need to get this egg incubated... and hidden, quickly. There are lots of angry dragons looking for this. It\'s good to see you again, by the way.' WHERE `entry`=27826;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'re the $R we\'ve been waiting for?  It\'s about time you got here. My legs could use a stretch. Come on boys!  Let\'s go kill us some black dragons!' WHERE `entry`=27827;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m not what you\'d call "very strong" or "battle-hardened", but I get the job done my own way. Lookin\' forward to fightin\' with you. I never fought with a fancy-lookin\' $C before.' WHERE `entry`=27828;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='One less dragon to worry about, one step closer to redemption. Onward, my soldiers!' WHERE `entry`=27829;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Two more dangerous black dragons have been removed from this egg hunt. Your greatest task, however, still awaits.' WHERE `entry`=27830;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Just think... Nyxondra may end up being the mother of the new black dragonflight. In death, she has given a gift to the future generations of Azeroth.' WHERE `entry`=27831;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The egg must always be moving. We are not safe anywhere. Deathwing, even in his madness, knows all the hidden places in this world. The egg must not rest.' WHERE `entry`=27832;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I\'d say we have a dragon problem, but it seems like they\'re a little more interested in New Kargath then they are in our small encampment. Nevertheless, I\'ve got top men focused on keeping the dragons at bay.$B$BOne problem that has gone unchecked, however, is the ogre camp to our southwest. A small army of combatants seems to have appeared outside of their hovel.$B$BWe can\'t sit and wait for them to flank us, soldier. Thin their ranks before they thin ours.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $R. However, I\'m afraid I don\'t have much to give you, other than this passionate round of applause. Oh, I do have these. Here, take your pick.' WHERE `entry`=27833;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I think you\'re ready, $N. You\'re getting the hang of this.' WHERE `entry`=27834;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='See?  No need to worry when Olaf is around. Just let me know, and I\'ll protect you from the monsters.' WHERE `entry`=27835;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I thank you, $N. This will make our prophetic visions that much clearer.' WHERE `entry`=27836;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes, $N. I can feel the disruption in the river fading. Yet, I feel the source of this taint still lingers.' WHERE `entry`=27837;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Yes. The waters are clearing up. I am certain I will be visited by a vision before the High Council meets. Be warned, $R. My vote will only be swayed by what I see. You might have helped us greatly here today, but if the vision sways me to make a case against war then that is the way my vote will be cast.' WHERE `entry`=27838;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Retrieve the Ancient Tol\'vir Armaments',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is quite timely. I will distribute these armaments to my best men and to the laborers that you recruited. I\'ve a feeling they\'ll show as much courage as my best trained captains.' WHERE `entry`=27839;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. We, are in your debt.' WHERE `entry`=27840;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=27841;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Do not be alarmed, $N. I am close to you, waiting in the shadows. You\'ve done well. You must continue the mission here - I am too valuable to risk my life against petty criminals like these.' WHERE `entry`=27842;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Once again, well done. With a few more pushes the battle will be ours.' WHERE `entry`=27843;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Traitors!!!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='My employers do not take kindly to traitors. On the flip side, they are renown for their kindness towards the loyal! You deserve to be rewarded!' WHERE `entry`=27844;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. Those soldiers deserve better than to be left face down in the mud.' WHERE `entry`=27845;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, more delicious Bread of the Dead, thank you!$B$BPlease, take this in return... a little something fun for the holiday.' WHERE `entry`=27846;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Brilliant! Now all I have to do is finish my work, and my Mayhem Reapers will cause...mayhem...on any Horde front! And there won\'t be any Defias knockoffs to steal my profits!' WHERE `entry`=27847;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s a shame that he was both a human and a worgen. Had he been a proud orc warrior I\'d have liked to charge into battle alongside such a fierce combatant. We can speak of ill-fated desires another day. It is time to take what is ours from the enemy.' WHERE `entry`=27848;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve followed orders well, $N. On behalf of the crown, I\'m rewarding you for your bravery on the battlefield.' WHERE `entry`=27849;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='COWARD!!! Vanessa VanCleef is a dirty human coward! How dare she flee from battle against the Horde and leave her unworthy subordinate to fight! No matter. Her ship is reward enough. The citizens of Stormwind will bear first hand witness to our awe inspiring power using a ship made in part by the very architect of their city!' WHERE `entry`=27850;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good work, $N. With this, it\'s only a matter of time until the orcs are fleeing for the portal or begging for surrender.' WHERE `entry`=27851;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We will fight to the last orc, $N. I hope you\'ll keep yourself alive long enough to properly destroy these trespassers.' WHERE `entry`=27852;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='No true member of the Horde should find pleasure in killing such terrified weaklings... without challenge, victory has no true thrill. But your dirty work has helped stave off the Alliance and protect our homes here. Be proud of your work for the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=27853;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You are a true champion, $N, to take the lives of so many on the battlefield. I hope it will be enough to save Stonard.' WHERE `entry`=27854;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='With no link to the outside, the Alliance must rely on what they\'ve brought to the swamp. We shall see if they can handle our home environment.' WHERE `entry`=27855;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You honor both the dead and the living with your courage, $N.' WHERE `entry`=27856;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Alliance is driven out! Stonard will be safe, thanks to your ferocity. Lok\'tar Ogar!' WHERE `entry`=27857;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You were not the only mortal that Rheastrasza confided in. I too earned the dragon\'s trust. I have already moved the real purified egg on to a safer location, away from the Badlands. It will continue to grow, out of Deathwing\'s sight. The red dragonflight is as benevolent as it is powerful. It was Rheastrasza\'s final wish that I give this to you.' WHERE `entry`=27859;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It still pains my heart to have asked you to do this, though I know there is no other way. You have saved those of us still holding on from a terrible menace.' WHERE `entry`=27860;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not bad, friend. You might make some gold out here - if you manage to stay alive.' WHERE `entry`=27863;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='No love in your heart for orcs I see. You really made a mess of that guy.' WHERE `entry`=27864;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='No love in your heart for dwarves I see. You really made a mess of that guy.' WHERE `entry`=27865;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wow! When I saw that... thing stumble into the arena, I thought you didn\'t stand a chance. But you proved me wrong. You tore it apart! Grizzly business.' WHERE `entry`=27866;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You really pulled that one out. I thought you were done for sure when he wolfed and started tearing up the arena. I guess I should know by now that you don\'t go down easy.' WHERE `entry`=27867;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Looks like this title is yours! You really pulled that one out of the fire. Congratulations. I hope the coin serves you well.' WHERE `entry`=27868;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The goblin sent you? She has a cunning eye, that one. She speaks the truth. I am here to stem the tide of corruption seeping from this temple. If you would save your people from a wicked fate, $N, I ask for your assistance.' WHERE `entry`=27869;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Trouble within the temple... I wish we could spare forces to deal with it. The war with Stonard is already raging, and we need every man we can get.' WHERE `entry`=27870;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We have no time to send orcs to the temple, $N. The humans come, and they are many. Stonard must be defended!' WHERE `entry`=27871;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ysera herself sent you to me? Oh! It\'s a honor to speak with a representative of the aspects. It\'s true that our shrine is in jeopardy. The harpies we once sheltered in our boughs have suddenly turned against us. But please, don\'t rejoin the fight until you are ready. Our shrine is no mere battleground. Use its peace and power to center yourself.' WHERE `entry`=27874;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Prayerblossom has been used by the Broken as a remedy since they settled in this swamp. If it soothes the physical form, it might be used for more powerful healing...' WHERE `entry`=27875;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It will have to be purified, but this will be most helpful. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=27876;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent!  We\'ll bury these immediately. Those Explorers\' League dimwits will never suspect us!' WHERE `entry`=27877;
