UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That must be the new I-Scream Cryocannon! Ain\'t she a beauty?! I\'m going to let you in on a secret, my good friend: the groundwork for a vast mercantile empire is being laid right here! Tell me... how do you feel about ice cream?' WHERE `entry`=28031;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ooh, these are nice. Now, leave me alone with my gizzards. I\'ve got studying to do! Yes, very interesting. Very interesting indeed...' WHERE `entry`=28032;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Deceit',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well well well. Look who come searching for Lunk this time! This sounds like case for Lunk\'s unique brand of no-kill problem-solve.' WHERE `entry`=28033;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Did I stutter?  I believe I clearly stated that I... won\'t... Wow, ye\'ve got some good moves there!  I\'m impressed!' WHERE `entry`=28034;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So, Rendan\'s on our side?  About time that oaf came around. Let\'s get moving, then.' WHERE `entry`=28035;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='You\'ve got some fight in you, $C. You might do well in the crucible.$B$BWhat!? You haven\'t heard of the Crucible of Carnage? That smarmy goblin Gurgthock and his Troll sidekick have been plastering us with leaflets ever since he set up shop here in the Highlands. Champions from all over Azeroth fight to the death in there. You should gather up some friends and see how you fare.$B$BThe Crucible is just to the southwest. Look for Wodin the Troll-Servant somewhere in the middle of a ring of bones.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hey, you\'re one big strong heap of $C. Can you handle the crucible? We got bookies are standing by!' WHERE `entry`=28038;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Welcome, friend, welcome! I\'m going to give you the chance to get involved at the ground level of a once-in-a-lifetime opportuntity. The entrepreneurial spirit knows nothing of the differences between the Alliance and the Horde! Tell me... how do you feel about ice cream?' WHERE `entry`=28042;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='That was an impressive aerial display, $N, but I wish it had come at a better time. Narkrall is a great warrior, but he\'s also an impatient fool. He\'s about to get himself killed ... and we\'re about to lose one of our most important weapons in the battle for the Highlands!' WHERE `entry`=28043;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Claw of Tichondrius... You hold a piece of the very demon that led the Legion to these woods, $N. Better for it to be in our hands than with the satyr. Hold still. I\'m going to pull you back to our plane and make sure you and the claw arrive here safely...' WHERE `entry`=28044;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh yeah! This is going to be the greatest flavor in the world! Look out, Tigule and Foror!!!' WHERE `entry`=28045;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s about time someone took those guys out.' WHERE `entry`=28046;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Do you hear that, $N? That\'s the sweet hum of the refrigeration kicking in. We\'ll be able to store our inventory down there in no time. Thank you!' WHERE `entry`=28047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Third pipe frozen',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Fourth pipe frozen' WHERE `entry`=28047;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Outstanding! Nothing can stop us from being the greatest purveyors of ice cream in all of Azeroth!' WHERE `entry`=28048;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh good, you\'re back! Don\'t leave me alone with her! She\'s crazy! Gimme that, I\'ll have you seeing the invisible in no time!' WHERE `entry`=28049;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='No way, you actually killed him?  We are having shark tacos tonight for sure!' WHERE `entry`=28050;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. They gave their lives for ice cream.' WHERE `entry`=28051;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well, here we are. I hope you\'re ready, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28052;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done good. I don\'t like slavery either.' WHERE `entry`=28054;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Strange how so many slaves cope poorly with freedom. It\'s a shame to have to do what we do, but such are the truths of war. Now, we must move on to more pressing tasks.' WHERE `entry`=28055;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A fight well-fought, $N!  I\'m beginning to feel the tide turn. Now, when you\'re ready, let\'s hit these Dark Irons where it really hurts!' WHERE `entry`=28056;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='It\'s a little known fact that dwarves, particularly of the Dark Iron variety, need rest! Lots of rest!$B$BNow I ask you; How can they sleep without pillows?  Exactly, $N, they can\'t. This is why you must steal their pillows.$B$BOnce you\'ve finished your cushion-thievery, talk with Taskmaster Scrange. He\'s a bit deeper in the cave, working on a covert project with Hansel.',`objectives_loc6`='Obtain 16 Dark Iron Pillows.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I see Evonice is up to her old tricks again. I guess I\'ll just... um... hang onto these pillows for a while. The important part is that you\'re here. We\'re going to need your help.' WHERE `entry`=28057;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is better than even I could have thought possible! The Chambermaid\'s magical pillow is mine! You better believe you\'re going to get a nice reward for this accomplishment, $N!' WHERE `entry`=28058;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You killed him?  We have been trying to take that guy out for weeks!  We thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28059;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Twilight\'s Hammer, eh?  I should\'ve expected as much. I\'m glad you arrived to help them out when you did. It looks like, despite all odds, we\'ve pressed our offensive to the doorstep of Calcinder\'s lair. It\'s now time to finish the job.' WHERE `entry`=28060;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thanks for rounding these up for us, $N. Kind of hard to fight a battle without any guns.' WHERE `entry`=28063;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Our task is complete, and it\'s all thanks to you, $N. I\'d like to offer you your choice from our coffers. In addition, I intend to make you a full-fledged member of our order. Welcome to the Thorium Brotherhood, $N. I\'m proud to call you a brother.' WHERE `entry`=28064;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You saved our men!  No words can express our gratitude $N.' WHERE `entry`=28065;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='King Varian Wrynn has requested that any able-bodied adventurer head to Blackrock Depths, northwest of Morgan\'s Vigil, immediately!$B$BThe Dark Iron dwarves pose a serious threat to the citizens of Redridge! If you so choose, head to Blackrock Depths and speak with Morgan, who has returned from her extended absence and wishes to enact her vengeance on the Dark Iron nation.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='You look eager to kill a few hundred Dark Irons in justice\'s name. Perfect.' WHERE `entry`=28068;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'ve managed to take this small area, but to do anything more we\'ll need your help.' WHERE `entry`=28069;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='King Varian Wrynn has requested that any able-bodied adventurer head to Scholomance, east of Andorhal, immediately!$B$BRas Frostwhisper and Darkmaster Gandling are still hard at work training powerful sorcerers for the scourge! If you so choose, head to Scholomance and speak with Weldon Barov, last living son of Barov and heir to much of the surrounding lands.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak with Weldon Barov.' WHERE `entry`=28082;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The Warchief has requested that any able-bodied adventurer head to Scholomance, east of Andorhal, immediately!$B$BRas Frostwhisper and Darkmaster Gandling are still hard at work training powerful sorcerers for the scourge! If you so choose, head to Scholomance and speak with Alexi Barov, one of the last heirs to the Barov fortune and our contact within the dark school.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak with Alexi Barov.' WHERE `entry`=28083;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I know nothing of the Elder Crone, Magatha. What I do know is that the Twilight\'s Hammer is destroying Highperch. Will you help me to stop them, $C?' WHERE `entry`=28085;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='They\'re precious. One day they\'ll grow strong, but until then, they must be protected.' WHERE `entry`=28086;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There\'ll be no more trapping this day!' WHERE `entry`=28087;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The Twilight\'s Hammer have the alpha male of Highperch pinned down. You must head east up the ramp and release Heartrazor before the pride loses it\'s patriarch!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='The great Heartrazor is a majestic creature. He has told me of his gratitude and fondness for you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28088;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I was wondering when reinforcements would show up. Suit up, $N. It\'s time to dispense some justice!' WHERE `entry`=28089;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good going. Doesn\'t look like much, does it?' WHERE `entry`=28090;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. Now we can start pushing our ground forces up towards Grim Batol.' WHERE `entry`=28091;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Works like a charm, every time.' WHERE `entry`=28092;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The gate is clear. Once your people finish clearing the canyon, we will speak to your leaders about the next move.' WHERE `entry`=28093;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText1_loc6`='Grim Batol entrance secured' WHERE `entry`=28093;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We make it look easy.' WHERE `entry`=28094;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So how was it? Everything that you dreamed it would be? Exciting, no?$B$BNo?$B$B<Darthalia sighs.>$B$BI can see that you\'re a true $G hero:heroine;. You need action. I guess a "desk job" isn\'t for you.' WHERE `entry`=28096;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The canyon is well fortified, but the distraction that the dragons are providing should be enough to allow us to break through.' WHERE `entry`=28097;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The pridelings did what? They must love you deeply for freeing them. Thank you, $N. You\'ve saved Highperch!' WHERE `entry`=28098;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Rasha\'krak',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is, unfortunately, as I expected. These bracers bear the indelible mark of the firelord and his minions. Very well. With no Horde or Alliance forces anywhere near this godforsaken gorge, it falls upon the Thorium Brotherhood to stop this Archduke before he spreads any more of his evil.' WHERE `entry`=28099;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You... yes, you! I have chosen you, $R, as my champion! You will do the work of Ruumbo!' WHERE `entry`=28100;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The red dragons have agreed to help! No small feat, I\'m sure. You have the thanks of the Alliance. We\'d already laid out plans for our ambush on a Twilight caravan by the time the dragons contacted us. They\'re helping by cutting off their retreat. The battle still rages. You can definitely be of aid.' WHERE `entry`=28101;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A few of the remaining satyr have fled into the deeper woods, but they have taken heavy losses. Good job, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28102;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent. Now we can start pushing our ground forces up towards Grim Batol.' WHERE `entry`=28103;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good going. Doesn\'t look like much, does it?' WHERE `entry`=28104;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent, $N. We will make our way out of here soon enough.' WHERE `entry`=28105;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We make it look easy.' WHERE `entry`=28107;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Like a well-oiled machine.' WHERE `entry`=28108;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The gate is clear. Once your people finish clearing the canyon, we will speak to your leaders about the next move.' WHERE `entry`=28109;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='We\'re in a bit of a bind, $C. Sarus\' spiders are starting to get a little uppity as we\'ve been unable to feed them for days. If we leave the murlocs will overtake our post! Furthermore, Warden Stillwater over at the Sludge Fields is demanding that we send him more humans! He is insatiable! We need help!' WHERE `entry`=28111;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is true then?  An outsider rescued Prince Nadun from the Neferset? We are truly in your debt, stranger.' WHERE `entry`=28112;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='See what can get done with a little cooperation? I\'ll make sure the claw is given to people responsible enough to contain such things... assuming it can\'t be destroyed.' WHERE `entry`=28113;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful! Now to place these eggs into a nice, dark alcove inside the mine and let the miracle of life happen!' WHERE `entry`=28114;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The bear gods are cruel masters. They will continue to populate this world with bears until the end of days. It is our right as civilized people to make use of this nuisance - for the betterment of us all!' WHERE `entry`=28115;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wonderful. Greta chose wisely when she asked you to perform this task. I will work the herbs immediately...' WHERE `entry`=28116;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You made it back out alive?  You are a stronger man than I, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28117;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Galus is dead?  Fantastic work $N, now we can send down the cleanup crew and get that cellblock ready for new prisoners.' WHERE `entry`=28118;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='The flowers you brought me were the essential ingredient.$B$BProtective barriers surround Shadow Hold, projected from demonic braziers. If we are to drive the Shadow Council from Felwood, then those braziers must be extinguished.$B$BThis vial has been infused with Crying Violet and the magic of the wilds. Fill it at the corrupted moonwell in the center of Jaedenar and return to me.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='This will do nicely, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28119;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These journals are in excellent condition $N. We will begin deciphering them immediately. Only time will tell what secrets they hold.' WHERE `entry`=28120;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good, $N! With their numbers weakened, we can soon begin our assault on their forces deep within Shadow Hold.' WHERE `entry`=28121;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You actually killed him?!  I can\'t believe it!' WHERE `entry`=28122;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' If the stories are true, $N, it was on this length of chain that Deathwing had once fastened the Demon Soul, forged in his bid to control the other dragonflights. The Demon Stone has long been destroyed but perhaps this hunk of elementium holds some residual power... You\'ve done a great thing today.' WHERE `entry`=28123;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m glad that you made it. Don\'t mind my new clothes. It seemed prudent to blend in.' WHERE `entry`=28124;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' You sure don\'t fool around, do you, $N? Well, it\'ll have to do.' WHERE `entry`=28125;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Use the Purified Moon Well Water to douse the four Braziers of Protection within Shadow Hold.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='With the Braziers gone, the druids of the Emerald Circle can enter Shadow Hold and clear out the last of the cultists. In time, it may even be used as the barrow den it once was. You have my thanks, $N. Please take this reward.' WHERE `entry`=28126;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `ObjectiveText3_loc6`='Extinguish the Brazier of Suffering',`ObjectiveText4_loc6`='Extinguish the Brazier of Hatred' WHERE `entry`=28126;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You give so much of yourself without requiring anything in return. The people of Thousand Needles are grateful, as am I.' WHERE `entry`=28127;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The cleansing of Shadow Hold will take much time and effort, but without your defeat of the Shadow Council, it would not be possible at all. Thank you, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28128;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The demons begin to fall! Take heed, $C. You will find even stronger foes deeper within Shadow Hold.' WHERE `entry`=28129;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Told you that village was full of wackos. Nice job clearing it out $N.' WHERE `entry`=28130;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Another demonic menace gone. It is time to find their master.' WHERE `entry`=28131;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Bring \'Efficient Excavations\' to Belloc Brightblade in Schnottz\'s Landing.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Oh look, it\'s one of little Schnottz\'s pamphlets. I\'ll just be taking that from you, if you don\'t mind.' WHERE `entry`=28132;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Once free of the chain, Torth died rather than submit again. I admire the creature. I will have his hide fashioned into a set of armor. This much is clear to me now: The Dragonmaw cannot stand alone if the Alliance backs the Wildhammer. Narkrall proved that. And you have proven the might of the Horde, again and again. I will rebuild our drake wings and take up position outside the Bastion of Twilight. You should continue to help out here in the Gullet and elsewhere in the Highlands.' WHERE `entry`=28133;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Orsis!  Of course! How could I not have seen this?' WHERE `entry`=28134;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Do you see what Deathwing\'s minions have done?  Great Orsis is now all but buried in the sand!' WHERE `entry`=28135;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Now that those three are dealt with, the combined forces from Freewind Post should be able to handle the rest of the cultists here.' WHERE `entry`=28136;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These fish will do nicely, $N. Keeping the troops fed and in good condition is our number one priority and you really came through for us here.' WHERE `entry`=28137;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These will do nicely. I do wonder what the warden has planned for them. Last I heard the Sludge Fields were overrun by some very bad things.' WHERE `entry`=28138;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Good. Now there\'s only one thing left to do.' WHERE `entry`=28139;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you. The rumors I\'d heard about you are proving true after all.' WHERE `entry`=28141;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It took you long enough. Do you think that we are playing games here?' WHERE `entry`=28142;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='At least we\'ll be prepared for any future incidents. Moving "supplies" like this around is a risky proposition. You never know who is going to open their big fat mouth.$B$B<Keyton raises what appears to be an eyebrow at you.>' WHERE `entry`=28144;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Fill the Antidote Vial with the the poison of 8 Venomblood Scorpid corpses.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N. We might yet save Iset.' WHERE `entry`=28145;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This should keep it happy and content for a few days. You\'ve done a good thing here, $N!' WHERE `entry`=28146;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What did you manage to get? I suppose we can piece something together from this. After all, you\'re not joining the cult. We just need to fool a few ogres.' WHERE `entry`=28147;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I will see these are burned swiftly and safely, $N. You have my thanks.' WHERE `entry`=28148;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Dat\'s de stuff, mon! Now can you hear dem? De spirits, dey be talkin\', but dey say nothing nice. Let us bring dem to de light.' WHERE `entry`=28149;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='There is little time for talk, $C. The druids fight valiantly against the satyr, but fel sorcery blocks their path. Luckily, I have a plan...' WHERE `entry`=28150;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hah! I\'m sure Twilight\'s Hammer wanted to number those ogres among their ranks. Now they\'ll probably have to fight them off instead. This is good, $N. With one well-placed $C we managed to do the work of a small army. I\'ll let Warlord Krogg know of your work here!' WHERE `entry`=28151;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, just what I was expecting. With these herbs, our preparations for Jaedenar are nearly ready.' WHERE `entry`=28152;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The Shadow Council is broken! One task remains...' WHERE `entry`=28153;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Muckgill you say? Never heard of him. What is this anyway? Some kind of fin or something?' WHERE `entry`=28154;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Truly incredible, $N. To journey within the very lair of evil here and slay every fiend that stands before you... I am overwhelmed. The Emerald Circle thanks you for your work here in Felwood. As for Andalar, we will send scouts to rescue him at once. He shall have a hero\'s welcome.' WHERE `entry`=28155;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Have you ever heard the saying "survival of the fittest?" What you\'re doing conflicts with natural law, $G buddy:lady;! This idiot should have died in the mines. There\'s no telling what kind of harm he\'ll cause to himself or another person now that you\'ve saved him from his inevitable demise.$B$BAnd you know who\'s fault that\'ll be, right?' WHERE `entry`=28156;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' I\'ll combine them into a suitable form. I\'ll keep it\'s use simple.' WHERE `entry`=28157;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc6`='Unbound',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='A simple task for a simple boy. Let us see if you have what it takes to finish the job.' WHERE `entry`=28158;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Surprising... you lived. I thank you for doing my dirty work, $C. You kept my hands clean while ridding me of some incompetent Grimtotem leaders. Not only do I have the Rattle of Bones, the Writ of History, and the Drums of War, but I now have the ultimate artifact: the Doomstone!' WHERE `entry`=28159;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wow, she\'s evil! But, what does it mean, $N? Is Magatha going to destroy us? Is she in charge of the Twilight\'s Hammer now? Whatever happens, you\'ve delivered us from our enemies. Please allow me to show you our gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=28160;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Wow, she\'s evil! But, what does it mean, $N? Is Magatha going to destroy us? Is she in charge of the Twilight\'s Hammer now? Whatever happens, you\'ve delivered us from our enemies. Please allow me to show you our gratitude.' WHERE `entry`=28161;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Looks like you were able to get the croc hides that we needed. Thanks $N, your contributions will not go unnoticed.' WHERE `entry`=28162;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Those filthy horde never stood a chance. Nice work, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28163;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='I just received word that you are needed in Orgrimmar, $N. Brother Silverhallow has asked for you to return to the city as quickly as you are able. His message didn\'t include any other information, and the matter seemed urgent.$B$BLook for Brother Silverhallow in the Goblin Slums of Orgrimmar.',`objectives_loc6`='Speak with Brother Silverhallow in the Goblin Slums of Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='I\'m glad to see you received my message.' WHERE `entry`=28164;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='D-Block is all clear?  Good work, $N. We will send down a crew to start cleaning up right away.' WHERE `entry`=28165;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Ah, dis be it, mon. We be ready to bring dem spirits out de shadows now.' WHERE `entry`=28166;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Did Nevin send you ahead? That means he\'s getting ready to end the mission, but there are still survivors to be rescued. We have to help them!' WHERE `entry`=28167;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Who are you? Did Sylvanas send you? Everything is FINE! Yes, perfectly fine! I\'ve got it all under control!$B$BWell, fine all things considered that is... We\'ve got a few problems that perhaps you could help with, $C.' WHERE `entry`=28168;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It\'s good to meet you, $C. We rarely come across survivors as strong and capable as you are. I can help get you decontaminated and on your way out of here.' WHERE `entry`=28169;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You see! De dead be nothing to be scared of. You brought de light to de darkness, mon, and never flinched. We can use dis cave now as a base of operations in de northern Highlands. You\'re de best, $N!' WHERE `entry`=28170;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It seems you are still with us. I\'m somewhat appreciative of that. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=28171;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I will see to it that these dragons are taken care of.' WHERE `entry`=28172;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You seem to have made use of the disturbing implements with ease. I take solace in knowing that some tools of evil can ultimately still lead to safeguarding life. Nothing is without purpose.' WHERE `entry`=28173;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='So you\'re in, then? Good.' WHERE `entry`=28174;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve started a wonderful thing this day, amidst all of this blood shed. It may take many years, but this ravaged land will be restored. It will be beautiful again.' WHERE `entry`=28175;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Lirastraza sent me ahead to the lair, suspecting the black dragon we are seeking may still be here. Judging by the hatchlings, it seems she was not mistaken.' WHERE `entry`=28176;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Those scorpids are easy to underestimate. You\'re lucky you didn\'t end up on the end of one of these barbs. Or maybe you\'re just good. I\'ll add these to the stockpile. We\'re not done yet, $R.' WHERE `entry`=28177;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='We\'ll need worg hides, and lots of them. It doesn\'t matter if they\'re torn, burned, or bloody, but we need plenty of them.$B$BActually, it\'s probably better if they\'re a little beat-up.$B$BYou\'ll find worgs both to the west and to the east of here.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Believe me, $N... I\'m just as anxious to get to the killing as you are. We\'ve got to keep to the plan. The armageddon will come soon enough. I\'ll keep these hides here.' WHERE `entry`=28178;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='This is exactly what we need. Don\'t worry, $N... the orc-killing will come soon enough.' WHERE `entry`=28179;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Gah!  Who are you? Oh, so Keeshan sent you?  Good. Would ya mind sticking around for a while?  It\'s nothing big... I just need you to kill some warlocks for me.' WHERE `entry`=28180;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I hope that\'s what Keeshan was looking for. It\'s not doing me much good right now, anyhow.' WHERE `entry`=28181;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Knowing the way those orcs operate, there\'ll be another one to take his place soon. I\'ll see if I can\'t sneak back into the altar before that happens. Thanks, buddy.' WHERE `entry`=28182;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Good, good, good. We can move on. Our war takes us east, away from Blackrock Mountain... for now.' WHERE `entry`=28183;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ll have to excuse me, but we\'re not taking visitors right now. I\'ll ask you to leave Chiselgrip out the same door you came in. Oh, Keeshan... is that you?' WHERE `entry`=28184;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Svarnos is finally dead?  Looks like we can finally get to work setting up that cellblock then. Thank you $N.' WHERE `entry`=28185;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The shackles!  We will begin the process of destroying these shackles immediately $N. Thank you for your help.' WHERE `entry`=28186;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Okay, $R! Zhis just got real!$B$BSomevone zhinks zhat zhey can get rid of me zhat easily, hmm?$B$BVe shall see about zhat! Nozhink can shtop zhis vork! Nozhink!$B$B<Schnottz looks around at the encroaching flames.>$B$BVe should probably get out of here.$B$BHuury up! Time is vastink!',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is times like zhese, zhat one learns who his friends really are...' WHERE `entry`=28187;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You cleared that area out?  Looks like you might be more useful to us that we thought, $R.' WHERE `entry`=28188;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Undoubtedly you did the right thing. Hopefully the humans that you saved will show similar mercy to you should the time of your planting ever come.$B$BThis is all assuming you rescued the humans and didn\'t splatter their brains all over the dirt - of course.$B$BKeep the shovel as a reminder of the horrors of the Sludge Fields and the depravity of mortals.' WHERE `entry`=28189;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='My rage quells at the news... perhaps I will find it easier to rest and heal now.$B$BMaybe my stomach will settle as well. Urgh...' WHERE `entry`=28190;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve proven a great ally. I would have never expected such upon our first meeting.' WHERE `entry`=28191;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='As you can see, they\'re all monsters! Most of my guards died and the ones that managed to escape are now holding down the barricades, preventing any of these potentially dangerous creatures from getting out.$B$BWe need your help!' WHERE `entry`=28192;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Zhey know nozhink, you say? Very vell, zhen. Zhe search goes on...' WHERE `entry`=28193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are perfect, $C. Wish us luck!' WHERE `entry`=28194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Commander Schnottz wants you to kill Captain Margun, Captain Cork, and Captain Kronkh',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Very good, $R...' WHERE `entry`=28195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Warden Stillwater flips through the journal, reading under his breath.>$B$BRamblings of a mad man! Clearly he had been ingesting the mushrooms. It is good that you brought this to me, $N. I will burn it myself!' WHERE `entry`=28196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Well done! Wilkes was hanged after we discovered that he was ingesting mass quantities of mushrooms and other highly toxic substances. After he died he awoke, reborn as an undead geist. Many of my guards fell to Wilkes before he ran off into hiding. Fearing something like this might happen again, we incinerated the Clerk until only bones were left!$B$BWhy would they willingly ingest toxic substances? I have no idea! This is a farm, $G sir:miss;, nothing more!' WHERE `entry`=28197;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='It is a great honor to meet you, $N!  I\'ve heard much about you.' WHERE `entry`=28198;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These samples will give us a better understanding of the mindless undead. Take these coins as a reward.' WHERE `entry`=28199;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Excellent job, $N. You might not think this adds up to much, but this might very well be the difference between life and death to one of our soldiers.' WHERE `entry`=28200;
