UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='A ride to the Highlands, then? I\'ve just the thing! I\'ll make room for yeh in me seaplane. I\'ll have to ditch the cat-food I was packing, yeh know, in case we crash in the mountains and ain\'t rescued fer weeks. On second thought, jes\' keep the cat food on yer lap, aye.' WHERE `entry`=28238;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc6`='Speak with Quartermaster Kaoshin at the Black Tooth Hovel in Burning Steppes.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Where have you been, grunt?  You\'re late!  Give me one reason why I shouldn\'t kill you on the spot!' WHERE `entry`=28239;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='<The eye speaks to you, its \'voice\' reverberating as if coming from everywhere at once.>$B$BYou seek my sight, $R? My powers come at a price. These disciples of the twilight have been honoring me with the blood of Wildhammer dwarves from the nearby ruins, but still I thirst. Perhaps you can do better.$B$BSlay my old masters, and my vision is yours. Honor me with the slaughter of the Shaman of the Black. Blood is blood, after all.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`=' Ah, the succulent thrill of life extinguished. Do you feel it, $C? Do you relish it as I do? No, I see not. You fight to protect the lives of others. Pity.' WHERE `entry`=28242;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You found one? A gen-u-ine Eye of Twilight? Lemme see. Oh Gods. It\'s lookin\' at me. It\'s lookin\' right back! I need a drink. Can you face that thing toward the wall or somethin\'?' WHERE `entry`=28243;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='What did you see, $N? Cho\'gall? Wait - he saw YOU!? Oh aye, that wee sneaky eye! It looks both ways. That cheeky looker! Where\'s me hammer!?' WHERE `entry`=28244;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Hmph. Good work, grunt.' WHERE `entry`=28245;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Not only did you pull off the executions, you made them all look like accidents! You were the right $R for this undercover work. Good job, soldier.' WHERE `entry`=28246;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You killed Obsidia within her own lair? Impressive, $R. I\'m sorry that I could not be there. You\'re true to your word, and you most certainly have the bite to back your bellow. Thank you.' WHERE `entry`=28247;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well, $N. We\'re in the process of preparing the attack now.' WHERE `entry`=28248;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You\'ve done well, $N. We\'re in the process of preparing the attack now.' WHERE `entry`=28249;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You showed those thieving little scoundrels!  Great job.' WHERE `entry`=28250;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='The worgen situation hasn\'t gotten any better and Helcular is really creeping me out.' WHERE `entry`=28251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I didn\'t count on obtaining an item like this. I will change our plans accordingly.' WHERE `entry`=28253;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You need a disguise?  Well, you came to the right place, honey. Let me take a look... mm-hmm. I know exactly what we\'ll do.' WHERE `entry`=28254;
