UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='I have a feeling we\'ll be hearing about you and your exploits for a long time, soldier. I look forward to fighting by your side in Redridge. You are dismissed.' WHERE `entry`=28278;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='Without those sergeants, Thorg\'izog will be hard-pressed getting his troops ready for battle. Already the dominoes are beginning to fall, $N.' WHERE `entry`=28279;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You did it, $N! Alliance ingenuity to the rescue. Of course, I don\'t have anything to help you fight the dismounted riders now that they\'re on the ground. You\'re a $C; improvise!' WHERE `entry`=28280;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='You sure know your way around a battlefield, $C. It looks like they\'re about to fall back. All we need is one decisive blow...' WHERE `entry`=28281;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='There\'s one Dragonmaw among this lot, the one they call "Narkrall: The Drake-Tamer." I don\'t know where he gets his power over those beasts, but the black terror he rides is as nasty a brute as ever took the skies over the Highlands.$B$B$N, Narkrall is the fiend who took my father\'s life and left Thundermar in my hands.$B$BI can\'t take him on alone, but I\'ve seen what you\'re capable of, $C. Maybe together we can end this.$B$BLet me know when you\'re ready, and we\'ll fight Narkrall together!',`objectives_loc6`='Slay Narkrall Rakeclaw. Speak with Colin Thundermar when you\'re ready.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='We did it, $N! Narkrall Rakeclaw lies dead at my feet, and Thundermar has weathered a storm of drakes! This wouldn\'t have been possible if it weren\'t for the help of the Alliance. I owe you a debt that I don\'t think can ever be repaid.' WHERE `entry`=28282;
