UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Have you met Sister Aquinne? She and I grew up together in Dolanaar, and she recently came to the city to study at the Temple of the Moon. We decided to go for a boat ride, but the clumsy oarsman managed to capsize the craft!$B$BWhen we got back to the shore, Aquinne\'s moon pendant was missing. The lakes in Darnassus are full of giant catfish who will gobble up anything shiny!$B$BI\'ve been catching them nonstop, hoping to find the one with her pendant. I don\'t suppose you want to help?',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='<Astaia takes the pendant from you.>$B$BUnderneath all the slime and tarnish, I think this is it! Aquinne will be so happy to have this back... after a thorough cleaning, of course. I can\'t thank you enough, $N.' WHERE `entry`=29324;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc6`='These are going to be delicious, I can already tell! Thanks, $N!' WHERE `entry`=29325;
