UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='Sometimes fishing means throwing something back, $C.$B$BWe\'ve been overfeeding these frogs for just that occasion. We\'ve fed these frogs bloated spiders, that were fed bloated flies, and now, we are going to feed a real monster.$B$BThe moat above, in the Ruins of Lordaeron, is home to our very own Moat Monster.$B$BToday is feeding day. But we must train it as well. In this bag, you will find a decoy kit and some Bloated Frogs. Use the decoy kit, then toss the frogs to the monster when it appears.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='The dead feed the flies. The flies feed the spiders. The spiders feed the frogs. The frogs feed our moat monster... It\'s a beautiful circle of life with the goal of ending life.' WHERE `entry`=29361;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc6`='You know of the Pools of Vision, yes?$B$BThere is a sort of mushroom that grows there... not the tough, rank fungi that dominates the place, but smaller, more delicate caps that grow beneath them.$B$BThey are rare and quite delicious, adding a flavor to meat dishes that one might even call magical.$B$B...what? No, really. They just taste good. That\'s it.',`objectives_loc6`='Gather 6 "Magic" Mushrooms from the Pools of Vision in Thunder Bluff. Deliver them to Aska Mistrunner in Thunder Bluff.',`offerrewardtext_loc6`='Thank you, $N! I\'m sure these will impart a simply magical taste to whatever dish they\'re used in.$B$BWhat? Stop looking at me like that!' WHERE `entry`=29362;
